GRAND LACKEY ERKH.name: Grand Lackey Erkh
GRAND LACKEY ERKH.flavorText: Esteemed leader of Rafaam's Inhuman Resources department.

ADDLED GRIZZLY.name: Addled Grizzly
ADDLED GRIZZLY.flavorText: Druids who spend too long in bear form are more susceptible to the whispers of the Old Gods. Right now they are whispering the lyrics to "La Bamba".

SHARP SHIPMENT.name: Sharp Shipment
SHARP SHIPMENT.flavorText: Pre-check is amazing these days. New rules say you don't have to take off your shoes, helmet, or daggers!

CLOWNFISH.name: Clownfish
CLOWNFISH.flavorText: His jokes are hilarious if you know Nerglish.

BAD LUCK ALBATROSS.name: Bad Luck Albatross
BAD LUCK ALBATROSS.flavorText: Legend holds that it's bad luck to harm it. So maybe just pat it on the head, okay?

POWER OVERWHELMING.name: Power Overwhelming
POWER OVERWHELMING.flavorText: We cannot even describe how horrible the death is. It's CRAZY bad! Maybe worse than that. Just don't do it.

BRAINSTORMER.name: Brainstormer
BRAINSTORMER.flavorText: Her hair was always like that.

TWILIGHT FLAMECALLER.name: Twilight Flamecaller
TWILIGHT FLAMECALLER.flavorText: Make sure you summon a Twilight Marshmallowcaller too! Mmmm Mmm Mmm!!

TERRORGUARD ESCAPEE.name: Terrorguard Escapee
TERRORGUARD ESCAPEE.flavorText: Poor guy is terrified, look at his faces.

ILLIDAN'S GIFT.name: Illidan's Gift
ILLIDAN'S GIFT.flavorText: "This gift's burden will always be yours to bear... I lost the receipt." -Illidan

EARTHEN RING FARSEER.name: Earthen Ring Farseer
EARTHEN RING FARSEER.flavorText: He can see really far, and he doesn't use a telescope like those filthy pirates.

SPIRIT OF THE DRAGONHAWK.name: Spirit of the Dragonhawk
SPIRIT OF THE DRAGONHAWK.flavorText: Dragonhawks aren’t known for their accuracy.

WRECK'EM AND DECK'EM.name: Wreck'em and Deck'em
WRECK'EM AND DECK'EM.flavorText: ...and Check'em for any signs of life.

COMMANDER SIVARA.name: Commander Sivara
COMMANDER SIVARA.flavorText: With six legs, gills, and an impressive array of magic, Sivara is an all-terrain-spellcaster.

EXARCH NAIELLE.name: Exarch Naielle
EXARCH NAIELLE.flavorText: The Great Dark Beyond is vast, with each world containing unknown wonders and horrors alike. To distinguish between the two, Naielle leads the Rangari in surveying all planets the Draenei set foot on.

LIGHTSPAWN.name: Lightspawn
LIGHTSPAWN.flavorText: Spawn of the Light? Or Pawn of the Lights?

SACRIFICIAL PACT.name: Sacrificial Pact
SACRIFICIAL PACT.flavorText: This is the reason that Demons never really become friends with Warlocks.

DIVINE SPIRIT.name: Divine Spirit
DIVINE SPIRIT.flavorText: Double the trouble. Double the fun!

ONYX BISHOP.name: Onyx Bishop
ONYX BISHOP.flavorText: B4 is a nice place to visit, but he wouldn't want to live there.

MC BLINGTRON.name: MC Blingtron
MC BLINGTRON.flavorText: If this is the outcome of the robot uprising, then sign me up!

DEMONBOLT.name: Demonbolt
DEMONBOLT.flavorText: Or as it’s known in troll, “De bolt, mon.”

ENCROACHING INSANITY.name: Encroaching Insanity
ENCROACHING INSANITY.flavorText: Pictured here is Loken stuck at his 20th hour on Diamond 5.

PREDATORY INSTINCTS.name: Predatory Instincts
PREDATORY INSTINCTS.flavorText: Somebody’s been eating their funnel cakes.

AUCTIONEER JAXON.name: Auctioneer Jaxon
AUCTIONEER JAXON.flavorText: "Who's up for a brand-new wisp? This thing's in perfect condition, folks! Never been played..."

SOGGOTH THE SLITHERER.name: Soggoth the Slitherer
SOGGOTH THE SLITHERER.flavorText: Don't tell Soggoth, but in the future he gets totally owned by the Master's Glaive and his skull becomes a tourist attraction.

SINRUNNER.name: Sinrunner
SINRUNNER.flavorText: Blanchy was said to be an affectionate and well-behaved horse in life. How she ended up in Revendreth? We're too afraid to ask.

FORBIDDEN FRUIT.name: Forbidden Fruit
FORBIDDEN FRUIT.flavorText: Not forbidden if you have a good dentist!

DUBIOUS PURCHASE.name: Dubious Purchase
DUBIOUS PURCHASE.flavorText: Beauty is in the eye of the scorpidholder.

MIND VISION.name: Mind Vision
MIND VISION.flavorText: I see what you did there.

SNACK RUN.name: Snack Run
SNACK RUN.flavorText: "I'll have two monster churros, a combo box of Yogg-Saron, and one of those turkey legs that ate the Silver Hand Recruit."

ONE HIT WONDER.name: One Hit Wonder
ONE HIT WONDER.flavorText: They're trying to get a second hit in with their next single, "Divine Shield".

TO MY SIDE!.name: To My Side!
TO MY SIDE!.flavorText: I hunt alone. Well, me and Misha. And Huffer. And Leokk.

FREEZING TRAP.name: Freezing Trap
FREEZING TRAP.flavorText: "Dang, that's cold." - appropriate response to Freezing Trap, or a mean joke.

FIDDLEFIRE IMP.name: Fiddlefire Imp
FIDDLEFIRE IMP.flavorText: Most find the stages set aflame by the Grimtotem too dangerous to perform on, but to him they're perfect!

BLESSING OF WISDOM.name: Blessing of Wisdom
BLESSING OF WISDOM.flavorText: Apparently with wisdom comes the knowledge that you should probably be attacking every turn.

BOOTY BAY BOOKIE.name: Booty Bay Bookie
BOOTY BAY BOOKIE.flavorText: Also makes a great librarian. She's really good at fixing books!

STRENGTH IN NUMBERS.name: Strength in Numbers
STRENGTH IN NUMBERS.flavorText: One minion, two minions... tree minions!

KEYMASTER ALABASTER.name: Keymaster Alabaster
KEYMASTER ALABASTER.flavorText: The key to his mastery is a solid stack of backup copies.

RUNIC ADORNMENT.name: Runic Adornment
RUNIC ADORNMENT.flavorText: Rune, rune on the wall, who's the greenest of them all?

DREK'THAR.name: Drek'Thar
DREK'THAR.flavorText: Inside your deck there are two wolves. One is a frostwolf. The other is a frostwolf. You are a Frostwolf.

SNIPE.name: Snipe
SNIPE.flavorText: A great sniper hits the spot. Just like a delicious flank of boar. Mmmmm.

SCOURGE RAGER.name: Scourge Rager
SCOURGE RAGER.flavorText: Why's he so mad? Well you'd be mad too if you were created as a joke!

CHILLIN' VOL'JIN.name: Chillin' Vol'jin
CHILLIN' VOL'JIN.flavorText: After one visit to the cryopractor, YOU TOO can be chillin' like a Vol'jin!

SI:7 INFILTRATOR.name: SI:7 Infiltrator
SI:7 INFILTRATOR.flavorText: What will she destroy? It’s a secret!

DRAGONBANE.name: Dragonbane
DRAGONBANE.flavorText: *Thunk* "That wasn’t a dragon!" *Thunk* "THAT wasn’t a dragon!"

BLOODSAIL FLYBOOTER.name: Bloodsail Flybooter
BLOODSAIL FLYBOOTER.flavorText: They’re pretty fly for some pirate guys.

MUCK PLUMBER.name: Muck Plumber
MUCK PLUMBER.flavorText: If you drink muck, you go to the Maw before you die.

WARSONG COMMANDER.name: Warsong Commander
WARSONG COMMANDER.flavorText: The Warsong clan is such drama. It's really not worth it to become a commander.

STAR ALIGNER.name: Star Aligner
STAR ALIGNER.flavorText: "You're a Sagittarius? Me too! Just gimme a sec."

MULTI-STRIKE.name: Multi-Strike
MULTI-STRIKE.flavorText: “I said you get two attack, not two attacks!”

UMBERWING.name: Umberwing
UMBERWING.flavorText: Demon Hunters refer to these glaives as "the ol’ flappy-attackys."

DRUM CIRCLE.name: Drum Circle
DRUM CIRCLE.flavorText: It's more of a drum pentagon, really.

PET PARROT.name: Pet Parrot
PET PARROT.flavorText: You are REQUIRED to give it crackers. It's the Bird Law.

DIRE WOLF ALPHA.name: Dire Wolf Alpha
DIRE WOLF ALPHA.flavorText: We are pretty excited about the upcoming release of Dire Wolf Beta, just repost this sign for a chance at a key.

SERENA BLOODFEATHER.name: Serena Bloodfeather
SERENA BLOODFEATHER.flavorText: She’s really into networking! After all, she’s introduced countless low-level Horde players to the Spirit Healer.

BUMBLING BELLHOP.name: Bumbling Bellhop
BUMBLING BELLHOP.flavorText: Put some respect on his name: Estebone Soulio Screamcardo Groantoya De la Grossa Ramirooze.

NECRIUM VIAL.name: Necrium Vial
NECRIUM VIAL.flavorText: Two near-death experiences for the price of one!

FOXY FRAUD.name: Foxy Fraud
FOXY FRAUD.flavorText: His other street con involves a druid. He can't pull it off without a plant.

GATTLESNAKE.name: Gattlesnake
GATTLESNAKE.flavorText: He used to be an ordinary snake until he slithered through a saloon during a brawl and walked out looking like this.

BLESSING OF KINGS.name: Blessing of Kings
BLESSING OF KINGS.flavorText: Given the number of kings who have been assassinated, are you sure you want their blessing?

SUBMERGED SPACEROCK.name: Submerged Spacerock
SUBMERGED SPACEROCK.flavorText: Time for some out of this world RNG.

ANCIENT OF WAR.name: Ancient of War
ANCIENT OF WAR.flavorText: Young Night Elves love to play "Who can get the Ancient of War to Uproot?" You lose if you get crushed to death.

HACK THE SYSTEM.name: Hack the System
HACK THE SYSTEM.flavorText: Anything can be hacked, if you're holding an axe.

UNTAMED BEASTMASTER.name: Untamed Beastmaster
UNTAMED BEASTMASTER.flavorText: All it takes is a tummy rub.

TIRION FORDRING.name: Tirion Fordring
TIRION FORDRING.flavorText: If you haven't heard the Tirion Fordring theme song, it's because it doesn't exist.

DARK IRON DWARF.name: Dark Iron Dwarf
DARK IRON DWARF.flavorText: Guardians of Dark Iron Ore. Perhaps the most annoying ore, given where you have to forge it.

THE STONEWRIGHT.name: The Stonewright
THE STONEWRIGHT.flavorText: She wrights stone better than she reads it.

COLDLIGHT SEER.name: Coldlight Seer
COLDLIGHT SEER.flavorText: The Coldlight murlocs reside in the darkest pits of the Abyssal Depths. So no, there's no getting away from murlocs.

LIFEGUARD.name: Lifeguard
LIFEGUARD.flavorText: Hey, no aggro in the pool!

OVERGROWTH.name: Overgrowth
OVERGROWTH.flavorText: Zangarmarsh: it's a fungal out there!

MAW AND PAW.name: Maw and Paw
MAW AND PAW.flavorText: Home is where the disfigured, rotten heart is.

MECHAROO.name: Mecharoo
MECHAROO.flavorText: Its project name was KAN-GA. The little one was R-00.

KORRAK THE BLOODRAGER.name: Korrak the Bloodrager
KORRAK THE BLOODRAGER.flavorText: “I live, I love, I slay, and I am undying.”

FLESHEATING GHOUL.name: Flesheating Ghoul
FLESHEATING GHOUL.flavorText: 'Flesheating' is an unfair name. It's just that there's not really much else for him to eat.

GROMMASH HELLSCREAM.name: Grommash Hellscream
GROMMASH HELLSCREAM.flavorText: Grommash drank the tainted blood of Mannoroth, dooming the orcs to green skin and red eyes! Maybe not his best decision.

DEEP SPACE CURATOR.name: Deep Space Curator
DEEP SPACE CURATOR.flavorText: *Gestures to empty room* "...and here is my curated collection of space."

BELLRINGER SENTRY.name: Bellringer Sentry
BELLRINGER SENTRY.flavorText: "Who are you? Eh, none of my business."

JUSTICAR TRUEHEART.name: Justicar Trueheart
JUSTICAR TRUEHEART.flavorText: It's like putting racing stripes and a giant spoiler on your hero power.

BLESSED CHAMPION.name: Blessed Champion
BLESSED CHAMPION.flavorText: This card causes double the trouble AND double the fun.

INSATIABLE FELHOUND.name: Insatiable Felhound
INSATIABLE FELHOUND.flavorText: Back-to-back winner of the annual hot dog eating contest... and the judge-eating contest.

KIDNAPPER.name: Kidnapper
KIDNAPPER.flavorText: He just wants people to see his vacation photos.

MORTAL STRIKE.name: Mortal Strike
MORTAL STRIKE.flavorText: "If you only use one ability, use Mortal Strike." - The Warrior Code, Line 6

STREET TRICKSTER.name: Street Trickster
STREET TRICKSTER.flavorText: His first trick: making your wallet disappear!

FROSTMOURNE.name: Frostmourne
FROSTMOURNE.flavorText: Death Nights, Frost Morn, what's next - Blood Noon?

GOBOGLIDE TECH.name: Goboglide Tech
GOBOGLIDE TECH.flavorText: The word "glide" is always in quotes in the manual.

MUSEUM CURATOR.name: Museum Curator
MUSEUM CURATOR.flavorText: He is forever cursing the kids who climb on the rails and the evil archeologists who animate the exhibits.

AMANI BERSERKER.name: Amani Berserker
AMANI BERSERKER.flavorText: If an Amani berserker asks "Joo lookin' at me?!", the correct response is "Nah, mon".

SNOWBLIND HARPY.name: Snowblind Harpy
SNOWBLIND HARPY.flavorText: Not snowblind; she can spot a level 51 noob over 40 yards away.

SALTY DOG.name: Salty Dog
SALTY DOG.flavorText: He's recently recovered from being a "scurvy dog."

SOOT SPEWER.name: Soot Spewer
SOOT SPEWER.flavorText: The inventor of the goblin shredder is involved in several patent disputes with the inventor of the soot spewer.

WHIRLING COMBATANT.name: Whirling Combatant
WHIRLING COMBATANT.flavorText: It's called capoeira! And yes, it is dangerous!

VILE APOTHECARY.name: Vile Apothecary
VILE APOTHECARY.flavorText: When he's feeling extra malicious, he uses the licorice-flavored one.

PUBLIC DEFENDER.name: Public Defender
PUBLIC DEFENDER.flavorText: Happy to defend any public offender!

SCAVENGING HYENA.name: Scavenging Hyena
SCAVENGING HYENA.flavorText: Hyenas prefer the bones of kodos or windserpents, but they'll eat pretty much anything. Even Brussels sprouts.

RECRUITER.name: Recruiter
RECRUITER.flavorText: Join the Argent Crusade! We have attractive tabards and you get to carry really nice swords!

OVERZEALOUS HEALER.name: Overzealous Healer
OVERZEALOUS HEALER.flavorText: In another universe, she's Genji's best friend.

PSYCHOPOMP.name: Psychopomp
PSYCHOPOMP.flavorText: "Come with me if you want to re-live."

DARKGLARE.name: Darkglare
DARKGLARE.flavorText: He's got a dark glare, but he sees crystal clear!

HEAVY PLATE.name: Heavy Plate
HEAVY PLATE.flavorText: "You asked for unbendable, unwavering armor–I don't see why you're upset."

TUSKARR TOTEMIC.name: Tuskarr Totemic
TUSKARR TOTEMIC.flavorText: Turns out the tuskarr aren't real choosy about their totems.

SHIFTER ZERUS.name: Shifter Zerus
SHIFTER ZERUS.flavorText: It's like being able to play with THREE angry chickens!

OPERA SOLOIST.name: Opera Soloist
OPERA SOLOIST.flavorText: It ain't over until the imp mother sings.

SEASIDE GIANT.name: Seaside Giant
SEASIDE GIANT.flavorText: Everywhere's the shallow end when you're 88 feet tall.

PROUD DEFENDER.name: Proud Defender
PROUD DEFENDER.flavorText: It'll take a humble offender to defeat him.

DA UNDATAKAH.name: Da Undatakah
DA UNDATAKAH.flavorText: First Deathrattle: Draw a card. Second: Draw 2 cards. Third: Throw Mon'kind off a steel cage and plummet sixteen feet through an announcer’s table.

ACADEMIC ESPIONAGE.name: Academic Espionage
ACADEMIC ESPIONAGE.flavorText: The tenth Pyroblast really felt like overkill.

FORBIDDEN SHAPING.name: Forbidden Shaping
FORBIDDEN SHAPING.flavorText: But the minion arrives covered in goo.

PHANTOM FREEBOOTER.name: Phantom Freebooter
PHANTOM FREEBOOTER.flavorText: There's no such thing as a free boot.

DRUID OF THE SCYTHE.name: Druid of the Scythe
DRUID OF THE SCYTHE.flavorText: She's a scythe for sore eyes.

KRYXIS THE VORACIOUS.name: Kryxis the Voracious
KRYXIS THE VORACIOUS.flavorText: Tried intermittent fasting. It didn't stick.

ICE BARRIER.name: Ice Barrier
ICE BARRIER.flavorText: This is Rank 1. Rank 2 is Chocolate Milk Barrier.

AYA BLACKPAW.name: Aya Blackpaw
AYA BLACKPAW.flavorText: Though young, Aya took over as the leader of Jade Lotus through her charisma and strategic acumen when her predecessor was accidentally crushed by a jade golem.

LUNA'S POCKET GALAXY.name: Luna's Pocket Galaxy
LUNA'S POCKET GALAXY.flavorText: Luna became head of the astronomy department when her boss invented the Pocket Black Hole.

WISPS OF THE OLD GODS.name: Wisps of the Old Gods
WISPS OF THE OLD GODS.flavorText: They're just normal wisps, actually. The "Of the Old Gods" bit is just marketing.

HIDDEN MEANING.name: Hidden Meaning
HIDDEN MEANING.flavorText: I'm telling you, if you play the song backwards at triple speed I SWEAR Mukla sings about the Burning Legion.

DOOM!.name: DOOM!
DOOM!.flavorText: We ran out of space for "DOOOOOOOOOOOM!!!!!"

BLOOD CRUSADER.name: Blood Crusader
BLOOD CRUSADER.flavorText: Defending Silvermoon takes a lot of blood, sweat, tears, and blood.

PRIMORDIAL DRAKE.name: Primordial Drake
PRIMORDIAL DRAKE.flavorText: Before he became a rap artist.

IMP-OSTER.name: Imp-oster
IMP-OSTER.flavorText: There is an imposter among us.

GRIFTAH.name: Griftah
GRIFTAH.flavorText: With Griftah in your deck, sometimes you start the game with The Coin!

SPITEFUL SMITH.name: Spiteful Smith
SPITEFUL SMITH.flavorText: She'll craft you a sword, but you'll need to bring her 5 Steel Ingots, 3 Motes of Earth, and the scalp of her last customer.

PRO GAMER.name: Pro Gamer
PRO GAMER.flavorText: Wow... who could have guessed? Another rock user ruining the meta for everyone as usual.

IGNITE.name: Ignite
IGNITE.flavorText: "So there I was in the Deadmines, I had VanCleef by the throat, and I was just about to let him have it when... <sniff> What's that smell?"

SERVANT OF YOGG-SARON.name: Servant of Yogg-Saron
SERVANT OF YOGG-SARON.flavorText: Yogg-Saron always likes to complain about how he has too many servants and there are too many mouths to feed.

WARGEAR.name: Wargear
WARGEAR.flavorText: WAR! GEAR! What is it good for?

MARK OF THE SPIKESHELL.name: Mark of the Spikeshell
MARK OF THE SPIKESHELL.flavorText: "I'm DEFINITELY turtle-y enough for the turtle club."

FEEDING TIME.name: Feeding Time
FEEDING TIME.flavorText: True, they're only 1/1s, but they eat as much as most 4/4s!

INSATIABLE DEVOURER.name: Insatiable Devourer
INSATIABLE DEVOURER.flavorText: You're not you when you're anima-starved.

COOL GHOUL.name: Cool Ghoul
COOL GHOUL.flavorText: He has disco fever! :D Because of the disco plague. :(

WITHER.name: Wither
WITHER.flavorText: The opponent's minion can't live wither without you.

GELBIN MEKKATORQUE.name: Gelbin Mekkatorque
GELBIN MEKKATORQUE.flavorText: He's the leader of the gnomes, and an incredible inventor. He's getting better, too; He turns things into chickens WAY less than he used to.

ANTIQUE HEALBOT.name: Antique Healbot
ANTIQUE HEALBOT.flavorText: They don't make 'em like they used to! (Because of explosions, mostly.)

INVIGORATING SERMON.name: Invigorating Sermon
INVIGORATING SERMON.flavorText: Every underdog sports coach knows this one.

TAVISH STORMPIKE.name: Tavish Stormpike
TAVISH STORMPIKE.flavorText: "Hurry up, laddie, we're getting overrun! Serpents everywhere! They may look cute, but do ye see the fury in their eyes?!" —Tavish Stormpike

ETHEREAL ORACLE.name: Ethereal Oracle
ETHEREAL ORACLE.flavorText: I see 2 spells in my future.

STRANGLETHORN TIGER.name: Stranglethorn Tiger
STRANGLETHORN TIGER.flavorText: The wonderful thing about tigers is tigers are wonderful things!

GLAIVEBOUND ADEPT.name: Glaivebound Adept
GLAIVEBOUND ADEPT.flavorText: "Initiate, this is your glaive. Think of it as an extension of yourself... Did you just throw it?!"

ASSASSINATE.name: Assassinate
ASSASSINATE.flavorText: If you don't want to be assassinated, move to the Barrens and change your name. Good luck!

MIGHT OF MENETHIL.name: Might of Menethil
MIGHT OF MENETHIL.flavorText: Menethil's Might, at night, fights the light, not quite the blight, right?

COCONUT CANNONEER.name: Coconut Cannoneer
COCONUT CANNONEER.flavorText: You think these just fell out of a coconut tree?

MESSMAKER.name: Messmaker
MESSMAKER.flavorText: The most painful 1 damage of your life.

GONK, THE RAPTOR.name: Gonk, the Raptor
GONK, THE RAPTOR.flavorText: There’s a word for Zandalari druids who refuse to pledge loyalty to Gonk: “Delicious.”

LOREKEEPER POLKELT.name: Lorekeeper Polkelt
LOREKEEPER POLKELT.flavorText: quicksort [] = [] quicksort (x:xs) = quicksort small ++ (x : quicksort large) where small = [y | y <- xs, y <= x] large = [y | y <- xs, y > x]

BLACK CAT.name: Black Cat
BLACK CAT.flavorText: She's so odd, you can't even.

KABAL OUTFITTER.name: Kabal Outfitter
KABAL OUTFITTER.flavorText: Don’t ask her for feathers on your necklace though.

WING WELDING.name: Wing Welding
WING WELDING.flavorText: This is not how you train your dragon.

HAND OF A'DAL.name: Hand of A'dal
HAND OF A'DAL.flavorText: When it meets the Hand of Gul'dan, they're SHAKING.

CROWD ROASTER.name: Crowd Roaster
CROWD ROASTER.flavorText: Every major show has an opening act to warm up the crowd.

SHIELD OF GALAKROND.name: Shield of Galakrond
SHIELD OF GALAKROND.flavorText: Realistically, she's the shield for Galakrond's big toe.

MOGOR THE OGRE.name: Mogor the Ogre
MOGOR THE OGRE.flavorText: Mogor helped reopen the Dark Portal once. You know you're in trouble when you have to rely on an ogre.

TORTOLLAN TRAVELER.name: Tortollan Traveler
TORTOLLAN TRAVELER.flavorText: Tortolla, preserve my energy for this hike!

PIRANHA LAUNCHER.name: Piranha Launcher
PIRANHA LAUNCHER.flavorText: A great improvement over the guppy launcher.

ORBITAL MOON.name: Orbital Moon
ORBITAL MOON.flavorText: The blood moon orbits once again.

SECRETKEEPER.name: Secretkeeper
SECRETKEEPER.flavorText: Where is Mankrik’s wife? She’ll never tell.

AMORPHOUS SLIME.name: Amorphous Slime
AMORPHOUS SLIME.flavorText: A crucial component of the Lordaeroneon Choice Awards.

SHADY DEALER.name: Shady Dealer
SHADY DEALER.flavorText: I have great deal for you... for 4 damage to your face!

DISCO AT THE END OF TIME.name: Disco at the End of Time
DISCO AT THE END OF TIME.flavorText: This is what you've been saving the last dance for.

SHADESTONE SKULKER.name: Shadestone Skulker
SHADESTONE SKULKER.flavorText: Sharing is caring - and they don't care.

HIPSTER.name: Hipster
HIPSTER.flavorText: Oh, so you like Hearthstone? Name every spell.

DIVINE HYMN.name: Divine Hymn
DIVINE HYMN.flavorText: Taken up an octave, it's highly effective against stained glass golems.

ARCANOSMITH.name: Arcanosmith
ARCANOSMITH.flavorText: He’s really just a Blacksmith, but he thought the fancy title would bring in more business.

THEOTAR, THE MAD DUKE.name: Theotar, the Mad Duke
THEOTAR, THE MAD DUKE.flavorText: "I'm afraid you've gone mad! You're entirely bonkers. But I'll tell you a secret. All the best souls are."

DISTRESS SIGNAL.name: Distress Signal
DISTRESS SIGNAL.flavorText: HELP! HEEELP! MY OPPONENT PLAYED CARDS!

AZERITE GIANT.name: Azerite Giant
AZERITE GIANT.flavorText: Either that giant isn't really giant, or that doorway is HUGE!

DRAGON'S BREATH.name: Dragon's Breath
DRAGON'S BREATH.flavorText: Dragons breathe fire, sure, but did you know they can also breathe Cotton Candy? It's harder to give them a reason to do that, though.

STARSTRUNG BOW.name: Starstrung Bow
STARSTRUNG BOW.flavorText: Shoot for the stars, but if you miss, aim for the enemy hero.

PLAGIARIZARRR.name: Plagiarizarrr
PLAGIARIZARRR.flavorText: He's also working on his own Hearthstone expansion: Festival of Epics.

SHIELD BLOCK.name: Shield Block
SHIELD BLOCK.flavorText: Shields were invented because Face Block is USELESS.

JADE SWARMER.name: Jade Swarmer
JADE SWARMER.flavorText: He's so good at swarming, he can swarm all by himself!

SHADO-PAN RIDER.name: Shado-Pan Rider
SHADO-PAN RIDER.flavorText: He needed a break after that business in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms. Naturally, he chose to spend his vacation in an icy snowscape killing monsters.

SHENANIGANS.name: Shenanigans
SHENANIGANS.flavorText: It's not personal, it's just monkey business.

RELIC OF PHANTASMS.name: Relic of Phantasms
RELIC OF PHANTASMS.flavorText: Xy'mox chuckled. "You mean the Chaos Emerald?"

SOUTHSEA CAPTAIN.name: Southsea Captain
SOUTHSEA CAPTAIN.flavorText: When he saves enough plunder, he's going to commission an enormous captain's hat. He has hat envy.

DIRE MOLE.name: Dire Mole
DIRE MOLE.flavorText: You especially don't want to make a dire mountain out of a dire mole hill.

TIMBER WOLF.name: Timber Wolf
TIMBER WOLF.flavorText: Other beasts totally dig hanging out with timber wolves.

DREAMING DRAKE.name: Dreaming Drake
DREAMING DRAKE.flavorText: Some dragons dream of conquering Azeroth, some just dream of being 5/6s.

CANDLESHOT.name: Candleshot
CANDLESHOT.flavorText: Once called Cahn’delar, Shortbow of the Ancient Whisker.

MUTATE.name: Mutate
MUTATE.flavorText: You'll get the transformation you want when murlocs fly.

BRING IT ON!.name: Bring It On!
BRING IT ON!.flavorText: Brrr, it's cold in here. Let's hope she doesn't have an Auctioneer!

INGENIOUS ARTIFICER.name: Ingenious Artificer
INGENIOUS ARTIFICER.flavorText: He always brags that he's at the top of the bell curve.

BATTLEPICKAXE.name: Battlepickaxe
BATTLEPICKAXE.flavorText: You can pick your battles, and you can pick your axes, but you can't uh… pick your friends' battlepickaxes?

BLACKHOWL GUNSPIRE.name: Blackhowl Gunspire
BLACKHOWL GUNSPIRE.flavorText: The upper windows used to be for aiming. Then we thought: "Hey! MORE cannons!"

DRAGONMAW OVERSEER.name: Dragonmaw Overseer
DRAGONMAW OVERSEER.flavorText: Ah, the Booterang... nothing cures peon laziness faster.

SPRINGPAW.name: Springpaw
SPRINGPAW.flavorText: The terrible thing about lynxes is lynxes are terrible things. Their teeth are made out of biting, their paws are made out of springs!

THE SCARAB LORD.name: The Scarab Lord
THE SCARAB LORD.flavorText: What did it cost? 41,400 Silithid Carapace Fragments, to start.

TEMPLE ENFORCER.name: Temple Enforcer
TEMPLE ENFORCER.flavorText: He also moonlights Thursday nights as a bouncer at the Pig and Whistle Tavern.

FRIZZ KINDLEROOST.name: Frizz Kindleroost
FRIZZ KINDLEROOST.flavorText: Frizz knows that baby dragons need warmth, care, and the highest possible level of goblin engineering.

SILVERMOON BROCHURE.name: Silvermoon Brochure
SILVERMOON BROCHURE.flavorText: It's lovely to visit this time of year. Just ignore that enormous scarred area outside.

ARCANE GIANT.name: Arcane Giant
ARCANE GIANT.flavorText: Claims to be drawn to Karazhan because of the ley lines. Actually, just loves Moroes’ cooking.

KIRIN TOR MAGE.name: Kirin Tor Mage
KIRIN TOR MAGE.flavorText: The Kirin Tor reside in the floating city of Dalaran. How do you make a Dalaran float? Two scoops of ice cream, one scoop of Dalaran.

SHUDDERWOCK.name: Shudderwock
SHUDDERWOCK.flavorText: Beware the Shudderwock, my son. We're fresh out of vorpal daggers.

THE CEASELESS EXPANSE.name: The Ceaseless Expanse
THE CEASELESS EXPANSE.flavorText: If you play this for its full Mana cost, you know what? You win. Good day sir!

STORMHAMMER.name: Stormhammer
STORMHAMMER.flavorText: It brings the storm before the calm.

RAY OF FROST.name: Ray of Frost
RAY OF FROST.flavorText: If you have zero chill, this can help.

CURSED BLADE.name: Cursed Blade
CURSED BLADE.flavorText: The Curse is that you have to listen to "MMMBop" on repeat.

ANIMATED AVALANCHE.name: Animated Avalanche
ANIMATED AVALANCHE.flavorText: Always sliding down mountains because it can't stop talking with its hands.

IMMOLATE.name: Immolate
IMMOLATE.flavorText: "Well if you cared about those cards so much, why didn't you play them?"

GRAND TOTEM EYS'OR.name: Grand Totem Eys'or
GRAND TOTEM EYS'OR.flavorText: Some say it can see straight into the soul of any who dare to read its flavor text...

OBSIDIAN DESTROYER.name: Obsidian Destroyer
OBSIDIAN DESTROYER.flavorText: No obsidian is safe around the Obsidian Destroyer!

FRACKING.name: Fracking
FRACKING.flavorText: For fhe person who jusf cannof decide whaf card fo puf info a deck!

SADDLEMASTER.name: Saddlemaster
SADDLEMASTER.flavorText: Seat covers. Check. Racing stripes. Check. Cupholder. Check.

EXPLODINATOR.name: Explodinator
EXPLODINATOR.flavorText: When it absolutely, positively, has to blow up overnight.

EVIL TOTEM.name: EVIL Totem
EVIL TOTEM.flavorText: A lot of people blame the parents when a totem goes bad.

WIND-UP MUSICIAN.name: Wind-Up Musician
WIND-UP MUSICIAN.flavorText: Sure to wind up your opponents.

ARGENT WATCHMAN.name: Argent Watchman
ARGENT WATCHMAN.flavorText: Who argent watches the Argent Watchman?

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/6a/VO_AT_109_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_109_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/a/a4/VO_AT_109_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_109_ATTACK_02.wav I saw that.
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/3a/VO_AT_109_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_109_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

THE PRIMUS.name: The Primus
THE PRIMUS.flavorText: As there is a Pantheon of titans, so is there also a Pantheon of Death, comprised of powerful rulers in the Shadowlands.

COLDTOOTH YETI.name: Coldtooth Yeti
COLDTOOTH YETI.flavorText: Its arrival heralds the Brain Freeze Yeti.

BLACK MORASS IMPOSTER.name: Black Morass Imposter
BLACK MORASS IMPOSTER.flavorText: Does something seem off about Medivh's apprentice to you?

BASH.name: Bash
BASH.flavorText: You might think bashing doesn't take a lot of practice. It doesn't.

WARSONG WRANGLER.name: Warsong Wrangler
WARSONG WRANGLER.flavorText: "Me? Playing favorites? I love my beasts all the same!"

SUCKERHOOK.name: Suckerhook
SUCKERHOOK.flavorText: A moderately better dining companion than Suckerbeard.

STONEHEART KING.name: Stoneheart King
STONEHEART KING.flavorText: I, too, am a king at playing Heart Stone.

ONCE UPON A TIME....name: Once Upon a Time...
ONCE UPON A TIME....flavorText: ...There was a humble little squirrel on a quest to defeat an evil dragon. With the help of its earthen friend, it saved the murloc princess from danger. The end.

REFLECTO ENGINEER.name: Reflecto Engineer
REFLECTO ENGINEER.flavorText: The whole thing's based on the Rubber-Glue Phenomenon.

RAZZLE-DAZZLER.name: Razzle-Dazzler
RAZZLE-DAZZLER.flavorText: Look out Dancin' Deryl, he's coming for your job.

NOURISH.name: Nourish
NOURISH.flavorText: Druids take nourishment from many things: the power of nature, the songbird's chirp, a chocolate cake.

OH, MANAGER!.name: Oh, Manager!
OH, MANAGER!.flavorText: "I'd like to speak with your admiral."

PERPLEXING ANOMALY.name: Perplexing Anomaly
PERPLEXING ANOMALY.flavorText: I'm so confused... this is really a headscratcher... it doesn't make any sense... why does it cost 3 Mana?

SONYA SHADOWDANCER.name: Sonya Shadowdancer
SONYA SHADOWDANCER.flavorText: Love like you've never been hurt. Dance like a 1/1 is watching.

MIMIRON'S HEAD.name: Mimiron's Head
MIMIRON'S HEAD.flavorText: Do not push the big red button!

HERALD OF LIGHT.name: Herald of Light
HERALD OF LIGHT.flavorText: Wake up! No sleeping in with the fishes!

MISCHIEF MAKER.name: Mischief Maker
MISCHIEF MAKER.flavorText: Fair trade is for noble-minded suckers with dignity and honor.

THE HEADLESS HORSEMAN.name: The Headless Horseman
THE HEADLESS HORSEMAN.flavorText: This flavor text, you would expect to rhyme and reference, to great effect! It starts out strong, but as you can tell it doesn't end very good.

LAB PATRON.name: Lab Patron
LAB PATRON.flavorText: When a Lab Patron fails out of school, they become a Grim Patron.

ARCHMAGE ANTONIDAS.name: Archmage Antonidas
ARCHMAGE ANTONIDAS.flavorText: Antonidas was the Grand Magus of the Kirin Tor, and Jaina's mentor. This was a big step up from being Grand Magus of Jelly Donuts.

SAVANNAH HIGHMANE.name: Savannah Highmane
SAVANNAH HIGHMANE.flavorText: In the jungle, the mighty jungle, the lion gets slowly consumed by hyenas.

EVISCERATE.name: Eviscerate
EVISCERATE.flavorText: There is a high cost to Eviscerating your opponent. You might tweak your elbow! That really hurts!

MAGEHUNTER.name: Magehunter
MAGEHUNTER.flavorText: Hates waiting. Abhors chit chat. Fond of the color purple.

DIVINE STAR.name: Divine Star
DIVINE STAR.flavorText: I could really use a wish right now.

SEEK GUIDANCE.name: Seek Guidance
SEEK GUIDANCE.flavorText: Xyrella was looking for spiritual guidance but found deck-building tips instead.

LOOSE SPECIMEN.name: Loose Specimen
LOOSE SPECIMEN.flavorText: You leave Deathstalker Rexxar alone in the lab for TWO minutes…

PRIDE'S FURY.name: Pride's Fury
PRIDE'S FURY.flavorText: Day 4: I think they're starting to suspect.

STORMPIKE BATTLE RAM.name: Stormpike Battle Ram
STORMPIKE BATTLE RAM.flavorText: Baa ram ewe! To your dwarves, your beard, Stormpike clan be true!

DARK CONVICTION.name: Dark Conviction
DARK CONVICTION.flavorText: In his court, Uther is judge, jury, AND executioner…

USHER OF SOULS.name: Usher of Souls
USHER OF SOULS.flavorText: Nothing unburdens your soul like a good ushing!

COLD BLOOD.name: Cold Blood
COLD BLOOD.flavorText: "I'm cold blooded, check it and see!"

GREYBOUGH.name: Greybough
GREYBOUGH.flavorText: The best time to plant a tree was 20 years ago. The next best time is when you lose a minion.

THICKHIDE KODO.name: Thickhide Kodo
THICKHIDE KODO.flavorText: The introduction of professions was devastating for kodo populations.

SIRA'KESS CULTIST.name: Sira'kess Cultist
SIRA'KESS CULTIST.flavorText: "Sira'kess, she's the best! Puts her followers to the test.

FEL BARRAGE.name: Fel Barrage
FEL BARRAGE.flavorText: Kurtrus leapt over a tombstone towards the demonic invaders, yelling "PEW! PEW!" as he shot them down with fel magic.

METEOROLOGIST.name: Meteorologist
METEOROLOGIST.flavorText: Some say the world will end in fire. Some say in ice. Why not BOTH?

FIELD OF STRIFE.name: Field of Strife
FIELD OF STRIFE.flavorText: I heard it's lovely there around this time of year.

GNOMEREGAN INFANTRY.name: Gnomeregan Infantry
GNOMEREGAN INFANTRY.flavorText: The gnomes are valiant and ready to return to their irradiated, poorly ventilated homeland!

TRINKET ARTIST.name: Trinket Artist
TRINKET ARTIST.flavorText: Many Draenei found new hobbies on the long journey from Argus.

WORGEN INFILTRATOR.name: Worgen Infiltrator
WORGEN INFILTRATOR.flavorText: If you want to stop a worgen from infiltrating, just yell, "No! Bad boy!"

ASSASSIN'S BLADE.name: Assassin's Blade
ASSASSIN'S BLADE.flavorText: Guaranteed to have been owned by a real assassin. Certificate of authenticity included.

XHILAG OF THE ABYSS.name: Xhilag of the Abyss
XHILAG OF THE ABYSS.flavorText: When ancient heroes drove a felhunter into the sea, they thought it was the end. But for Xhilag, it was only the beginning...

SNOWFLIPPER PENGUIN.name: Snowflipper Penguin
SNOWFLIPPER PENGUIN.flavorText: On land, a group of penguins is called a "waddle."

RUNED ORB.name: Runed Orb
RUNED ORB.flavorText: The most dangerous Winter Veil ornament.

DRUID OF THE SABER.name: Druid of the Saber
DRUID OF THE SABER.flavorText: That's saberTEETH, not like curved pirate blades. That's a different kind of druid. Druid of the Curved Pirate Blades.

BLOOD TAP.name: Blood Tap
BLOOD TAP.flavorText: Come join us in the tavern! We have whatever you're drinking on tap. Yes, even that.

HOUNDMASTER.name: Houndmaster
HOUNDMASTER.flavorText: "Who let the dogs out?" he asks. It's rhetorical.

EXPENDABLE PERFORMERS.name: Expendable Performers
EXPENDABLE PERFORMERS.flavorText: When someone gets injured, it's considered performance art.

HARRISON JONES.name: Harrison Jones
HARRISON JONES.flavorText: “That belongs in the Hall of Explorers!”

NAGA SEA WITCH.name: Naga Sea Witch
NAGA SEA WITCH.flavorText: If she had studied harder, she would have been a C+ witch.

HULLBREAKER.name: Hullbreaker
HULLBREAKER.flavorText: Breaks through the hard shell to reach the ship's gooey interior.

FINJA, THE FLYING STAR.name: Finja, the Flying Star
FINJA, THE FLYING STAR.flavorText: The last true master of Finjitsu.

HOT AIR BALLOON.name: Hot Air Balloon
HOT AIR BALLOON.flavorText: The Gadgetzan Pilgrim's Bounty parade is missing a float this year.

DIRE FRENZY.name: Dire Frenzy
DIRE FRENZY.flavorText: It's always Huffer. And Huffer. And Huffer. And Huffer.

BATTLE RAGE.name: Battle Rage
BATTLE RAGE.flavorText: "You won't like me when I'm angry."

HUNTING MASTIFF.name: Hunting Mastiff
HUNTING MASTIFF.flavorText: "Shh! You're going to start a howl!"

ORNERY DIREHORN.name: Ornery Direhorn
ORNERY DIREHORN.flavorText: "It's an herbivore. How dangerous can it be?" - Famous last words

COLISEUM MANAGER.name: Coliseum Manager
COLISEUM MANAGER.flavorText: Meets monthly with the gladiators to discuss career goals.

POTION OF ILLUSION.name: Potion of Illusion
POTION OF ILLUSION.flavorText: Unfortunately, there's no potion that can make you unsee all the faces in that bottle.

COBRA SHOT.name: Cobra Shot
COBRA SHOT.flavorText: "Cobra Shot" hurts way, way, way more than "Cobra Cuddle."

EXARCH MALADAAR.name: Exarch Maladaar
EXARCH MALADAAR.flavorText: The Auchenai order was founded to preserve the memory of Draenei that have passed. But why stop at remembrance when they can live once more?

PLAGUED GRAIN.name: Plagued Grain
PLAGUED GRAIN.flavorText: Oh, don’t mind the smell. They're just aged!

PRIDE SEEKER.name: Pride Seeker
PRIDE SEEKER.flavorText: When you're putting your head in the lion's mouth, you may as well dress the part.

LADY ASHVANE.name: Lady Ashvane
LADY ASHVANE.flavorText: This is your brain on Azerite.

DOOMGUARD.name: Doomguard
DOOMGUARD.flavorText: Summoning a doomguard is risky. Someone is going to die.

HOLY SMITE.name: Holy Smite
HOLY SMITE.flavorText: It doesn't matter how pious you are. Everyone needs a good smiting now and again.

SHADE OF NAXXRAMAS.name: Shade of Naxxramas
SHADE OF NAXXRAMAS.flavorText: I would've thought the giant, floating necropolis that is Naxxramas would cast a bigger shadow.

DISCIPLE OF GOLGANNETH.name: Disciple of Golganneth
DISCIPLE OF GOLGANNETH.flavorText: Warning: If you are not made of rocks, do not stand in lightning water.

REHYDRATE.name: Rehydrate
REHYDRATE.flavorText: Just doing our part as the Hearthstone development team in reminding you to drink more water!

FLIGHT MASTER.name: Flight Master
FLIGHT MASTER.flavorText: Your gryphon will be summoned following a brief safety demonstration.

TSUNAMI.name: Tsunami
TSUNAMI.flavorText: Hop in, the water's cold! And angry. And alive.

GHOULISH ALCHEMIST.name: Ghoulish Alchemist
GHOULISH ALCHEMIST.flavorText: AND I THREW IT ON THE GROUND!

FELSTEEL EXECUTIONER.name: Felsteel Executioner
FELSTEEL EXECUTIONER.flavorText: "My mom said I could be anything I want."

QUICKSAND ELEMENTAL.name: Quicksand Elemental
QUICKSAND ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Use a light abrasive to buff blemishes away but use a heavy abrasive to debuff problems.

RIGHTEOUS DEFENSE.name: Righteous Defense
RIGHTEOUS DEFENSE.flavorText: Paladins... Always stealing someone else’s thunder. And stats.

ILLIDARI FELBLADE.name: Illidari Felblade
ILLIDARI FELBLADE.flavorText: A whirling dervish of demonic devastation.

SHARP-EYED SEEKER.name: Sharp-Eyed Seeker
SHARP-EYED SEEKER.flavorText: If you give it treats, it will give you shiny objects!

PROVING GROUNDS.name: Proving Grounds
PROVING GROUNDS.flavorText: 1v1 me on Proving Grounds, DH only, no items, 4 stocks.

ABSORBENT PARASITE.name: Absorbent Parasite
ABSORBENT PARASITE.flavorText: Your beasts' iron levels are high, what have you been feeding them?

WARSONG ENVOY.name: Warsong Envoy
WARSONG ENVOY.flavorText: "What do you mean we didn’t give the flag to the Druid?"

JACKPOT!.name: Jackpot!
JACKPOT!.flavorText: Find someone who looks at you the way Hooktusk looks at loot.

CLEARANCE PROMOTER.name: Clearance Promoter
CLEARANCE PROMOTER.flavorText: "Sorry, we just sold our last Worgen Greaser figure."

PATIENT ASSASSIN.name: Patient Assassin
PATIENT ASSASSIN.flavorText: He’s not really that patient. It just takes a while for someone to walk by that he can actually reach.

BANE OF DOOM.name: Bane of Doom
BANE OF DOOM.flavorText: My advice to you is to avoid Doom, if possible.

LESSER SPINEL SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Spinel Spellstone
LESSER SPINEL SPELLSTONE.flavorText: A story concluded, the kobolds had fought Yet here is a spellstone Azari forgot Pawned off to shops, considered a trinket Dark powers contained, none would think it

BLOODSAIL RECRUITER.name: Bloodsail Recruiter
BLOODSAIL RECRUITER.flavorText: I want YOU! To plunder from the innocent!

TUSKARR FISHERMAN.name: Tuskarr Fisherman
TUSKARR FISHERMAN.flavorText: If you bring him 500 fish, he'll give you this sweet Kalu'ak Fishing Pole.

COLDLIGHT ORACLE.name: Coldlight Oracle
COLDLIGHT ORACLE.flavorText: They can see the future. In that future both players draw more cards. Spoooky.

IMPFERNO.name: Impferno
IMPFERNO.flavorText: Imps don't get mad when you set them on fire. They think it's cozy.

MUKLA'S CHAMPION.name: Mukla's Champion
MUKLA'S CHAMPION.flavorText: An elegant gorilla, for a more civilized age.
