BLOODBOIL BRUTE.name: Bloodboil Brute
BLOODBOIL BRUTE.flavorText: Call Gurtogg a brute if you like, but no one else cares about the wounded like he does.

PRISON OF YOGG-SARON.name: Prison of Yogg-Saron
PRISON OF YOGG-SARON.flavorText: "We've finally captured Yogg-Saron! How should we keep him contained?" "How about... an open pit... right below us... with four loose chains?" "PERFECT!"

FIRE FLY.name: Fire Fly
FIRE FLY.flavorText: Archnemeses: small children with glass jars.

PILFERED POWER.name: Pilfered Power
PILFERED POWER.flavorText: The Hozen don't get paid much, but at least they get to keep any excess mana.

CRIMSON SIGIL RUNNER.name: Crimson Sigil Runner
CRIMSON SIGIL RUNNER.flavorText: He's not the fastest of the bunch, but he'll take a stab at it anyway.

TWISTING NETHER.name: Twisting Nether
TWISTING NETHER.flavorText: The Twisting Nether is a formless place of magic and illusion and destroyed minions.

SHATTERED SUN CLERIC.name: Shattered Sun Cleric
SHATTERED SUN CLERIC.flavorText: They always have a spare flask of Sunwell Energy Drink™!

RAGING FELSCREAMER.name: Raging Felscreamer
RAGING FELSCREAMER.flavorText: Screaming loudly will not reduce the cost of non-demonic goods.

KARGAL BATTLESCAR.name: Kargal Battlescar
KARGAL BATTLESCAR.flavorText: One if by land, two if by tree.

LEARN DRACONIC.name: Learn Draconic
LEARN DRACONIC.flavorText: Upon taking up the spellbook, Reno realized with a start: "I can't read."

THE SCOURGE.name: The Scourge
THE SCOURGE.flavorText: “You speak of justice? Of cowardice? I will show you the justice of the grave and the true meaning of fear.”

HOLY SPRINGWATER.name: Holy Springwater
HOLY SPRINGWATER.flavorText: Issa bah oh auh woh ah!

PAINTER'S VIRTUE.name: Painter's Virtue
PAINTER'S VIRTUE.flavorText: For when the Light hits the painting at a certain angle.

CRYOPRACTOR.name: Cryopractor
CRYOPRACTOR.flavorText: It's really hard to book an appointment, she always gives her clients the cold shoulder.

BALINDA STONEHEARTH.name: Balinda Stonehearth
BALINDA STONEHEARTH.flavorText: Imagine her surprise, ending up in a game called Hearthstone.

LIFEDRINKER.name: Lifedrinker
LIFEDRINKER.flavorText: In a pinch, he'll also settle for Holy Water: Zero.

EXPLOSIVE SHOT.name: Explosive Shot
EXPLOSIVE SHOT.flavorText: Pull the pin, count to 5, then shoot. Then duck.

BOULDERFIST OGRE.name: Boulderfist Ogre
BOULDERFIST OGRE.flavorText: "ME HAVE GOOD STATS FOR THE COST"

SEA REAVER.name: Sea Reaver
SEA REAVER.flavorText: A little better than Sea Minus Reaver.

COSPLAY CONTESTANT.name: Cosplay Contestant
COSPLAY CONTESTANT.flavorText: She's the winner of the Valeera Cosplay Contest! Second place was Valeera.

THE RYECLEAVER.name: The Ryecleaver
THE RYECLEAVER.flavorText: Legend has it that this dreaded blade is be able to slice through even the most stale of sourdough baguettes.

CRYSTAL WELDER.name: Crystal Welder
CRYSTAL WELDER.flavorText: For all you weld-heads out there, this flavor text is a deep cut.

ANUB'ARAK.name: Anub'arak
ANUB'ARAK.flavorText: Was actually a pretty nice guy before, you know, the whole Lich King thing.

LIVING ROOTS.name: Living Roots
LIVING ROOTS.flavorText: 2 out of 2 saplings recommend that you summon the saplings.

EMPEROR THAURISSAN.name: Emperor Thaurissan
EMPEROR THAURISSAN.flavorText: His second greatest regret is summoning an evil Firelord who enslaved his entire people.

SILVERMOON SENTINEL.name: Silvermoon Sentinel
SILVERMOON SENTINEL.flavorText: I spent 8 mana polishing this shield, PLEASE don't make me bash you with it.

TRANSMOGRIFIER.name: Transmogrifier
TRANSMOGRIFIER.flavorText: All it takes is some imagination and a cardboard box.

SHATTERING BLAST.name: Shattering Blast
SHATTERING BLAST.flavorText: Let's be honest, they weren't going to unfreeze anyway.

EMERALD HIVE QUEEN.name: Emerald Hive Queen
EMERALD HIVE QUEEN.flavorText: She rules the emerald hive at the end of the yellow brick trail.

PARALLAX CANNON.name: Parallax Cannon
PARALLAX CANNON.flavorText: Math is now cannon in the Warcraft universe.

AMANI WAR BEAR.name: Amani War Bear
AMANI WAR BEAR.flavorText: "I used to farm for hours! Now they just come in packs?"

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/f/fd/TRL_550_AmaniWarBear_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ TRL_550_AmaniWarBear_Play.wav <summon sound>

GEOSCULPTOR YIP.name: Geosculptor Yip
GEOSCULPTOR YIP.flavorText: Once crafted a gauntlet out of earwax and pure ambition.

SEWER CRAWLER.name: Sewer Crawler
SEWER CRAWLER.flavorText: His clothing is "ratty" in more ways than one.

GHOULS' NIGHT.name: Ghouls' Night
GHOULS' NIGHT.flavorText: "Ohmygosh, did you hear what Jessicorpse said to Deathanny??"

DIRE FROSTWOLF.name: Dire Frostwolf
DIRE FROSTWOLF.flavorText: Tips to survive a frostwolf attack: -Stay calm -Lay down -Drizzle steak sauce over your body Brought to you by the Frostwolf Council for Alliance Safety.

EXPLORER'S HAT.name: Explorer's Hat
EXPLORER'S HAT.flavorText: Harrison Jones was disappointed that he didn't get to be part of the League of Explorers, but his hat did.

HIDDEN GEM.name: Hidden Gem
HIDDEN GEM.flavorText: This will be a staple in Unicorn Priest.

GRIMESTREET ENFORCER.name: Grimestreet Enforcer
GRIMESTREET ENFORCER.flavorText: "Sir, you don't have a permit to park your mount here."

HENCH-CLAN BURGLAR.name: Hench-Clan Burglar
HENCH-CLAN BURGLAR.flavorText: She’s more of a rat burglar.

DESERT SPEAR.name: Desert Spear
DESERT SPEAR.flavorText: Goes on the right, next to the desert spoon.

LIGHTWARDEN.name: Lightwarden
LIGHTWARDEN.flavorText: She’s smaller than her sisters Mediumwarden and Heavywarden.

HEADCRACK.name: Headcrack
HEADCRACK.flavorText: When all else fails, nothing beats a swift whack upside the head.

POWER SLIDER.name: Power Slider
POWER SLIDER.flavorText: There's a huge difference between a battle-axe and an axe-guitar. One is for combat, and the other is for combat AND rocking out.

SHAKY ZIPGUNNER.name: Shaky Zipgunner
SHAKY ZIPGUNNER.flavorText: The Grimy Goons can get you any weapon you want but if you want it to not explode you gotta pay extra.

SOUTH COAST CHIEFTAIN.name: South Coast Chieftain
SOUTH COAST CHIEFTAIN.flavorText: It got the conch. You let it speak!

RELIC OF DIMENSIONS.name: Relic of Dimensions
RELIC OF DIMENSIONS.flavorText: A glaive is a glaive, but a mystery box could be anything! It could even be a glaive!

CENARIUS.name: Cenarius
CENARIUS.flavorText: Yes, he's a demigod. No, he doesn't need to wear a shirt.

MANA ADDICT.name: Mana Addict
MANA ADDICT.flavorText: She’s trying to kick the habit, but still takes some mana whenever she has a stressful day.

AVIANA.name: Aviana
AVIANA.flavorText: Call her "Tweety". She'll find it real funny. I PROMISE.

SIEGEBREAKER.name: Siegebreaker
SIEGEBREAKER.flavorText: Has a side hustle as a siegebroker.

BONE FLINGER.name: Bone Flinger
BONE FLINGER.flavorText: It’s the scourge bringing, plague slinging, bone flinging basher!

GLUGG THE GULPER.name: Glugg the Gulper
GLUGG THE GULPER.flavorText: Food can be scarce in the Abyssal Depths, leading its top predators to pursue any potential source of sustenance. Even extra crunchy ones.

SHALLOW GRAVEDIGGER.name: Shallow Gravedigger
SHALLOW GRAVEDIGGER.flavorText: It's hard to put them six feet under when you're three feet tall.

MALTED MAGMA.name: Malted Magma
MALTED MAGMA.flavorText: Most celebrities nope out at this one.

MARSH HYDRA.name: Marsh Hydra
MARSH HYDRA.flavorText: Three heads of marsh-mashing, bog-bashing, swamp-stomping fury!

TINKER'S SHARPSWORD OIL.name: Tinker's Sharpsword Oil
TINKER'S SHARPSWORD OIL.flavorText: "Get ready to strike oil!" - Super-cheesy battle cry

FORMER CHAMP.name: Former Champ
FORMER CHAMP.flavorText: The last time he saw action, Undertaker ruled the meta.

IMPRISONED PHOENIX.name: Imprisoned Phoenix
IMPRISONED PHOENIX.flavorText: It's actually pretty easy to escape chains when you can burst into flames.

COLD CASE.name: Cold Case
COLD CASE.flavorText: And that's why you keep your skeletons in your closet instead of your freezer.

KURTRUS, DEMON-RENDER.name: Kurtrus, Demon-Render
KURTRUS, DEMON-RENDER.flavorText: "I dedicated my life to vanquishing demons, but I never thought to face the demons in me. Maybe, in time, I can help quell the demons in you." -Kurtrus, to Cariel

DARK CULTIST.name: Dark Cultist
DARK CULTIST.flavorText: The Cult of the Damned has found it's best not to mention their name when recruiting new cultists.

SPIRIT POACHER.name: Spirit Poacher
SPIRIT POACHER.flavorText: Always poach from your local spirit shelter.

MIND BLAST.name: Mind Blast
MIND BLAST.flavorText: This spell blasts you directly in the MIND.

BATTLEFIEND.name: Battlefiend
BATTLEFIEND.flavorText: Say what you like about my hatchet-headed hooligan, he’s my battle-friend.

CELESTIAL PROJECTIONIST.name: Celestial Projectionist
CELESTIAL PROJECTIONIST.flavorText: What if we're not really here, y'know? What if we're all just, like, projections in the mind of some cosmic entity? How would we know?

CASCADING DISASTER.name: Cascading Disaster
CASCADING DISASTER.flavorText: Please keep all hands, arms, feet and legs inside the ride until the monster comes to a complete stop.

HIGH PRIESTESS JEKLIK.name: High Priestess Jeklik
HIGH PRIESTESS JEKLIK.flavorText: If you love Jeklik, set her free. YOU CAN'T GET RID OF HER.

CORPSE WIDOW.name: Corpse Widow
CORPSE WIDOW.flavorText: Her marriage survived death, but it decayed pretty quickly after that.

SPIRIT OF THE TIGER.name: Spirit of the Tiger
SPIRIT OF THE TIGER.flavorText: Less of a cantrip and more of a cat-nip.

BRONZE DRAGONKNIGHT.name: Bronze Dragonknight
BRONZE DRAGONKNIGHT.flavorText: He had been here before, and in some ways, he would always be fighting in Silithus.

THE SKELETON KNIGHT.name: The Skeleton Knight
THE SKELETON KNIGHT.flavorText: Apparently it really was just a flesh wound.

AUCHENAI DEATH-SPEAKER.name: Auchenai Death-Speaker
AUCHENAI DEATH-SPEAKER.flavorText: He sees no evil. He hears no evil. Eh, he speaks a little evil.

FIREBALL.name: Fireball
FIREBALL.flavorText: This spell is useful for burning things. If you're looking for spells that toast things, or just warm them a little, you're in the wrong place.

BLAZING INVOCATION.name: Blazing Invocation
BLAZING INVOCATION.flavorText: A lot of shaman have started vaping their invocations.

POCKET DIMENSION.name: Pocket Dimension
POCKET DIMENSION.flavorText: On average, this gets you around 3 cards. And none of them have Overload.

ETERNAL SERVITUDE.name: Eternal Servitude
ETERNAL SERVITUDE.flavorText: What do you mean I don't get overtime pay for this?!

STREETWISE INVESTIGATOR.name: Streetwise Investigator
STREETWISE INVESTIGATOR.flavorText: "Hmmmm… Call it a hunch, but I'm starting to think that there may be some kind of criminal activity going on in Gadgetzan."

QUALITY ASSURANCE.name: Quality Assurance
QUALITY ASSURANCE.flavorText: I assure you this card is quality.

FAERIE DRAGON.name: Faerie Dragon
FAERIE DRAGON.flavorText: Adorable. Immune to Magic. Doesn't pee on the rug. The perfect pet!

COSTUMED SINGER.name: Costumed Singer
COSTUMED SINGER.flavorText: Who knows which forgotten, washed-up, former C-list celebrity might be in there!

CAPTURE COLDTOOTH MINE.name: Capture Coldtooth Mine
CAPTURE COLDTOOTH MINE.flavorText: We hit a huge haul! Or wait… no, it's just a coin.

TEACHER'S PET.name: Teacher's Pet
TEACHER'S PET.flavorText: Really goes the extra mile to get the Hay+.

SNOWFALL GUARDIAN.name: Snowfall Guardian
SNOWFALL GUARDIAN.flavorText: You’re finally awake! That fall looked really bad. Demon Hunters? Mercenaries? What are you talking about? Come on, I just unpacked a Golden Moorabi, let’s go build a Freeze Shaman deck.

UMBRAL SKULKER.name: Umbral Skulker
UMBRAL SKULKER.flavorText: "Three gold?! Do you have any idea how long this quest chain was?"

WAILING SOUL.name: Wailing Soul
WAILING SOUL.flavorText: This soul just wails on you. Dang, soul, let up already.

HEALING WAVE.name: Healing Wave
HEALING WAVE.flavorText: Favored by shaman who study the art of restoration and healing, this spell would feel smug, if it had feelings.

RUNEFUELED GOLEM.name: Runefueled Golem
RUNEFUELED GOLEM.flavorText: Hmm, glyph gauge is running low. Better fill up at the next town.

DARK WISPERS.name: Dark Wispers
DARK WISPERS.flavorText: Don't worry; we fired the person who named this card.

FURY (RANK 1).name: Fury (Rank 1)
FURY (RANK 1).flavorText: Rank 3 is when your mom uses your middle name.

TOYSNATCHING GEIST.name: Toysnatching Geist
TOYSNATCHING GEIST.flavorText: So THAT'S how the Geist stole Winterveil!

ICE LANCE.name: Ice Lance
ICE LANCE.flavorText: The trick is not to break the lance. Otherwise, you have "Ice Pieces." Ice Pieces aren't as effective.

CLUTCHMOTHER ZAVAS.name: Clutchmother Zavas
CLUTCHMOTHER ZAVAS.flavorText: A bit of a snob: still refuses to drive anything with automatic transmission.

WARDEN OF CHAINS.name: Warden of Chains
WARDEN OF CHAINS.flavorText: Can’t stay out too late. I gotta head back home to the ol’ ball and chained demon.

FEL SUMMONER.name: Fel Summoner
FEL SUMMONER.flavorText: All's well that ends fel when the fel summoner summons well.

DRAIN LIFE.name: Drain Life
DRAIN LIFE.flavorText: "I've just sucked one year of your life away."

CHAOS CREATION.name: Chaos Creation
CHAOS CREATION.flavorText: So THIS is who's been Greening everything!

WINDSPEAKER.name: Windspeaker
WINDSPEAKER.flavorText: Is there anything worse than a Windspeaker with halitosis?

MIRROR ENTITY.name: Mirror Entity
MIRROR ENTITY.flavorText: "You go first." - Krush'gor the Behemoth, to his pet boar.

PORTAL OVERFIEND.name: Portal Overfiend
PORTAL OVERFIEND.flavorText: It’s like an interdimensional game of demon tag.

LIGHTFUSED MANASABER.name: Lightfused Manasaber
LIGHTFUSED MANASABER.flavorText: Oh no, I ran out of fused Mana!

ANIMA EXTRACTOR.name: Anima Extractor
ANIMA EXTRACTOR.flavorText: After we are done you're welcome to help yourself to cookies and apple juice. Thank you for your donation!

ARCHMAGE.name: Archmage
ARCHMAGE.flavorText: You earn the title of Archmage when you can destroy anyone who calls you on it.

WILD PYROMANCER.name: Wild Pyromancer
WILD PYROMANCER.flavorText: BOOM BABY BOOM! BAD IS GOOD! DOWN WITH GOVERNMENT!

HELPLESS HATCHLING.name: Helpless Hatchling
HELPLESS HATCHLING.flavorText: It can’t be all that helpful. Not wif dose widdle wings!

VAST WISDOM.name: Vast Wisdom
VAST WISDOM.flavorText: My wisdom is SO vast that I can count up to THREE!

IVUS, THE FOREST LORD.name: Ivus, the Forest Lord
IVUS, THE FOREST LORD.flavorText: He's always welcome at the local tavern, unlike a certain Ancient.

VICIOUS SCALEHIDE.name: Vicious Scalehide
VICIOUS SCALEHIDE.flavorText: They make wonderful pets if you're not allergic to blood loss.

VOODOO DOLL.name: Voodoo Doll
VOODOO DOLL.flavorText: "Aww, I love it! It even kinda looks like me."

LOKEN, JAILER OF YOGG-SARON.name: Loken, Jailer of Yogg-Saron
LOKEN, JAILER OF YOGG-SARON.flavorText: Really great at his job! - Yogg-Saron

VEILED WORSHIPPER.name: Veiled Worshipper
VEILED WORSHIPPER.flavorText: If you’re not wearing your regulation cultist clothing, how will Galakrond know to devour you last?

GYROCOPTER.name: Gyrocopter
GYROCOPTER.flavorText: The hula doll is still absolutely required.

VIOLET ILLUSIONIST.name: Violet Illusionist
VIOLET ILLUSIONIST.flavorText: She’s much more cheerful after losing the ‘n’ in her name.

VULGAR HOMUNCULUS.name: Vulgar Homunculus
VULGAR HOMUNCULUS.flavorText: Fortunately he has an even number of fingers.

voicelines.attack:
https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/87/VO_LOOT_013_Male_Demon_Play_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_LOOT_013_Male_Demon_Play_02.wav Hey, twerp! Go away.
  • ▶️ VO_LOOT_013_Male_Demon_Play_03.wav Phew, you stink!

EXPLODING BLOATBAT.name: Exploding Bloatbat
EXPLODING BLOATBAT.flavorText: We've all been there after a night of one-too-many funnel cakes.

LAST STAND.name: Last Stand
LAST STAND.flavorText: If you play two Last Stands in one game, you're a liar.

MALORNE.name: Malorne
MALORNE.flavorText: When Malorne isn't mauling hordes of demons, he enjoys attending parties, though he prefers to go stag.

LUCKYSOUL HOARDER.name: Luckysoul Hoarder
LUCKYSOUL HOARDER.flavorText: Always brings his own reusable shopping bag, satchel, barrel, trunk, tray, and fluffy pillow.

ANTIQUE FLINGER.name: Antique Flinger
ANTIQUE FLINGER.flavorText: One man's treasure is another man's statue to the face.

TROUBLED MECHANIC.name: Troubled Mechanic
TROUBLED MECHANIC.flavorText: In space, no one can hear you talk about your troubles.

ANIMATED ARMOR.name: Animated Armor
ANIMATED ARMOR.flavorText: Try putting it on. Wait, let me get my camera.

LIBRAM OF HOPE.name: Libram of Hope
LIBRAM OF HOPE.flavorText: "Think you got lethal? Libram of NOPE!"

PEASANT.name: Peasant
PEASANT.flavorText: Better pay them, or they'll join the Defias.

RESURRECT.name: Resurrect
RESURRECT.flavorText: I walked into the dungeon and noticed a slain adventurer. In his final moments, he had scrawled out a message in the dust on the wall beside him. Two words: "rez plz"

CLEAVE.name: Cleave
CLEAVE.flavorText: Hey you two…could you stand next to each other for a second…

SHIVERING SORCERESS.name: Shivering Sorceress
SHIVERING SORCERESS.flavorText: Remember to use your sick days wisely.

CLASS ACTION LAWYER.name: Class Action Lawyer
CLASS ACTION LAWYER.flavorText: "Have you or a loved one ever been injured in a Consecration?"

CHAOS GAZER.name: Chaos Gazer
CHAOS GAZER.flavorText: No matter the game rules, it's always playing Go Fish.

HAMMER OF THE NAARU.name: Hammer of the Naaru
HAMMER OF THE NAARU.flavorText: The naaru wasn't using it. It doesn't have arms.

JOYMANCER JEPETTO.name: Joymancer Jepetto
JOYMANCER JEPETTO.flavorText: Joymancy (noun): The practice of bringing joy to others through the use of magic. (see also: ethics)

CORPSETAKER.name: Corpsetaker
CORPSETAKER.flavorText: Her extensive collection of corpses includes one of nearly every type. She'd love for you to join it.

ELEMENTAL ALLIES.name: Elemental Allies
ELEMENTAL ALLIES.flavorText: Reno’s lucky he wasn’t caught by a fire elemental.

TWILIGHT RUNNER.name: Twilight Runner
TWILIGHT RUNNER.flavorText: Every morning you find two dead cards at your doorstep.

DEATHSTALKER REXXAR.name: Deathstalker Rexxar
DEATHSTALKER REXXAR.flavorText: "You were too slow, old friend. The hunt began long ago. And now... it will never end."

ICE BREAKER.name: Ice Breaker
ICE BREAKER.flavorText: A great way to end a conversation.

MURMY.name: Murmy
MURMY.flavorText: Unlike other mummies, they rolled him up with rice, sliced cucumbers, and soy sauce on the side.

CATTLE RUSTLER.name: Cattle Rustler
CATTLE RUSTLER.flavorText: What once started as a small-time cat burglary gig has turned into a life of cattle rustling. What a shame.

ANGRY CHICKEN.name: Angry Chicken
ANGRY CHICKEN.flavorText: There is no beast more frightening (or ridiculous) than a fully enraged chicken.

SP-3Y3-D3R.name: SP-3Y3-D3R
SP-3Y3-D3R.flavorText: The itsy bitsy spider magnetized onto the water spout.

VOIDGILL.name: Voidgill
VOIDGILL.flavorText: If you stare into the abyss, it’s said that it will stare back at you. What happens to those who’ve gazed at it their entire lives?

NOSTALGIC GNOME.name: Nostalgic Gnome
NOSTALGIC GNOME.flavorText: She remembers Alterac Valley like it was 833 days ago.

SKY RAIDER.name: Sky Raider
SKY RAIDER.flavorText: Maybe he should've hatched a plan that could actually carry booty back too.

MANA CYCLONE.name: Mana Cyclone
MANA CYCLONE.flavorText: It'll put a good spin on your spells.

BANANA VENDOR.name: Banana Vendor
BANANA VENDOR.flavorText: There's always money in the banana stand.

WALNUT SPRITE.name: Walnut Sprite
WALNUT SPRITE.flavorText: How do you make a walnut laugh? Crack it up!

DRAGONLING MECHANIC.name: Dragonling Mechanic
DRAGONLING MECHANIC.flavorText: She is still working on installing the rocket launcher add-on for Mr. Bitey.

CALL TO ADVENTURE.name: Call to Adventure
CALL TO ADVENTURE.flavorText: Even the smallest minion can change the outcome of the game.

SHIVER THEIR TIMBERS!.name: Shiver Their Timbers!
SHIVER THEIR TIMBERS!.flavorText: Who knew there was overlap between pirates and lumberjacks?

BARKSKIN.name: Barkskin
BARKSKIN.flavorText: Make like a tree… and gain armor.

BONESHREDDER.name: Boneshredder
BONESHREDDER.flavorText: Is that his makeup or just his natural fur pattern?

NOZDORMU THE ETERNAL.name: Nozdormu the Eternal
NOZDORMU THE ETERNAL.flavorText: Live life in the fast lane. As long as your opponent does too.

BLOOD SHARD BRISTLEBACK.name: Blood Shard Bristleback
BLOOD SHARD BRISTLEBACK.flavorText: I'm bringin' bristle back (Yeah) Those other minions don't know how to act (Yeah) I think it's special how these crystals crack (Yeah) So turn around and I'll give you a smack (Yeah) (Take 'em to the Barrens)

LOCK AND LOAD.name: Lock and Load
LOCK AND LOAD.flavorText: Rexxar narrowed his eyes, grabbed his machine gun, and said: "It's go time. Lock and load." This card pays homage to that special moment.

ALEXSTRASZA.name: Alexstrasza
ALEXSTRASZA.flavorText: Alexstrasza the Life-Binder brings life and hope to everyone. Except Deathwing. And Malygos. And Nekros.

CLERIC OF SCALES.name: Cleric of Scales
CLERIC OF SCALES.flavorText: If she can't find a spell, it's a clerical error.

OVERPLANNER.name: Overplanner
OVERPLANNER.flavorText: "Hey kids, what do you call an arrogant skydiving pirate? A condescending con descending!"

DEEPMINER BRANN.name: Deepminer Brann
DEEPMINER BRANN.flavorText: This is a very on-brannd effect.

INVIGORATE.name: Invigorate
INVIGORATE.flavorText: No. 3 Most Internally Contentious Hearthstone Card of 2022.

ANNOY-O-TROUPE.name: Annoy-o-Troupe
ANNOY-O-TROUPE.flavorText: Some classes get Void Lords, other classes get Annoyed Lords.

FLAMETONGUE TOTEM.name: Flametongue Totem
FLAMETONGUE TOTEM.flavorText: Totemsmiths like to use the rarest woods for their totems. There are even rumors of totems made of Ironbark Protectors.

BLOOD-QUEEN LANA'THEL.name: Blood-Queen Lana'thel
BLOOD-QUEEN LANA'THEL.flavorText: As a young blood-princess she learned the proper way for a lady to curtsy, how to address fellow members of royalty, and how to bite them.

GALAKROND, THE TEMPEST.name: Galakrond, the Tempest
GALAKROND, THE TEMPEST.flavorText: Hagatha cried out over the winds: "Truly, you are as powerful as the Maelstrom!" To which the Tempest answered: "I AM THE MAELSTROM."

THORNMANTLE MUSICIAN.name: Thornmantle Musician
THORNMANTLE MUSICIAN.flavorText: She calls the hyena her "little chef". Not sure what that's about.

PRINCESS TALANJI.name: Princess Talanji
PRINCESS TALANJI.flavorText: Everyone wants to be a princess, but nobody ever considers the size of the hat.

WATCHER OF THE SUN.name: Watcher of the Sun
WATCHER OF THE SUN.flavorText: "I've got my eye on y-AAA I'M BLIND!"

LASER BARRAGE.name: Laser Barrage
LASER BARRAGE.flavorText: "I say we take off and laser barrage the entire site from orbit - it's the only way to be sure."

CONSERVATOR NYMPH.name: Conservator Nymph
CONSERVATOR NYMPH.flavorText: Whatever you do, don't water your Treants after midnight!

SCAVENGER'S INGENUITY.name: Scavenger's Ingenuity
SCAVENGER'S INGENUITY.flavorText: "A beast, barely alive. Gentlemen, we can rebuild it! Make it stronger, faster... spikier."

XB-488 DISPOSALBOT.name: XB-488 Disposalbot
XB-488 DISPOSALBOT.flavorText: You'll be so surprised when you figure out what XB stands for.

ANIMAL COMPANION.name: Animal Companion
ANIMAL COMPANION.flavorText: You could summon Misha, Leokk, or Huffer! Huffer is more trouble than he's worth.

LAB RECRUITER.name: Lab Recruiter
LAB RECRUITER.flavorText: Join the chemistry lab! We've got all the solutions.

SHADOWTOUCHED KVALDIR.name: Shadowtouched Kvaldir
SHADOWTOUCHED KVALDIR.flavorText: Four out of five deck doctors say this works great with Reno Jackson!

DIRTY TRICKS.name: Dirty Tricks
DIRTY TRICKS.flavorText: "Ahh sand in my eyes! Also, I'm being stabbed."

GRAL, THE SHARK.name: Gral, the Shark
GRAL, THE SHARK.flavorText: “… We’re gonna need a bigger board.”

GOLAKKA CRAWLER.name: Golakka Crawler
GOLAKKA CRAWLER.flavorText: Universally adored by both control decks and ninjas.

HARVEST GOLEM.name: Harvest Golem
HARVEST GOLEM.flavorText: "Overheat threshold exceeded. System failure. Wheat clog in port two. Shutting down."

COPPERTAIL IMPOSTER.name: Coppertail Imposter
COPPERTAIL IMPOSTER.flavorText: It was fitting in fine until it gathered nuts and bolts.

MOJOMASTER ZIHI.name: Mojomaster Zihi
MOJOMASTER ZIHI.flavorText: Sadly, she was still two credits short of her Witch Doctorate.

FORBIDDEN RITUAL.name: Forbidden Ritual
FORBIDDEN RITUAL.flavorText: Actually, C'Thun gives his full support for this ritual.

EAGLEHORN BOW.name: Eaglehorn Bow
EAGLEHORN BOW.flavorText: First Lesson: Put the pointy end in the other guy.

MANA RESERVOIR.name: Mana Reservoir
MANA RESERVOIR.flavorText: If it soaks too long, it becomes a reservoir hog.

FROSTBOLT.name: Frostbolt
FROSTBOLT.flavorText: It is customary to yell "Chill out!" or "Freeze!" or "Ice ice, baby!" when you play this card.

SPURFANG.name: Spurfang
SPURFANG.flavorText: He's always smiling… Not by choice, but because it hurts to close his mouth.

RAGNAROS THE FIRELORD.name: Ragnaros the Firelord
RAGNAROS THE FIRELORD.flavorText: Ragnaros was summoned by the Dark Iron dwarves, who were eventually enslaved by the Firelord. Summoning Ragnaros often doesn’t work out the way you want it to.

FELFIRE THRUSTERS.name: Felfire Thrusters
FELFIRE THRUSTERS.flavorText: The coolness factor of a fire decal is universal.

ARGENT SQUIRE.name: Argent Squire
ARGENT SQUIRE.flavorText: "I solemnly swear to uphold the Light, purge the world of darkness, and to eat only burritos." - The Argent Dawn Oath

THE BEAST WITHIN.name: The Beast Within
THE BEAST WITHIN.flavorText: Undoes years of obedience school training.

FOSSILIZED KALEIDOSAUR.name: Fossilized Kaleidosaur
FOSSILIZED KALEIDOSAUR.flavorText: He's not that bad if you don't die turn 4.

LUSHWATER MURCENARY.name: Lushwater Murcenary
LUSHWATER MURCENARY.flavorText: You can't just switch sides because they have more fish!

TUSKARRRR TRAWLER.name: Tuskarrrr Trawler
TUSKARRRR TRAWLER.flavorText: "Fish scales? Junk. A gravestone? Junk. This weird looking puzzle box? Junk. AHA! An Ancharrr!"

SUSPICIOUS ALCHEMIST.name: Suspicious Alchemist
SUSPICIOUS ALCHEMIST.flavorText: Side effects may include feeling totally fine! Don't even worry about it.

SESSELIE OF THE FAE COURT.name: Sesselie of the Fae Court
SESSELIE OF THE FAE COURT.flavorText: They claim they're from the Fae Court, but that might be a Fae Kout.

WISPERING WOODS.name: Wispering Woods
WISPERING WOODS.flavorText: We didn't actually fire the guy who named Dark Wispers.

SI:7 EXTORTION.name: SI:7 Extortion
SI:7 EXTORTION.flavorText: "It's a dangerous world out there. It'd be a shame if your protection insurance were to suddenly run out…"

ARGENT PROTECTOR.name: Argent Protector
ARGENT PROTECTOR.flavorText: "I'm not saying you can dodge fireballs. I'm saying with this shield, you won't have to."

BEAR TRAP.name: Bear Trap
BEAR TRAP.flavorText: You'll never guess what's in that conveniently bear-sized, bear-smelling box.

LOTHAR.name: Lothar
LOTHAR.flavorText: Has been around since before there were paladins and those newfangled paladin mechs.

EVIL CABLE RAT.name: EVIL Cable Rat
EVIL CABLE RAT.flavorText: Gradually driven to darkness by the promise of unobtainable cheese.

HUNGRY DRAGON.name: Hungry Dragon
HUNGRY DRAGON.flavorText: Hungry Hungry Dragon is NOT a fun game.

QUEEN OF PAIN.name: Queen of Pain
QUEEN OF PAIN.flavorText: Her sister is the Queen of Pane who sells windows and shower doors.

ZAP!.name: Zap!
ZAP!.flavorText: The material components for this spell are wool socks and a rug.

THE REPLICATOR-INATOR.name: The Replicator-inator
THE REPLICATOR-INATOR.flavorText: Dr. Boom is the greatest inventor in the Tri-Zone area!

YOUTHFUL BREWMASTER.name: Youthful Brewmaster
YOUTHFUL BREWMASTER.flavorText: His youthful enthusiasm doesn’t always equal excellence in his brews. Don’t drink the Mogu Stout!

DRUID OF THE SWARM.name: Druid of the Swarm
DRUID OF THE SWARM.flavorText: The druid awoke from troubling dreams to find herself transformed into a giant spider.

PRAISE GALAKROND!.name: Praise Galakrond!
PRAISE GALAKROND!.flavorText: "Turn to Galakrond, Chapter 3 Verse 12. 'SNARL! ROAR! GRAAAAGH!' Let us reflect on this wisdom."

SHIELD SHATTER.name: Shield Shatter
SHIELD SHATTER.flavorText: "Is the shield being shattered or doing the shattering?" "Yes."

PLAGUEMAW THE ROTTING.name: Plaguemaw the Rotting
PLAGUEMAW THE ROTTING.flavorText: This is why you should brush your teeth three times a day!

UTGARDE GRAPPLESNIPER.name: Utgarde Grapplesniper
UTGARDE GRAPPLESNIPER.flavorText: Note: The dragon may be a little cranky upon arrival.

THE LICH KING.name: The Lich King
THE LICH KING.flavorText: "All that I am: anger, cruelty, vengeance, 8 attack - I bestow upon you, my chosen knight."

DRAKKARI DEFENDER.name: Drakkari Defender
DRAKKARI DEFENDER.flavorText: Sometimes, the best defense is an offensive troll.

RICOCHET SHOT.name: Ricochet Shot
RICOCHET SHOT.flavorText: Simple geometry? Actually, I find it's quite complex.

SWARM OF LIGHTBUGS.name: Swarm of Lightbugs
SWARM OF LIGHTBUGS.flavorText: No, I asked for 'lightNING in a bottle'!

ARMOR VENDOR.name: Armor Vendor
ARMOR VENDOR.flavorText: "You look like the kind of person that would buy three sets of armor. One to wear, a spare, and a spare for the spare."

GLACIATE.name: Glaciate
GLACIATE.flavorText: We now have a more accurate answer to the age-old question "What's cooler than being cool?"

GALLOPING SAVIOR.name: Galloping Savior
GALLOPING SAVIOR.flavorText: "Look to my coming on the first light of the third card."

TINKMASTER OVERSPARK.name: Tinkmaster Overspark
TINKMASTER OVERSPARK.flavorText: Tinkmaster Overspark nearly lost his Tinker's license after the Great Ironforge Squirrel Stampede of '09.

SINISTER SOULCAGE.name: Sinister Soulcage
SINISTER SOULCAGE.flavorText: Also a pretty neat night light!

ARCANE ARTIFICER.name: Arcane Artificer
ARCANE ARTIFICER.flavorText: Ethereal armor dissipates in 6 hours which can cause extreme awkwardness for first time buyers.

GRIMY GADGETEER.name: Grimy Gadgeteer
GRIMY GADGETEER.flavorText: "You look like a Gadgetgun 3000-Mark IV man, am I right?"

STAFF OF THE PRIMUS.name: Staff of the Primus
STAFF OF THE PRIMUS.flavorText: THE PRIMUS, RULER OF MALDRAXXUS, MASTER STRATEGIST, AND wielder of toothpicks!

FELFIN NAVIGATOR.name: Felfin Navigator
FELFIN NAVIGATOR.flavorText: Return my fishes to me, and I myself shall carry you to the gates of Mrrhalla!

PRESCIENCE.name: Prescience
PRESCIENCE.flavorText: Wait don't change the channel! I love this vision.

HIGH ABBESS ALURA.name: High Abbess Alura
HIGH ABBESS ALURA.flavorText: She's all about hitting the books. Literally.

WOECLEAVER.name: Woecleaver
WOECLEAVER.flavorText: Turn that frown into TWO frowns!

HERALD OF NATURE.name: Herald of Nature
HERALD OF NATURE.flavorText: A mother of plants in mother of pearl.

DREADHOUND HANDLER.name: Dreadhound Handler
DREADHOUND HANDLER.flavorText: The handler being undead speaks to a spotty safety record.

KOR'KRON ELITE.name: Kor'kron Elite
KOR'KRON ELITE.flavorText: The Kor'kron are the elite forces of Garrosh Hellscream. Let's just say you don't want to run into these guys while wearing a blue tabard.

BONELORD FROSTWHISPER.name: Bonelord Frostwhisper
BONELORD FROSTWHISPER.flavorText: Downside? Not if you want to be a Death Knight!

CAPTAIN GALVANGAR.name: Captain Galvangar
CAPTAIN GALVANGAR.flavorText: It wasn't the ravages of war that took Galvangar, it was hypothermia.

MOONLIT GUIDANCE.name: Moonlit Guidance
MOONLIT GUIDANCE.flavorText: Guff always makes the best decisions after 2 AM.

VICIOUS SLITHERSPEAR.name: Vicious Slitherspear
VICIOUS SLITHERSPEAR.flavorText: He goes by ‘Fun-Loving Slitherspear’ on his dating profile.

N'ZOTH, THE CORRUPTOR.name: N'Zoth, the Corruptor
N'ZOTH, THE CORRUPTOR.flavorText: Has not been able to get "Under the Sea" out of his head for like FIVE THOUSAND YEARS.

MECHWARPER.name: Mechwarper
MECHWARPER.flavorText: Mechs that summon mechs? What's next? Donuts that summon donuts? Mmmmm.

HODIR, FATHER OF GIANTS.name: Hodir, Father of Giants
HODIR, FATHER OF GIANTS.flavorText: Giant ladies, this one's a Keeper.

ALGALON THE OBSERVER.name: Algalon the Observer
ALGALON THE OBSERVER.flavorText: That's so Algalon, it’s the future he can see.

BARBARIC SORCERESS.name: Barbaric Sorceress
BARBARIC SORCERESS.flavorText: Her four arms are for casting, and her forearms are for crushing.

LICENSED ADVENTURER.name: Licensed Adventurer
LICENSED ADVENTURER.flavorText: "Just point me in the vague direction of the things you want smashed, and you got yourself a deal!"

STEAMWHEEDLE SNIPER.name: Steamwheedle Sniper
STEAMWHEEDLE SNIPER.flavorText: Goblins seldom have the patience for sniping. Most prefer lobbing explosives.

PLAGUE OF MADNESS.name: Plague of Madness
PLAGUE OF MADNESS.flavorText: Don't bring a candle to a knife fight.

BONE BREAKER.name: Bone Breaker
BONE BREAKER.flavorText: Many weapons are bone breakers if you swing hard enough.

PATCHES THE PILOT.name: Patches the Pilot
PATCHES THE PILOT.flavorText: Finally, a Patches you want to draw on turn 1!

ATTORNEY-AT-MAW.name: Attorney-at-Maw
ATTORNEY-AT-MAW.flavorText: When the going gets tough, you don't want a criminal lawyer... you want a criminal lawyer...

CONJURER'S CALLING.name: Conjurer's Calling
CONJURER'S CALLING.flavorText: If only you’d let it go to voicemail…

TRIPLE SEVENS.name: Triple Sevens
TRIPLE SEVENS.flavorText: If you count the 'seven' in the name, there's actually four total 7s, not three. Huge oversight from the designers.

EVERYFIN IS AWESOME.name: Everyfin is Awesome
EVERYFIN IS AWESOME.flavorText: Everyfin is cool when you're part of a murloc team!

DREDGER STAFF.name: Dredger Staff
DREDGER STAFF.flavorText: The dredger staff held the dredger knife and said, "Dredger bow before the Sire!"

ACIDMAW.name: Acidmaw
ACIDMAW.flavorText: With the help of his trusty sidekick Dreadscale, the giant jormungar Acidmaw is ready to face any knight!

ARCANE SERVANT.name: Arcane Servant
ARCANE SERVANT.flavorText: "Would sir like me to punch something?"

SPIRIT OF THE LYNX.name: Spirit of the Lynx
SPIRIT OF THE LYNX.flavorText: Much of this shrine’s power lies in the can-opener noise it makes.

VULPERA SCOUNDREL.name: Vulpera Scoundrel
VULPERA SCOUNDREL.flavorText: A spell is a spell, but the mystery choice could be anything! (It's also a spell.)

FELSTALKER.name: Felstalker
FELSTALKER.flavorText: This puppy chews up cards instead of shoes.

TOPIOR THE SHRUBBAGAZZOR.name: Topior the Shrubbagazzor
TOPIOR THE SHRUBBAGAZZOR.flavorText: They got a dragon that burns 1000 gallons of anima a week.

PLAYMAKER.name: Playmaker
PLAYMAKER.flavorText: "Here's the plan: you go left, I go right, and the wounded guy takes the hit."

CRYPT KEEPER.name: Crypt Keeper
CRYPT KEEPER.flavorText: How many crypts could a Crypt Keeper keep if a Crypt Keeper could keep crypts?

RECKONING.name: Reckoning
RECKONING.flavorText: He would henceforth be known as "Karmerr, the Doom of Kazzak."

SHRINK RAY.name: Shrink Ray
SHRINK RAY.flavorText: Actually works by enlarging the rest of the world.

SNEAKY DEVIL.name: Sneaky Devil
SNEAKY DEVIL.flavorText: The result of a tragic accident involving a Defias Thug, a Wand of Polymorph, and a bundle of Fel Lotus.

CORE HOUND.name: Core Hound
CORE HOUND.flavorText: You don’t tame a Core Hound. You just train it to eat someone else before it eats you.

FAL'DOREI STRIDER.name: Fal'dorei Strider
FAL'DOREI STRIDER.flavorText: What’s worse? Seeing the spider, or NOT seeing the spider, but knowing it’s somewhere in your deck?

GRAND EMPRESS SHEK'ZARA.name: Grand Empress Shek'zara
GRAND EMPRESS SHEK'ZARA.flavorText: So is a Grand Empress an empress that's grand or an empress's empress?

NERUBIAN SWARMGUARD.name: Nerubian Swarmguard
NERUBIAN SWARMGUARD.flavorText: How long can this go on? Apparently even in death.

OAKEN SUMMONS.name: Oaken Summons
OAKEN SUMMONS.flavorText: The Guild used oak trees until they all turned to ash.

PLAGUE OF DEATH.name: Plague of Death
PLAGUE OF DEATH.flavorText: Don't worry, there's a happy little funhouse right under that sand pit.

COUNTERSPELL.name: Counterspell
COUNTERSPELL.flavorText: What's the difference between a mage playing with Counterspell and a mage who isn't? The mage who isn't is getting Pyroblasted in the face.

HUDDLE UP.name: Huddle Up
HUDDLE UP.flavorText: Spell, Naga, Naga, Naga, Naga, Naga, Naga, Naga...

BALLOON MERCHANT.name: Balloon Merchant
BALLOON MERCHANT.flavorText: It's a shiny yellow balloon! But it can be popped with a single point of damage.

BONE GLAIVE.name: Bone Glaive
BONE GLAIVE.flavorText: Resourceful Demon Hunters find a use for every part of the Demon.

KANGOR'S ENDLESS ARMY.name: Kangor's Endless Army
KANGOR'S ENDLESS ARMY.flavorText: "That's three, Kangor. Three isn't endless." - Countess Ashmore

XYRELLA.name: Xyrella
XYRELLA.flavorText: On the Night of Falling Stars, Xyrella had a vision of a shattered naaru. "Go to the Barrens," the being said. "Seek the shards of my broken body. Restore me, and I will restore your daughter."

FROSTWEAVE DUNGEONEER.name: Frostweave Dungeoneer
FROSTWEAVE DUNGEONEER.flavorText: It's a woven blanket of ice but surprisingly comforting.

MORTAL COIL.name: Mortal Coil
MORTAL COIL.flavorText: If your spells look like horrifying skulls, let's be honest, you should get to draw some cards.

ASTRAL SERPENT.name: Astral Serpent
ASTRAL SERPENT.flavorText: Call it lazy all you want, but it does have two more cards than you.

NOSTALGIC INITIATE.name: Nostalgic Initiate
NOSTALGIC INITIATE.flavorText: Nostalgic Initiate: "Man I wish I could relive my college days..." Kel'thuzad: "Say no more."

SWIFTSCALE TRICKSTER.name: Swiftscale Trickster
SWIFTSCALE TRICKSTER.flavorText: If you play your cards fast enough, who's to say how much they cost?

CORROSIVE SLUDGE.name: Corrosive Sludge
CORROSIVE SLUDGE.flavorText: The result of centuries of terrible sanitation.

HOBART GRAPPLEHAMMER.name: Hobart Grapplehammer
HOBART GRAPPLEHAMMER.flavorText: Grapplehammer is the horrible mind behind the Automatic Piranha Launcher (banned in 7 districts)!

KAZAKUS.name: Kazakus
KAZAKUS.flavorText: The mysterious leader of the Kabal is NOT a dragon, and does NOT deal in illegal potions. Any public statements to the contrary will be met with litigation and Dragonfire Potions.

BLOWTORCH SABOTEUR.name: Blowtorch Saboteur
BLOWTORCH SABOTEUR.flavorText: Before he came along, we went through a lot of duct tape.

KOBOLD GEOMANCER.name: Kobold Geomancer
KOBOLD GEOMANCER.flavorText: In the old days, Kobolds were the finest candle merchants in the land. Then they got pushed too far...

HENCH-CLAN HOGSTEED.name: Hench-Clan Hogsteed
HENCH-CLAN HOGSTEED.flavorText: This is CLEARLY their first rodeo.

BLOOD TREANT.name: Blood Treant
BLOOD TREANT.flavorText: The blood of my enemies makes for some great fertilizer!

HAND OF PROTECTION.name: Hand of Protection
HAND OF PROTECTION.flavorText: This spell has been renamed so many times, even paladins don’t know what it should be called anymore.

MOZAKI, MASTER DUELIST.name: Mozaki, Master Duelist
MOZAKI, MASTER DUELIST.flavorText: Treats her students like her peers, which means defeating them in one-sided duels all day long.

CUSTOMS ENFORCER.name: Customs Enforcer
CUSTOMS ENFORCER.flavorText: Anything to declare? "yes... CHAMPION! Azeroth cries out..."

EYESTALK OF C'THUN.name: Eyestalk of C'Thun
EYESTALK OF C'THUN.flavorText: C'Thun sees all...even next week's lottery numbers.

MAD BOMBER.name: Mad Bomber
MAD BOMBER.flavorText: He's not really all that crazy, he is just not as careful with explosives as he should be.

TAUREN WARRIOR.name: Tauren Warrior
TAUREN WARRIOR.flavorText: Tauren Warrior: Champion of Mulgore, Slayer of Quilboar, Rider of Thunderbluff Elevators.

MANA GEODE.name: Mana Geode
MANA GEODE.flavorText: Gadgetzan, where even the pet rocks have pet rocks.

DRAGON TALES.name: Dragon Tales
DRAGON TALES.flavorText: "Once upon a time, there was a maaaagical toy shop, filled with wonder and Dragons!"

VOID FLAYER.name: Void Flayer
VOID FLAYER.flavorText: The Void, just like onions, has flayers.

MYSTERIOUS CHALLENGER.name: Mysterious Challenger
MYSTERIOUS CHALLENGER.flavorText: He may sound surly and antisocial, but he's actually just really shy.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/53/VO_AT_079_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_079_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/ec/VO_AT_079_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_079_ATTACK_02.wav Stop asking questions!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/c1/VO_AT_079_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_079_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

BIG DREAMS.name: Big Dreams
BIG DREAMS.flavorText: Just a small town Taunka Livin' in a lonely... waunka

BREAKDANCE.name: Breakdance
BREAKDANCE.flavorText: "Commander! Uhh... I'm... Pretty sure we just got served? I'm not really trained for this."

DRYSCALE DEPUTY.name: Dryscale Deputy
DRYSCALE DEPUTY.flavorText: He's here to tip the scales in our favor… and moisturize them too.

BLACKWING CORRUPTOR.name: Blackwing Corruptor
BLACKWING CORRUPTOR.flavorText: He got his name when he gave Blackwing some comic books and rock & roll records.

COMMENCEMENT.name: Commencement
COMMENCEMENT.flavorText: "Remember, graduates—you carry a heavy weight on your shoulders now."

MASKED CONTENDER.name: Masked Contender
MASKED CONTENDER.flavorText: Knew Mysterious Challenger back when he was a Mysterious Squire.

DEATHCHILLER.name: Deathchiller
DEATHCHILLER.flavorText: Man, death is like the most chill state... you've got nothing to do but relax.

SLAM.name: Slam
SLAM.flavorText: "Dun da dun, dun da dun": if you've heard an ogre sing this, it's too late.

IMPRISONED HOMUNCULUS.name: Imprisoned Homunculus
IMPRISONED HOMUNCULUS.flavorText: He got a time out for excessive vulgarity.

MANA TIDE TOTEM.name: Mana Tide Totem
MANA TIDE TOTEM.flavorText: It is said that some shaman can say "Floatin' totem" 10 times, fast.

FELSOUL JAILER.name: Felsoul Jailer
FELSOUL JAILER.flavorText: He can lock 'em up, but he just can't keep 'em.

BOISTEROUS BARD.name: Boisterous Bard
BOISTEROUS BARD.flavorText: As a kid, she fought with rocks. Now she fights with ROCK!

SHRINKMEISTER.name: Shrinkmeister
SHRINKMEISTER.flavorText: After the debacle of the Gnomish World Enlarger, gnomes are wary of size-changing inventions.

TIME-LOST RAPTOR.name: Time-Lost Raptor
TIME-LOST RAPTOR.flavorText: Much of his time lost no-lifeing Diablo IV.

TWIG OF THE WORLD TREE.name: Twig of the World Tree
TWIG OF THE WORLD TREE.flavorText: For druids who want to branch out.

PROVOKE.name: Provoke
PROVOKE.flavorText: "Heh, Greetings. Heh, Greetings. Heh, Greetings. I will crush you!"

SILVERFURY STALWART.name: Silverfury Stalwart
SILVERFURY STALWART.flavorText: Don't strike until you see the whites of their teeth.

SOULFREEZE.name: Soulfreeze
SOULFREEZE.flavorText: An effective way to freeze someone's soul is to just freeze their body.

ONYXIA THE BROODMOTHER.name: Onyxia the Broodmother
ONYXIA THE BROODMOTHER.flavorText: Throw more dots, throw more dots, more dots, more dots!

STRONGMAN.name: Strongman
STRONGMAN.flavorText: Sure, it looks impressive until you realize it's a barrel of helium.

SQUALLHUNTER.name: Squallhunter
SQUALLHUNTER.flavorText: "Oh, the weather outside is frightful… But Squallhunter's so delightful! And since we've gone down this road--overload, overload, overload!"

MOONFIRE.name: Moonfire
MOONFIRE.flavorText: "Cast Moonfire, and never stop." - How to Be a Druid, Chapter 5, Section 3

BACKSTAB.name: Backstab
BACKSTAB.flavorText: It's funny how often yelling "Look over there!" gets your opponent to turn around.

SKULKING GEIST.name: Skulking Geist
SKULKING GEIST.flavorText: It's as though a million Jade Idols cried out, and were suddenly silenced.

ENCHANTED RAVEN.name: Enchanted Raven
ENCHANTED RAVEN.flavorText: Once upon a midnight restive, Medivh pondered, feeling festive!

CARIA FELSOUL.name: Caria Felsoul
CARIA FELSOUL.flavorText: This is what happens when you keep taking the advice of the little demon on your shoulder.

HOLY NOVA.name: Holy Nova
HOLY NOVA.flavorText: If the Holy Light forsakes you, good luck casting this spell. Also, you're probably a jerk.

THASSARIAN.name: Thassarian
THASSARIAN.flavorText: A natural born leader. And an unnatural reborn leader.

PARCHED DESPERADO.name: Parched Desperado
PARCHED DESPERADO.flavorText: I'm green And I'm about to die Da ba dee da ba di

SPITEFUL SUMMONER.name: Spiteful Summoner
SPITEFUL SUMMONER.flavorText: Sometimes she'll summon a Doomsayer. Out of spite.

AVENGE.name: Avenge
AVENGE.flavorText: Several paladins have joined together to deliver justice under the name "Justice Force". Their lawyer talked them out of calling themselves the Justice League.

THE FIRES OF ZIN-AZSHARI.name: The Fires of Zin-Azshari
THE FIRES OF ZIN-AZSHARI.flavorText: One heck of a hot tub.

HALAZZI, THE LYNX.name: Halazzi, the Lynx
HALAZZI, THE LYNX.flavorText: Remember, you’re only as strong as your weakest lynx.

SPIRIT JAILER.name: Spirit Jailer
SPIRIT JAILER.flavorText: "Sure, they're in your deck, but the mind is like, the REAL prison."

CULT MASTER.name: Cult Master
CULT MASTER.flavorText: She may be an evil cult master, but she still calls her parents once a week.

NATURAL TALENT.name: Natural Talent
NATURAL TALENT.flavorText: Unfortunately, they got 2nd place at the talent show with their synchronized swimming routine.

ABUSIVE SERGEANT.name: Abusive Sergeant
ABUSIVE SERGEANT.flavorText: ADD ME TO YOUR DECK, MAGGOT!

SPLITTING FESTEROOT.name: Splitting Festeroot
SPLITTING FESTEROOT.flavorText: No use crying over split Festeroot,

KOBOLD APPRENTICE.name: Kobold Apprentice
KOBOLD APPRENTICE.flavorText: Horrible secret: The Darkness is immune to Arcane Missiles.

GIFT OF LUMINANCE.name: Gift of Luminance
GIFT OF LUMINANCE.flavorText: You get a small version of yourself in a snow globe to remember the moment.

RAVENCALLER.name: Ravencaller
RAVENCALLER.flavorText: That Friends and Familiars Plan is really paying off!

GORILLABOT A-3.name: Gorillabot A-3
GORILLABOT A-3.flavorText: A-1 and A-2 went nuts, when they should have gone bolts.

HORN OF WINTER.name: Horn of Winter
HORN OF WINTER.flavorText: Much better than the Horn of Loseter.

EATER OF SECRETS.name: Eater of Secrets
EATER OF SECRETS.flavorText: You don't want to be around after it has eaten an explosive trap. You thought Sludge Belcher was bad...

SIPHON SOUL.name: Siphon Soul
SIPHON SOUL.flavorText: You probably should avoid siphoning your own soul. You might create some kind of weird infinite loop.

ELITE TAUREN CHIEFTAIN.name: Elite Tauren Chieftain
ELITE TAUREN CHIEFTAIN.flavorText: He's looking for a drummer. The current candidates are: Novice Engineer, Sen'jin Shieldmasta', and Ragnaros the Firelord.

DUNK TANK.name: Dunk Tank
DUNK TANK.flavorText: "When I said bring a tank to the dungeon, this is not what I had in mind!"

DOOMSAYER.name: Doomsayer
DOOMSAYER.flavorText: He's almost been right so many times. He was sure it was coming during the Cataclysm.

LIGHTWELL.name: Lightwell
LIGHTWELL.flavorText: It isn't clear if people ignore the Lightwell, or if it is just invisible.

FLAME IMP.name: Flame Imp
FLAME IMP.flavorText: Imps like being on fire. They just do.

LAKKARI SACRIFICE.name: Lakkari Sacrifice
LAKKARI SACRIFICE.flavorText: They asked, “And what must we give in return?” Gul’dan lowered his hood and answered: “Six… cards…”

RAZA THE CHAINED.name: Raza the Chained
RAZA THE CHAINED.flavorText: "Could you do me a favor and get the keys from Kazakus?"

RALLY!.name: Rally!
RALLY!.flavorText: One for the squire, two for the gnome, three for the glory, and GO, GO, GO!

ZUL'JIN.name: Zul'jin
ZUL'JIN.flavorText: If you can dodge an axe, you can dodge a ball.

RAIDING PARTY.name: Raiding Party
RAIDING PARTY.flavorText: And a bowl of chips. And some of those little cocktail weenies!

HOLY WATER.name: Holy Water
HOLY WATER.flavorText: For a healthier option, try Holy Water: Zero.

EQUALITY.name: Equality
EQUALITY.flavorText: We are all special unique snowflakes... with 1 Health.

ANCIENT OF LORE.name: Ancient of Lore
ANCIENT OF LORE.flavorText: Go ahead, carve your initials in him.

MAGICAL DOLLHOUSE.name: Magical Dollhouse
MAGICAL DOLLHOUSE.flavorText: Build your own dollhouse in 3 easy steps! 1. Build a castle. 2. Miniaturize it. 3. GLITTER!

BRAWL.name: Brawl
BRAWL.flavorText: Do you know the first rule of Brawl Club?

COBALT SPELLKIN.name: Cobalt Spellkin
COBALT SPELLKIN.flavorText: Spews more spells than a sleep-talking wizard.

LOAD THE CHAMBER.name: Load the Chamber
LOAD THE CHAMBER.flavorText: Wait! Before we duel, I gotta install these shaders.

GNOMISH INVENTOR.name: Gnomish Inventor
GNOMISH INVENTOR.flavorText: She's never quite sure what she's making, she just knows it's AWESOME!

UNEXPECTED RESULTS.name: Unexpected Results
UNEXPECTED RESULTS.flavorText: Sometimes science is more art than science. A lot of people don’t get that.

FORKED LIGHTNING.name: Forked Lightning
FORKED LIGHTNING.flavorText: If you combine it with Spooned Lightning and Knived Lightning, you have the full dining set.

MAGICFIN.name: Magicfin
MAGICFIN.flavorText: The best part is when he pulls Deathwing out of a top hat!

HOLOGRAM OPERATOR.name: Hologram Operator
HOLOGRAM OPERATOR.flavorText: Help me, Temporary Draenei. You're my only hope!

CYCLOPIAN HORROR.name: Cyclopian Horror
CYCLOPIAN HORROR.flavorText: What are the qualifications for being a 'Horror?' Just how horrible do you have to be?

WOUND PREY.name: Wound Prey
WOUND PREY.flavorText: You steal the cranberry juice, you pay the price.

FIRELANDS PORTAL.name: Firelands Portal
FIRELANDS PORTAL.flavorText: Come to beautiful Firelands! Where it's "Way nicer than the Abyssal Maw!"

GALAKROND, THE WRETCHED.name: Galakrond, the Wretched
GALAKROND, THE WRETCHED.flavorText: Fel-flames slowly writhed around the skeleton, until the great bones knit themselves together into a demonic monstrosity. Rafaam shielded his face from the heat but could not hide his grin.

FIRE PLUME HARBINGER.name: Fire Plume Harbinger
FIRE PLUME HARBINGER.flavorText: Good for summoning elementals. Great for making s'mores.

RAVENHOLDT ASSASSIN.name: Ravenholdt Assassin
RAVENHOLDT ASSASSIN.flavorText: Just mail him a package with a name and 10,000 gold. He'll take care of the rest.

HAKKAR, THE SOULFLAYER.name: Hakkar, the Soulflayer
HAKKAR, THE SOULFLAYER.flavorText: ATTENTION: Do not enter any major city while infected with the Corrupted Blood!

COBALT SCALEBANE.name: Cobalt Scalebane
COBALT SCALEBANE.flavorText: You get a sword! And you get a sword! Everybody gets a sword!

WITCHWOOD PIPER.name: Witchwood Piper
WITCHWOOD PIPER.flavorText: She rids villages of annoying pests, like rats and children.

SCARLET PURIFIER.name: Scarlet Purifier
SCARLET PURIFIER.flavorText: The Scarlet Crusade is doing market research to find out if the "Mauve Crusade" would be better received.

DANGEROUS CLIFFSIDE.name: Dangerous Cliffside
DANGEROUS CLIFFSIDE.flavorText: It's not as dangerous as it looks… IT'S EVEN MORE DANGEROUS!

UN'GORO BROCHURE.name: Un'Goro Brochure
UN'GORO BROCHURE.flavorText: Our Un'Goro package includes the Tortollan travel tour! Just don't mind the Devilsaurs.

ANGRY HELHOUND.name: Angry Helhound
ANGRY HELHOUND.flavorText: When you wake up on the all 3 wrong sides of the bed.

VENOMSTRIKE BOW.name: Venomstrike Bow
VENOMSTRIKE BOW.flavorText: "You know you only have to coat the arrowhead in poison and not the entire bow, right?"

DOUBLE AGENT.name: Double Agent
DOUBLE AGENT.flavorText: And under the Alliance tabard? Another Horde tabard.

THE FIST OF RA-DEN.name: The Fist of Ra-den
THE FIST OF RA-DEN.flavorText: The mighty Ra-den was known as the Keeper of Storms. Unfortunately, he could not keep his fist.

FOOD FIGHT.name: Food Fight
FOOD FIGHT.flavorText: Now THIS is the deadliest catch.

SALOON BREWMASTER.name: Saloon Brewmaster
SALOON BREWMASTER.flavorText: Brewmaster Bru brought Barrelbrim bursting barrels of barely brewed barley brew. Barrelbrim bought Bru's barley brew, barring the barrels broken from the brazen brunch brawl.

MARK OF THE LOTUS.name: Mark of the Lotus
MARK OF THE LOTUS.flavorText: The mark of the Lotus is a little flower drawn in permanent marker on the ankle.

OVERCONFIDENT ORC.name: Overconfident Orc
OVERCONFIDENT ORC.flavorText: "I am da powerful! You are da poop!"

CURSED CASTAWAY.name: Cursed Castaway
CURSED CASTAWAY.flavorText: She was an ordinary castaway... until she found that cursed volleyball.

WRETCHED TUTOR.name: Wretched Tutor
WRETCHED TUTOR.flavorText: "If you like my tutoring, you'll love my sister the art therapist, my father the driver, and my mother the housekeeper."

INI STORMCOIL.name: Ini Stormcoil
INI STORMCOIL.flavorText: Before setting her sights on exploration, Ini was known for many inventions, such as the airborne breadmaking dirigible, the hypersprocket 200X zoom binoculars, and jobes (jean robes).

DWARF PLANET.name: Dwarf Planet
DWARF PLANET.flavorText: Hey, who let Magni Bronzebeard, who we all know is famous for his Magni Touch, land on this planet!?

AZURE DRAKE.name: Azure Drake
AZURE DRAKE.flavorText: They initially planned to be the Beryl or Cerulean drakes, but those felt a tad too pretentious.

JAR DEALER.name: Jar Dealer
JAR DEALER.flavorText: What's in the jar? It could be anyone!

ZEALOUS INITIATE.name: Zealous Initiate
ZEALOUS INITIATE.flavorText: Ok, Initiate. You need to settle down and do your job. In this case, that means die so someone else can get a minor buff.

DEVOURER OF SOULS.name: Devourer of Souls
DEVOURER OF SOULS.flavorText: Winner of the Scourge's annual funnel cake devouring contest 12 years running.

BARNES.name: Barnes
BARNES.flavorText: He used to play every part, until Moroes confiscated his Orb of Deception.

GLITTER MOTH.name: Glitter Moth
GLITTER MOTH.flavorText: Some moths are attracted to flame. This one's attracted to disco.

WATER ELEMENTAL.name: Water Elemental
WATER ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Don't summon a water elemental at a party. It'll dampen the mood.

JACE DARKWEAVER.name: Jace Darkweaver
JACE DARKWEAVER.flavorText: As a former mage, making the transition from fire to felfire was quite easy.

DISPOSSESSED SOUL.name: Dispossessed Soul
DISPOSSESSED SOUL.flavorText: I'm afraid it came as a great shock to her when she died.

REDBAND WASP.name: Redband Wasp
REDBAND WASP.flavorText: Also comes in other colors, but red's in fashion this season.

HERALD OF LOKHOLAR.name: Herald of Lokholar
HERALD OF LOKHOLAR.flavorText: “I don’t care how hot it is. I am not going over there to be your air conditioning."

EARTH REVENANT.name: Earth Revenant
EARTH REVENANT.flavorText: Have you guys seen a pair of rock legs lying around anywhere?

ARCANE OVERFLOW.name: Arcane Overflow
ARCANE OVERFLOW.flavorText: On this ship, when you can’t use an int, learn how to float.

JEWELED MACAW.name: Jeweled Macaw
JEWELED MACAW.flavorText: It’s not LITERALLY jeweled. The goblins were terribly disappointed.

VILEFIEND.name: Vilefiend
VILEFIEND.flavorText: Dreamed of becoming a Stylefiend, but fel was never in season.

MEDIVH'S VALET.name: Medivh's Valet
MEDIVH'S VALET.flavorText: "Magus Medivh sir, I've brought the flaming balloons, as you requested."

BOG BEAST.name: Bog Beast
BOG BEAST.flavorText: I'm sure at least one of those bones is from an actual beast.

ROTTING NECROMANCER.name: Rotting Necromancer
ROTTING NECROMANCER.flavorText: You can't spell dredge without D-E-D.

GREAT HALL.name: Great Hall
GREAT HALL.flavorText: It's fabulous! It's grand! It's, well it's really very nice.

CAROUSEL GRYPHON.name: Carousel Gryphon
CAROUSEL GRYPHON.flavorText: "When does this bird land in Stormwind? I've been flying for hours!"

BLOOD OF THE ANCIENT ONE.name: Blood of The Ancient One
BLOOD OF THE ANCIENT ONE.flavorText: Add two cups of Blood of the Ancient One to one cup of lemon juice. Add just a dash of sugar and stir. Delicious!

PRISMATIC BEAM.name: Prismatic Beam
PRISMATIC BEAM.flavorText: Seven colors of the rainbow, one for each enemy minion.

ALTERED CHORD.name: Altered Chord
ALTERED CHORD.flavorText: I'll never understand how bands and orchestras allow musicians that just…. play... off-key. Would love opinions on this.

STORMPIKE QUARTERMASTER.name: Stormpike Quartermaster
STORMPIKE QUARTERMASTER.flavorText: Frozen funnel cakes taste just like ice cream, if you pretend real hard.

FUNGALMANCER.name: Fungalmancer
FUNGALMANCER.flavorText: Fungalmancy is the easy major for those who can't cut it at Waxmancy.

PRIESTESS VALISHJ.name: Priestess Valishj
PRIESTESS VALISHJ.flavorText: Some of the more stoic priestesses worry that she's living too lavishjly.

DANCING SWORDS.name: Dancing Swords
DANCING SWORDS.flavorText: They like to dance to reggae.

SCREWJANK CLUNKER.name: Screwjank Clunker
SCREWJANK CLUNKER.flavorText: If it breaks, just kick it a couple of times while yelling "Durn thing!"

I KNOW A GUY.name: I Know a Guy
I KNOW A GUY.flavorText: Well… a guy who knows a guy.

FURNACE FUEL.name: Furnace Fuel
FURNACE FUEL.flavorText: Remember Ultrasaur? This is him now. Feel old yet?

GLACIER RACER.name: Glacier Racer
GLACIER RACER.flavorText: It’s just not the same without a super suit.

DR. BOOM, MAD GENIUS.name: Dr. Boom, Mad Genius
DR. BOOM, MAD GENIUS.flavorText: "Of course I've gone mad with power. Ever try going mad without it?"

JADE CHIEFTAIN.name: Jade Chieftain
JADE CHIEFTAIN.flavorText: Seeing his Jade Golem grow up into the tall, handsome 6/6 standing before him was the proudest moment of his life.

MUCK POOLS.name: Muck Pools
MUCK POOLS.flavorText: Making a dredger is easier than you'd think. You don't need to worry about mucking it up!

SELFLESS HERO.name: Selfless Hero
SELFLESS HERO.flavorText: "Don't worry about me… I'll just be here... under these tentacles."

HEAT WAVE.name: Heat Wave
HEAT WAVE.flavorText: This is the hottest summer of your life so far.

UNIDENTIFIED MAUL.name: Unidentified Maul
UNIDENTIFIED MAUL.flavorText: When all you have is an unidentified maul, everything else looks like an unidentified nail.

BLOODIED KNIGHT.name: Bloodied Knight
BLOODIED KNIGHT.flavorText: Chillwind Yeti would NEVER betray you like this.

GLADIATOR'S LONGBOW.name: Gladiator's Longbow
GLADIATOR'S LONGBOW.flavorText: The longbow allows shots to be fired from farther away and is useful for firing on particularly odorous targets.

DREAD INFERNAL.name: Dread Infernal
DREAD INFERNAL.flavorText: "INFERNOOOOOOOOOO!" - Jaraxxus, Eredar Lord of the Burning Legion

MURLOC TINYFIN.name: Murloc Tinyfin
MURLOC TINYFIN.flavorText: High mortality rate, from often being hugged to death.

MURLOC WARLEADER.name: Murloc Warleader
MURLOC WARLEADER.flavorText: Do Murlocs ever get tired of making the same old sound? Nope! Mrglglrglglglglglglgl!

SPIKED HOGRIDER.name: Spiked Hogrider
SPIKED HOGRIDER.flavorText: Did you know the Hogchoppers compete every year at the Mirage Raceway? They do. It's a real group.

ALUNETH.name: Aluneth
ALUNETH.flavorText: PHENOMENAL ARCANE POWER…itty bitty living space.

SHIELD SLAM.name: Shield Slam
SHIELD SLAM.flavorText: "What is a better weapon? The sharp one your enemies expect, or the blunt one they ignore?" - The Art of Warrior, Chapter 9

ANCIENT BREWMASTER.name: Ancient Brewmaster
ANCIENT BREWMASTER.flavorText: Most pandaren say his brew tastes like yak. But apparently that's a compliment.

DROWN.name: Drown
DROWN.flavorText: If you play it on a Naga, they drown in their sorrows instead.

FORENSIC DUSTER.name: Forensic Duster
FORENSIC DUSTER.flavorText: He had plenty of experience with dusting things from his time as a butler, so when a murder was committed he saw a real job opportunity!

EMBRACE DARKNESS.name: Embrace Darkness
EMBRACE DARKNESS.flavorText: Once you both get comfortable, darkness is actually pretty snuggly.

CAGE HEAD.name: Cage Head
CAGE HEAD.flavorText: You get your head stuck in a cage ONCE, and all of a sudden you've got a new nickname.

PRIMALFIN LOOKOUT.name: Primalfin Lookout
PRIMALFIN LOOKOUT.flavorText: Lookout is a self-appointed title that's mostly an excuse to beat things up.

TAR LORD.name: Tar Lord
TAR LORD.flavorText: Tar Lord, man... legendary monster? Aw, forget it.

ARENA TREASURE CHEST.name: Arena Treasure Chest
ARENA TREASURE CHEST.flavorText: Yeah it's great, but did you see the Arena Treasure Arms?!

MURLOCULA.name: Murlocula
MURLOCULA.flavorText: The best part of Murlocula is when he said "IT'S MRRGLIN' TIME" and totally mrrgled those guys.

BURDEN OF PRIDE.name: Burden of Pride
BURDEN OF PRIDE.flavorText: A group of burdens is called a pride.

SOUL BARRAGE.name: Soul Barrage
SOUL BARRAGE.flavorText: Works especially well on jazz musicians.

INNER RAGE.name: Inner Rage
INNER RAGE.flavorText: They're only smiling on the outside.

AUCHENAI PHANTASM.name: Auchenai Phantasm
AUCHENAI PHANTASM.flavorText: “Okay kids did everyone remember to heal before we left?”

CRYSTOLOGY.name: Crystology
CRYSTOLOGY.flavorText: "The Light is neither a particle nor a wave. It's more of a juice, really."

LIGHTMAW NETHERDRAKE.name: Lightmaw Netherdrake
LIGHTMAW NETHERDRAKE.flavorText: Do you think it's a glass half full kind of Netherdrake, or a glass half empty, inescapable void kind of Netherdrake?

MIND CONTROL TECH.name: Mind Control Tech
MIND CONTROL TECH.flavorText: Mind Control technology is getting better, but that's not saying much.

CURSE OF AGONY.name: Curse of Agony
CURSE OF AGONY.flavorText: Now, fools, you shall all understand my back pain!

RIN, THE FIRST DISCIPLE.name: Rin, the First Disciple
RIN, THE FIRST DISCIPLE.flavorText: Signed and sealed, she delivers oblivion.

LINE HOPPER.name: Line Hopper
LINE HOPPER.flavorText: There are two things Demon Hunters know: hopping, and cutting.

FENCING COACH.name: Fencing Coach
FENCING COACH.flavorText: Good fencers make good neighbors, right?

CHORUS RIFF.name: Chorus Riff
CHORUS RIFF.flavorText: What do you mean, what do you mean, I SAY WHAT DO YOU MEEEEEAN, mean, mean, meaaaaaaan this chorus is repetitive?

LADY VASHJ.name: Lady Vashj
LADY VASHJ.flavorText: Personal handmaiden to Queen Azshara turned lieutenant to Illidan Stormrage. Also quite the hair sssstylist.

JUKEBOX TOTEM.name: Jukebox Totem
JUKEBOX TOTEM.flavorText: If you really love Hearthstone, put another coin in the Totem baby!

GRAVE SHAMBLER.name: Grave Shambler
GRAVE SHAMBLER.flavorText: I think one of the necromancers got a little carried away.

ETHEREAL AUGMERCHANT.name: Ethereal Augmerchant
ETHEREAL AUGMERCHANT.flavorText: According to him, undamaged minions just spell problems.

GO WITH THE FLOW.name: Go with the Flow
GO WITH THE FLOW.flavorText: Just go with the flow, bro! No mo' woe fo' yo'!

MULCH.name: Mulch
MULCH.flavorText: Is this a noun or a verb? We will never know.

SOULBOUND SPIRE.name: Soulbound Spire
SOULBOUND SPIRE.flavorText: Ah yes, EVERY Starship needs a fragile obelisk full of dead people!

BLOODSCALP STRATEGIST.name: Bloodscalp Strategist
BLOODSCALP STRATEGIST.flavorText: “Shoot them in the face” is more of a tactic than a strategy.

ENTOMB.name: Entomb
ENTOMB.flavorText: It's perfectly safe as long as you remember to put in air holes.

MAIDEN OF THE LAKE.name: Maiden of the Lake
MAIDEN OF THE LAKE.flavorText: Not a good basis for a system of government.

DESPERATE STAND.name: Desperate Stand
DESPERATE STAND.flavorText: They're grateful for the help, but most minions would prefer not dying in the first place.

TOPSY TURVY.name: Topsy Turvy
TOPSY TURVY.flavorText: "Help! I've fallen and I can't get down!"

HIGH INQUISITOR WHITEMANE.name: High Inquisitor Whitemane
HIGH INQUISITOR WHITEMANE.flavorText: No one told her that champions want to sleep in.

GOLD ROAD GRUNT.name: Gold Road Grunt
GOLD ROAD GRUNT.flavorText: No, no, no, Gold Roads are very different from Yellow Brick Roads.

BOMB WRANGLER.name: Bomb Wrangler
BOMB WRANGLER.flavorText: Bomb Wranglers tend to have short fuses and even shorter lifespans.

REAP WHAT YOU SOW.name: Reap What You Sow
REAP WHAT YOU SOW.flavorText: With a hat like that, I'd say their tailor did all of the sowing.

SAVAGERY.name: Savagery
SAVAGERY.flavorText: It is true that some druids are savage, but others still enjoy a quiet moment and a spot of tea.

SKELETAL SIDEKICK.name: Skeletal Sidekick
SKELETAL SIDEKICK.flavorText: He's got your back. And your arm.

AZSHARAN GARDENS.name: Azsharan Gardens
AZSHARAN GARDENS.flavorText: That's not what I meant when I asked you to water the garden.

HARDCORE CULTIST.name: Hardcore Cultist
HARDCORE CULTIST.flavorText: Thumb in = devil horns. Thumb out = I love you. A VERY important distinction when you're at a metal concert.

FURBOLG MOSSBINDER.name: Furbolg Mossbinder
FURBOLG MOSSBINDER.flavorText: Behold, the unstoppable power of MOSS!

TOUCH OF THE NATHREZIM.name: Touch of the Nathrezim
TOUCH OF THE NATHREZIM.flavorText: "You're giving your soul to me? I'm touched."

MIRAGE CALLER.name: Mirage Caller
MIRAGE CALLER.flavorText: Mirage is actually the name of its long-lost cat.

BOUNTY BOARD.name: Bounty Board
BOUNTY BOARD.flavorText: Reno's desire to be a face known around the Badlands might have backfired a little bit.

MURLOC TASTYFIN.name: Murloc Tastyfin
MURLOC TASTYFIN.flavorText: He was destined for the soup. One way or another…

TIGRESS PLUSHY.name: Tigress Plushy
TIGRESS PLUSHY.flavorText: The sheervalue of this card is undeniable.

GOBLIN SAPPER.name: Goblin Sapper
GOBLIN SAPPER.flavorText: He’s not such a binge exploder anymore. These days, he only explodes socially.

FIRE ELEMENTAL.name: Fire Elemental
FIRE ELEMENTAL.flavorText: He can never take a bath. Ewww.

HOWDYFIN.name: Howdyfin
HOWDYFIN.flavorText: You know who to blame if your drinking water tastes a little fishy.

ORIGAMI DRAGON.name: Origami Dragon
ORIGAMI DRAGON.flavorText: The fire will give you a papercut, which CAN burn. Does that count?

WOBBLING RUNTS.name: Wobbling Runts
WOBBLING RUNTS.flavorText: The fourth one fell off in a tragic accident. They don't talk about it.

MAGISTER'S APPRENTICE.name: Magister's Apprentice
MAGISTER'S APPRENTICE.flavorText: "If this is the work I'll be doing, maybe I don't want to be just like you someday..."

WARPATH.name: Warpath
WARPATH.flavorText: "Left, right, left, right, there's none of the enemy left… Right?"

BEATBOXER.name: Beatboxer
BEATBOXER.flavorText: "ERROR. CANNOT COMPUTE 'NO PUNCHING ALLOWED DURING MUSICAL PERFORMANCE'."

PURIFY.name: Purify
PURIFY.flavorText: Even better than a hot shower with vigorous scrubbing!

SNOWED IN.name: Snowed In
SNOWED IN.flavorText: “What do you mean school isn’t cancelled?! It’s a snow day!”

CONDITIONING (RANK 1).name: Conditioning (Rank 1)
CONDITIONING (RANK 1).flavorText: Now drop and give me 5 Mana.

CROP ROTATION.name: Crop Rotation
CROP ROTATION.flavorText: "Dave, you're never gunna believe this! The plants ARE the zombies!"

LIVEWIRE LANCE.name: Livewire Lance
LIVEWIRE LANCE.flavorText: The lance is heavy but it’s the battery pack that really does a number on the shoulders.

PHALANX COMMANDER.name: Phalanx Commander
PHALANX COMMANDER.flavorText: Turns out he's really good at herding cats.

FORGOTTEN TORCH.name: Forgotten Torch
FORGOTTEN TORCH.flavorText: Why does a forgotten torch turn into a roaring torch with no provocation? It's one of life's many mysteries.

DIMENSIONAL CORE.name: Dimensional Core
DIMENSIONAL CORE.flavorText: At the core of every Starship is a Naaru giving its own energy as a power source. At the core of every Draenei is their unbridled faith in the Naaru.

SPITTING CAMEL.name: Spitting Camel
SPITTING CAMEL.flavorText: Were you expectorating another bad pun?

CLAWFURY ADEPT.name: Clawfury Adept
CLAWFURY ADEPT.flavorText: The Inept Clawfury is a danger only to themselves.

SHOCKSPITTER.name: Shockspitter
SHOCKSPITTER.flavorText: That blue raspberry candy was very sour.

BESTIAL WRATH.name: Bestial Wrath
BESTIAL WRATH.flavorText: The seething wrath is just beneath the surface. Beneath that is wild abandon, followed by slight annoyance.

DRUID OF THE CLAW.name: Druid of the Claw
DRUID OF THE CLAW.flavorText: Cat or Bear? Cat or Bear?! I just cannot CHOOSE!

OVERGROWN BEANSTALK.name: Overgrown Beanstalk
OVERGROWN BEANSTALK.flavorText: You'd need to be pretty jacked to climb this.

FIGHT OVER ME.name: Fight Over Me
FIGHT OVER ME.flavorText: And you thought the battles between the Alliance and Horde got ugly…

DESERT NESTMATRON.name: Desert Nestmatron
DESERT NESTMATRON.flavorText: Not as sweet as the Dessert Nestmatron, but still just as refreshing!

SHADOW CLONE.name: Shadow Clone
SHADOW CLONE.flavorText: "You thought you were attacking face, but it was me! You!"

MADAM GOYA.name: Madam Goya
MADAM GOYA.flavorText: She has set up her Black Market here in Gadgetzan for one purpose, to make a KILLING when Beanie Babies make their inevitable comeback.

DRAGONHAWK RIDER.name: Dragonhawk Rider
DRAGONHAWK RIDER.flavorText: Check it out. You can do barrel rolls on this thing.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/27/VO_AT_083_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_083_ATTACK_02.wav Seriously!?
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/6f/VO_AT_083_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_083_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

DUNE SCULPTOR.name: Dune Sculptor
DUNE SCULPTOR.flavorText: Come for the magic show, stay for the sand castles.

SUNFURY PROTECTOR.name: Sunfury Protector
SUNFURY PROTECTOR.flavorText: She carries a shield, but only so she can give it to someone she can stand behind.

AZERITE VEIN.name: Azerite Vein
AZERITE VEIN.flavorText: When the ground trembles near it, are those earthquakes or heartbeats?

ORBITAL HALO.name: Orbital Halo
ORBITAL HALO.flavorText: I can see your halo. HALO. Haaaalo.

AMBASSADOR FAELIN.name: Ambassador Faelin
AMBASSADOR FAELIN.flavorText: For thousands of years, Faelin has longed to return to his homeland. Will Zin-Azshari be as he hopes, or are the secrets of the deep better left forgotten?

RUMMAGING KOBOLD.name: Rummaging Kobold
RUMMAGING KOBOLD.flavorText: "Broken longsword is brand new shortsword." - Kobold Proverb

ACE HUNTER KREEN.name: Ace Hunter Kreen
ACE HUNTER KREEN.flavorText: This grandmaster marksman loves winning tournaments and eating a bit of ice cream.

MAGIC DART FROG.name: Magic Dart Frog
MAGIC DART FROG.flavorText: There's a powerful throat in this frog.

COLIFERO THE ARTIST.name: Colifero the Artist
COLIFERO THE ARTIST.flavorText: You are what you paint! And Colifero is paint.

CORRUPTED ASHBRINGER.name: Corrupted Ashbringer
CORRUPTED ASHBRINGER.flavorText: Put your faith in the blight!

QUARTERMASTER.name: Quartermaster
QUARTERMASTER.flavorText: His specialty? Dividing things into four pieces.

DIREHORN HATCHLING.name: Direhorn Hatchling
DIREHORN HATCHLING.flavorText: His mom could beat up your mom.

SHADOWBOMBER.name: Shadowbomber
SHADOWBOMBER.flavorText: Shadowbomber does her job, but she's kind of phoning it in at this point.

LOTUS ILLUSIONIST.name: Lotus Illusionist
LOTUS ILLUSIONIST.flavorText: If you think her Xavius and Sylvanas cosplay is great, wait till you see her Reno Jackson!

VOID TERROR.name: Void Terror
VOID TERROR.flavorText: If you put this into your deck, you WILL lose the trust of your other minions.

WRATH.name: Wrath
WRATH.flavorText: The talk around the Ratchet Inn is that this card is too good and should be a Legendary.

CABALIST'S TOME.name: Cabalist's Tome
CABALIST'S TOME.flavorText: What's in there? I bet it's cookie recipes!

THRALL, DEATHSEER.name: Thrall, Deathseer
THRALL, DEATHSEER.flavorText: "Do not be afraid. Approach. The dead will sleep… for now."

THORNGROWTH SENTRIES.name: Thorngrowth Sentries
THORNGROWTH SENTRIES.flavorText: Maybe we shouldn't drink from this Oasis…

DREADSCALE.name: Dreadscale
DREADSCALE.flavorText: Let's be clear about this: ACIDMAW is the sidekick.

STATIC WAVEFORM.name: Static Waveform
STATIC WAVEFORM.flavorText: LET ME SEE YOU MAKE SOME NOISE!!!

CRYSTAL MERCHANT.name: Crystal Merchant
CRYSTAL MERCHANT.flavorText: I won't ask about your mana curve if you don't ask where I got these.

ACOLYTE OF PAIN.name: Acolyte of Pain
ACOLYTE OF PAIN.flavorText: He trained when he was younger to be an acolyte of joy, but things didn’t work out like he thought they would.

DARING ESCAPE.name: Daring Escape
DARING ESCAPE.flavorText: Impossible to cast without cackling evilly.

SUNFURY CLERGY.name: Sunfury Clergy
SUNFURY CLERGY.flavorText: Why is the sun so mad? Won't anyone ask about its feelings?

PACK THE HOUSE.name: Pack the House
PACK THE HOUSE.flavorText: How many Pack the Houses would a pack house if a pack could house Pack the House?

THOUGHTSTEAL.name: Thoughtsteal
THOUGHTSTEAL.flavorText: "What do you get when you cast Thoughtsteal on an Orc? Nothing!" - Tauren joke

LADY ANACONDRA.name: Lady Anacondra
LADY ANACONDRA.flavorText: Do you think she got her name before or after she turned into a snake?

REINFORCED PLATING.name: Reinforced Plating
REINFORCED PLATING.flavorText: I am become death, destroyer of azerite.

VILE LIBRARY.name: Vile Library
VILE LIBRARY.flavorText: What type of vial library has 0 vials in it!?

POISONED BLADE.name: Poisoned Blade
POISONED BLADE.flavorText: How much more poisoned can a blade get? The answer is a lot. A lot more poisoned.

CHEF NOMI.name: Chef Nomi
CHEF NOMI.flavorText: His cooking is always very well done.

STARVING BUZZARD.name: Starving Buzzard
STARVING BUZZARD.flavorText: If you feed him, he loses his whole identity.

RUSTSTEED RAIDER.name: Ruststeed Raider
RUSTSTEED RAIDER.flavorText: Three-time winner (and sole survivor) of the Crashes of Outland motocross!

DRAGONCASTER.name: Dragoncaster
DRAGONCASTER.flavorText: It’s challenging to perform magic on dragonback. It’s so easy to drop the rabbit.

ARCH-VILLAIN RAFAAM.name: Arch-Villain Rafaam
ARCH-VILLAIN RAFAAM.flavorText: Minions must wash hands before being LIQUIDATED AND REPLACED BY SOMEONE BETTER.

GROVE TENDER.name: Grove Tender
GROVE TENDER.flavorText: Likes: Hiking and the great outdoors. Dislikes: Goblin shredders and sandals. (Can’t find any that fit!).

NITHOGG.name: Nithogg
NITHOGG.flavorText: Not to be confused with Nithogger.

DEATHWING THE DESTROYER.name: Deathwing the Destroyer
DEATHWING THE DESTROYER.flavorText: "He’s Deathwing? That one's Deathwing? You're Deathwing!? I'm DEATHWING! ARE THERE ANY OTHER DEATHWINGS I SHOULD KNOW ABOUT?"

LADY S'THENO.name: Lady S'theno
LADY S'THENO.flavorText: Only a S'theno deals in absolutes.

WAKENER OF SOULS.name: Wakener of Souls
WAKENER OF SOULS.flavorText: The alarm again!? Wake me up in 5 more eternities.

STICKY SITUATION.name: Sticky Situation
STICKY SITUATION.flavorText: "Now this is what I'd call..." "...just shut up."

SHARD OF THE NAARU.name: Shard of the Naaru
SHARD OF THE NAARU.flavorText: Fell from the sky, huh? I'll give you ten gold.

FISHFLINGER.name: Fishflinger
FISHFLINGER.flavorText: The scent of fish lingers on the fishflinger's fish fingers.

GNASH.name: Gnash
GNASH.flavorText: It's rude to gnash with your mouth open.

EMERISS.name: Emeriss
EMERISS.flavorText: Taste your world's corruption! It tastes like chicken.

SIPHON MANA.name: Siphon Mana
SIPHON MANA.flavorText: Why spend mine when I can take yours?

PUPPETMASTER DORIAN.name: Puppetmaster Dorian
PUPPETMASTER DORIAN.flavorText: Though Dorian may officially be working under Dr. Boom, we all know who's really pulling the strings...

FAN OF KNIVES.name: Fan of Knives
FAN OF KNIVES.flavorText: I wouldn't say I LOVE knives, but I'm definitely a fan.

NAGA CORSAIR.name: Naga Corsair
NAGA CORSAIR.flavorText: Hook-tails are nice and all but she keeps getting stuck on things.

VANNDAR STORMPIKE.name: Vanndar Stormpike
VANNDAR STORMPIKE.flavorText: His favorite modes of transportation? Van, car, board, bike.

MAGIC TRICK.name: Magic Trick
MAGIC TRICK.flavorText: The world is not ready for an illusion of this depth and intricacy!

MONSTROUS PARROT.name: Monstrous Parrot
MONSTROUS PARROT.flavorText: What kind of crackers are you feeding that thing?

RAVAGING GHOUL.name: Ravaging Ghoul
RAVAGING GHOUL.flavorText: But goes by "Ravishing Ghoul" when he hits the club.

OVERLORD SAURFANG.name: Overlord Saurfang
OVERLORD SAURFANG.flavorText: Eats more than his fair share of sour candy.

SNEAKY SNAKES.name: Sneaky Snakes
SNEAKY SNAKES.flavorText: You're a sneaky lil snake, aren'tcha?

GADGETZAN AUCTIONEER.name: Gadgetzan Auctioneer
GADGETZAN AUCTIONEER.flavorText: He used to run the black market auction house, but there was just too much violence and he had to move.

CONFESSOR PALETRESS.name: Confessor Paletress
CONFESSOR PALETRESS.flavorText: She sees into your past and makes you face your fears. Most common fear: Getting Majordomo out of Sneed's Old Shredder.

DELIVERANCE.name: Deliverance
DELIVERANCE.flavorText: In 30 minutes or less, or else it’s free!

ARCANE EXPLOSION.name: Arcane Explosion
ARCANE EXPLOSION.flavorText: This spell is much better than Arcane Implosion.

REMIXED RHAPSODY.name: Remixed Rhapsody
REMIXED RHAPSODY.flavorText: "Is this real life?" "No, this is a card game."

DARKEST HOUR.name: Darkest Hour
DARKEST HOUR.flavorText: It's always darkest just before you find the light switch.

QUEENSGUARD.name: Queensguard
QUEENSGUARD.flavorText: Archnemesis of the Guardian of Kings.

SAUNA REGULAR.name: Sauna Regular
SAUNA REGULAR.flavorText: She's getting that "falls off the bone" tenderness.

KODORIDER.name: Kodorider
KODORIDER.flavorText: Someone called her a Rhinorider, and she's NOT HAPPY.
