SUNBORNE VAL'KYR.name: Sunborne Val'kyr
SUNBORNE VAL'KYR.flavorText: Bring valor to Odyn's halls, Champion!

MANA WYRM.name: Mana Wyrm
MANA WYRM.flavorText: These wyrms feed on arcane energies, and while they are generally considered a nuisance rather than a real threat, you really shouldn't leave them alone with a bucket of mana.

LADY LIADRIN.name: Lady Liadrin
LADY LIADRIN.flavorText: When it comes to spells, she loves 'em then she librams.

RAZORGLAIVE SENTINEL.name: Razorglaive Sentinel
RAZORGLAIVE SENTINEL.flavorText: For the worgen that has everything: more claws.

LIGHTNING BOLT.name: Lightning Bolt
LIGHTNING BOLT.flavorText: Lightning Bolt! Lightning Bolt! Lightning Bolt!

EERIE STATUE.name: Eerie Statue
EERIE STATUE.flavorText: Don't blink! Don't turn your back, don't look away, and DON'T BLINK.

LIGHT'S JUSTICE.name: Light's Justice
LIGHT'S JUSTICE.flavorText: Prince Malchezaar was a collector of rare weapons. He'd animate them and have them dance for him.

OLD MURK-EYE.name: Old Murk-Eye
OLD MURK-EYE.flavorText: He's a legend among murlocs. "Mrghllghghllghg!", they say.

BLIND BOX.name: Blind Box
BLIND BOX.flavorText: THREE Flame Imps?? C'mon, where's my pity timer?!

BLIZZARD.name: Blizzard
BLIZZARD.flavorText: This spell can be very Entertaining.

LILYPAD LURKER.name: Lilypad Lurker
LILYPAD LURKER.flavorText: Honestly, the frog did nothing wrong.

RAZORPETAL VOLLEY.name: Razorpetal Volley
RAZORPETAL VOLLEY.flavorText: The result of a fundamental misunderstanding of the phrase "flower power".

SHOWDOWN!.name: Showdown!
SHOWDOWN!.flavorText: An epic confrontation between the outlaws and the in-laws.

GENTLE MEGASAUR.name: Gentle Megasaur
GENTLE MEGASAUR.flavorText: "Low, low rents! Must enjoy a nomadic lifestyle. Quasi-sentient, bipedal, amphibious humanoids ONLY!"

SHADOW WORD: PAIN.name: Shadow Word: Pain
SHADOW WORD: PAIN.flavorText: A step up from a spell cast by many beginning acolytes: "Shadow Word: Annoy".

GLAIVESHARK.name: Glaiveshark
GLAIVESHARK.flavorText: Can smell a drop of vengeance in the water up to a mile away.

SEEPING OOZELING.name: Seeping Oozeling
SEEPING OOZELING.flavorText: Uh, you might want to get that looked at.

TOTEM CRUNCHER.name: Totem Cruncher
TOTEM CRUNCHER.flavorText: When regular totem hours won't cut it.

EXOTIC MOUNTSELLER.name: Exotic Mountseller
EXOTIC MOUNTSELLER.flavorText: *Taps roof of mammoth* “You can fit so many squirrels in this thing!”

DRAGON ROAR.name: Dragon Roar
DRAGON ROAR.flavorText: Not to be confused with Dragon Yodel.

HEISTBARON TOGWAGGLE.name: Heistbaron Togwaggle
HEISTBARON TOGWAGGLE.flavorText: A staunch ally of Rafaam, at least while the shinies keep flowing.

SHIELDBEARER.name: Shieldbearer
SHIELDBEARER.flavorText: Have you seen the size of the shields in this game?? This is no easy job.

BONE WRAITH.name: Bone Wraith
BONE WRAITH.flavorText: It uses only the eco-friendly bones from free-range humanoids.

BETRAYAL.name: Betrayal
BETRAYAL.flavorText: Everyone has a price. Gnomes, for example, can be persuaded by stuffed animals and small amounts of chocolate.

LIGHT OF THE NAARU.name: Light of the Naaru
LIGHT OF THE NAARU.flavorText: "Light it up!" - Command given to both Lightwardens and Goblins holding Flamecannons.

FIENDISH RITES.name: Fiendish Rites
FIENDISH RITES.flavorText: "You have the right to sacrifice an ally. If you do not have an ally, then one will be sacrificed for you."

SUDDEN GENESIS.name: Sudden Genesis
SUDDEN GENESIS.flavorText: Being hurt can make you another person.

HOLLOW ABOMINATION.name: Hollow Abomination
HOLLOW ABOMINATION.flavorText: As soon as you land your first Honorable Kill, trust me, you'll be hooked!

DOMINO EFFECT.name: Domino Effect
DOMINO EFFECT.flavorText: WHY DO THEY NEVER RUN TO THE SIDE?????

KRAG'WA, THE FROG.name: Krag'wa, the Frog
KRAG'WA, THE FROG.flavorText: Krag'wa has a ritual to honor his friends and a ritual to devour his enemies. No one can tell them apart.

BEAKERED LIGHTNING.name: Beakered Lightning
BEAKERED LIGHTNING.flavorText: Working in a shaman's lab, it's important to be well-grounded.

RELENTLESS WORG.name: Relentless Worg
RELENTLESS WORG.flavorText: It's the Year of the Worg! Wait - what do you mean 'wolf'?

TRAPDOOR SPIDER.name: Trapdoor Spider
TRAPDOOR SPIDER.flavorText: I can respect that they're important for the ecosystem, as long as you keep them waaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaay over there.

MISCHIEVOUS IMP.name: Mischievous Imp
MISCHIEVOUS IMP.flavorText: Why is it when something happens, it is always you three?

RECYCLE.name: Recycle
RECYCLE.flavorText: Druidic recycling involves putting plastics in one bin and enemy minions in another bin.

FIRETREE WITCHDOCTOR.name: Firetree Witchdoctor
FIRETREE WITCHDOCTOR.flavorText: If your tree is on fire - stop, drop, and troll.

HIGHLORD FORDRAGON.name: Highlord Fordragon
HIGHLORD FORDRAGON.flavorText: "Through my faith and my courage, I shall be protected. And through my honor and sacrifice, another will rise in my place."

VENTURE CO. MERCENARY.name: Venture Co. Mercenary
VENTURE CO. MERCENARY.flavorText: No Job is too big. No fee is too big.

BLUR.name: Blur
BLUR.flavorText: "What are you trying to tell me? That I can dodge axes?" "I’m trying to tell you that when you’re a Demon Hunter, you won’t have to."

ABOMINATION.name: Abomination
ABOMINATION.flavorText: Abominations enjoy Fresh Meat and long walks on the beach.

NOSTALGIC CLOWN.name: Nostalgic Clown
NOSTALGIC CLOWN.flavorText: He used to be kind of corrupt, but now he performs purely for the fun of it.

SARONITE TASKMASTER.name: Saronite Taskmaster
SARONITE TASKMASTER.flavorText: Don't even think of asking for time off.

OGRE BRUTE.name: Ogre Brute
OGRE BRUTE.flavorText: Ogres have really terrible short-term chocolate.

SPOT THE DIFFERENCE.name: Spot the Difference
SPOT THE DIFFERENCE.flavorText: Ah, I see now! One of them is a picture of a Chillwind Yeti, and the other is a Blood Elf.

STORMPIKE AID STATION.name: Stormpike Aid Station
STORMPIKE AID STATION.flavorText: Known by some as the “Stormpike Naptime Lounge.”

CHILLWIND YETI.name: Chillwind Yeti
CHILLWIND YETI.flavorText: He always dreamed of coming down from the mountains and opening a noodle shop, but he never got the nerve.

UNDERBELLY FENCE.name: Underbelly Fence
UNDERBELLY FENCE.flavorText: She’ll take anything you have—except scruples and a good work ethic.

SUDDEN BETRAYAL.name: Sudden Betrayal
SUDDEN BETRAYAL.flavorText: You thought he was your bro-bold, but turns out he's your foe-bold.

LEPER GNOME.name: Leper Gnome
LEPER GNOME.flavorText: He really just wants to be your friend, but the constant rejection is starting to really get to him.

CORSAIR CACHE.name: Corsair Cache
CORSAIR CACHE.flavorText: Where's a corsair's favorite place to hide treasure? Under their deck!

RING MATRON.name: Ring Matron
RING MATRON.flavorText: But where does she keep them?

CLOCKWORK AUTOMATON.name: Clockwork Automaton
CLOCKWORK AUTOMATON.flavorText: Most mechs are pretty chill, but this one is all wound up.

TOMB SPIDER.name: Tomb Spider
TOMB SPIDER.flavorText: Less serious than its cousin, the Grave Spider.

POLYMORPH: JELLYFISH.name: Polymorph: Jellyfish
POLYMORPH: JELLYFISH.flavorText: While Ini’s first use of the Spontaneous Gelatin Transmalgamizer may have gotten her banned from the Gnomish Cooking Convention, she’s never one to throw away a new invention.

MIXOLOGIST.name: Mixologist
MIXOLOGIST.flavorText: You can't put your pinky up when you only have 3 fingers.

RAJ NAZ'JAN.name: Raj Naz'jan
RAJ NAZ'JAN.flavorText: When you play the Coin, he deals emotional damage.

DECK OF CHAOS.name: Deck of Chaos
DECK OF CHAOS.flavorText: Yeah, it's chaos, but it's organized chaos.

DRACONIC STUDIES.name: Draconic Studies
DRACONIC STUDIES.flavorText: Our Draconic Studies program has a high rate of burnout.

SCALELORD.name: Scalelord
SCALELORD.flavorText: It's about what they have in common, not what makes them different.

MADAME LAZUL.name: Madame Lazul
MADAME LAZUL.flavorText: Of course she knows the future, she’s been looking at your cards the WHOLE TIME!

MUTANUS THE DEVOURER.name: Mutanus the Devourer
MUTANUS THE DEVOURER.flavorText: As long as Naralex stays under the blanket, Mutanus can't get him.

FANOTTEM, LORD OF THE OPERA.name: Fanottem, Lord of the Opera
FANOTTEM, LORD OF THE OPERA.flavorText: Writing a compelling symphony takes time. Usually around 20 turns or more.

THROW GLAIVE.name: Throw Glaive
THROW GLAIVE.flavorText: "No, no, I said SHOW me the glaive!"

DRYWHISKER ARMORER.name: Drywhisker Armorer
DRYWHISKER ARMORER.flavorText: Kobolds use anything for armor: Pots, pans, garbage cans… even other kobolds.

DEMONIC STUDIES.name: Demonic Studies
DEMONIC STUDIES.flavorText: "Do you wanna summon a demon? I wanna summon a demon!"

SEANCE.name: Seance
SEANCE.flavorText: “The spirits spoke to me.” "What did they say?" "You had lethal two turns ago."

FORLORN STALKER.name: Forlorn Stalker
FORLORN STALKER.flavorText: He's going to leave the dying up to you, if that's cool.

CAULDRON ELEMENTAL.name: Cauldron Elemental
CAULDRON ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Decorating tip: Unused cauldrons can make a lovely elemental display.

ACOLYTE OF AGONY.name: Acolyte of Agony
ACOLYTE OF AGONY.flavorText: It takes many years of practiced study in order to fully master agony.

BARON GEDDON.name: Baron Geddon
BARON GEDDON.flavorText: Baron Geddon was Ragnaros's foremost lieutenant, until he got FIRED.

BLOODBOUND IMP.name: Bloodbound Imp
BLOODBOUND IMP.flavorText: ALWAYS read the terms and conditions.

R.C. RAMPAGE.name: R.C. Rampage
R.C. RAMPAGE.flavorText: This place has really gone to the dogs.

AMALGAM OF THE DEEP.name: Amalgam of the Deep
AMALGAM OF THE DEEP.flavorText: Most explorers call it a success to find just one new species. Imagine Finley's excitement when he identified ten at once!

DEMONIC DYNAMICS.name: Demonic Dynamics
DEMONIC DYNAMICS.flavorText: The Blue Imp Group sure knows how to put on a show!

RUNE DAGGER.name: Rune Dagger
RUNE DAGGER.flavorText: Turns out being stabbed makes you more vulnerable to magic.

TORTOLLAN PILGRIM.name: Tortollan Pilgrim
TORTOLLAN PILGRIM.flavorText: A tortollan made it to the desert!

MAL'GANIS.name: Mal'Ganis
MAL'GANIS.flavorText: Mal'Ganis doesn't like being betrayed, so if you discard him, watch out.

SUNFIRE SMITHING.name: Sunfire Smithing
SUNFIRE SMITHING.flavorText: It's simple, just throw it into the sun.

YOINK!.name: Yoink!
YOINK!.flavorText: Saying the spell’s name makes it work better.

TAME BEAST (RANK 1).name: Tame Beast (Rank 1)
TAME BEAST (RANK 1).flavorText: "Trust me laddie, I never eat seafood!"

SHADOWY FIGURE.name: Shadowy Figure
SHADOWY FIGURE.flavorText: Terrible at shadow puppets: “This is… a tentacle! And this is… two tentacles!”

TO THE FRONT!.name: To the Front!
TO THE FRONT!.flavorText: Except healers. You go to the back.

WINGED GUARDIAN.name: Winged Guardian
WINGED GUARDIAN.flavorText: Take these broken wings, be reborn, and learn to fly again.

ARCANE BREATH.name: Arcane Breath
ARCANE BREATH.flavorText: One of many side effects from eating mana cookies.

POWER SPIKE.name: Power Spike
POWER SPIKE.flavorText: Jeff, when I said this deck needs a power spike I did not mean it like that.

CATACOMB GUARD.name: Catacomb Guard
CATACOMB GUARD.flavorText: A little dark down here. So much for "serving the Light."

UNDERLIGHT ANGLING ROD.name: Underlight Angling Rod
UNDERLIGHT ANGLING ROD.flavorText: "I said I wanted the ASHbringer not FISHbringer!"

NECROTIC MORTICIAN.name: Necrotic Mortician
NECROTIC MORTICIAN.flavorText: Her hair, just like her name, is full of 'tic's.

CANNONMASTER SMYTHE.name: Cannonmaster Smythe
CANNONMASTER SMYTHE.flavorText: "Smythe, it's been a real blast serving the Alliance with you."

SPECTRAL PILLAGER.name: Spectral Pillager
SPECTRAL PILLAGER.flavorText: It turns out you CAN take it with you.

REWIND.name: Rewind
REWIND.flavorText: If you don't find the spell you want, just cast this one more time and see if you get lucky.

FUNNEL CAKE.name: Funnel Cake
FUNNEL CAKE.flavorText: After all this time…. I thought it'd be bigger!

E.T.C., BAND MANAGER.name: E.T.C., Band Manager
E.T.C., BAND MANAGER.flavorText: "This next band features the one and only M.C. Tech on the drums, the fungal king of the keyboard Loatheb, and the showstopping vocal chops of Spellbreaker!"

SHIP'S CANNON.name: Ship's Cannon
SHIP'S CANNON.flavorText: If you hear someone yell, "Cannonball!" you're about to get wet. Or crushed.

K'ARA, THE DARK STAR.name: K'ara, the Dark Star
K'ARA, THE DARK STAR.flavorText: Velen had never seen a shooting star in real life, so when the opportunity arose…

FILLETFIGHTER.name: Filletfighter
FILLETFIGHTER.flavorText: "What do you mean this isn't the meal you asked for? ! I made you a Fillet Minion!"

SILVER HAND KNIGHT.name: Silver Hand Knight
SILVER HAND KNIGHT.flavorText: It's good to be a knight. Less so to be one's squire.

ON THE HUNT.name: On the Hunt
ON THE HUNT.flavorText: The mastiff giggles if you don't hit any ducks.

TWILIGHT DECEPTOR.name: Twilight Deceptor
TWILIGHT DECEPTOR.flavorText: Nobody asks questions if you're carrying a clipboard.

RAZORFEN HUNTER.name: Razorfen Hunter
RAZORFEN HUNTER.flavorText: Someone did mess with Tuskerr once. ONCE.

OVERLORD'S WHIP.name: Overlord's Whip
OVERLORD'S WHIP.flavorText: "This merit badge is for cruelty. This one's for whipping. And this one is for embroidery..."

IRONBEAK OWL.name: Ironbeak Owl
IRONBEAK OWL.flavorText: Their wings are silent but their screech is... whatever the opposite of silent is.

JAZZ BASS.name: Jazz Bass
JAZZ BASS.flavorText: No birds, plural, were harmed in the making of this bass.

SILVERMOON GUARDIAN.name: Silvermoon Guardian
SILVERMOON GUARDIAN.flavorText: The first time they tried to guard Silvermoon against the scourge, it didn’t go so well…

CONVINCING DISGUISE.name: Convincing Disguise
CONVINCING DISGUISE.flavorText: Okay gang, let's see who's really under the mask… *gasp* Old Man Bru'kan!?

CRAZED ALCHEMIST.name: Crazed Alchemist
CRAZED ALCHEMIST.flavorText: "You'll love my new recipe!" he says... especially if you're not happy with your current number of limbs.

HOODED ACOLYTE.name: Hooded Acolyte
HOODED ACOLYTE.flavorText: Wait, what kind of acolyte doesn't wear a hood?

TIMEWARDEN.name: Timewarden
TIMEWARDEN.flavorText: When are we getting the Silver, Gold, and Diamond dragonflight?

SOLAR FLARE.name: Solar Flare
SOLAR FLARE.flavorText: Saruun is quite the dancer. Their pirouette is deadly.

TESS GREYMANE.name: Tess Greymane
TESS GREYMANE.flavorText: Those who cannot remember their card history are doomed to repeat it.

SPIRIT OF THE RAPTOR.name: Spirit of the Raptor
SPIRIT OF THE RAPTOR.flavorText: “Loti! LOTI! Drop it. Drop it Loti! Down! Down Loti!”

MES'ADUNE THE FRACTURED.name: Mes'Adune the Fractured
MES'ADUNE THE FRACTURED.flavorText: Cracking open an elemental with the boys.

UNITE THE MURLOCS.name: Unite the Murlocs
UNITE THE MURLOCS.flavorText: Form feet and legs! Form arms and body! Oh. Sorry. I was thinking about Mechafin.

GIGAFIN.name: Gigafin
GIGAFIN.flavorText: How much storage does Gigafin's Maw have? About a giga bite.

DUPLICATE.name: Duplicate
DUPLICATE.flavorText: The one time when duping cards won't get your account banned!

TAR CREEPER.name: Tar Creeper
TAR CREEPER.flavorText: If you won't come to the tar pits, we'll bring them to you!

CULTIVATION.name: Cultivation
CULTIVATION.flavorText: Calling this an 8 mana card is missing the forest for the trees.

FARRAKI BATTLEAXE.name: Farraki Battleaxe
FARRAKI BATTLEAXE.flavorText: Only two things in life are certain: death and axes.

UNDERCITY HUCKSTER.name: Undercity Huckster
UNDERCITY HUCKSTER.flavorText: Psst! Wanna buy a random class card (from your opponent's class)?

WARGLAIVES OF AZZINOTH.name: Warglaives of Azzinoth
WARGLAIVES OF AZZINOTH.flavorText: The blades glow green from things unseen, dark dreams whirling in the felfire gleam.

VALDRIS FELGORGE.name: Valdris Felgorge
VALDRIS FELGORGE.flavorText: I don't mean to pry, but you don't by chance happen to have six fingers on both of your hands?

YMIRJAR FROSTBREAKER.name: Ymirjar Frostbreaker
YMIRJAR FROSTBREAKER.flavorText: Also gains +1 Attack for each time your opponent mispronounces his name.

VRYKUL NECROLYTE.name: Vrykul Necrolyte
VRYKUL NECROLYTE.flavorText: If at first you don't succeed, vry, vry again.

ZAI, THE INCREDIBLE.name: Zai, the Incredible
ZAI, THE INCREDIBLE.flavorText: Following this act will be her younger brother, Frank the Mediocre.

KOR'VAS BLOODTHORN.name: Kor'vas Bloodthorn
KOR'VAS BLOODTHORN.flavorText: Illidan taught her that demon hunters should sacrifice EVERYTHING… but she still brought Lifesteal just in case.

MEDIVH, THE GUARDIAN.name: Medivh, the Guardian
MEDIVH, THE GUARDIAN.flavorText: If you think the party's great now, just wait 'til he invites the orcs over!

HOT SPRING GUARDIAN.name: Hot Spring Guardian
HOT SPRING GUARDIAN.flavorText: NONE SHALL PASS until at least an hour after eating.

FOAMRENDER.name: Foamrender
FOAMRENDER.flavorText: No honey, we have Shadowmourne at home.

DEMOLISHER.name: Demolisher
DEMOLISHER.flavorText: Laying siege isn't fun for anyone. It's not even all that effective, now that everyone has a flying mount.

OBSIDIAN SHARD.name: Obsidian Shard
OBSIDIAN SHARD.flavorText: You know you’re a Rogue when a sharp rock makes you go “Ooh! Dagger!”

EYE OF SHADOW.name: Eye of Shadow
EYE OF SHADOW.flavorText: It's hard to makeup flavor text sometimes.

MUTATING LIFEFORM.name: Mutating Lifeform
MUTATING LIFEFORM.flavorText: Who knows how many amazing discoveries are out there! ... Nevermind, I'm going home.

JUDGMENT OF JUSTICE.name: Judgment of Justice
JUDGMENT OF JUSTICE.flavorText: Look, we don't need a jury. We've got a paladin right here!

KABAL COURIER.name: Kabal Courier
KABAL COURIER.flavorText: Hey, you park your kodo under a harpy nest, you get what you deserve.

LIVING MONUMENT.name: Living Monument
LIVING MONUMENT.flavorText: This is not the greatest card in the world. This is just a monument.

DESERT CAMEL.name: Desert Camel
DESERT CAMEL.flavorText: Dang. This card is sweet. Almost as sweet as Dessert Camel.

MAD SUMMONER.name: Mad Summoner
MAD SUMMONER.flavorText: Does he summon because of his madness, or is he mad from all the summoning?

HIDDEN OBJECTS.name: Hidden Objects
HIDDEN OBJECTS.flavorText: There are 99 gnomes in this picture. Can YOU find them all?

NEXUS-PRINCE SHAFFAR.name: Nexus-Prince Shaffar
NEXUS-PRINCE SHAFFAR.flavorText: Whatever you do, do not give him OR his ethereal parrot a magical lamp.

CLOCKWORK GIANT.name: Clockwork Giant
CLOCKWORK GIANT.flavorText: He and Mountain Giant don't get along.

SWIPE.name: Swipe
SWIPE.flavorText: When a bear rears back and extends his arms, he's about to Swipe! ... or hug.

SNAKE TRAP.name: Snake Trap
SNAKE TRAP.flavorText: Why did it have to be snakes?

CHAOS STRIKE.name: Chaos Strike
CHAOS STRIKE.flavorText: "What do we want?" "CHAOS!" "When do we want it?" "WHEN LEAST EXPECTED!"

STILTSTEPPER.name: Stiltstepper
STILTSTEPPER.flavorText: Circus school was tough, sometimes you had to step on people to make it to the top.

FIREGUARD DESTROYER.name: Fireguard Destroyer
FIREGUARD DESTROYER.flavorText: Ragnaros interviews hundreds of Fire Elementals for the position of "Destroyer" but very few have what it takes.

LESSER RUBY SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Ruby Spellstone
LESSER RUBY SPELLSTONE.flavorText: The final stone undid its master Spun into wards by nameless caster Azari wailed a savage roar Now sealed in nether, evermore.

BLOOD BOIL.name: Blood Boil
BLOOD BOIL.flavorText: And once your blood is at a boil, throw in the plaguetti.

DRAGONHATCHER.name: Dragonhatcher
DRAGONHATCHER.flavorText: Which came first? The dragon or the dragonhatcher?

MOUNTAIN GIANT.name: Mountain Giant
MOUNTAIN GIANT.flavorText: His mother said that he was just big boned.

SIR FINLEY OF THE SANDS.name: Sir Finley of the Sands
SIR FINLEY OF THE SANDS.flavorText: "The sands shall be my sea! And this scarab shall be my, er, strange and wriggly boat!"

UNLICENSED APOTHECARY.name: Unlicensed Apothecary
UNLICENSED APOTHECARY.flavorText: Get the ingredients wrong on ONE healing potion and they take your license. What a world!

CURSED DISCIPLE.name: Cursed Disciple
CURSED DISCIPLE.flavorText: Politer than his brother, the cursing disciple, but far more evil.

MARK OF THE WILD.name: Mark of the Wild
MARK OF THE WILD.flavorText: Not to be confused with Jim of the Wild.

PINT-SIZED SUMMONER.name: Pint-Sized Summoner
PINT-SIZED SUMMONER.flavorText: She's quite jealous of the Gallon-Sized Summoner.

MUKLA, TYRANT OF THE VALE.name: Mukla, Tyrant of the Vale
MUKLA, TYRANT OF THE VALE.flavorText: Pro tip: DO NOT BOGART THE BANANAS.

TESTING DUMMY.name: Testing Dummy
TESTING DUMMY.flavorText: Don't worry, they're having a blast. MUAHAHAHAHAAAA!

TUNDRA RHINO.name: Tundra Rhino
TUNDRA RHINO.flavorText: Tundra rhinos are often mistaken for kodos. Or am I mistaken?

CRYOMANCER.name: Cryomancer
CRYOMANCER.flavorText: She loves Frozen. I mean who doesn't?

SI:7 AGENT.name: SI:7 Agent
SI:7 AGENT.flavorText: The agents of SI:7 are responsible for Stormwind's covert activities. Their duties include espionage, assassination, and throwing surprise birthday parties for the royal family.

ZOK FOGSNOUT.name: Zok Fogsnout
ZOK FOGSNOUT.flavorText: Despite having only 3 digits on each hand, Zok plays Bass like he has 5.

NECROTIC GEIST.name: Necrotic Geist
NECROTIC GEIST.flavorText: An eye for an eye, and a ghoul for a ghoul.

WHISPERS OF EVIL.name: Whispers of EVIL
WHISPERS OF EVIL.flavorText: Madame Lazul’s ASMR program is off to a promising start!

BLACKJACK STUNNER.name: Blackjack Stunner
BLACKJACK STUNNER.flavorText: "I'm about to ruin this 10-cost minion's whole career."

WORKSHOP MISHAP.name: Workshop Mishap
WORKSHOP MISHAP.flavorText: IT HAS BEEN DAYS SINCE LAST ACCIDENT.

SMUGGLER'S RUN.name: Smuggler's Run
SMUGGLER'S RUN.flavorText: One of the most famous busts in Gadgetzan’s history happened on Smuggler’s Run, where Sergeant Sally apprehended a cadre of Grimy Goons transporting a massive number of illegal fish heads.

HOARDING DRAGON.name: Hoarding Dragon
HOARDING DRAGON.flavorText: Keeps his two cents to himself.

FLIGHT OF THE BRONZE.name: Flight of the Bronze
FLIGHT OF THE BRONZE.flavorText: You're telling me Hearthstone will make a 1 Mana 5/5 with Taunt? Maybe when bronze flies!

FOREBODING FLAME.name: Foreboding Flame
FOREBODING FLAME.flavorText: "I am the harbinger of the end times! Soon, destruction will reign and chaos will ensue in the culmination of your demise: waking up 15 minutes before your alarm!"

EAT! THE! IMP!.name: Eat! The! Imp!
EAT! THE! IMP!.flavorText: No need for flavor text, it's seasoned perfectly!

BRILLIANT MACAW.name: Brilliant Macaw
BRILLIANT MACAW.flavorText: He's been repeating the same shanty for a month. Four pirates walked the plank last week. Middle of the ocean, just walked right off.

WRETCHED TILLER.name: Wretched Tiller
WRETCHED TILLER.flavorText: If you ever tried to plow permafrost, you’d be wretched, too.

BLOODCLAW.name: Bloodclaw
BLOODCLAW.flavorText: This weapon – ow! Requires a little – OWW! Finesse.

ARGUNITE GOLEM.name: Argunite Golem
ARGUNITE GOLEM.flavorText: Golem Bling never really caught on - the fad crumbled after the Cataclysm.

GURUBASHI CHICKEN.name: Gurubashi Chicken
GURUBASHI CHICKEN.flavorText: “Ya hold it by da feet, mon. Den ya THROW.”

SCAVENGING SHIVARRA.name: Scavenging Shivarra
SCAVENGING SHIVARRA.flavorText: Say what you want but finding a matching set of six swords takes commitment.

RING TOSS.name: Ring Toss
RING TOSS.flavorText: If you liked it, then you shoulda put a ring on it!

BOLVAR FORDRAGON.name: Bolvar Fordragon
BOLVAR FORDRAGON.flavorText: Spoiler alert: Bolvar gets melted and then sits on an ice throne and everyone forgets about him.

LIGHTSHOW.name: Lightshow
LIGHTSHOW.flavorText: Always remember P.L.U.R.: Peace, Laser-beams, Unity, Respect.

TOOTH OF NEFARIAN.name: Tooth of Nefarian
TOOTH OF NEFARIAN.flavorText: Nefarian: Lord of Blackrock, creator of the chromatic dragonflight, victim of several root canals.

CURSED CAMPAIGN.name: Cursed Campaign
CURSED CAMPAIGN.flavorText: Their group has been trying to schedule the next session since Kobolds and Catacombs came out.

ENHANCED DREADLORD.name: Enhanced Dreadlord
ENHANCED DREADLORD.flavorText: Photo actually taken across the street in the reflection of a doorknob.

SWORD EATER.name: Sword Eater
SWORD EATER.flavorText: How tough is he? He eats swords for breakfast! Without any milk.

STORMPIKE COMMANDO.name: Stormpike Commando
STORMPIKE COMMANDO.flavorText: The Stormpike Commandos are demolition experts. They also bake a mean cupcake.

SWAMPQUEEN HAGATHA.name: Swampqueen Hagatha
SWAMPQUEEN HAGATHA.flavorText: Rafaam mainly enjoys working with Hagatha because she never laughs at Dr. Boom's jokes.

RESERVED SPOT.name: Reserved Spot
RESERVED SPOT.flavorText: She needs a spot to make sure she can quickly get to her trunk.

SENSORY DEPRIVATION.name: Sensory Deprivation
SENSORY DEPRIVATION.flavorText: You'll come out a new person.

SEN'JIN SHIELDMASTA.name: Sen'jin Shieldmasta
SEN'JIN SHIELDMASTA.flavorText: Sen'jin Village is nice, if you like trolls and dust.

AL'AKIR THE WINDLORD.name: Al'Akir the Windlord
AL'AKIR THE WINDLORD.flavorText: He is the weakest of the four Elemental Lords. And the other three don't let him forget it.

BLOODMAGE THALNOS.name: Bloodmage Thalnos
BLOODMAGE THALNOS.flavorText: He's in charge of the Annual Scarlet Monastery Blood Drive!

BURLY ROCKJAW TROGG.name: Burly Rockjaw Trogg
BURLY ROCKJAW TROGG.flavorText: He's burly because he does CrossFit.

CLAW.name: Claw
CLAW.flavorText: The claw decides who will stay and who will go.

ARGUS, THE EMERALD STAR.name: Argus, the Emerald Star
ARGUS, THE EMERALD STAR.flavorText: Once a proud titan, Argus was fated to meet a darker end. Sargeras and his demons would later corrupt and shatter Argus to use his power for themselves.

IMPRISONED SCRAP IMP.name: Imprisoned Scrap Imp
IMPRISONED SCRAP IMP.flavorText: His impish imports imply impressively impetuous impropriety.

SHRIEKING SHROOM.name: Shrieking Shroom
SHRIEKING SHROOM.flavorText: Auditioning for the next Fungal Idol.

NORTHERN NAVIGATION.name: Northern Navigation
NORTHERN NAVIGATION.flavorText: Leads directly to Greatfather Winter's workshop.

BIG GAME HUNTER.name: Big Game Hunter
BIG GAME HUNTER.flavorText: Mere devilsaurs no longer excite him. Soon he'll be trying to catch Onyxia with only a dull Krol Blade.

WINDFURY.name: Windfury
WINDFURY.flavorText: Windfury is like Earthfury and Firefury, but more light and airy.

FLEETHOOF PEARLTUSK.name: Fleethoof Pearltusk
FLEETHOOF PEARLTUSK.flavorText: Guest interactions may vary over the duration of the visit.

DREAD CORSAIR.name: Dread Corsair
DREAD CORSAIR.flavorText: "Yarrrr" is a pirate word that means "Greetings, milord."

XARIL, POISONED MIND.name: Xaril, Poisoned Mind
XARIL, POISONED MIND.flavorText: It's basically your own fault if you go around drinking weird green potions handed out by creepy mantid dudes.

FRESH SCENT.name: Fresh Scent
FRESH SCENT.flavorText: *Sniff, sniff* Elite troops... *sniff, sniff* ...armed to the teeth and... *sniff, sniff* ...BAAACON!

FEAST OF SOULS.name: Feast of Souls
FEAST OF SOULS.flavorText: Nothing fills you up like soul food!

MIC DROP.name: Mic Drop
MIC DROP.flavorText: The perfect card to play after emoting.

TWIN SLICE.name: Twin Slice
TWIN SLICE.flavorText: The slice so nice, it'll cut you twice.

PLATED BEETLE.name: Plated Beetle
PLATED BEETLE.flavorText: "Ok, your party has defeated the beetle." "I put it on my head." "What?" "I put it on my head. Like a hat."

ARCANITE REAPER.name: Arcanite Reaper
ARCANITE REAPER.flavorText: No… actually you should fear the Reaper.

BOOK OF SPECTERS.name: Book of Specters
BOOK OF SPECTERS.flavorText: Known throughout the land as the Spooky-nomicon.

KALECGOS.name: Kalecgos
KALECGOS.flavorText: He was once the Aspect of Magic but gave it up to focus on cheap tricks.

INVENT-O-MATIC.name: Invent-o-matic
INVENT-O-MATIC.flavorText: The inventor was really proud, until they realized inventing something that invents things makes for poor job security.

PILE OF BONES.name: Pile of Bones
PILE OF BONES.flavorText: It's a very well-organized pile, I'll give you that.

THE BLACK KNIGHT.name: The Black Knight
THE BLACK KNIGHT.flavorText: He was sent by the Lich King to disrupt the Argent Tournament. We can pretty much mark that a failure.

GUNSLINGER KURTRUS.name: Gunslinger Kurtrus
GUNSLINGER KURTRUS.flavorText: "I have given up (a single copy of) EVERYTHING! What have YOU sacrificed?"

FROSTWOLF WARLORD.name: Frostwolf Warlord
FROSTWOLF WARLORD.flavorText: The Frostwolves are locked in combat with the Stormpike Expedition over control of Alterac Valley. Every attempt at peace-talks has ended with Captain Galvangar killing the mediator.

LEEROY JENKINS.name: Leeroy Jenkins
LEEROY JENKINS.flavorText: At least he has Angry Chicken.

HUNTER'S MARK.name: Hunter's Mark
HUNTER'S MARK.flavorText: Never play 'Hide and Go Seek' with a Hunter.

HALKIAS.name: Halkias
HALKIAS.flavorText: Everybody tough until the sinstones start walking.

SWAMP DRAGON EGG.name: Swamp Dragon Egg
SWAMP DRAGON EGG.flavorText: Would you eat them in a ditch? Would you eat them with a witch?

FRENZIED FELWING.name: Frenzied Felwing
FRENZIED FELWING.flavorText: Not to be confused with the "friendsy” felwing.

CRAM SESSION.name: Cram Session
CRAM SESSION.flavorText: The font of the arcane gives nearly limitless access to power and energy! But it can't keep you awake, for that we still use coffee.

KNUCKLES.name: Knuckles
KNUCKLES.flavorText: When confronted with accusations of performance-enhancing bananas, Knuckles replied, "I get my fruit from trees I knock down with my bare hands like everyone else."

SHIELDBREAKER.name: Shieldbreaker
SHIELDBREAKER.flavorText: Can also break up fights, relationships, and unions.

NORTHSHIRE CLERIC.name: Northshire Cleric
NORTHSHIRE CLERIC.flavorText: They help the downtrodden and distressed. Also they sell cookies.

MOLTEN BLAST.name: Molten Blast
MOLTEN BLAST.flavorText: Well, how would YOU celebrate after finals week?!

VOIDWALKER.name: Voidwalker
VOIDWALKER.flavorText: No relation to "The Voidsteppers", the popular Void-based dance troupe.

GIGGLING INVENTOR.name: Giggling Inventor
GIGGLING INVENTOR.flavorText: "I shall build a mighty golden paladin! And he will GREET the WORLD!"

ICEBLOOD GARRISON.name: Iceblood Garrison
ICEBLOOD GARRISON.flavorText: On weekends, it hosts the local community theater rehearsals.

GHASTLY GRAVEDIGGER.name: Ghastly Gravedigger
GHASTLY GRAVEDIGGER.flavorText: Some people take their secrets to the grave.

FLORIST.name: Florist
FLORIST.flavorText: Trade district. Trade district a shop. Color Legendary. Color Legendary golden. Rose is a rose is a rose is a rose.

SHOPLIFTER GOLDBEARD.name: Shoplifter Goldbeard
SHOPLIFTER GOLDBEARD.flavorText: "Arr, this plunder be great for Cap'n Fourteeth's baby shower!"

BLADE OF C'THUN.name: Blade of C'Thun
BLADE OF C'THUN.flavorText: C'Thun demands a sacrifice! Preferably a Deathwing.

SPIRIT ALPHA.name: Spirit Alpha
SPIRIT ALPHA.flavorText: Just like in the natural world, the alpha of the species is bright purple.

ARCANE INTELLECT.name: Arcane Intellect
ARCANE INTELLECT.flavorText: Playing this card makes you SMARTER. And let's face it: we could all stand to be a little smarter.

WASTELAND ASSASSIN.name: Wasteland Assassin
WASTELAND ASSASSIN.flavorText: They'll never see me coming, what with my glowing body, eyes and daggers.

FROTHING BERSERKER.name: Frothing Berserker
FROTHING BERSERKER.flavorText: He used to work as an accountant before he tried his hand at Berserkering.

DRAGON CONSORT.name: Dragon Consort
DRAGON CONSORT.flavorText: Everybody wants someone to snuggle with. Even giant armored scaly draconic beasts of destruction.

LAMPLIGHTER.name: Lamplighter
LAMPLIGHTER.flavorText: The elemental licked the oil and everybody laughed.

TWISTED TETHER.name: Twisted Tether
TWISTED TETHER.flavorText: First, convince your opponent that you just want to play tetherball. Then, you GET 'EM!

WILD BLOODSTINGER.name: Wild Bloodstinger
WILD BLOODSTINGER.flavorText: Tame Bloodstingers would politely invite your minion to tea.

CENARION HOLD.name: Cenarion Hold
CENARION HOLD.flavorText: After the War of the Shifting Sands, Cenarion Hold became a strategic outpost, awaiting the moment when the armies of C'Thun would rise once again.

ILLUMINATOR.name: Illuminator
ILLUMINATOR.flavorText: "LUMOS!" is not what they yell. What do you think this is, Hogwarts?

NAT PAGLE.name: Nat Pagle
NAT PAGLE.flavorText: Nat Pagle, Azeroth's premier fisherman! He invented the Auto-Angler 3000, the Extendo-Pole 3000, and the Lure-o-matic 2099 (still in testing).

BLUEGILL WARRIOR.name: Bluegill Warrior
BLUEGILL WARRIOR.flavorText: He just wants a hug. A sloppy... slimy... hug.

OBSESSIVE FAN.name: Obsessive Fan
OBSESSIVE FAN.flavorText: "Obsessed? No! I'm just really really really really really really really really really really into E.T.C.'s music and everything he says, does, thinks, lives, and breathes!"

VELAROK WINDBLADE.name: Velarok Windblade
VELAROK WINDBLADE.flavorText: His deceptive manipulations have dug the Bloodrock Company into a hole they can't get out of.

PLAGIARIZE.name: Plagiarize
PLAGIARIZE.flavorText: Copying is just using your resources wisely.

FELFIRE BONFIRE.name: Felfire Bonfire
FELFIRE BONFIRE.flavorText: It was then that Marsh and Mallow understood the meaning of their new nicknames.

RAT TRAP.name: Rat Trap
RAT TRAP.flavorText: MISSING: One giant rat. Please return to King Togwaggle.

STAMPEDING KODO.name: Stampeding Kodo
STAMPEDING KODO.flavorText: This Kodo is so big that he can stampede by himself.

EXPLOSIVE RUNES.name: Explosive Runes
EXPLOSIVE RUNES.flavorText: Sometimes it's safer NOT to read the warning signs.

CANNON BARRAGE.name: Cannon Barrage
CANNON BARRAGE.flavorText: Why fire your cannons strategically when you can fire them all at once?

CAPTAIN GREENSKIN.name: Captain Greenskin
CAPTAIN GREENSKIN.flavorText: He was this close to piloting a massive juggernaut into Stormwind Harbor. If it weren't for those pesky kids!

DEADLINE.name: Deadline
DEADLINE.flavorText: For all you procrastinators out there, don't worry. That's why we added Tradeable.

GLOOMSTONE GUARDIAN.name: Gloomstone Guardian
GLOOMSTONE GUARDIAN.flavorText: From the same people who brought you Choose One, and Choose Twice, comes the exciting prequel: Choose NEITHER!

SENSE DEMONS.name: Sense Demons
SENSE DEMONS.flavorText: Generally demons are pretty obvious and you don’t need a spell to sense them.

RECKLESS APPRENTICE.name: Reckless Apprentice
RECKLESS APPRENTICE.flavorText: It’s all a great learning experience until someone accidentally aggros the boss.

ONYXIA.name: Onyxia
ONYXIA.flavorText: Onyxia long manipulated the Stormwind Court by disguising herself as Lady Katrana Prestor. You would have thought that the giant wings and scales would have been a giveaway.

WYRMREST AGENT.name: Wyrmrest Agent
WYRMREST AGENT.flavorText: Keeping tabs on the Grand Tournament is priority 1 for the five mighty Dragonflights!

AWAKEN THE MAKERS.name: Awaken the Makers
AWAKEN THE MAKERS.flavorText: They keep hitting the Snooze button.

TEN GALLON HAT.name: Ten Gallon Hat
TEN GALLON HAT.flavorText: It actually only holds three quarters of a gallon, but that doesn't sound as good.

THUNDERBRINGER.name: Thunderbringer
THUNDERBRINGER.flavorText: You can lead a horse to water, but you can't stop it from electrocuting everything in the water.

GUILD TRADER.name: Guild Trader
GUILD TRADER.flavorText: Somehow, she manages six different professions.

TWO-FACED INVESTOR.name: Two-Faced Investor
TWO-FACED INVESTOR.flavorText: Should never have opened that joint account...

SUNSPOT DRAGON.name: Sunspot Dragon
SUNSPOT DRAGON.flavorText: THIS is why you shouldn't look directly at the sun.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/28/BT_726_DragonmawSkyStalker_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ BT_726_DragonmawSkyStalker_Play.wav <summon sound>

HAGATHA'S SCHEME.name: Hagatha's Scheme
HAGATHA'S SCHEME.flavorText: "All shall suffer!" "But Hagatha, those are your minions..." "I said ALL!!!"

STONESPLINTER TROGG.name: Stonesplinter Trogg
STONESPLINTER TROGG.flavorText: The only thing worse than smelling troggs is listening to their poetry.

UNSTABLE FELBOLT.name: Unstable Felbolt
UNSTABLE FELBOLT.flavorText: Warning! Your minions are seated in the splash zone.

TOTEM GOLIATH.name: Totem Goliath
TOTEM GOLIATH.flavorText: It was an art project, and nobody knew when to stop.

PRISMATIC JEWEL KIT.name: Prismatic Jewel Kit
PRISMATIC JEWEL KIT.flavorText: The divine trick to jewelcrafting is tumbling your own rocks.

GLOWSTONE TECHNICIAN.name: Glowstone Technician
GLOWSTONE TECHNICIAN.flavorText: "Windell! More light!" "I'm givin' it all she's got, Kangor!"

MANUFACTURING ERROR.name: Manufacturing Error
MANUFACTURING ERROR.flavorText: You thought the 9-piece puzzle would be easy, didn't you?

CLOCKWORK KNIGHT.name: Clockwork Knight
CLOCKWORK KNIGHT.flavorText: It takes a lot to wind him up.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/eb/VO_AT_096_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_096_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/c3/VO_AT_096_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_096_ATTACK_02.wav Time. To. Die.
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/b8/VO_AT_096_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_096_DEATH_03.wav My. Time's. Up.

CRACKLING RAZORMAW.name: Crackling Razormaw
CRACKLING RAZORMAW.flavorText: Wasn't clever enough to go AROUND the electric fence.

MASTER JOUSTER.name: Master Jouster
MASTER JOUSTER.flavorText: Needs just a few more ratings points to become Grandmaster Jouster.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/a/ac/VO_AT_112_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_112_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/37/VO_AT_112_ATTACK_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_112_ATTACK_03.wav Prepare to lose!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/0/0a/VO_AT_112_DEATH_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_112_DEATH_04.wav Inconceivable!

RAVENOUS KRAKEN.name: Ravenous Kraken
RAVENOUS KRAKEN.flavorText: He's witewally hitting the squiddy wight now.

FRANTIC HIPPOGRYPH.name: Frantic Hippogryph
FRANTIC HIPPOGRYPH.flavorText: It's killed and it'll kill again!

BURNING HEART.name: Burning Heart
BURNING HEART.flavorText: A 100% ethically sourced fire elemental heart is very hard to come by. This one definitely wasn't.

CAVE HYDRA.name: Cave Hydra
CAVE HYDRA.flavorText: Can be upgraded into a Cave Lurker.

IRONFORGE PORTAL.name: Ironforge Portal
IRONFORGE PORTAL.flavorText: Come to beautiful Ironforge! Where irons are forged and the forges are iron!

TANGLEFUR MYSTIC.name: Tanglefur Mystic
TANGLEFUR MYSTIC.flavorText: Doom! Only doom for you! But pay good tip, maybe less doom.

APOTHECARY'S CARAVAN.name: Apothecary's Caravan
APOTHECARY'S CARAVAN.flavorText: If you won't bring out your dead, we'll bring the dead to you.

SPIRIT OF THE TIDES.name: Spirit of the Tides
SPIRIT OF THE TIDES.flavorText: Cleans the ocean better than any store-brand competitor - guaranteed or your Mana back!

RUSTY RECYCLER.name: Rusty Recycler
RUSTY RECYCLER.flavorText: Ironic. It could recycle others, but not itself.

CORPSE FARM.name: Corpse Farm
CORPSE FARM.flavorText: It ain't much, but it's dishonest work.

HIPPOGRYPH.name: Hippogryph
HIPPOGRYPH.flavorText: Known for its ferocious grace, the hippogryph is a truly majestic creature. Except when molting.

TALENTED ARCANIST.name: Talented Arcanist
TALENTED ARCANIST.flavorText: "Ey mon, you don't get this good just on raw talent ... but it helps."

CUTPURSE.name: Cutpurse
CUTPURSE.flavorText: He has a giant collection of purses now. One for every outfit!

SEEDCLOUD BUCKLER.name: Seedcloud Buckler
SEEDCLOUD BUCKLER.flavorText: A shield to some, a frisbee to others (mainly dogs).

SPIRIT HEALER.name: Spirit Healer
SPIRIT HEALER.flavorText: "You again? What did I tell you about trying to fight ALL the quilboars."

HEMATURGE.name: Hematurge
HEMATURGE.flavorText: She's here to PUMP! YOU UP!

EXPLOSIVE EVOLUTION.name: Explosive Evolution
EXPLOSIVE EVOLUTION.flavorText: Let's give a big hand for goblin experimentation!

AMULET OF UNDYING.name: Amulet of Undying
AMULET OF UNDYING.flavorText: Didn't seem to work out too well for this guy.

ANCIENT TOTEM.name: Ancient Totem
ANCIENT TOTEM.flavorText: This is SO much cuter than Tinyfin.

OASIS SNAPJAW.name: Oasis Snapjaw
OASIS SNAPJAW.flavorText: His dreams of flying and breathing fire like his idol will never be realized.

SHADOWREAPER ANDUIN.name: Shadowreaper Anduin
SHADOWREAPER ANDUIN.flavorText: "I will tell you what Velen never taught me. Whosoever stands before the Light… inevitably casts a shadow."

GADGETZAN FERRYMAN.name: Gadgetzan Ferryman
GADGETZAN FERRYMAN.flavorText: Is it just me, or is there something fishy about that ferryman?

BARITONE IMP.name: Baritone Imp
BARITONE IMP.flavorText: He used to be an epic sax guy, but now he's just a common.

OGRE NINJA.name: Ogre Ninja
OGRE NINJA.flavorText: He didn't have the grades to get into ninja school, but his dad pulled some strings.

MALFUNCTION.name: Malfunction
MALFUNCTION.flavorText: Bug Report: This card works perfectly.

ARCANE SHOT.name: Arcane Shot
ARCANE SHOT.flavorText: Magi conjured arcane arrows to sell to hunters, until hunters learned just enough magic to do it themselves. The resulting loss of jobs sent Stormwind into a minor recession.

ALL TERRAIN VOIDHOUND.name: All Terrain Voidhound
ALL TERRAIN VOIDHOUND.flavorText: 4 claw drive, independent joint suspension AND a 7 mana warranty? Where do I sign?

HI HO SILVERWING.name: Hi Ho Silverwing
HI HO SILVERWING.flavorText: I swear this minion had 3000 Attack at one point!

FATESPINNER.name: Fatespinner
FATESPINNER.flavorText: Her clothing? Pure silk, of course.

RUNI, TIME EXPLORER.name: Runi, Time Explorer
RUNI, TIME EXPLORER.flavorText: In the future, Xyrella's daughter would become a hero of time, but Nozdormu needed her now, for this moment.

TIP THE SCALES.name: Tip the Scales
TIP THE SCALES.flavorText: Hold on, I need to get some murlocs to weigh in on this.

SUNSCALE RAPTOR.name: Sunscale Raptor
SUNSCALE RAPTOR.flavorText: And they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they—

JEWEL OF N'ZOTH.name: Jewel of N'Zoth
JEWEL OF N'ZOTH.flavorText: This coveted gem calls for you to free it… and unleash an inescapable prison.

THUNDERHEAD.name: Thunderhead
THUNDERHEAD.flavorText: Most of his friends are still Metalheads.

FLAG RUNNER.name: Flag Runner
FLAG RUNNER.flavorText: I see your argument, but…do you have a flag?

COGMASTER'S WRENCH.name: Cogmaster's Wrench
COGMASTER'S WRENCH.flavorText: For tightening cogs and smashin' troggs!

GRIM PATRON.name: Grim Patron
GRIM PATRON.flavorText: If you love getting your face punched, come to the Grim Guzzler!

POSSE POSSESSION.name: Posse Possession
POSSE POSSESSION.flavorText: Keep your friends close, your enemies closer, and your shadows at gunpoint.

KING MUKLA.name: King Mukla
KING MUKLA.flavorText: King Mukla wanders Jaguero Isle, searching for love.

TREASURE DISTRIBUTOR.name: Treasure Distributor
TREASURE DISTRIBUTOR.flavorText: As the illiterate pirates always say: There is no 'I' in 'piracy'.

ALIEN ENCOUNTERS.name: Alien Encounters
ALIEN ENCOUNTERS.flavorText: Close encounters of the cuddly kind.

EVIL CONSCRIPTER.name: EVIL Conscripter
EVIL CONSCRIPTER.flavorText: Kobold! There’s a place you can handle I said kobold! When you’re short in the candle Cast a spell with the E! V! I! L!

FYE, THE SETTING SUN.name: Fye, the Setting Sun
FYE, THE SETTING SUN.flavorText: There is a dragon way down in Bloodrock They call the Setting Sun

SECOND-RATE BRUISER.name: Second-Rate Bruiser
SECOND-RATE BRUISER.flavorText: He'll be a first-rate bruiser once he gets used to his contacts.

WOODLAND WONDERS.name: Woodland Wonders
WOODLAND WONDERS.flavorText: Is this a standup fight or another bug hunt?

CROSSROADS GOSSIPER.name: Crossroads Gossiper
CROSSROADS GOSSIPER.flavorText: Not afraid to spill the tea.

FACE COLLECTOR.name: Face Collector
FACE COLLECTOR.flavorText: “I’ll trade you a Malfurion for an Anduin.”

THE EXODAR.name: The Exodar
THE EXODAR.flavorText: Limitless potential! Boundless hope! Fourth rate space insurance.

AVIAN WATCHER.name: Avian Watcher
AVIAN WATCHER.flavorText: He mostly watches light romantic comedies.

BLOODSAIL CORSAIR.name: Bloodsail Corsair
BLOODSAIL CORSAIR.flavorText: Every pirate uses the same four digits to access Automated Gold Dispensers. It's called the "Pirate's Code".

CHAOTIC TENDRIL.name: Chaotic Tendril
CHAOTIC TENDRIL.flavorText: "So are you good, evil, or neutral?" "Just chaotic."

TOME TAMPERING.name: Tome Tampering
TOME TAMPERING.flavorText: An overdue book calls for a do-over.

SOULBURNER VARIA.name: Soulburner Varia
SOULBURNER VARIA.flavorText: Captain's Log. 8/11/2023 There are 60 minutes remaining until the Flavor Text is due. It is Friday at 4 PM. We are out of stamina and ideas. Please send funnies, punnies, quippies, or your finest hahas. - The Design Team

DRAENEI TOTEMCARVER.name: Draenei Totemcarver
DRAENEI TOTEMCARVER.flavorText: It's nice to find a real craftsman in this day and age of mass-produced totems.

STITCHED CREATION.name: Stitched Creation
STITCHED CREATION.flavorText: To defend Naxxramas from the oncoming adventurers, the Scourge created a monstrosity the world had never seen before: an abomination wearing clothes!!

FRIGID SNOBOLD.name: Frigid Snobold
FRIGID SNOBOLD.flavorText: Ironically, the natural enemy of the snobold is THE CANDLE.

BOGGSPINE KNUCKLES.name: Boggspine Knuckles
BOGGSPINE KNUCKLES.flavorText: I would NOT want to put my hand in there. It's... SQUISHY.

SLEEP WITH THE FISHES.name: Sleep with the Fishes
SLEEP WITH THE FISHES.flavorText: If you're sleeping with the fishes, we highly suggest not bringing an electric blanket.

BLOODREAVER GUL'DAN.name: Bloodreaver Gul'dan
BLOODREAVER GUL'DAN.flavorText: "Still you refuse to bend your knee? None can escape death, you old fool. And in death… all will serve me…"

ANNOY-O-TRON.name: Annoy-o-Tron
ANNOY-O-TRON.flavorText: The inventor of the Annoy-o-Tron was immediately expelled from Tinkerschool, Tinkertown, and was eventually exiled from the Eastern Kingdoms altogether.

SHINING SENTINEL.name: Shining Sentinel
SHINING SENTINEL.flavorText: OMG, I FINALLY GOT A SHINING SENTINEL AFTER 3 PHASES AND 8192 RESETS!!!!!

SLEEPY RESIDENT.name: Sleepy Resident
SLEEPY RESIDENT.flavorText: Shouldn’t this be a Priest card?

PRIESTESS OF ELUNE.name: Priestess of Elune
PRIESTESS OF ELUNE.flavorText: If she threatens to "moon" you, it's not what you think.

KEENEYE SPOTTER.name: Keeneye Spotter
KEENEYE SPOTTER.flavorText: "No Rexxar, not the face, the minion right there. Yep that one righ-- Rexxar no!"

PHANTOM MILITIA.name: Phantom Militia
PHANTOM MILITIA.flavorText: Recruited from the Gilnean opera house.

DIMENSIONAL RIPPER.name: Dimensional Ripper
DIMENSIONAL RIPPER.flavorText: The first dimensional ripper had a point. The second fell flat. The THIRD one really started to take shape!

BRAIN FREEZE.name: Brain Freeze
BRAIN FREEZE.flavorText: "The professor called on me, and I totally froze!"

PEON.name: Peon
PEON.flavorText: Joke's on the peon: the job's never done.

EDWIN, DEFIAS KINGPIN.name: Edwin, Defias Kingpin
EDWIN, DEFIAS KINGPIN.flavorText: He’s not going to tear down the walls of Stormwind sitting around in the Hall of Fame.

SHADOWSTEP.name: Shadowstep
SHADOWSTEP.flavorText: Rogue dance troops will sometimes Shadowstep away at the end of a performance. Crowds love it.

EARTHQUAKE.name: Earthquake
EARTHQUAKE.flavorText: Shake it, sh-sh-sh-shake it like a Kalimdor fissure.

LUSHWATER SCOUT.name: Lushwater Scout
LUSHWATER SCOUT.flavorText: Only knows how to play "Careless Murgl" and "Mrgl Mrgl Little Star."

TRAIL MIX.name: Trail Mix
TRAIL MIX.flavorText: You can tell this is an escapist fantasy game because there are no raisins.

NEXUS-CHAMPION SARAAD.name: Nexus-Champion Saraad
NEXUS-CHAMPION SARAAD.flavorText: The ethereals have their own jousting tournament, and Saraad is the reigning champion. Also he won the ethereal hot dog eating contest.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/bd/VO_AT_127_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_127_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/ca/VO_AT_127_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_127_ATTACK_02.wav You had your chance.
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/64/VO_AT_127_DEATH_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_127_DEATH_04.wav <death sound>

GRAND MAGISTER ROMMATH.name: Grand Magister Rommath
GRAND MAGISTER ROMMATH.flavorText: A powerful mage known for his proficiencies in Fire, Frost, and Algebra.

DARKSCALE HEALER.name: Darkscale Healer
DARKSCALE HEALER.flavorText: Healing is just something she does in her free time. It's more of a hobby really.

FROSTBITE.name: Frostbite
FROSTBITE.flavorText: The sad reality of a raging toothpaste addiction.

RESEARCH PROJECT.name: Research Project
RESEARCH PROJECT.flavorText: Abstract: Analyzing systemic applications of coldlight data sets vis-a-vis shuffle-related paradigms. Conclusion: Yay, cards!

\"HEALTH\" DRINK.name: "Health" Drink
\"HEALTH\" DRINK.flavorText: Do not exceed recommend daily serving size of 0 grams.

ABYSSAL WAVE.name: Abyssal Wave
ABYSSAL WAVE.flavorText: Often followed up with a chasmic handshake.

GORM THE WORLDEATER.name: Gorm the Worldeater
GORM THE WORLDEATER.flavorText: His diet consists of entire WORLDS! Because moons upset his tummy.

CHAIN LIGHTNING (RANK 1).name: Chain Lightning (Rank 1)
CHAIN LIGHTNING (RANK 1).flavorText: Still better than receiving a chain letter.

GRIMSCALE ORACLE.name: Grimscale Oracle
GRIMSCALE ORACLE.flavorText: These are the brainy murlocs. It turns out that doesn’t mean much.

METAMORFIN.name: Metamorfin
METAMORFIN.flavorText: Always wanted to be the green ranger.

SOLAR ECLIPSE.name: Solar Eclipse
SOLAR ECLIPSE.flavorText: When the Moon is between the Sun and the Azeroth.

FACELESS SHAMBLER.name: Faceless Shambler
FACELESS SHAMBLER.flavorText: "What is that thing?!" "I'm not sure, but it seems to be sort of Ysera shaped."

TWISTED PACK.name: Twisted Pack
TWISTED PACK.flavorText: Twist it! Rip it! Play it!

ECHO OF MEDIVH.name: Echo of Medivh
ECHO OF MEDIVH.flavorText: Medivh's echo haunts Karazhan, eternally cheating at chess and Hearthstone.

ENVOY OF PROSPERITY.name: Envoy of Prosperity
ENVOY OF PROSPERITY.flavorText: "Our prosperity is beyond a shadow of a doubt!"

DESPERATE MEASURES.name: Desperate Measures
DESPERATE MEASURES.flavorText: Desperate times call for disparate secrets.

UNYIELDING VINDICATOR.name: Unyielding Vindicator
UNYIELDING VINDICATOR.flavorText: Strike and smash, until it is done.

TRANSFER STUDENT.name: Transfer Student
TRANSFER STUDENT.flavorText: Oh, the places you'll go! There is so much to fight! There are boards to be explored. There are dreams to take flight.

IREBOUND BRUTE.name: Irebound Brute
IREBOUND BRUTE.flavorText: "You don't understand… ogres are an untapped market for vengeance and hatred!"

SABRETOOTH STALKER.name: Sabretooth Stalker
SABRETOOTH STALKER.flavorText: It's gotten a bit long in the tooth.

LUNAR ECLIPSE.name: Lunar Eclipse
LUNAR ECLIPSE.flavorText: When the Azeroth is between the Sun and the Moon.

SNAP FREEZE.name: Snap Freeze
SNAP FREEZE.flavorText: Lick the ice block. I triple-double-dog-dare-you.

MOSH'OGG ENFORCER.name: Mosh'Ogg Enforcer
MOSH'OGG ENFORCER.flavorText: Can’t break the rules if you can’t read ‘em.

BULL DOZER.name: Bull Dozer
BULL DOZER.flavorText: Leave them alone for two minutes and they go right into sleep mode.

LAY DOWN THE LAW.name: Lay Down the Law
LAY DOWN THE LAW.flavorText: The official term for "Because I said so!".

CIRCUS AMALGAM.name: Circus Amalgam
CIRCUS AMALGAM.flavorText: Who needs a petting zoo when you have all the creatures right here?!

ZOLA THE GORGON.name: Zola the Gorgon
ZOLA THE GORGON.flavorText: Her name seems a bit cheesy.

MORTUARY MACHINE.name: Mortuary Machine
MORTUARY MACHINE.flavorText: The ankle bone's connected to the shin bone. The knuckle bone's connected to the... eh, it'll be fine.

EXPLORE UN'GORO.name: Explore Un'Goro
EXPLORE UN'GORO.flavorText: It turns out cards DO grow on trees!

DUNEMAUL SHAMAN.name: Dunemaul Shaman
DUNEMAUL SHAMAN.flavorText: He just closes his eyes and goes for it. Raarararrrarar!

YOGG-SARON, HOPE'S END.name: Yogg-Saron, Hope's End
YOGG-SARON, HOPE'S END.flavorText: I spell your doom... Y-O-U-R D-O-O-M!

HALF-TIME SCAVENGER.name: Half-Time Scavenger
HALF-TIME SCAVENGER.flavorText: One player's trash is another's “Best In Slot”.

BLOOD GUARD.name: Blood Guard
BLOOD GUARD.flavorText: Has never donated blood and doesn’t plan on ever doing so.

COMPETITIVE SPIRIT.name: Competitive Spirit
COMPETITIVE SPIRIT.flavorText: Competition can be an inspiration to improve oneself. Or kill all the competitors.

ESCAPE POD.name: Escape Pod
ESCAPE POD.flavorText: You can only have two in your deck because we are confident that the Draenei will never run into any dire situations that would warrant any more!

SINSTONE GRAVEYARD.name: Sinstone Graveyard
SINSTONE GRAVEYARD.flavorText: A graveyard in the realm of the dead; a bit redundant, don't you think?

CAGEMATCH CUSTODIAN.name: Cagematch Custodian
CAGEMATCH CUSTODIAN.flavorText: Cleans up after a dust up.

SHROOMSCAVATE.name: Shroomscavate
SHROOMSCAVATE.flavorText: As Globb shroominated on his situation, toiling endlessly in the mushroom mines, he came to the startling realization. His boss wasn't a very fun guy.

CRYSTALLINE ORACLE.name: Crystalline Oracle
CRYSTALLINE ORACLE.flavorText: Being made of light has its disadvantages, but at least it's always looking on the bright side.

LESSER AMETHYST SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Amethyst Spellstone
LESSER AMETHYST SPELLSTONE.flavorText: A purple stone Azari carved For dark hearts, craving, power-starved. The first to bow, the warlock Rin, Embraced the darkness, slew her kin.

REMIXED TOTEMCARVER.name: Remixed Totemcarver
REMIXED TOTEMCARVER.flavorText: Music always sounds better on old, wooden speakers.

FLIK SKYSHIV.name: Flik Skyshiv
FLIK SKYSHIV.flavorText: Junior explorers scan the night sky in fear of her candle’s flame!

MURLOC KNIGHT.name: Murloc Knight
MURLOC KNIGHT.flavorText: Hee hee! Look at his cute little feet.

HIGH NOON DUELIST.name: High Noon Duelist
HIGH NOON DUELIST.flavorText: "My ultimate is rea- ah, errr, I mean, I have enough Mana."

TWILIGHT GEOMANCER.name: Twilight Geomancer
TWILIGHT GEOMANCER.flavorText: "Ok C'Thun, repeat after me: 'Your mother was a hamster.'"

RECOMBOBULATOR.name: Recombobulator
RECOMBOBULATOR.flavorText: For when you didn’t combobulate quite right the first time around.

KABAL CHEMIST.name: Kabal Chemist
KABAL CHEMIST.flavorText: Sure you could have that Polymorph potion, but wouldn't you rather have this mystery potion? It could be anything. Even a Polymorph potion!

RADAR DETECTOR.name: Radar Detector
RADAR DETECTOR.flavorText: "Yup! I definitely don't know how to read radar."

BENEATH THE GROUNDS.name: Beneath the Grounds
BENEATH THE GROUNDS.flavorText: Can you hold these eggs for just a second? I promise they're not full of giant enraged undead spider things.

BUSY PEON.name: Busy Peon
BUSY PEON.flavorText: Chopping wood, mining gold and repairing buildings? None of these pursuits called to Grob...pencil doodling on wood was his true labor of love.

EDWIN VANCLEEF.name: Edwin VanCleef
EDWIN VANCLEEF.flavorText: He led the Stonemasons in the reconstruction of Stormwind, and when the nobles refused to pay, he founded the Defias Brotherhood to, well, deconstruct Stormwind.

BIOLOGY PROJECT.name: Biology Project
BIOLOGY PROJECT.flavorText: Step 1: Grow giant evil strawberry. Step 2: ???? Step 3: Rule Azeroth!

GREEN-THUMB GARDENER.name: Green-Thumb Gardener
GREEN-THUMB GARDENER.flavorText: Sometimes all a plant needs is, like, A LOT of water.

BLOOD IMP.name: Blood Imp
BLOOD IMP.flavorText: Imps are content to hide and viciously taunt everyone nearby.

SANDHOOF WATERBEARER.name: Sandhoof Waterbearer
SANDHOOF WATERBEARER.flavorText: Used to carrying for his team.

MYSTERIOUS VISITOR.name: Mysterious Visitor
MYSTERIOUS VISITOR.flavorText: Dave, we can tell this letter is fake - it's in your handwriting. And take off that stupid hood, you're embarrassing us.

NEPTULON THE TIDEHUNTER.name: Neptulon the Tidehunter
NEPTULON THE TIDEHUNTER.flavorText: Neptulon, tired of filling hands, is now throwing hands.

THE HARVESTER OF ENVY.name: The Harvester of Envy
THE HARVESTER OF ENVY.flavorText: "Ah, permission shmermission! You can borrow anything you want, anytime, as long as if you give it back before it's missed. Everyone knows that! Right?"

VILESPINE SLAYER.name: Vilespine Slayer
VILESPINE SLAYER.flavorText: 'Cause slayers gonna slay, slay, slay, slay, slay.

RAISE DEAD.name: Raise Dead
RAISE DEAD.flavorText: Technically, it’s just really late healing.

OH MY YOGG!.name: Oh My Yogg!
OH MY YOGG!.flavorText: Many wonders lie within, but they are not mere toys when your mind is their plaything.

MOLTEN BLADE.name: Molten Blade
MOLTEN BLADE.flavorText: It’s a sword! It’s a knife! It’s a swizzle-stick!

ENTER THE COLISEUM.name: Enter the Coliseum
ENTER THE COLISEUM.flavorText: You have to get past the vendors first. So many are lost to shopping...

RIMESCALE SIREN.name: Rimescale Siren
RIMESCALE SIREN.flavorText: She will freeze the Scourge dead in their tracks.

DRAGONSLAYER.name: Dragonslayer
DRAGONSLAYER.flavorText: A pair of stout dwarves nearly averted the Cataclysm.

REMOTE-CONTROLLED GOLEM.name: Remote-Controlled Golem
REMOTE-CONTROLLED GOLEM.flavorText: Someone got a little too excited inventing a can opener.

POUNCE.name: Pounce
POUNCE.flavorText: Comes with an overwhelming urge to jump into the nearest open box.

PARADE LEADER.name: Parade Leader
PARADE LEADER.flavorText: He's always going to reign on his parade.

SKULL OF GUL'DAN.name: Skull of Gul'dan
SKULL OF GUL'DAN.flavorText: A fellow of evil possessed, of most devious shadow. He hath turned on his kin a thousand times, and now, how abhorred in all imagination he is!

DEATHBORNE.name: Deathborne
DEATHBORNE.flavorText: Kel'Thuzad thinks adding a silent 'e' at the end of words makes them sound cooler.

DARK BARGAIN.name: Dark Bargain
DARK BARGAIN.flavorText: A prime example of lose-lose negotiating.

WRETCHED EXILE.name: Wretched Exile
WRETCHED EXILE.flavorText: If you're cold, they're cold. Let your wretches inside.

SILTFIN SPIRITWALKER.name: Siltfin Spiritwalker
SILTFIN SPIRITWALKER.flavorText: The elements respond to anyone who calls them for a worthy cause, even if you call them by yelling, "MRGHRGLGLGL!"

ELVEN MINSTREL.name: Elven Minstrel
ELVEN MINSTREL.flavorText: "After that gig in Hamlin went south, I swore off rats."

NATURAL CAUSES.name: Natural Causes
NATURAL CAUSES.flavorText: What if the suspect was framed? What if the murder weapon was... a plant?

DEATH METAL KNIGHT.name: Death Metal Knight
DEATH METAL KNIGHT.flavorText: He prefers listening to bands dead rather than live.

GLIDE.name: Glide
GLIDE.flavorText: "Come with me, and you'll see, a whole new hand of possibly the same cards."

SHU'MA.name: Shu'ma
SHU'MA.flavorText: How to tell your mother to go away.

KNIFE JUGGLER.name: Knife Juggler
KNIFE JUGGLER.flavorText: Ambitious Knife Jugglers sometimes graduate to Bomb Jugglers. They never last long enough to make it onto a card though.

NIGHT PROWLER.name: Night Prowler
NIGHT PROWLER.flavorText: Listen to the mew-sic of the night.

HOGGER, DOOM OF ELWYNN.name: Hogger, Doom of Elwynn
HOGGER, DOOM OF ELWYNN.flavorText: When C'thun went to sleep, he checked under his bed for Hogger.

INFECTIOUS GHOUL.name: Infectious Ghoul
INFECTIOUS GHOUL.flavorText: They call him that because of his laughter! Also his plague.

INFINITIZE THE MAXITUDE.name: Infinitize the Maxitude
INFINITIZE THE MAXITUDE.flavorText: When your music is instrumental, it doesn't matter if the words make no sense.

COLD FEET.name: Cold Feet
COLD FEET.flavorText: Looks like some of the dancers still need to warm up.

IMP KING RAFAAM.name: Imp King Rafaam
IMP KING RAFAAM.flavorText: Not even death can stop Rafaam from pursuing a life of crime.

VIOLET WARDEN.name: Violet Warden
VIOLET WARDEN.flavorText: He's got magic, a shield, and an unwavering obsession with the color purple.

WARTBRINGER.name: Wartbringer
WARTBRINGER.flavorText: “Does she cause them with magic, or just…like have a bucket she brings with her?”

DOOMCALLER.name: Doomcaller
DOOMCALLER.flavorText: "Hello, is Doom there? No? Can I leave a message?"

LESSER SAPPHIRE SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Sapphire Spellstone
LESSER SAPPHIRE SPELLSTONE.flavorText: A stone of blue, embraced with glee By murloc lords beneath the sea Soon numberless they swarmed the shore First two, then four, then more...and more...

TORGHAST CUSTODIAN.name: Torghast Custodian
TORGHAST CUSTODIAN.flavorText: Why is it a common? Well we couldn't make it a LEGendary minion!

DEATHSPEAKER.name: Deathspeaker
DEATHSPEAKER.flavorText: It helps to speak really, really loud.

BEASTSTALKER TAVISH.name: Beaststalker Tavish
BEASTSTALKER TAVISH.flavorText: Tavish left home to forge his own path. But it still led him back to Alterac to kick some Frostwolf butt.

CARVING CHISEL.name: Carving Chisel
CARVING CHISEL.flavorText: Look at your stone. Visualize the totem within. Then gently...

BARON RIVENDARE.name: Baron Rivendare
BARON RIVENDARE.flavorText: There used to be five Horsemen but one of them left because a job opened up in the deadmines and the benefits were better.

WALKING DEAD.name: Walking Dead
WALKING DEAD.flavorText: Watch out for the Scourge, KAAARRRRLLLL!

FACELESS MANIPULATOR.name: Faceless Manipulator
FACELESS MANIPULATOR.flavorText: The Faceless Ones are servants of Yogg-Saron, and they feed on fear. Right now they are feeding on your fear of accidentally disenchanting all your good cards.

MANA WRAITH.name: Mana Wraith
MANA WRAITH.flavorText: They come out at night to eat leftover mana crystals. "Mmmmmm," they say.

FLASH SALE.name: Flash Sale
FLASH SALE.flavorText: HOW LOW! HOW LOW! HOW LOW!

HELM OF HUMILIATION.name: Helm of Humiliation
HELM OF HUMILIATION.flavorText: <whispers> "...and your father was a Murloc too."

HIDDEN OASIS.name: Hidden Oasis
HIDDEN OASIS.flavorText: Amazing that it's been hidden, given the twenty-foot treant splashing around in it.

TAINTHEART TORMENTER.name: Taintheart Tormenter
TAINTHEART TORMENTER.flavorText: Oh boo hoo, did someone's World Tree burn down?

FEARSOME DOOMGUARD.name: Fearsome Doomguard
FEARSOME DOOMGUARD.flavorText: They were originally called Cuddleguards, but they were not inspiring the proper amount of fear.

SNOOZIN' ZOOKEEPER.name: Snoozin' Zookeeper
SNOOZIN' ZOOKEEPER.flavorText: You snooze, you lose (track of a very large and hungry panther).

SING-ALONG BUDDY.name: Sing-Along Buddy
SING-ALONG BUDDY.flavorText: One of the buttons makes you sound JUST like Ragnaros. BY FIRE BE HEARD!

POTION VENDOR.name: Potion Vendor
POTION VENDOR.flavorText: Everyone gets two because that’s all she can hold.

GOBLIN BLASTMAGE.name: Goblin Blastmage
GOBLIN BLASTMAGE.flavorText: If you can't find a bomb to throw, just pick up any goblin invention and throw that.

SUNWALKER.name: Sunwalker
SUNWALKER.flavorText: She doesn’t ACTUALLY walk on the Sun. It's just a name. Don’t worry!

WAXADRED.name: Waxadred
WAXADRED.flavorText: Waxadred the dragon fought for his king, frolicking through the fields melting everything!

GROTESQUE DRAGONHAWK.name: Grotesque Dragonhawk
GROTESQUE DRAGONHAWK.flavorText: They say that "grotesque is in the eye of the beholder," but that's just because they've never seen a Grotesque Dragonhawk. Yikes!

BACKSTREET LEPER.name: Backstreet Leper
BACKSTREET LEPER.flavorText: Quit playing games with his heart. And his fingers. And foot. It's rude.

STAMPEDE.name: Stampede
STAMPEDE.flavorText: Many hunters long for the pitter-patter of enormous feet.

THE NAMELESS ONE.name: The Nameless One
THE NAMELESS ONE.flavorText: Used to be called " , the Nameless," but everyone got confused.

MASS HYSTERIA.name: Mass Hysteria
MASS HYSTERIA.flavorText: Black Friday gets worse every year.

FORGE OF WILLS.name: Forge of Wills
FORGE OF WILLS.flavorText: Standing in the Forge of Wills fills you with a sense of DETERMINATION.

SNOW SHREDDER.name: Snow Shredder
SNOW SHREDDER.flavorText: "Yeah dude, snowboarding is like, totally safe. I've only ever been injured once."

SINISTER STRIKE.name: Sinister Strike
SINISTER STRIKE.flavorText: There's something about this strike that just feels off. Sinister, even.

SNAPDRAGON.name: Snapdragon
SNAPDRAGON.flavorText: Good synergy with Crackledragon, not so much with Popdragon.

IMMOLATION AURA.name: Immolation Aura
IMMOLATION AURA.flavorText: If you can't take the heat, stop standing in the fire.

VALIDATED DOOMSAYER.name: Validated Doomsayer
VALIDATED DOOMSAYER.flavorText: Really feels good about himself and is in a much better place now. But… he sure does miss piloting those shredders.

REPLICAT-O-TRON.name: Replicat-o-tron
REPLICAT-O-TRON.flavorText: According to the Boom Labs sales brochure, it "impractically makes itself!"

INVENTOR BOOM.name: Inventor Boom
INVENTOR BOOM.flavorText: The best part of inventing stuff is blowing it up!

LESSER EMERALD SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Emerald Spellstone
LESSER EMERALD SPELLSTONE.flavorText: An emerald stone for Tauren hands Who sought its strength to save their lands Their tribes now lost, their rage released Who’s hunting now? And who’s the beast?

WORGEN GREASER.name: Worgen Greaser
WORGEN GREASER.flavorText: Hair products are 79% of his monthly budget.

PARAGON OF LIGHT.name: Paragon of Light
PARAGON OF LIGHT.flavorText: She’s all fun and games until someone rings that stupid bell.

IGNEOUS LAVAGORGER.name: Igneous Lavagorger
IGNEOUS LAVAGORGER.flavorText: Lava shark, doo doo doo doo doo doo.

DARKSHIRE ALCHEMIST.name: Darkshire Alchemist
DARKSHIRE ALCHEMIST.flavorText: The secret ingredient: liquified funnel cake.

INZAH.name: Inzah
INZAH.flavorText: Inzah plays the trumpet, saxophone, piano, guitar, AND bass. No wonder he's always so overloaded!

CULT NEOPHYTE.name: Cult Neophyte
CULT NEOPHYTE.flavorText: Make a new recruit's deficiencies your efficiencies.

TREESPEAKER.name: Treespeaker
TREESPEAKER.flavorText: Honestly, his delivery is a little wooden.

INSIGHT.name: Insight
INSIGHT.flavorText: Shouldn't the eyes be facing backwards for insight?

ARCANE NULLIFIER X-21.name: Arcane Nullifier X-21
ARCANE NULLIFIER X-21.flavorText: There was some hard talk between gnome magi and engineers about inventing this mech.

GIBBERING REJECT.name: Gibbering Reject
GIBBERING REJECT.flavorText: Don't get it wet or feed it after midnight.

DRAGONBLIGHT CULTIST.name: Dragonblight Cultist
DRAGONBLIGHT CULTIST.flavorText: Galakrond would be extra mad if he was resurrected with gnaw marks on his bones.

KEZAN MYSTIC.name: Kezan Mystic
KEZAN MYSTIC.flavorText: They pretend to be wise and enlightened, but they mostly just hate to be left out of a secret.

TENTACLES FOR ARMS.name: Tentacles for Arms
TENTACLES FOR ARMS.flavorText: That's right. Garrosh just slapped you to death with a tentacle.

NECRIUM APOTHECARY.name: Necrium Apothecary
NECRIUM APOTHECARY.flavorText: Necrium: Get the afterlife without the aftertaste!

FAR SIGHT.name: Far Sight
FAR SIGHT.flavorText: Drek'thar can't see, but he can see. You know what I mean? It's ok if you don't.

SCORP-O-MATIC.name: Scorp-o-matic
SCORP-O-MATIC.flavorText: Back in my day, we had to manually scorp.

KAYN SUNFURY.name: Kayn Sunfury
KAYN SUNFURY.flavorText: "Armor and heals may slow my zeal, but fel and glaives excite me!"

ALDOR PEACEKEEPER.name: Aldor Peacekeeper
ALDOR PEACEKEEPER.flavorText: The Aldor hate two things: the Scryers and smooth jazz.

ARA'LON.name: Ara'lon
ARA'LON.flavorText: If I had a nickel for every time a Hunter Legendary minion in Castle Nathria summoned three different companions, I'd have two nickels - which isn't a lot, but it's weird that it happened twice.

SHADOWFLAME.name: Shadowflame
SHADOWFLAME.flavorText: Start with a powerful minion and stir in Shadowflame and you have a good time!

TOXIC SEWER OOZE.name: Toxic Sewer Ooze
TOXIC SEWER OOZE.flavorText: When Sergeant Sally shows up unexpectedly, DO NOT FLUSH YOUR MANA CRYSTALS DOWN THE TOILET.

IMPRISONED SUNGILL.name: Imprisoned Sungill
IMPRISONED SUNGILL.flavorText: Imprisoned for ten thousand years! Not because it's a demon. Because of the dancing.

CAPTAIN'S PARROT.name: Captain's Parrot
CAPTAIN'S PARROT.flavorText: Pirates and Parrots go together like Virmen and Carrots.

FOE REAPER 4000.name: Foe Reaper 4000
FOE REAPER 4000.flavorText: Foe reaping is really not so different from harvest reaping, at the end of the day.

CRYOPRESERVATION.name: Cryopreservation
CRYOPRESERVATION.flavorText: Remember to take the elementals out of the freezer before Mom gets home!

PLAGUED PROTODRAKE.name: Plagued Protodrake
PLAGUED PROTODRAKE.flavorText: "What’s in the drake?! WHAT’S IN THE DRAKE?"

OGRE WARMAUL.name: Ogre Warmaul
OGRE WARMAUL.flavorText: Simple, misguided, and incredibly dangerous. You know, like most things ogre.

SILVERWARE GOLEM.name: Silverware Golem
SILVERWARE GOLEM.flavorText: From the secret research labs of the Swiss Army.

KHADGAR.name: Khadgar
KHADGAR.flavorText: "What do you call two minions summoned at once? Twinions, haha! Wait... where are you going?"

MURLOC HOLMES.name: Murloc Holmes
MURLOC HOLMES.flavorText: When you have eliminated the imfroggable, whatever remains, however uncroakable, must be the truth.

TAKE TO THE SKIES.name: Take to the Skies
TAKE TO THE SKIES.flavorText: This is one step above reaching for the skies.

TRAM OPERATOR.name: Tram Operator
TRAM OPERATOR.flavorText: The guy in the back is screaming… because the train ride is so fun!

ETHEREAL ARCANIST.name: Ethereal Arcanist
ETHEREAL ARCANIST.flavorText: The ethereals are wrapped in cloth to give form to their non-corporeal bodies. Also because it's nice and soft.

EXCAVATED EVIL.name: Excavated Evil
EXCAVATED EVIL.flavorText: MOM! DAD! DON'T TOUCH IT! IT'S EVIL!!!!!!

DOCTOR HOLLI'DAE.name: Doctor Holli'dae
DOCTOR HOLLI'DAE.flavorText: If anything can heal the Badlands, it is the power of frogs!

CARELESS CRAFTER.name: Careless Crafter
CARELESS CRAFTER.flavorText: How about YOU try folding paper with only three fingers!?

STARFALL.name: Starfall
STARFALL.flavorText: Is the sky falling? Yes. Yes it is.

SPREADING PLAGUE.name: Spreading Plague
SPREADING PLAGUE.flavorText: In the past, plagues were spread by mice or fleas. These days they're spread by elves.

TWILIGHT WHELP.name: Twilight Whelp
TWILIGHT WHELP.flavorText: The twilight whelps are basically magic-vampires. Despite this, they are not a reference to any popular series of novels.

UNDERBELLY OOZE.name: Underbelly Ooze
UNDERBELLY OOZE.flavorText: It's always accepting of the less successful adventurers.

AMITUS, THE PEACEKEEPER.name: Amitus, the Peacekeeper
AMITUS, THE PEACEKEEPER.flavorText: As a champion of harmony, Amitus abstained from the Pantheon's many conflicts until one day, shortly after the corruption of Sargeras, she vanished altogether.

ASPHYXIATE.name: Asphyxiate
ASPHYXIATE.flavorText: I find your abundance of Attack disturbing.

FELWALKER.name: Felwalker
FELWALKER.flavorText: How it feels to chew Fel Gum.

BACKFIRE.name: Backfire
BACKFIRE.flavorText: "That's the last time I let an imp spit gasoline into my car."

SILVERBACK PATRIARCH.name: Silverback Patriarch
SILVERBACK PATRIARCH.flavorText: He likes to act like he's in charge, but the silverback matriarch actually runs things.

BRANCHING PATHS.name: Branching Paths
BRANCHING PATHS.flavorText: Three paths diverged in a darkened hall, and I – I took the one less traveled by, And got eaten by a slime.

GARDEN GNOME.name: Garden Gnome
GARDEN GNOME.flavorText: "Greetings, my little shrubs... It's whittlin' time."

SHELDRAS MOONTREE.name: Sheldras Moontree
SHELDRAS MOONTREE.flavorText: Sheldras really went to the park for his pilgrimage.

MISSILE LAUNCHER.name: Missile Launcher
MISSILE LAUNCHER.flavorText: We asked, "Where do the missiles go?" and he answered, "Yes."

DARK PACT.name: Dark Pact
DARK PACT.flavorText: "Don't worry about the fine print. Just sign here."

VOLCANIC LUMBERER.name: Volcanic Lumberer
VOLCANIC LUMBERER.flavorText: The roots, the roots, the roots is on fire!

AEROSOILIZER.name: Aerosoilizer
AEROSOILIZER.flavorText: Banned in Wild for opening a hole in the ozone layer.

ZILLIAX.name: Zilliax
ZILLIAX.flavorText: Everything but the kitchen sink. Oh wait, there's one on his back.

SOULSTEALER.name: Soulstealer
SOULSTEALER.flavorText: "Wanna see what destruction looks like? Here it is in undead form - it's your boy Soulstealer!"

MARK OF THE LOA.name: Mark of the Loa
MARK OF THE LOA.flavorText: Ah, yes. Mark. The mightiest Loa.

UMBRAL OWL.name: Umbral Owl
UMBRAL OWL.flavorText: It sleeps with one eye open.

KRUL THE UNSHACKLED.name: Krul the Unshackled
KRUL THE UNSHACKLED.flavorText: Spicklefizz pondered his life choices as he looked at the chain around his neck. "Become a warlock," they said. "You get to enslave demons," they said.

UR'ZUL RAGER.name: Ur'zul Rager
UR'ZUL RAGER.flavorText: The Burning Legion is host to many horrors, but a 3 Mana 5/1 is the worst of all!

DEHYDRATE.name: Dehydrate
DEHYDRATE.flavorText: JUST A LITTLE FURTHER LITTLE GUY, YOU CAN MAKE IT!!!

ORIGAMI FROG.name: Origami Frog
ORIGAMI FROG.flavorText: For extra-realistic fly-snatching action, use tape!

HOLY MAKI ROLL.name: Holy Maki Roll
HOLY MAKI ROLL.flavorText: If you use all 10 mana, that's called the 'Lunch Special.'

CLERIC OF AN'SHE.name: Cleric of An'she
CLERIC OF AN'SHE.flavorText: When it's her turn to cook, she'll always go for a Light sear.

RIGHTEOUSNESS.name: Righteousness
RIGHTEOUSNESS.flavorText: Shield yourself in righteousness! It feels like a warm fuzzy blanket.

WARSONG GRUNT.name: Warsong Grunt
WARSONG GRUNT.flavorText: Where do you think the chickens learned to be angry?

SCALEWORM.name: Scaleworm
SCALEWORM.flavorText: A popular local alternative to bananas.

ANCESTRAL SPIRIT.name: Ancestral Spirit
ANCESTRAL SPIRIT.flavorText: It was just a flesh wound.

NOFIN CAN STOP US.name: Nofin Can Stop Us
NOFIN CAN STOP US.flavorText: "I'm having a good time! I don't want to stop at all!"

FLAMECANNON.name: Flamecannon
FLAMECANNON.flavorText: Calling something a flamecannon really doesn't do much to distinguish it from other goblin devices.

ANCIENT VOID HOUND.name: Ancient Void Hound
ANCIENT VOID HOUND.flavorText: What happened to my 1/1 Void Pup? And the glee club?!

WILD GROWTH.name: Wild Growth
WILD GROWTH.flavorText: Grow your own mana crystals with this Mana Crystal Growth Kit, only 39.99!

STEAMCLEANER.name: Steamcleaner
STEAMCLEANER.flavorText: Business is slow since the anima shortage began. Things just don't get stained like they used to!

MOAT LURKER.name: Moat Lurker
MOAT LURKER.flavorText: He really enjoys lurking and gets a lot of job satisfaction out of it.

PHARAOH'S BLESSING.name: Pharaoh's Blessing
PHARAOH'S BLESSING.flavorText: Life hack: Sneeze near a pharaoh.

BLESSING OF AUTHORITY.name: Blessing of Authority
BLESSING OF AUTHORITY.flavorText: A paladin fights with honor! We don't go face... until next turn!

LADY IN WHITE.name: Lady in White
LADY IN WHITE.flavorText: She was a lady in polka dots until the gnomish laundromat incident.

RESISTANCE AURA.name: Resistance Aura
RESISTANCE AURA.flavorText: Perfect for defending against Beasts. Specifically small ones. Like, a very specific species of small insectoid animal. Ants. It resists ants.

MASKED REVELER.name: Masked Reveler
MASKED REVELER.flavorText: "It's party time! P-A-R-T-Why? Because I gotta!"

ALEXSTRASZA'S CHAMPION.name: Alexstrasza's Champion
ALEXSTRASZA'S CHAMPION.flavorText: "Put more spikes on her. No, more spikes. What part of 'more spikes' do you not understand? MORE SPIKES!" - Alexstrasza

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/7b/VO_AT_071_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_071_PLAY_01.wav

SIMULACRUM.name: Simulacrum
SIMULACRUM.flavorText: It's like déjà vu, times two.

EVOCATION.name: Evocation
EVOCATION.flavorText: You too could be the winner of the national spelling spree!

WEAPONS EXPERT.name: Weapons Expert
WEAPONS EXPERT.flavorText: "Yes, Your Honor, this appears to be some sort of blade."

ORGRIMMAR ASPIRANT.name: Orgrimmar Aspirant
ORGRIMMAR ASPIRANT.flavorText: "Four out of three orcs struggle with math." - Angry Zurge

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/62/VO_AT_066_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_066_PLAY_01.wav
