voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/d/d9/VO_AT_066_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_066_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

FROZEN CLONE.name: Frozen Clone
FROZEN CLONE.flavorText: It's like déjà vu, times two.

TEMPORUS.name: Temporus
TEMPORUS.flavorText: Follows adventurers, seeking the ultimate time magic: the ability to reload.

STEWART THE STEWARD.name: Stewart the Steward
STEWART THE STEWARD.flavorText: How many bites does it take to get the center of an hors d'oeuvre?

CHALK ARTIST.name: Chalk Artist
CHALK ARTIST.flavorText: Well it's either a dragon or a dinosaur - chalk it up to art style.

KANRETHAD EBONLOCKE.name: Kanrethad Ebonlocke
KANRETHAD EBONLOCKE.flavorText: After Illidan's downfall, Kanrethad formed the Council of the Black Harvest to study Illidan's fel magic. Some say he was... green with envy.

ORDER IN THE COURT.name: Order in the Court
ORDER IN THE COURT.flavorText: "I have nothing BUT contempt for this court!"

WICKED SKELETON.name: Wicked Skeleton
WICKED SKELETON.flavorText: It's minions like these that give normal, law-abiding skeletons a bad rap.

HARMONIC POP.name: Harmonic Pop
HARMONIC POP.flavorText: Here with supporting vocals: Snap and Crackle!

CLOAKED HUNTRESS.name: Cloaked Huntress
CLOAKED HUNTRESS.flavorText: She's practically GIVING your secrets away!

NETHERSPITE HISTORIAN.name: Netherspite Historian
NETHERSPITE HISTORIAN.flavorText: She can tell you all about the history of people not STANDING IN THE GREEN BEAM!

KABAL TALONPRIEST.name: Kabal Talonpriest
KABAL TALONPRIEST.flavorText: Inkmaster Solia had to figure out how to tattoo feathers.

ANCESTRAL HEALING.name: Ancestral Healing
ANCESTRAL HEALING.flavorText: I personally prefer some non-ancestral right-the-heck-now healing, but maybe that is just me.

GRIMESTREET OUTFITTER.name: Grimestreet Outfitter
GRIMESTREET OUTFITTER.flavorText: If you bargain hard, he'll throw in the hat.

EMPEROR COBRA.name: Emperor Cobra
EMPEROR COBRA.flavorText: The Sholazar Basin is home to a lot of really horrible things. If you're going to visit, wear bug spray. And plate armor.

ICE FISHING.name: Ice Fishing
ICE FISHING.flavorText: Glow fish, war fish... blow fish, more fish...

CONSECRATION.name: Consecration
CONSECRATION.flavorText: Consecrated ground glows with Holy energy. But it smells a little, too.

BURROW BUSTER.name: Burrow Buster
BURROW BUSTER.flavorText: We almost went with the name "Giant Drill", but then it would've HAD to be an 8/8.

BLADE FLURRY.name: Blade Flurry
BLADE FLURRY.flavorText: "Look, it's not just about waving daggers around really fast. It's a lot more complicated than that." - Shan, Rogue Trainer

LIFEBINDER'S GIFT.name: Lifebinder's Gift
LIFEBINDER'S GIFT.flavorText: Everyone's investing in Nature spells these days, but that bubble is about to burst.

ANCIENT SHIELDBEARER.name: Ancient Shieldbearer
ANCIENT SHIELDBEARER.flavorText: Back in her day, each shield weighed two tons and she had to carry four of them on each arm!

COILFANG WARLORD.name: Coilfang Warlord
COILFANG WARLORD.flavorText: Prepare for the staunch conch launch!

TOUR GUIDE.name: Tour Guide
TOUR GUIDE.flavorText: "Here is the original blueprint for the Academy grounds! Don't mind those so-called dark chambers… They'll be at the end of the tour."

SNEAKY DELINQUENT.name: Sneaky Delinquent
SNEAKY DELINQUENT.flavorText: All right, now open your lid and say "Ahh!"

SECRET PASSAGE.name: Secret Passage
SECRET PASSAGE.flavorText: I use this to sneak out at night and do some villainous baking in the kitchen.

MURLOC GROWFIN.name: Murloc Growfin
MURLOC GROWFIN.flavorText: Grows up to 8x its size! Just add water!

STALWART AVENGER.name: Stalwart Avenger
STALWART AVENGER.flavorText: A good defense is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense!

DRUID OF THE FANG.name: Druid of the Fang
DRUID OF THE FANG.flavorText: The Druids of the Fang live in the Wailing Caverns. They wear cool snake shirts and tell snake jokes and say "bro" a lot.

RUNAWAY BLACKWING.name: Runaway Blackwing
RUNAWAY BLACKWING.flavorText: It has been 5 minutes since our last Azeroth Racing League violation.

SEAWEED STRIKE.name: Seaweed Strike
SEAWEED STRIKE.flavorText: Even as mechs, fish will still end up wrapped in seaweed.

HOLY COWBOY.name: Holy Cowboy
HOLY COWBOY.flavorText: Wait, but… Isn't he more of a 'holy kodoboy'?

PRIMORDIAL PROTECTOR.name: Primordial Protector
PRIMORDIAL PROTECTOR.flavorText: I thought the "shape of water" meant something else.

NECROLORD DRAKA.name: Necrolord Draka
NECROLORD DRAKA.flavorText: We originally planned on giving Rogue a Legendary minion called "The Moon", but SOMEONE jumped in the frame.

LIGHTNING STORM.name: Lightning Storm
LIGHTNING STORM.flavorText: An umbrella won't be effective, I'm afraid.

ROTGILL.name: Rotgill
ROTGILL.flavorText: In the summer: Hotgill. Mechanized: Botgill. Everyone else: Notgill.

SMALL-TIME RECRUITS.name: Small-Time Recruits
SMALL-TIME RECRUITS.flavorText: Now we know why they wear tiny watches.

KUL TIRAN CHAPLAIN.name: Kul Tiran Chaplain
KUL TIRAN CHAPLAIN.flavorText: The maritime Kul Tiran clergy are unique among priests for using holy saltwater.

DWARVEN ARCHAEOLOGIST.name: Dwarven Archaeologist
DWARVEN ARCHAEOLOGIST.flavorText: She's making great progress on paying off that advanced degree.

KEEN REFLEX.name: Keen Reflex
KEEN REFLEX.flavorText: All of Onyxia's whelps were no match for Kurtrus' backflip.

RIFTCLEAVER.name: Riftcleaver
RIFTCLEAVER.flavorText: Brings you face to face with your destructive impulses.

ENCUMBERED PACK MULE.name: Encumbered Pack Mule
ENCUMBERED PACK MULE.flavorText: "Now I can pick up EVERY knick-knack."

SELF-SHARPENING SWORD.name: Self-Sharpening Sword
SELF-SHARPENING SWORD.flavorText: You no longer have to bring a stack of 2 swords to a test!

SHADOWFIEND.name: Shadowfiend
SHADOWFIEND.flavorText: Hopes to be promoted to "Shadowfriend" someday.

WAYWARD SAGE.name: Wayward Sage
WAYWARD SAGE.flavorText: Carry on my wayward sage. There'll be peace and no more rage.

DANCE FLOOR.name: Dance Floor
DANCE FLOOR.flavorText: I don't think Rush would ever be here.

THE LIGHT! IT BURNS!.name: The Light! It Burns!
THE LIGHT! IT BURNS!.flavorText: Wait, if you're over there, then who's messing with the lights?!

FARM HAND.name: Farm Hand
FARM HAND.flavorText: I know it's an Undead hand, but bending your pinky in that way can NOT be good for your joints.

BACKSTAGE BOUNCER.name: Backstage Bouncer
BACKSTAGE BOUNCER.flavorText: Doesn't see your name on the list. Also doesn't know how to read the names on the list.

MESSENGER BUZZARD.name: Messenger Buzzard
MESSENGER BUZZARD.flavorText: The bird brings the word (which happens to be bird).

COILSKAR COMMANDER.name: Coilskar Commander
COILSKAR COMMANDER.flavorText: Then thou shalt count to three, no more, no less. Three shall be the number thou shalt count, and the number of the counting shall be three. Four shalt thou not count, neither count thou two, excepting that thou then proceed to three. Five is right out.

SIR FINLEY, THE INTREPID.name: Sir Finley, the Intrepid
SIR FINLEY, THE INTREPID.flavorText: And exactly how does Finley turn everyone into a murloc?

GLOWFLY SWARM.name: Glowfly Swarm
GLOWFLY SWARM.flavorText: Glowflies are distant relations to spelling bees.

HOZEN HEALER.name: Hozen Healer
HOZEN HEALER.flavorText: He didn't go to school for healing, but we keep losing all the good healers to Ratchet, so I guess we'll take him.

WHIRLING ZAP-O-MATIC.name: Whirling Zap-o-matic
WHIRLING ZAP-O-MATIC.flavorText: If you pay a little extra, you can get it in "candy-apple red."

LIL' EXORCIST.name: Lil' Exorcist
LIL' EXORCIST.flavorText: Warlocks have the town exorcist on speed dial in case they unleash the wrong demon.

DRINK SERVER.name: Drink Server
DRINK SERVER.flavorText: Make sure to tip to help him with his fin-ances.

RENO, LONE RANGER.name: Reno, Lone Ranger
RENO, LONE RANGER.flavorText: With an uncertain past and a questionable future, Reno was lucky to find his home on the range.

ZILLIAX DELUXE 3000.name: Zilliax Deluxe 3000
ZILLIAX DELUXE 3000.flavorText: It only took us 2998 prototypes to figure out how to make the perfect card... by having YOU do it!

ARKWING PILOT.name: Arkwing Pilot
ARKWING PILOT.flavorText: Delivered in under 30 minutes, or your Arkwings are free!

SANCTUARY.name: Sanctuary
SANCTUARY.flavorText: Few quests are completed by cowering under a table.

CHROMIE, TIMEHOPPER.name: Chromie, Timehopper
CHROMIE, TIMEHOPPER.flavorText: "Noz, you're telling me you built a time machine...out of a Hearthstone card?"

RADIANCE OF AZSHARA.name: Radiance of Azshara
RADIANCE OF AZSHARA.flavorText: Uses Arcane, Fire, and Frost magic to vanquish Queen Azshara's foes. And for her skincare routine!

FEL FISSURE.name: Fel Fissure
FEL FISSURE.flavorText: This will clear the board, I'm fisSURE of it!

CONDEMN (RANK 1).name: Condemn (Rank 1)
CONDEMN (RANK 1).flavorText: "I wished you no harm, but for your cruelty, by the light, I condemn you all!" Xyrella shouted, unaware that irony was not her strong suit.

CRIMSON HOTHEAD.name: Crimson Hothead
CRIMSON HOTHEAD.flavorText: Has a real passion for spelling.

LESSER OPAL SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Opal Spellstone
LESSER OPAL SPELLSTONE.flavorText: For those seeking glory and power Be not swayed by Azari the Devourer The opal grants victory to the weak But leaves your soul barren and bleak

FLAMESTRIKE.name: Flamestrike
FLAMESTRIKE.flavorText: When the ground is on fire, you should not stop, drop, and roll.

SPIRIT OF THE SHARK.name: Spirit of the Shark
SPIRIT OF THE SHARK.flavorText: It has Stealth, but its ominous theme music keeps giving it away.

SHADOWHOOF SLAYER.name: Shadowhoof Slayer
SHADOWHOOF SLAYER.flavorText: Was a humble Elven Archer before Sargeras got to him.

LORD OF THE ARENA.name: Lord of the Arena
LORD OF THE ARENA.flavorText: He used to be a 2100+ rated arena player, but that was years ago and nobody can get him to shut up about it.

MAESTRA OF THE MASQUERADE.name: Maestra of the Masquerade
MAESTRA OF THE MASQUERADE.flavorText: She doesn't drop character until after the DVD commentary.

POWER OF THE WILD.name: Power of the Wild
POWER OF THE WILD.flavorText: Never look a panther in the eye. Or is it 'Always look a panther in the eye'? Well, it's one of those.

MAZE GUIDE.name: Maze Guide
MAZE GUIDE.flavorText: "And if you look to your left, you'll see an even larger statue of Sire Denathrius!"

UR'ZUL GIANT.name: Ur'zul Giant
UR'ZUL GIANT.flavorText: Nothing personal, tiny human. I have many mouths to feed.

GLOOM STAG.name: Gloom Stag
GLOOM STAG.flavorText: Majestic. Ethereal. Still pretty down in the dumps, though.

RENOWNED PERFORMER.name: Renowned Performer
RENOWNED PERFORMER.flavorText: Cutting the assistant in half is the easy part.

GIBBERLING.name: Gibberling
GIBBERLING.flavorText: "As a Linguistics student I have studied the Gibberlings. I have determined they are speaking Gibberish."

BITTERTIDE HYDRA.name: Bittertide Hydra
BITTERTIDE HYDRA.flavorText: It's actually only the middle head that's bitter. The others are sweet and spicy.

SPLINTERGRAFT.name: Splintergraft
SPLINTERGRAFT.flavorText: We're going to need some bigger tweezers.

DRAGONMAW SENTINEL.name: Dragonmaw Sentinel
DRAGONMAW SENTINEL.flavorText: On the side, she's training for the annual Dragonmaw hammer throw tournament.

SHARK PUNCHER.name: Shark Puncher
SHARK PUNCHER.flavorText: "And remember, if you come face-to-face with a shark, punch it in the nose." "Yes. Me punch you in nose with shark." "No, th- OW!"

DUSKBOAR.name: Duskboar
DUSKBOAR.flavorText: Often excluded from dinner parties. To be fair, he is very boaring.

BLESSING OF MIGHT.name: Blessing of Might
BLESSING OF MIGHT.flavorText: "As in, you MIGHT want to get out of my way." - Toad Mackle, recently buffed.

GILNEAN ROYAL GUARD.name: Gilnean Royal Guard
GILNEAN ROYAL GUARD.flavorText: Admittedly, they kind of dropped the ball with Prince Liam.

FROST NOVA.name: Frost Nova
FROST NOVA.flavorText: Hey man, that's cold. Literally and metaphorically.

DISCIPLE OF C'THUN.name: Disciple of C'Thun
DISCIPLE OF C'THUN.flavorText: C’Thun’s recruiting pitch involves cookies, which is why it’s the most popular Old God.

BIRDWATCHING.name: Birdwatching
BIRDWATCHING.flavorText: A bird in the hand is worth two in the deck.

CARNIVAL BARKER.name: Carnival Barker
CARNIVAL BARKER.flavorText: The barking initially confused faire-goers, so he switched to words.

TOXIC ARROW.name: Toxic Arrow
TOXIC ARROW.flavorText: What doesn't kill you makes you toxic.

FROST QUEEN SINDRAGOSA.name: Frost Queen Sindragosa
FROST QUEEN SINDRAGOSA.flavorText: With her final breath, Sindragosa cursed her consort and all who abandoned her to die in Icecrown. When she was reborn by the hands of the Lich King, her first freezing exhale wrought only pain.

STORMWIND KNIGHT.name: Stormwind Knight
STORMWIND KNIGHT.flavorText: They're still embarrassed about "The Deathwing Incident".

SATED THRESHADON.name: Sated Threshadon
SATED THRESHADON.flavorText: Bet you can't eat just one murloc!

AQUATIC FORM.name: Aquatic Form
AQUATIC FORM.flavorText: How long can YOU hold your breath underwater?

METALTOOTH LEAPER.name: Metaltooth Leaper
METALTOOTH LEAPER.flavorText: Don't leave them out in the rain. In Un'Goro Crater there is a whole colony of rust-tooth leapers.

GIANT SAND WORM.name: Giant Sand Worm
GIANT SAND WORM.flavorText: Banned from every all-you-can-eat buffet on Azeroth.

HYDROLOGIST.name: Hydrologist
HYDROLOGIST.flavorText: Murloc hydrologists are pretty rare. Most murloc undergrads pick computer science.

WILDERNESS PACK.name: Wilderness Pack
WILDERNESS PACK.flavorText: Don't bother asking, "Can we keep them?" The answer is no.

BONEMARE.name: Bonemare
BONEMARE.flavorText: Attacks her job with unbridled enthusiasm.

DERANGED DOCTOR.name: Deranged Doctor
DERANGED DOCTOR.flavorText: Unfortunately, his doctorate is in Murloc Literature.

BAKU THE MOONEATER.name: Baku the Mooneater
BAKU THE MOONEATER.flavorText: In her defense, it did look like a cookie.

SPELLBOOK BINDER.name: Spellbook Binder
SPELLBOOK BINDER.flavorText: You're bound to love his work!

BAZAAR BURGLARY.name: Bazaar Burglary
BAZAAR BURGLARY.flavorText: Just when you set up your "All-Natural Scented Candles" at the farmer's market and then some STUPID KOBOLD COMES AND TAKES THEM ALL!

POLYMORPH.name: Polymorph
POLYMORPH.flavorText: There was going to be a pun in this flavor text, but it just came out baa-d.

SCABBS CUTTERBUTTER.name: Scabbs Cutterbutter
SCABBS CUTTERBUTTER.flavorText: "Never lie, steal, cheat, or drink. Unless you're compelled to, that is…" —Scabbs Cutterbutter

FEROCIOUS HOWL.name: Ferocious Howl
FEROCIOUS HOWL.flavorText: Have you ever heard the wolf cry to the blue corn moon?

VOID SCRIPTURE.name: Void Scripture
VOID SCRIPTURE.flavorText: The Old Gods like to think of them as "Addendums."

COORDINATED STRIKE.name: Coordinated Strike
COORDINATED STRIKE.flavorText: Undisputed champions of "Dancing with the Satyrs."

PEN FLINGER.name: Pen Flinger
PEN FLINGER.flavorText: The pen is also a more aerodynamic short-range projectile than the sword.

ZIXOR, APEX PREDATOR.name: Zixor, Apex Predator
ZIXOR, APEX PREDATOR.flavorText: A living terror. Teleports at will. Feasts on tainted helboar meat. No head scritches unless you're Leoroxx.

COLOSSUS OF THE MOON.name: Colossus of the Moon
COLOSSUS OF THE MOON.flavorText: Strike him down, and you'll face the Colossus of the New Moon.

GIFT OF THE NAARU.name: Gift of the Naaru
GIFT OF THE NAARU.flavorText: What do I look like, a charity?

POPULAR PIXIE.name: Popular Pixie
POPULAR PIXIE.flavorText: Popular Pixie personally prefers particularly powerful pop performances.

SEABREEZE CHALICE.name: Seabreeze Chalice
SEABREEZE CHALICE.flavorText: If your luck has been particularly poor lately, try the extra salted rim!

HEARTTHROB.name: Heartthrob
HEARTTHROB.flavorText: Oh no, Harth! Look out! He's here to rob you!

RINGMASTER WHATLEY.name: Ringmaster Whatley
RINGMASTER WHATLEY.flavorText: His main qualification is that he'll work with anyone. Or anything.

BRIDGE RIFF.name: Bridge Riff
BRIDGE RIFF.flavorText: Can be played in other places too.

THRALLMAR FARSEER.name: Thrallmar Farseer
THRALLMAR FARSEER.flavorText: He's stationed in the Hellfire Peninsula, but he's hoping for a reassignment closer to Orgrimmar, or really anywhere the ground is less on fire.

BRUTAL ANNIHILAN.name: Brutal Annihilan
BRUTAL ANNIHILAN.flavorText: Sometimes, problems can be solved by throwing everything you've got at it. This is not one of those times.

FAIRGROUND FOOL.name: Fairground Fool
FAIRGROUND FOOL.flavorText: "What did Illidan say when his rocketeer broke down on the Darkmoon racetrack? YOU ARE NOT REPAIRED!"

DEATHWING.name: Deathwing
DEATHWING.flavorText: Once a noble dragon known as Neltharion, Deathwing lost his mind and shattered Azeroth before finally being defeated. Daddy issues?

CATHEDRAL GARGOYLE.name: Cathedral Gargoyle
CATHEDRAL GARGOYLE.flavorText: Fly like an eagle, drop like a rock.

GRAVE DEFILER.name: Grave Defiler
GRAVE DEFILER.flavorText: She keeps her Fel spells nice and organized in her defiling cabinet.

INNERVATE.name: Innervate
INNERVATE.flavorText: Some druids still have flashbacks from strangers yelling "Innervate me!!" at them.

WORKHORSE.name: Workhorse
WORKHORSE.flavorText: Give me ONE reason why a horse shouldn’t be allowed in the travel agency.

VOLATILE SKELETON.name: Volatile Skeleton
VOLATILE SKELETON.flavorText: These ice sculpures look so realistic!

LIGHTSHOWER ELEMENTAL.name: Lightshower Elemental
LIGHTSHOWER ELEMENTAL.flavorText: The forecast calls for light showers, but you won’t need an umbrella.

LIBRAM OF JUSTICE.name: Libram of Justice
LIBRAM OF JUSTICE.flavorText: Proper justice. Throw the book at him!

KOBOLD BARBARIAN.name: Kobold Barbarian
KOBOLD BARBARIAN.flavorText: What is best in life? To make candle. To keep candle. To hear lamentations of candle-takers.

AIR GUITARIST.name: Air Guitarist
AIR GUITARIST.flavorText: Nailing that solo was a breeze.

GRIMOIRE OF SACRIFICE.name: Grimoire of Sacrifice
GRIMOIRE OF SACRIFICE.flavorText: "What kind of bedtime story is this?"

MALEFIC ROOK.name: Malefic Rook
MALEFIC ROOK.flavorText: Was a regular Pawn but Fel in with the wrong toys.

KIDNAP.name: Kidnap
KIDNAP.flavorText: Check your coat, but don't check the coat closet.

MISTAKE.name: Mistake
MISTAKE.flavorText: We like to think of it as a happy accident.

CRAZED CONDUCTOR.name: Crazed Conductor
CRAZED CONDUCTOR.flavorText: "The Twisting Nether is singing to me… WHAT IS THAT MELODY!?"

A LIGHT IN THE DARKNESS.name: A Light in the Darkness
A LIGHT IN THE DARKNESS.flavorText: Wait, how can you have a light in the dark? If you turn on a light while it’s dark, doesn’t that mean it’s no longer dark?

RUNIC EGG.name: Runic Egg
RUNIC EGG.flavorText: Oh man! Runic omelettes are the best!

PRISMATIC LENS.name: Prismatic Lens
PRISMATIC LENS.flavorText: Mined exclusively from the dark side of the moon.

BATTY GUEST.name: Batty Guest
BATTY GUEST.flavorText: His favorite food is chocolate cereal.

FERAL SPIRIT.name: Feral Spirit
FERAL SPIRIT.flavorText: Spirit wolves are like regular wolves with pom-poms.

INJURED MARAUDER.name: Injured Marauder
INJURED MARAUDER.flavorText: He’ll keep going despite the neighsayers.

ANONYMOUS INFORMANT.name: Anonymous Informant
ANONYMOUS INFORMANT.flavorText: It turns out she wasn't so great at keeping secrets after all.

ABOMINABLE BOWMAN.name: Abominable Bowman
ABOMINABLE BOWMAN.flavorText: Frosty the Bowman... was an angry hateful soul... with a fresh hewn bow and a missing nose...

SHIMMER SHOT.name: Shimmer Shot
SHIMMER SHOT.flavorText: I hope I don't jinx the outcome.

CRYSTAL CLUSTER.name: Crystal Cluster
CRYSTAL CLUSTER.flavorText: And if you can't fit any of the Elementals… do better.

SILVERMOON PORTAL.name: Silvermoon Portal
SILVERMOON PORTAL.flavorText: What's Millhouse Manastorm doing in Silvermoon?

MURGUR MURGURGLE.name: Murgur Murgurgle
MURGUR MURGURGLE.flavorText: Murlocs are not native to Outland. When the Sungills arrived, one among them rose to the challenge of this dark world. They call him... Murgurgle. Murgur Murgurgle.

CI'CIGI.name: Ci'Cigi
CI'CIGI.flavorText: She once bought a 1of1 Golden Skull of Gul'dan written entirely in Thalassian for 2,000,000 Gold.

TANARIS HOGCHOPPER.name: Tanaris Hogchopper
TANARIS HOGCHOPPER.flavorText: The Hogchoppers are well-known throughout Kalimdor for being a real, actual group.

MEAT GRINDER.name: Meat Grinder
MEAT GRINDER.flavorText: After the Horde and Alliance sieged Icecrown Citadel, they took these back to use in their delis.

SPIRIT ECHO.name: Spirit Echo
SPIRIT ECHO.flavorText: I guess you can say they’re… “soul survivors.”

HUMONGOUS RAZORLEAF.name: Humongous Razorleaf
HUMONGOUS RAZORLEAF.flavorText: Loves goblins. In a light cream sauce.

LI'NA, SHOP MANAGER.name: Li'Na, Shop Manager
LI'NA, SHOP MANAGER.flavorText: Somebody has to do the paperwork around here.

DEATH REVENANT.name: Death Revenant
DEATH REVENANT.flavorText: How's everyone doing? Hurt? Bleeding? Wounded? ... Excellent.

RENO JACKSON.name: Reno Jackson
RENO JACKSON.flavorText: Reno is a four-time winner of the 'Best Accessorized Explorer' award.

TOUGH CROWD.name: Tough Crowd
TOUGH CROWD.flavorText: "Your music's bad and you should feel bad."

BLOODSAIL RAIDER.name: Bloodsail Raider
BLOODSAIL RAIDER.flavorText: "I only plunder on days that end in 'y'."

DEPUTIZATION AURA.name: Deputization Aura
DEPUTIZATION AURA.flavorText: You're my favorite deput- oh. You died… Ok just kidding, THAT guy is my favorite deputy.

OCCULT CONJURER.name: Occult Conjurer
OCCULT CONJURER.flavorText: Like mirror image, but more secretive and angsty.

AGGRAMAR, THE AVENGER.name: Aggramar, the Avenger
AGGRAMAR, THE AVENGER.flavorText: Formerly a trusted lieutenant of Sargeras, Aggramar helped him fight the demonic legions across many worlds before he was corrupted.

SPELLBREAKER.name: Spellbreaker
SPELLBREAKER.flavorText: Spellbreakers can rip enchantments from magic-wielders. The process is painless and can be performed on an outpatient basis.

BLADED LADY.name: Bladed Lady
BLADED LADY.flavorText: While you were busy learning magic, she studied the blade.

KOLOGARN.name: Kologarn
KOLOGARN.flavorText: "So am I just supposed to stand here forever, or...?"

JADE TELEGRAM.name: Jade Telegram
JADE TELEGRAM.flavorText: Golem-gram for Han'Cho! Golem-gram for Han'Cho!

LYRA THE SUNSHARD.name: Lyra the Sunshard
LYRA THE SUNSHARD.flavorText: Arise, fair sun, and kill my envious foes. They don't have a legendary as beautiful as you.

THE LEVIATHAN.name: The Leviathan
THE LEVIATHAN.flavorText: Built by Ini Stormcoil, this massive vessel can withstand almost anything you put it through... although she would prefer you didn't!

RAZORPETAL LASHER.name: Razorpetal Lasher
RAZORPETAL LASHER.flavorText: The reason why there are no zombies in Un'goro.

SKETCHY INFORMATION.name: Sketchy Information
SKETCHY INFORMATION.flavorText: "I trust the Forsaken as far as I can smell them. Which, I guess is actually pretty far."

SURFALOPOD.name: Surfalopod
SURFALOPOD.flavorText: Hi! Octopus expert here. This is NOT funny. Octopi only do this when they're extremely rad.

INJURED HAULER.name: Injured Hauler
INJURED HAULER.flavorText: With how many cacti are all over the Badlands, this job has to be some sort of sick joke.

PYROTECHNICIAN.name: Pyrotechnician
PYROTECHNICIAN.flavorText: The difference between a pyrotechnician and a pyromaniac is a paycheck.

ACTIVATE THE OBELISK.name: Activate the Obelisk
ACTIVATE THE OBELISK.flavorText: A one-eyed, one stone, towering purple minion healer.

HARMONIC MOOD.name: Harmonic Mood
HARMONIC MOOD.flavorText: ROYGBive your hero +2 Attack this turn.

ACORNBEARER.name: Acornbearer
ACORNBEARER.flavorText: You’d be nuts to mess with the squirrel squad.

LORD MARROWGAR.name: Lord Marrowgar
LORD MARROWGAR.flavorText: And now, Lord Marrowgar with the weather.

IRON JUGGERNAUT.name: Iron Juggernaut
IRON JUGGERNAUT.flavorText: The Iron Juggernaut guards Orgrimmar and has just earned the "Employee of the Month" award!

CARICATURE ARTIST.name: Caricature Artist
CARICATURE ARTIST.flavorText: "Pfffft…. You look RIDICULOUS! And I haven't even drawn the mustache yet!"

SWORD OF JUSTICE.name: Sword of Justice
SWORD OF JUSTICE.flavorText: I dub you Sir Loin of Beef!

MAGISTER DAWNGRASP.name: Magister Dawngrasp
MAGISTER DAWNGRASP.flavorText: Magister is a humble title for one who united warring armies against the greatest threat to Azeroth.

ACROBATICS.name: Acrobatics
ACROBATICS.flavorText: He soars through the air with the greatest of fleas.

RAGING WORGEN.name: Raging Worgen
RAGING WORGEN.flavorText: If he's raging now, just wait until he gets nerfed.

NITROBOOST POISON.name: Nitroboost Poison
NITROBOOST POISON.flavorText: Pouring iced milk into your vehicle's fuel tank does NOT provide a Nitro boost, but it does go great with your victory cookies.

MAELSTROM PORTAL.name: Maelstrom Portal
MAELSTROM PORTAL.flavorText: They bill this as a popular resort attraction, but they try and get your money up front.

TICKING ABOMINATION.name: Ticking Abomination
TICKING ABOMINATION.flavorText: Abomination. Emphasis on the second syllable.

KABAL SONGSTEALER.name: Kabal Songstealer
KABAL SONGSTEALER.flavorText: Gadgetzan Writer’s Award goes to the player who writes the most compelling fanfic about why this Arakkoa has a golden frog in his hand!

REMIXED TUNING FORK.name: Remixed Tuning Fork
REMIXED TUNING FORK.flavorText: You can tune a fork, but you can't tune a fish.

TUSKPIERCER.name: Tuskpiercer
TUSKPIERCER.flavorText: It's the Barrens, everything has tusks! The Quilboar have tusks, the boars have tusks, the tusks have tusks.

IRON HIDE.name: Iron Hide
IRON HIDE.flavorText: Week 6. I remain covered head to toe with scales. They do not yet realize that I am not a dinosaur.

LANDSLIDE.name: Landslide
LANDSLIDE.flavorText: "And they win it by a landslide! Wait, where did all the other racers go?"

GADGETZAN JOUSTER.name: Gadgetzan Jouster
GADGETZAN JOUSTER.flavorText: It's not HER fault you didn't put a spinning saw blade on your horse.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/8e/VO_AT_133_ATTACK_ALT1_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_133_ATTACK_ALT1_03.wav Full speed!

MI'DA, PURE LIGHT.name: Mi'da, Pure Light
MI'DA, PURE LIGHT.flavorText: Unfortunately, Mi’da’s touch will not turn things to gold.

CHILLFALLEN BARON.name: Chillfallen Baron
CHILLFALLEN BARON.flavorText: He hates when people call 60 degree weather cold.

SMUGGLER'S CRATE.name: Smuggler's Crate
SMUGGLER'S CRATE.flavorText: Are you sure these are the crates that are supposed to go to the Gadgetzan petting zoo?

VENGEFUL VISAGE.name: Vengeful Visage
VENGEFUL VISAGE.flavorText: The mirror shows us nothing less than the deepest, darkest desire of our hearts: to go face.

LOREWALKER CHO.name: Lorewalker Cho
LOREWALKER CHO.flavorText: Lorewalker Cho archives and shares tales from the land of Pandaria, but his favorite story is the one where Joey and Phoebe go on a road trip.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e8/VO_Tutorial06_CHO_02_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_Tutorial06_CHO_02_03.wav

VICIOUS BLOODWORM.name: Vicious Bloodworm
VICIOUS BLOODWORM.flavorText: Not to be confused with the Viscous Bloodworm.

HORDE OPERATIVE.name: Horde Operative
HORDE OPERATIVE.flavorText: "We all have our secrets. I mean, your secrets."

INCANTER'S FLOW.name: Incanter's Flow
INCANTER'S FLOW.flavorText: "Gettin' them discounts in bulk amounts, spells can come, and spells can go, castin' costs drop with my sweet, sweet flow."

SUSPICIOUS USHER.name: Suspicious Usher
SUSPICIOUS USHER.flavorText: "Oh please, let me take your jacket, luggage, and absurdly large shoulder pads."

LONE CHAMPION.name: Lone Champion
LONE CHAMPION.flavorText: He is a champion, with no friends. He'll keep on fighting, til the end!

SUMMONING PORTAL.name: Summoning Portal
SUMMONING PORTAL.flavorText: NOT LESS THAN 1! Don't get any ideas!

VENGEFUL SPIRIT.name: Vengeful Spirit
VENGEFUL SPIRIT.flavorText: Sheesh, even the spirits are edgy when it comes to Demon Hunters.

HOLY GLOWSTICKS.name: Holy Glowsticks
HOLY GLOWSTICKS.flavorText: Somewhere there's a Naaru missing a couple of shards.

ZOOBOT.name: Zoobot
ZOOBOT.flavorText: The Murloc is taking the picture.

ALTRUIS THE OUTCAST.name: Altruis the Outcast
ALTRUIS THE OUTCAST.flavorText: Altruis betrayed Illidan to forge his own way in Outland. With Blackjack. And Netherdrakes.

IMP GANG BOSS.name: Imp Gang Boss
IMP GANG BOSS.flavorText: His imp gang likes to sneak into Stormwind to spraypaint "Ragnaros Rulez" on the Mage Tower.

APEXIS BLAST.name: Apexis Blast
APEXIS BLAST.flavorText: Lonely mages can still have a blast!

KING KRUSH.name: King Krush
KING KRUSH.flavorText: The best defense against King Krush is to have someone you don’t like standing in front of you.

TEAR REALITY.name: Tear Reality
TEAR REALITY.flavorText: One time it gave me a black flower, a smiling pot, and a foil first edition Dracthyr.

PLANTED EVIDENCE.name: Planted Evidence
PLANTED EVIDENCE.flavorText: So you're telling me this wasn't Natural Causes?

FABLE STABLEHAND.name: Fable Stablehand
FABLE STABLEHAND.flavorText: She took over the job when Feeble Steeblehand left.

SCOURGE TAMER.name: Scourge Tamer
SCOURGE TAMER.flavorText: He's a hunter AND a gatherer.

BACKROOM BOUNCER.name: Backroom Bouncer
BACKROOM BOUNCER.flavorText: "WHY ARE YOU IN THE BACK ROOM? WHO IS WATCHING THE FRONT?!"

BRITTLESKIN ZOMBIE.name: Brittleskin Zombie
BRITTLESKIN ZOMBIE.flavorText: I was born with glass bones and paper skin.

NIGHTBANE TEMPLAR.name: Nightbane Templar
NIGHTBANE TEMPLAR.flavorText: Originally joined to be Arcanagos’ Templar, but has to admit that ordering pizza has become waaaay easier.

OVERLORD RUNTHAK.name: Overlord Runthak
OVERLORD RUNTHAK.flavorText: Knows how to lift everyone up while tearing every enemy down.

ARCANE ANOMALY.name: Arcane Anomaly
ARCANE ANOMALY.flavorText: He used to get work as a Spatial Anomaly, but he got tired of having his polarity reversed.

SIRE DENATHRIUS.name: Sire Denathrius
SIRE DENATHRIUS.flavorText: History has a way of altering villains so that we can no longer see ourselves in them. Unfortunately for the Venthyr, they all look like Sire Denathrius.

SAFETY GOGGLES.name: Safety Goggles
SAFETY GOGGLES.flavorText: Remember, always be safe in the lab to mitigate injuries! *painfully snaps goggles onto face*

VALEERA THE HOLLOW.name: Valeera the Hollow
VALEERA THE HOLLOW.flavorText: "Run away. Hide in your precious keeps, behind your walls and your bodyguards. Night always falls, and shadows will fill your hallowed halls. One day, one of those shadows will be me."

INQUISITIVE CREATION.name: Inquisitive Creation
INQUISITIVE CREATION.flavorText: This mech eats books for breakfast.

ETERNAL LAYOVER.name: Eternal Layover
ETERNAL LAYOVER.flavorText: Get away from it all! Forever.

REDGILL RAZORJAW.name: Redgill Razorjaw
REDGILL RAZORJAW.flavorText: One fish, two fish, red fish replaces blue fish.

FLESHSHAPER.name: Fleshshaper
FLESHSHAPER.flavorText: Even THIS is better than paper straws.

KELI'DAN THE BREAKER.name: Keli'dan the Breaker
KELI'DAN THE BREAKER.flavorText: He calms down a lot if you just give him a turn.

THE BEAST.name: The Beast
THE BEAST.flavorText: He lives in Blackrock Mountain. He eats Gnomes. That's pretty much it.

TIGHT-LIPPED WITNESS.name: Tight-Lipped Witness
TIGHT-LIPPED WITNESS.flavorText: People keep asking for her award-winning vegetarian chili recipe, but she just can't spill the beans.

PAPARAZZI.name: Paparazzi
PAPARAZZI.flavorText: When you're a Legendary minion, you get a shiny orange gem, a dragon emblem, and about 100 of these people following you everywhere.

PTERRORDAX HATCHLING.name: Pterrordax Hatchling
PTERRORDAX HATCHLING.flavorText: Aww. So cute. Want to feed him another finger?

NAJAK HEXXEN.name: Najak Hexxen
NAJAK HEXXEN.flavorText: "I've got friends on the other side... of the battlefield."

DRUID OF THE REEF.name: Druid of the Reef
DRUID OF THE REEF.flavorText: “Wow, there’s a whole sunken city down here!”

SPECTRAL CUTLASS.name: Spectral Cutlass
SPECTRAL CUTLASS.flavorText: So sharp it can cut through a spectral tomato!

HARBINGER CELESTIA.name: Harbinger Celestia
HARBINGER CELESTIA.flavorText: She wanders realities, taking on many forms. One was a unicorn princess.

RITUAL OF DOOM.name: Ritual of Doom
RITUAL OF DOOM.flavorText: "Who wants to sing the Doom song?!"

VECTUS.name: Vectus
VECTUS.flavorText: Don’t let that dark magic worry you. He’ll ensure they hatch without a scratch.

BOG SLOSHER.name: Bog Slosher
BOG SLOSHER.flavorText: It's the bane of freshly mopped floors everywhere.

CHAINED GUARDIAN.name: Chained Guardian
CHAINED GUARDIAN.flavorText: Eternally jealous of the Unchained Gladiator.

CACTUS RAGER.name: Cactus Rager
CACTUS RAGER.flavorText: What doesn't kill ya makes you deader.

WISH UPON A STAR.name: Wish Upon a Star
WISH UPON A STAR.flavorText: "What are you going to wish for?" "I wish I had just a liiiiiiiittle more Attack and Health!" "...Really? You don't want, like, a million more?"

NOVICE ZAPPER.name: Novice Zapper
NOVICE ZAPPER.flavorText: The novices would prefer that he did not.

SILVER HAND REGENT.name: Silver Hand Regent
SILVER HAND REGENT.flavorText: The Silver Hand is the best paladin organization. The Argent Crusaders are super jealous.

BRITTLEBONE DESTROYER.name: Brittlebone Destroyer
BRITTLEBONE DESTROYER.flavorText: Broke many a leg in drama class.

AEGWYNN, THE GUARDIAN.name: Aegwynn, the Guardian
AEGWYNN, THE GUARDIAN.flavorText: With Medivh as her son, nothing YOU do could ever disappoint her.

SPELLSLINGER.name: Spellslinger
SPELLSLINGER.flavorText: Does he sling spells, or do his spells linger about. Who can say?

MOGU FLESHSHAPER.name: Mogu Fleshshaper
MOGU FLESHSHAPER.flavorText: He's here to shape *clap* you up!

VOIDTOUCHED ATTENDANT.name: Voidtouched Attendant
VOIDTOUCHED ATTENDANT.flavorText: Don't TOUCH the Void. You don't know where it's been.

TOXIC REINFORCEMENTS.name: Toxic Reinforcements
TOXIC REINFORCEMENTS.flavorText: In the event of a sudden loss of cabin pressure, a slingshot will be deployed for convenient evacuation.

FLESH BEHEMOTH.name: Flesh Behemoth
FLESH BEHEMOTH.flavorText: Perfect for fleshing out your Undead deck.

PHASE STALKER.name: Phase Stalker
PHASE STALKER.flavorText: It's not just a phase! I don't have to tell you anything! GAWSH!

HEARTBREAKER HEDANIS.name: Heartbreaker Hedanis
HEARTBREAKER HEDANIS.flavorText: Hedanis has won over the hearts and minds of millions of fans all over Azeroth! Shadow magic had nothing to do with it - not that you asked or anything.

COMMANDING SHOUT.name: Commanding Shout
COMMANDING SHOUT.flavorText: "Shout! Shout! Let it all out!" - Advice to warriors-in-training

TROGG BEASTRAGER.name: Trogg Beastrager
TROGG BEASTRAGER.flavorText: Still angry that the Gadgetzan Rager Club wouldn't accept him as a member.

EVIL RECRUITER.name: EVIL Recruiter
EVIL RECRUITER.flavorText: I'm starting to think the lackeys aren't evil, just taken advantage of.

CURSED VAGRANT.name: Cursed Vagrant
CURSED VAGRANT.flavorText: Little did he know… it was really the talbuk leg that was cursed.

TROGG GEMTOSSER.name: Trogg Gemtosser
TROGG GEMTOSSER.flavorText: Oh no! You're throwing valuable gems at me! Please stop!

RAM WRANGLER.name: Ram Wrangler
RAM WRANGLER.flavorText: Not getting trampled is really the trick here.

NEERU FIREBLADE.name: Neeru Fireblade
NEERU FIREBLADE.flavorText: Look at this guy! He’s obviously evil! OBVIOUSLY!!!

SPLENDIFEROUS WHIZBANG.name: Splendiferous Whizbang
SPLENDIFEROUS WHIZBANG.flavorText: After his work at Boomsday Labs, he's taken what Dr. Boom taught him and applied it to the most important inventions of all - TOYS!!!

BLOODSCENT VILEFIN.name: Bloodscent Vilefin
BLOODSCENT VILEFIN.flavorText: Tired of eating Jellyfish and Peanut Butter fish, it’s moved on to more gruesome meals.

LIGHTFORGED CRUSADER.name: Lightforged Crusader
LIGHTFORGED CRUSADER.flavorText: Self-appointed president of the Paladins Only Paladin Club.

RAVENOUS PTERRORDAX.name: Ravenous Pterrordax
RAVENOUS PTERRORDAX.flavorText: For better results, feed your pterrordax low-fat, high-fiber minions.

SANC'AZEL.name: Sanc'Azel
SANC'AZEL.flavorText: That castle has some serious drip.

BEAMING SIDEKICK.name: Beaming Sidekick
BEAMING SIDEKICK.flavorText: Sure, I'll carry the water! And the food! And the tents! And the cursed monkey paw!

SNOWFURY GIANT.name: Snowfury Giant
SNOWFURY GIANT.flavorText: This minion goes all the way to 11!

POWER WORD: REPLICATE.name: Power Word: Replicate
POWER WORD: REPLICATE.flavorText: Available as a bundle, along with Power Words: Detonate, Animate, Annihilate, and Paper Weight.

QUICK PICK.name: Quick Pick
QUICK PICK.flavorText: QUICK! Pick which quick pick trick will stick in the thick of the wick! Lickety split!

LIGHTFORGED BLESSING.name: Lightforged Blessing
LIGHTFORGED BLESSING.flavorText: Some might call this a lightforgery.

SHADOW WORD: FORBID.name: Shadow Word: Forbid
SHADOW WORD: FORBID.flavorText: At last, Priest has no more weaknesses.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/28/BT_726_DragonmawSkyStalker_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ BT_726_DragonmawSkyStalker_Play.wav <summon sound>

SINISTER DEAL.name: Sinister Deal
SINISTER DEAL.flavorText: "So, what's in the sack?" "Something... sinister." "Okay, it's a deal."

NINE LIVES.name: Nine Lives
NINE LIVES.flavorText: Beware the night of the living pets!

ARCH-THIEF RAFAAM.name: Arch-Thief Rafaam
ARCH-THIEF RAFAAM.flavorText: He's very good at retrieving artifacts. From other people's museums.

REPENTANCE.name: Repentance
REPENTANCE.flavorText: Repentance often comes in the moment before obliteration. Curious.

TOYRANTUS.name: Toyrantus
TOYRANTUS.flavorText: Dr. Boom was definitely a dinosaur kid.

SUMMONER DARKMARROW.name: Summoner Darkmarrow
SUMMONER DARKMARROW.flavorText: Some people say your name can influence what career you go into. Summoner Darkmarrow is not one of those people.

ANTI-MAGIC SHELL.name: Anti-Magic Shell
ANTI-MAGIC SHELL.flavorText: Using a spell to counter magic - a bit hypocritical don't you think?

UNLEASH THE HOUNDS.name: Unleash the Hounds
UNLEASH THE HOUNDS.flavorText: You must read the name of this card out loud each time you play it.

DESECRATED GRAVEYARD.name: Desecrated Graveyard
DESECRATED GRAVEYARD.flavorText: People are dying to get in.

TROLL CENTURION.name: Troll Centurion
TROLL CENTURION.flavorText: Centurion? Ha, come back when you’re a millennion.

JUNGLE PANTHER.name: Jungle Panther
JUNGLE PANTHER.flavorText: Stranglethorn is a beautiful place to visit, but you wouldn't want to live there.

RATCATCHER.name: Ratcatcher
RATCATCHER.flavorText: He's on the hunt for Togwaggle's missing rat.

WICKED STAB (RANK 1).name: Wicked Stab (Rank 1)
WICKED STAB (RANK 1).flavorText: Always go for the glowing weak point.

SADDLE UP!.name: Saddle Up!
SADDLE UP!.flavorText: And then they rode off into the sunset, not knowing they left their stove on.

UNPOPULAR HAS-BEEN.name: Unpopular Has-Been
UNPOPULAR HAS-BEEN.flavorText: Oh man, she used to rock more than ANYONE back in the Year of the Kraken. I wish I could've seen her perform back then…

VETERAN WARMEDIC.name: Veteran Warmedic
VETERAN WARMEDIC.flavorText: In times of war, warmedics bring their own medics.

DARKMOON RABBIT.name: Darkmoon Rabbit
DARKMOON RABBIT.flavorText: That's no ordinary rabbit! That's the most foul, cruel, and bad-tempered rodent you ever set eyes on!

EVASIVE FEYWING.name: Evasive Feywing
EVASIVE FEYWING.flavorText: I've never heard of this fey-dragon called "Brightwing," but if I HAD, I’d say we’d be best friends.

FAIRY TALE FOREST.name: Fairy Tale Forest
FAIRY TALE FOREST.flavorText: Man, I wish fairy tales were real, Durg'tash the Sorcerer.

WHIRLWIND TEMPEST.name: Whirlwind Tempest
WHIRLWIND TEMPEST.flavorText: And your minions with mega-windfury get... dizzy.

BELLOWING FLAMES.name: Bellowing Flames
BELLOWING FLAMES.flavorText: Too much bellowing. Not enough flames.

SHIELDMAIDEN.name: Shieldmaiden
SHIELDMAIDEN.flavorText: She has three shieldbearers in her party to supply her with back ups when she gets low on durability.

STONEHEARTH VINDICATOR.name: Stonehearth Vindicator
STONEHEARTH VINDICATOR.flavorText: “True strength comes from within your deck” is a whole lot less inspiring.

MIND CONTROL.name: Mind Control
MIND CONTROL.flavorText: Nominated as "Spell Most Likely to Make Your Opponent Punch the Wall."

VOLCANIC DRAKE.name: Volcanic Drake
VOLCANIC DRAKE.flavorText: Volcanic Drakes breathe lava instead of fire. The antacid vendor at Thorium Point does a brisk business with them.

KINGSBANE.name: Kingsbane
KINGSBANE.flavorText: But it has a soft spot for emperors.

RUNED MITHRIL ROD.name: Runed Mithril Rod
RUNED MITHRIL ROD.flavorText: "Please, I need these greens to disenchant them." —Every Enchanter Ever

RED GIANT.name: Red Giant
RED GIANT.flavorText: Lots of cards get played around it, but it's the real star.

MISTER MUKLA.name: Mister Mukla
MISTER MUKLA.flavorText: Music is Mukla's escape from his anger. When he's on-stage, it's like he's a whole different gorilla… Until you boo him.

SOLEMN VIGIL.name: Solemn Vigil
SOLEMN VIGIL.flavorText: Each year, folk gather in front of Blackrock Mountain to mourn those who were mind-controlled into the lava.

HECKLEFANG HYENA.name: Hecklefang Hyena
HECKLEFANG HYENA.flavorText: Even their teeth are laughing at you.

BLOOD KNIGHT.name: Blood Knight
BLOOD KNIGHT.flavorText: The Blood Knights get their holy powers from the Sunwell, which you should NOT bathe in.

SHADOW WORD: RUIN.name: Shadow Word: Ruin
SHADOW WORD: RUIN.flavorText: Discovered by a worgen priest after a giant spilled a drink on her new white robes.

BLIGHTBLOOD BERSERKER.name: Blightblood Berserker
BLIGHTBLOOD BERSERKER.flavorText: He should really go see a dentist about that tusk. And a dermatologist. And a therapist.

CROSSROADS WATCH POST.name: Crossroads Watch Post
CROSSROADS WATCH POST.flavorText: All of Barrens Chat is recorded and kept on thousands of scrolls stored beneath this tower.

YSERA.name: Ysera
YSERA.flavorText: Ysera rules the Emerald Dream. Which is some kind of green-mirror-version of the real world, or something?

MECHANO-EGG.name: Mechano-Egg
MECHANO-EGG.flavorText: When you need more iron in your diet.

DEMON COMPANION.name: Demon Companion
DEMON COMPANION.flavorText: Owning a pet can be real hell at times.

ALLIANCE BANNERMAN.name: Alliance Bannerman
ALLIANCE BANNERMAN.flavorText: Back in my day, we had to carry our inspiration uphill both ways to war.

WING COMMANDER ICHMAN.name: Wing Commander Ichman
WING COMMANDER ICHMAN.flavorText: “Mulverick, it’s not your flying, it’s your faction.”

AGAINST ALL ODDS.name: Against All Odds
AGAINST ALL ODDS.flavorText: Time to EVEN out the playing field.

FROSTSABER MATRIARCH.name: Frostsaber Matriarch
FROSTSABER MATRIARCH.flavorText: They say “don’t poke the bear”, but they NEVER said “don’t poke the frostsaber or her cubs”.

DOZING KELPKEEPER.name: Dozing Kelpkeeper
DOZING KELPKEEPER.flavorText: *Yaaaaawn* wake me up in another 5 Mana.

DAMAGED STEGOTRON.name: Damaged Stegotron
DAMAGED STEGOTRON.flavorText: Sadly the warranty does not cover fireballs or acts of Boom.

TOXICOLOGIST.name: Toxicologist
TOXICOLOGIST.flavorText: Double-majoring in culinary sciences was definitely a mistake.

DISRUPTIVE SPELLBREAKER.name: Disruptive Spellbreaker
DISRUPTIVE SPELLBREAKER.flavorText: WHO IS THE BLOOD ELVES' DENTIST?

BAYFIN BODYBUILDER.name: Bayfin Bodybuilder
BAYFIN BODYBUILDER.flavorText: Loves to run in flow motion.

MAWSWORN BAILIFF.name: Mawsworn Bailiff
MAWSWORN BAILIFF.flavorText: Bailiff, bring in the dancing lobsters!

HELLFIRE.name: Hellfire
HELLFIRE.flavorText: It's spells like these that make it hard for Warlocks to get decent help.

SHADOW MADNESS.name: Shadow Madness
SHADOW MADNESS.flavorText: You can rationalize it all you want, it's still a mean thing to do.

NEED FOR GREED.name: Need for Greed
NEED FOR GREED.flavorText: Sorry guys, I TOTALLY meant to click greed.

PRIMAL TALISMANS.name: Primal Talismans
PRIMAL TALISMANS.flavorText: All that remained from the first kobold colony: a single talisman and the word "Flamestrike."

GAME MASTER.name: Game Master
GAME MASTER.flavorText: "You hear the mrgrgls of angry murlocs approaching. Roll initiative!"

GORGONZORMU.name: Gorgonzormu
GORGONZORMU.flavorText: Don't remove this from your deck or else you'll be cutting the cheese.

SETHEKK VEILWEAVER.name: Sethekk Veilweaver
SETHEKK VEILWEAVER.flavorText: The Sethekk weren't able to survive this long by being wasteful with their power. Or their wacky hats.

NETHERSOUL BUSTER.name: Nethersoul Buster
NETHERSOUL BUSTER.flavorText: Why did the demon cross the streams? To get to The Other Side.

CITY ARCHITECT.name: City Architect
CITY ARCHITECT.flavorText: "Oh, wait, I had this turned the wrong way. This was supposed to be a tower."

TWILIGHT DRAKE.name: Twilight Drake
TWILIGHT DRAKE.flavorText: Twilight drakes feed on Mystical Energy. And Tacos.

INKVEIL AMBUSHER.name: Inkveil Ambusher
INKVEIL AMBUSHER.flavorText: You’ve got it wrong. She releases ink when you’re scared.

KING OF BEASTS.name: King of Beasts
KING OF BEASTS.flavorText: He never sleeps. Not even in the mighty jungle.

PYROBLAST.name: Pyroblast
PYROBLAST.flavorText: Take the time for an evil laugh after you draw this card.

THE CURATOR.name: The Curator
THE CURATOR.flavorText: The Curator guards Azeroth’s deadliest creatures, but it’s secretly terrified of squirrels.

STOCKADES GUARD.name: Stockades Guard
STOCKADES GUARD.flavorText: "You there! Defend this prison with your life. It's my break."

FIRST FLAME.name: First Flame
FIRST FLAME.flavorText: You never forget your first love: fire.

SCARLET CRUSADER.name: Scarlet Crusader
SCARLET CRUSADER.flavorText: Never wash your whites with a Scarlet Crusader.

HOLY CHAMPION.name: Holy Champion
HOLY CHAMPION.flavorText: She really likes seeing people get better. That's why she hurts them in the first place.

TWILIGHT MEDIUM.name: Twilight Medium
TWILIGHT MEDIUM.flavorText: This twilight is too dark. And this twilight is too bright. But THIS twilight is juuuuuuuuust right!

COSMIC ANOMALY.name: Cosmic Anomaly
COSMIC ANOMALY.flavorText: INGREDIENTS: STAR-STUFF, BLUE 1, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS.

FORGED IN FLAME.name: Forged in Flame
FORGED IN FLAME.flavorText: Don't worry, your wounds are self-cauterizing!

WANDERING MONSTER.name: Wandering Monster
WANDERING MONSTER.flavorText: Not all who wander are lost. This one is lost though, for sure.

MARUUT STONEBINDER.name: Maruut Stonebinder
MARUUT STONEBINDER.flavorText: Savior of the World Pillar, Maruut valiantly fought the Twilight's Hammer to aid Therazane against the Cataclysm.

MYRA ROTSPRING.name: Myra Rotspring
MYRA ROTSPRING.flavorText: On her first day on the job, Myra removed the smoke detectors.

RING OF COURAGE.name: Ring of Courage
RING OF COURAGE.flavorText: Now to find the Ring of Wisdom and Ring of Power.

HOLY LIGHT.name: Holy Light
HOLY LIGHT.flavorText: If you are often bathed in Holy Light, you should consider wearing sunscreen.

MIDWAY MANIAC.name: Midway Maniac
MIDWAY MANIAC.flavorText: Faire owners hate him! Learn his secrets with one simple spell!

OBSIDIAN STATUE.name: Obsidian Statue
OBSIDIAN STATUE.flavorText: The original artist spent many hours with a fine chisel perfecting the facial expression for maximum tauntiness.

HUNGRY ETTIN.name: Hungry Ettin
HUNGRY ETTIN.flavorText: How can he be hungry… if he's Ettin!?

SPELLBENDER.name: Spellbender
SPELLBENDER.flavorText: While it's fun to intercept enemy lightning bolts, a spellbender much prefers to intercept opposing Marks of the Wild. It just feels meaner. And blood elves... well, they're a little mean.

WINDCHILL.name: Windchill
WINDCHILL.flavorText: The thermometer says it’s 0° right now, but with the windchill it feels like -25°.

MARK OF NATURE.name: Mark of Nature
MARK OF NATURE.flavorText: Druids call it the "Mark of Nature." Everyone else calls it "needing a bath."

NOBLE MOUNT.name: Noble Mount
NOBLE MOUNT.flavorText: The Horde rued the day that Cariel was allowed to take her pet to work.

VILE CALL.name: Vile Call
VILE CALL.flavorText: "We're calling to inform you that your vehicle's insurance is about to expire."

SERENITY.name: Serenity
SERENITY.flavorText: Ra-den loves teaching yoga on his off-hours.

EARTH SHOCK.name: Earth Shock
EARTH SHOCK.flavorText: Earth Shock? Shouldn't it be "Azeroth Shock"?

SILVER VANGUARD.name: Silver Vanguard
SILVER VANGUARD.flavorText: Float like a Faerie Dragon, sting like a Hivequeen.

GOLDWING.name: Goldwing
GOLDWING.flavorText: This HAS to be worth more dust, right?

WARHORSE TRAINER.name: Warhorse Trainer
WARHORSE TRAINER.flavorText: He doesn't even get Sundays off. Every day he's hostling.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/d/dc/VO_AT_075_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_075_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/3e/VO_AT_075_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_075_ATTACK_02.wav Charge!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/3c/VO_AT_075_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_075_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

THE GALACTIC PROJECTION ORB.name: The Galactic Projection Orb
THE GALACTIC PROJECTION ORB.flavorText: Look closely in the ball and you'll see the expansion of space and time itself. Or their projections, anyway.

SILAS DARKMOON.name: Silas Darkmoon
SILAS DARKMOON.flavorText: "You might remember me from such attractions as 'Being Shot out of a Cannon' or 'That Carousel Ate My Friend.'"

DARK TRANSFORMATION.name: Dark Transformation
DARK TRANSFORMATION.flavorText: The Northrend Arm Wrestling Championship just found its new champion.

HOGGER.name: Hogger
HOGGER.flavorText: Hogger is super powerful. If you kill him, it's because he let you.

MASTER OAKHEART.name: Master Oakheart
MASTER OAKHEART.flavorText: His adventuring party consists of Goldshire Footman, Frostwolf Grunt and Hadronox.

DEATHBRINGER SAURFANG.name: Deathbringer Saurfang
DEATHBRINGER SAURFANG.flavorText: "In hindsight, maybe I should have let the Alliance have all the fun back at the Wrathgate."

CATCH OF THE DAY.name: Catch of the Day
CATCH OF THE DAY.flavorText: Only its fish mother thinks it's a catch.

VEREESA WINDRUNNER.name: Vereesa Windrunner
VEREESA WINDRUNNER.flavorText: Good things come in threes: Windrunner sisters and arrows of Thori'dal.

SHADOWFORM.name: Shadowform
SHADOWFORM.flavorText: If a bright light shines on a priest in Shadowform… do they cast a shadow?

FELGUARD.name: Felguard
FELGUARD.flavorText: Yes, he'll fight for you. BUT HE'S NOT GOING TO LIKE IT.

KEEPER OF ULDAMAN.name: Keeper of Uldaman
KEEPER OF ULDAMAN.flavorText: U da man! No, U da man!

STAMPEDING ROAR.name: Stampeding Roar
STAMPEDING ROAR.flavorText: The Gurubashi Arena has an extremely permissive policy on pets in the workplace.

WICKERFLAME BURNBRISTLE.name: Wickerflame Burnbristle
WICKERFLAME BURNBRISTLE.flavorText: Wickerflame spent years as a recruit for the Goons, never making the big-time because he always fired his chest-cannon too slowly. "Hey," he thought, "maybe if I keep my beard lit on fire, I can do this faster." BOOM, promoted.

UNPOWERED MAULER.name: Unpowered Mauler
UNPOWERED MAULER.flavorText: After a stressful work day it really needs an outlet.

MUROZOND, THIEF OF TIME.name: Murozond, Thief of Time
MUROZOND, THIEF OF TIME.flavorText: By unwinding the fall of C'Thun, Murozond would claim the Old God's power, and with it, the world.

SORCERER'S APPRENTICE.name: Sorcerer's Apprentice
SORCERER'S APPRENTICE.flavorText: Apprentices are great for bossing around. "Conjure me some mana buns! And a coffee! Make that a mana coffee!"

ELVEN ARCHER.name: Elven Archer
ELVEN ARCHER.flavorText: Don't bother asking her out on a date. She'll shoot you down.

CLASH OF THE COLOSSALS.name: Clash of the Colossals
CLASH OF THE COLOSSALS.flavorText: Don’t let this distract you from the fact that in 1998, Ozumat threw Neptulon off Shell in a Cell, and plummeted 16 fathoms through an announcer’s table.

GNOMISH EXPERIMENTER.name: Gnomish Experimenter
GNOMISH EXPERIMENTER.flavorText: He's legitimately surprised every time he turns himself into a chicken.

CHATTY MACAW.name: Chatty Macaw
CHATTY MACAW.flavorText: Stop repeating yourself! Stop repeating yourself!

STARSHOOTER.name: Starshooter
STARSHOOTER.flavorText: Shoot for the stars! And if you miss, just don't hit me.

TWISTED WORGEN.name: Twisted Worgen
TWISTED WORGEN.flavorText: Sometimes the Old Gods' corruptions gives you power untold, sometimes you get +1 Attack. We can’t all be winners in the Eldritch lottery.

SHADOWCLOTH NEEDLE.name: Shadowcloth Needle
SHADOWCLOTH NEEDLE.flavorText: Makes light of the darkest repair jobs.

RAZORFEN BEASTMASTER.name: Razorfen Beastmaster
RAZORFEN BEASTMASTER.flavorText: It's a homebrew variant on my favorite role-playing game.

PRINCE MALCHEZAAR.name: Prince Malchezaar
PRINCE MALCHEZAAR.flavorText: He was super excited to acquire Gorehowl at a garage sale! Then super disappointed to find out it was a foam reproduction.

CALL IN THE FINISHERS.name: Call in the Finishers
CALL IN THE FINISHERS.flavorText: When you really need a job done… but you don't really care if it gets done right.

SOUTHSEA SQUIDFACE.name: Southsea Squidface
SOUTHSEA SQUIDFACE.flavorText: Quick! Before I drown! Let me sharpen your sword for you.

CORRIDOR SLEEPER.name: Corridor Sleeper
CORRIDOR SLEEPER.flavorText: In the workshop, I go deeper. In the mulligan, I'm a keeper. This time, I'm even cheaper. You guessed it right, I'm Corridor Sleeper.

SHIELD OF HONOR.name: Shield of Honor
SHIELD OF HONOR.flavorText: "Sir, this shield would've been more helpful last turn!"

VIBRANT SQUIRREL.name: Vibrant Squirrel
VIBRANT SQUIRREL.flavorText: Oh, they're cute now. Just wait till they unleash a Savage Roar.

MISH-MASH MOSHER.name: Mish-Mash Mosher
MISH-MASH MOSHER.flavorText: In the pit, he feels more alive than ever.

GIFTWRAPPED WHELP.name: Giftwrapped Whelp
GIFTWRAPPED WHELP.flavorText: Don't forget to poke fire-breathing holes in the box!

DRAGON EGG.name: Dragon Egg
DRAGON EGG.flavorText: Think of them as bullets for your dragon gun.

FROM THE SCRAPHEAP.name: From the Scrapheap
FROM THE SCRAPHEAP.flavorText: Well that's a load of scrap.

MENACING NIMBUS.name: Menacing Nimbus
MENACING NIMBUS.flavorText: Electra stores her elementals in the cloud.

DEATHWING, MAD ASPECT.name: Deathwing, Mad Aspect
DEATHWING, MAD ASPECT.flavorText: Bite that one, bite that other one, claw this one, swallow that one whole....

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/8b/VO_DRG_026_Male_Dragon_Attack_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_DRG_026_Male_Dragon_Attack_03.wav CATACLYSM!

AL'AKIR, THE WINDS OF TIME.name: Al'Akir, the Winds of Time
AL'AKIR, THE WINDS OF TIME.flavorText: Murozond sought unlikely allies in his fight against the Bronze Dragonflight.

BOOK WYRM.name: Book Wyrm
BOOK WYRM.flavorText: His favorites are classic tragedies like "The Hobbit" and "Grendel".

ROBES OF PROTECTION.name: Robes of Protection
ROBES OF PROTECTION.flavorText: Warning: Robes of Protection are intended for targeted effects only and are not an effective defense against Flamestrike, Twisting Nether, or other AOE attacks.

STONE DRAKE.name: Stone Drake
STONE DRAKE.flavorText: "I am the great Stone Drake - good morning!"

PRIEST OF THE DECEASED.name: Priest of the Deceased
PRIEST OF THE DECEASED.flavorText: "Funnel cakes? I haven't had those in years…"

DART TRAP.name: Dart Trap
DART TRAP.flavorText: Five years of tap-dancing lessons are FINALLY going to pay off!

HOWLFIEND.name: Howlfiend
HOWLFIEND.flavorText: The problem is that he carries those cards in his mouth.

TOL'VIR STONESHAPER.name: Tol'vir Stoneshaper
TOL'VIR STONESHAPER.flavorText: He spends a lot of time keeping himself in stoneshape.

OGRE MAGI.name: Ogre Magi
OGRE MAGI.flavorText: Training Ogres in the art of spellcasting is a questionable decision.

REMORSELESS WINTER.name: Remorseless Winter
REMORSELESS WINTER.flavorText: In the Badlands, this is a Rare.

SPREADING MADNESS.name: Spreading Madness
SPREADING MADNESS.flavorText: Most citizens of Darkshire wear those surgical masks to prevent spreading Madness to tourists.

ORACLE OF ELUNE.name: Oracle of Elune
ORACLE OF ELUNE.flavorText: Even the moon goddess needs to back up her databases.

MAGNATAUR ALPHA.name: Magnataur Alpha
MAGNATAUR ALPHA.flavorText: Playing him also gets you into the Magnataur Beta.

EMERALD REAVER.name: Emerald Reaver
EMERALD REAVER.flavorText: Not to be confused with clubbing enthusiast Emerald Raver.

HIDDEN WISDOM.name: Hidden Wisdom
HIDDEN WISDOM.flavorText: Find your own wisdom. Perhaps behind the couch.

PSYCHIC CONJURER.name: Psychic Conjurer
PSYCHIC CONJURER.flavorText: "I see... a WISP? Why do you have a wisp?!"

MOUNT HYJAL IMPOSTER.name: Mount Hyjal Imposter
MOUNT HYJAL IMPOSTER.flavorText: Among Tyrande's forces, Murozond had planted agents to ensure Archimonde's victory.

WILFRED FIZZLEBANG.name: Wilfred Fizzlebang
WILFRED FIZZLEBANG.flavorText: He can summon anything, even a FEARSOME DOOMGUARD*. *He's pretty sure this is going to work out.

MUENSTEROSITY.name: Muensterosity
MUENSTEROSITY.flavorText: We were going to put some cheesy joke here, but we goudan't come up with anything.

NAGA'S PRIDE.name: Naga's Pride
NAGA'S PRIDE.flavorText: Lionfish, Naga, and Spears, oh my!

HYLDNIR FROSTRIDER.name: Hyldnir Frostrider
HYLDNIR FROSTRIDER.flavorText: Don't be fooled, that polar bear's the one in charge.

SNEAKY SCOUT.name: Sneaky Scout
SNEAKY SCOUT.flavorText: Do you know what they call Scouts that aren't sneaky? Target practice.

FIERY WAR AXE.name: Fiery War Axe
FIERY WAR AXE.flavorText: During times of tranquility and harmony, this weapon was called by its less popular name, Chilly Peace Axe.

LIVING SEED (RANK 1).name: Living Seed (Rank 1)
LIVING SEED (RANK 1).flavorText: Every desert needs an oasis. And it's Guff's duty to make it happen.

BLAST TORTOISE.name: Blast Tortoise
BLAST TORTOISE.flavorText: Who's that minion? ... Iiiiit's Blast Tortoise! "Blast tortoise."

BIOLUMINESCENCE.name: Bioluminescence
BIOLUMINESCENCE.flavorText: The perfect card for Spell Damage Shaman and Spelling Bee Shaman.

SIGIL OF ALACRITY.name: Sigil of Alacrity
SIGIL OF ALACRITY.flavorText: Red means stop. Purple means GO REALLY FAST.

SANITIZE.name: Sanitize
SANITIZE.flavorText: We were originally going to make a joke about a popular streamer, but one of our designers is a total germaphobe.

UNBOUND ELEMENTAL.name: Unbound Elemental
UNBOUND ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Unlike bound elementals, Unbound ones really enjoy a night on the town.

GYREWORM.name: Gyreworm
GYREWORM.flavorText: This game of ring toss just got really intense.

ANETHERON.name: Anetheron
ANETHERON.flavorText: Leads every demonic invasion. Hopefully this one turns out better than the World Tree.

GLOW-TRON.name: Glow-Tron
GLOW-TRON.flavorText: They tried for weeks to make a stealth version, but eventually decided to just let it glow.

ARKONITE DEFENSE CRYSTAL.name: Arkonite Defense Crystal
ARKONITE DEFENSE CRYSTAL.flavorText: I was just asking if that's what you wanted your Starship to look like, there's no need to get defensive.

WARSONG OUTRIDER.name: Warsong Outrider
WARSONG OUTRIDER.flavorText: When it comes to the Warsong clan, outriders are the insiders.

SEA SHILL.name: Sea Shill
SEA SHILL.flavorText: She shills shea sells down at the sea shtore.

HADRONOX.name: Hadronox
HADRONOX.flavorText: The viziers of Azjol-Nerub released Hadronox as a last-ditch effort to hold back the Lich King. They did so by VERY carefully scooping him up in a LARGE newspaper and releasing him.

SIGHTLESS MAGISTRATE.name: Sightless Magistrate
SIGHTLESS MAGISTRATE.flavorText: Does "Justice is Blind" still apply with Spectral Sight?

ARROW SMITH.name: Arrow Smith
ARROW SMITH.flavorText: "What do you mean it's a violin bow!?!"

FRIGHTENED FLUNKY.name: Frightened Flunky
FRIGHTENED FLUNKY.flavorText: Some people just aren't cut out to be supervillain material.

MALYGOS.name: Malygos
MALYGOS.flavorText: Malygos hates it when mortals use magic. He gets so mad!

ULTIMATE INFESTATION.name: Ultimate Infestation
ULTIMATE INFESTATION.flavorText: Ghouls in the pipe, five by five.

KAEL'THAS SINSTRIDER.name: Kael'thas Sinstrider
KAEL'THAS SINSTRIDER.flavorText: You heard about Kael'thas? That's messed up, right?

STAND AGAINST DARKNESS.name: Stand Against Darkness
STAND AGAINST DARKNESS.flavorText: Or if you're too tired, you can just kind of lean against the darkness.

ADAPTIVE AMALGAM.name: Adaptive Amalgam
ADAPTIVE AMALGAM.flavorText: We've only explored 5% of the ocean. So there's like a 95% chance this is accurate.

MOLTEN GIANT.name: Molten Giant
MOLTEN GIANT.flavorText: He gets terrible heartburn. BECAUSE HE IS FULL OF LAVA.

TOME OF INTELLECT.name: Tome of Intellect
TOME OF INTELLECT.flavorText: Just a compilation of napkins of intellect.

DART THROW.name: Dart Throw
DART THROW.flavorText: Did you know: Hitting the same target twice is only for skilled players. This has been a 'Dart Fact'!

RED CARD.name: Red Card
RED CARD.flavorText: Finally, Demon Hunter has expanded its color palette to TWO colors!

ALLOY ADVISOR.name: Alloy Advisor
ALLOY ADVISOR.flavorText: Numbers may betray you, but steel... steel you can trust.

SYLVANAS WINDRUNNER.name: Sylvanas Windrunner
SYLVANAS WINDRUNNER.flavorText: Sylvanas was turned into the Banshee Queen by Arthas, but he probably should have just killed her because it just pissed her off.

TOWN CRIER.name: Town Crier
TOWN CRIER.flavorText: When he was younger, he was the town crybaby.

TRIPLEWICK TRICKSTER.name: Triplewick Trickster
TRIPLEWICK TRICKSTER.flavorText: You no take candle! Or second candle. You can take third candle though.

AVALANCHE.name: Avalanche
AVALANCHE.flavorText: One of our more snowbally cards.

SHIRVALLAH, THE TIGER.name: Shirvallah, the Tiger
SHIRVALLAH, THE TIGER.flavorText: On bended knee Thekal placed his weapon upon Shirvallah’s altar, whereupon she slowly knocked it off with her paw.

FELFIRE IN THE HOLE!.name: Felfire in the Hole!
FELFIRE IN THE HOLE!.flavorText: Fear not, feebleminded friends, for failure to fell your foes with felfire is fundamentally farfetched!

HOLLOW HOUND.name: Hollow Hound
HOLLOW HOUND.flavorText: Uh oh, the hollow hound is coming out of its cage! Don't worry though, it's doing just fine.

ENERGY SHAPER.name: Energy Shaper
ENERGY SHAPER.flavorText: '"I can do a snake for you?"

STORM GIANT.name: Storm Giant
STORM GIANT.flavorText: Storm Giant, Frost Giant, Molten Giant... I want Fair-weather and Sunshine Giant!

THE STORM BRINGER.name: The Storm Bringer
THE STORM BRINGER.flavorText: Finally, Electra can work from home.

SUNFURY CHAMPION.name: Sunfury Champion
SUNFURY CHAMPION.flavorText: Champion of the Great Blood Elf Bake Off 12 years running.

MELTEMENTAL.name: Meltemental
MELTEMENTAL.flavorText: "Who left these wet bracers on the ground?"

DEFIAS RINGLEADER.name: Defias Ringleader
DEFIAS RINGLEADER.flavorText: He stole the deed to town years ago, so technically the town is his. He just calls people Scrub to be mean.

BLACKWATER PIRATE.name: Blackwater Pirate
BLACKWATER PIRATE.flavorText: "Look, they fell off the back of a ship, do you want them or not? I have a meeting with Y'Shaarj in like ten minutes."

WIDOWBLOOM SEEDSMAN.name: Widowbloom Seedsman
WIDOWBLOOM SEEDSMAN.flavorText: Sometimes a blue thumb is better than a green one.

QUESTING ADVENTURER.name: Questing Adventurer
QUESTING ADVENTURER.flavorText: "Does anyone have some extra Boar Pelts?"

CLEAR CONSCIENCE.name: Clear Conscience
CLEAR CONSCIENCE.flavorText: Do you swear to give the buff, the whole buff, and nothing but the buff, so help you Kyrestia?

FALLEN SUN CLERIC.name: Fallen Sun Cleric
FALLEN SUN CLERIC.flavorText: It's hard to keep a Shattered Sun Cleric down.

ABYSSAL ENFORCER.name: Abyssal Enforcer
ABYSSAL ENFORCER.flavorText: The Kabal print this on every package of illicit Mana Crystals: WARNING - DO NOT PUT WITHIN REACH OF ABYSSALS. THIS IS NOT APPROVED FOR USE BY FLAMING DEMONS OF ANY KIND.

ROYAL LIBRARIAN.name: Royal Librarian
ROYAL LIBRARIAN.flavorText: Books on how to flip the Auction House are down that way.

VOL'JIN.name: Vol'jin
VOL'JIN.flavorText: Vol'jin is a shadow hunter, which is like a shadow priest except more voodoo.

DREAMPETAL FLORIST.name: Dreampetal Florist
DREAMPETAL FLORIST.flavorText: Unlike gnomes, dreampetals grow more than 3 feet tall.

ARCANE BOLT.name: Arcane Bolt
ARCANE BOLT.flavorText: Just you wait until I have 8 mana!

HALDURON BRIGHTWING.name: Halduron Brightwing
HALDURON BRIGHTWING.flavorText: I wanted to generate a legendary, but I held da wrong Brightwing.

LOST TALLSTRIDER.name: Lost Tallstrider
LOST TALLSTRIDER.flavorText: The message, "If found, please return to Mulgore," is tattooed on his rear.

THE RAT KING.name: The Rat King
THE RAT KING.flavorText: "I'm the giant rat that makes all of da rules!"

FULL-BLOWN EVIL.name: Full-Blown Evil
FULL-BLOWN EVIL.flavorText: This isn’t your average, everyday evil. This is ADVANCED evil.

TAE'THELAN BLOODWATCHER.name: Tae'thelan Bloodwatcher
TAE'THELAN BLOODWATCHER.flavorText: He's a big fan of Control Death Knight live streams.

VAPORIZE.name: Vaporize
VAPORIZE.flavorText: Rumor has it that Deathwing brought about the Cataclysm after losing a game to this card. We may never know the truth.

BARREL OF MONKEYS.name: Barrel of Monkeys
BARREL OF MONKEYS.flavorText: There used to be four monkeys, but then one fell off and bumped his head.

WISDOM OF NORGANNON.name: Wisdom of Norgannon
WISDOM OF NORGANNON.flavorText: Now all we need is the power and courage of Norgannon.

TOMB TRAITOR.name: Tomb Traitor
TOMB TRAITOR.flavorText: You enjoy raiding, I enjoying traitoring. We are not the same.

SPELLWARD JEWELER.name: Spellward Jeweler
SPELLWARD JEWELER.flavorText: The fanciest possible way of distracting enemies with shiny things.

SKELETON CREW.name: Skeleton Crew
SKELETON CREW.flavorText: They don't sweat, breathe or need lit candles... what more could you ask?

WASTE REMOVER.name: Waste Remover
WASTE REMOVER.flavorText: Always follow the three Rs: REDUCE their world to ash, REUSE their bones as paperweights, and RECYCLE!

CONCEAL.name: Conceal
CONCEAL.flavorText: Rogues conceal everything but their emotions. You can't get 'em to shut up about feelings.

TINY KNIGHT OF EVIL.name: Tiny Knight of Evil
TINY KNIGHT OF EVIL.flavorText: "No, no, no. I asked for a tiny JESTER of evil."

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/8e/VO_AT_021_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_021_ATTACK_02.wav Here we go!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/d/d5/VO_AT_021_DEATH_05.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_021_DEATH_05.wav <death sound>

SI:7 OPERATIVE.name: SI:7 Operative
SI:7 OPERATIVE.flavorText: What do you mean you're out of ponies?

STARLIGHT WHELP.name: Starlight Whelp
STARLIGHT WHELP.flavorText: Starlight, star bright, first whelp I see tonight.

IMP MASTER.name: Imp Master
IMP MASTER.flavorText: She would enjoy the job a lot more if she just could get the imps to QUIT BITING HER.

PROPHET VELEN.name: Prophet Velen
PROPHET VELEN.flavorText: He's been exiled from his home, and all his brothers turned evil, but otherwise he doesn't have a lot to complain about.

TOAD OF THE WILDS.name: Toad of the Wilds
TOAD OF THE WILDS.flavorText: "Someday we'll find it. The Oasis Connection. The peons, the caravans, and me."

BLAZING POWER.name: Blazing Power
BLAZING POWER.flavorText: Apply heat directly to the damaged area.

MYSTERY WINNER.name: Mystery Winner
MYSTERY WINNER.flavorText: Yeah, but the mystery prize could be anything! Even a boat!

GRAND FINALE.name: Grand Finale
GRAND FINALE.flavorText: Considering all the other hazards at Darkmoon, overindulgent pyrotechnics seem downright pedestrian.

CHUM BUCKET.name: Chum Bucket
CHUM BUCKET.flavorText: Time to go in for the krill.

ASTRAL VIGILANT.name: Astral Vigilant
ASTRAL VIGILANT.flavorText: Draenei are so dedicated that they remain vigilant even in death.

STEELDANCER.name: Steeldancer
STEELDANCER.flavorText: Pretty powerful if you blade your cards right.

NAT, THE DARKFISHER.name: Nat, the Darkfisher
NAT, THE DARKFISHER.flavorText: You can take away his humanity, but you will never take away his fishing pole.

ARCHSPORE MSSHI'FN.name: Archspore Msshi'fn
ARCHSPORE MSSHI'FN.flavorText: Brave leader of the Sporeggar. Guided by the philosophy that one should not mssh with matters that are not one's msshiness.

SPECTRAL SIGHT.name: Spectral Sight
SPECTRAL SIGHT.flavorText: "Pick a card, any card! Preferably the left- or right-most card."

CUTLASS COURIER.name: Cutlass Courier
CUTLASS COURIER.flavorText: It may be a cutlass, but you can cut lads with it too.

THE MARSH QUEEN.name: The Marsh Queen
THE MARSH QUEEN.flavorText: Question: What's scarier, one giant angry dinosaur or 20 smaller vicious ones? Answer: AHHHHHHH THEY FOUND MEEEEEE

SUMMER FLOWERCHILD.name: Summer Flowerchild
SUMMER FLOWERCHILD.flavorText: "Ugh, those Winter Floweradults just don't get our music."

RUNE OF THE ARCHMAGE.name: Rune of the Archmage
RUNE OF THE ARCHMAGE.flavorText: “It’s not a slot machine! It took YEARS of rigorous studying the intricacies of the universe to unravel the strands of reality. The arcane knowledge alone would enfeeble even the most brilliant of minds. Give it the credence it deserves. It’s a magic slot machine.”

BARTEND-O-BOT.name: Bartend-O-Bot
BARTEND-O-BOT.flavorText: Bartend-O-Bot! Make my Outcast card DO SOMETHING!

HALEH, MATRON PROTECTORATE.name: Haleh, Matron Protectorate
HALEH, MATRON PROTECTORATE.flavorText: Oh, how do you solve a problem like Onyxia?

HIGH CULTIST BASALEPH.name: High Cultist Basaleph
HIGH CULTIST BASALEPH.flavorText: "It's not a cult! It's a collection of like-minded individuals that enjoy undead. And rituals. And doing what I say. "

MOONFANG.name: Moonfang
MOONFANG.flavorText: Moonforehead just didn't have the same ring to it.

UNIDENTIFIED SHIELD.name: Unidentified Shield
UNIDENTIFIED SHIELD.flavorText: The kobold stared at the bundle for a long time. “Ah hah!” he said. “It’s a shield.”

FORBIDDEN FLAME.name: Forbidden Flame
FORBIDDEN FLAME.flavorText: WARNING: This flame is not to be used unless you are a licensed acolyte of the Old Gods.

OBLITERATE.name: Obliterate
OBLITERATE.flavorText: Why is 6 afraid of 7? Because Obliterate 9!

SCREAMING BANSHEE.name: Screaming Banshee
SCREAMING BANSHEE.flavorText: Her singing will be sure to wake you up (wake you up inside).

AUDIO SPLITTER.name: Audio Splitter
AUDIO SPLITTER.flavorText: "I tried to give him some constructive criticism but gosh, he really hates feedback!"

AZSHARAN SCAVENGER.name: Azsharan Scavenger
AZSHARAN SCAVENGER.flavorText: Some local Murloc populations have adapted to survive in the harsh conditions of the ruins, much to the fascination of Sir Finley.

BOUNCING BLADE.name: Bouncing Blade
BOUNCING BLADE.flavorText: Only goblins would think this was a good idea. Even they are starting to have their doubts.

CRUEL DINOMANCER.name: Cruel Dinomancer
CRUEL DINOMANCER.flavorText: As that old saying goes: "you don't get into dinomancing to make friends."

FAN CLUB.name: Fan Club
FAN CLUB.flavorText: "Well that was weird. Yeah, I just walked up to the president of the fan club, he blabbered on for like 10 minutes, and then gave me a bike voucher..."

MAGATHA, BANE OF MUSIC.name: Magatha, Bane of Music
MAGATHA, BANE OF MUSIC.flavorText: Not to be confused with that one other "-agatha" that likes when you play minions.

VOLUME UP.name: Volume Up
VOLUME UP.flavorText: You have to pay Mana to do that!? I thought it was just in the settings menu!

DARK IRON SKULKER.name: Dark Iron Skulker
DARK IRON SKULKER.flavorText: He loves skulking. He skulks after hours just for the joy of it, but his friends are pretty worried he'll get burnt out.

SAVAGE ROAR.name: Savage Roar
SAVAGE ROAR.flavorText: What do they roar? Nobody can quite tell, but it sounds like "Elephant Macho Breeze". It's probably not that, though.

JINYU WATERSPEAKER.name: Jinyu Waterspeaker
JINYU WATERSPEAKER.flavorText: Waterspeakers can tell the future! So the Jade Lotus employs them to speculate on the Auction House.

TOTEM GOLEM.name: Totem Golem
TOTEM GOLEM.flavorText: What happens when you glue a buncha totems together.

EVASIVE WYRM.name: Evasive Wyrm
EVASIVE WYRM.flavorText: Deftly dodges spells like a real wiggle wyrm.

MIXTAPE.name: Mixtape
MIXTAPE.flavorText: That tape has got poetry and clarinet on it, Garona. POETRY. AND CLARINET.

MASS DISPEL.name: Mass Dispel
MASS DISPEL.flavorText: It dispels buffs, powers, hopes, and dreams.

VOIDLORD.name: Voidlord
VOIDLORD.flavorText: Never let it hold your checkbook.

ICICLE.name: Icicle
ICICLE.flavorText: This may appear weak at frost glance, but it's actually a very ice spell.

DISTRESSED KVALDIR.name: Distressed Kvaldir
DISTRESSED KVALDIR.flavorText: Oh look at that, I have been impaled.

KROLUSK BARKSTRIPPER.name: Krolusk Barkstripper
KROLUSK BARKSTRIPPER.flavorText: My friend went krolusk tipping once… once!

BRONZE HERALD.name: Bronze Herald
BRONZE HERALD.flavorText: This is why you shouldn’t shoot the messenger.

PLOT TWIST.name: Plot Twist
PLOT TWIST.flavorText: It’s coming from inside the deck!

WHISPERS OF THE DEEP.name: Whispers of the Deep
WHISPERS OF THE DEEP.flavorText: And in the darkest of depths, the sailor heard a command from inside his own mind… “You will also buff my original card to 9 Mana.”

HORN OF WRATHION.name: Horn of Wrathion
HORN OF WRATHION.flavorText: You can count the rings and find out Wrathion's true age.

SAFEGUARD.name: Safeguard
SAFEGUARD.flavorText: Keep it secret. Keep it safeguarded!

WEAPONIZED PI\u00d1ATA.name: Weaponized Piñata
WEAPONIZED PI\u00d1ATA.flavorText: It'll be fine. It's not like they have any reason to hate us.

GOLDSHIRE FOOTMAN.name: Goldshire Footman
GOLDSHIRE FOOTMAN.flavorText: If 1/2 minions are all that is defending Goldshire, you would think it would have been overrun years ago.

ESCAPED MANASABER.name: Escaped Manasaber
ESCAPED MANASABER.flavorText: Captive manasabers don't behave much better--they're always scratching your furniture and coughing up mana balls.

BOGSHAPER.name: Bogshaper
BOGSHAPER.flavorText: The tricky part is getting them to HOLD their shape.

IDENTITY THEFT.name: Identity Theft
IDENTITY THEFT.flavorText: Identity theft is not a joke, Jim!

GRUMBLE, WORLDSHAKER.name: Grumble, Worldshaker
GRUMBLE, WORLDSHAKER.flavorText: The grumbling grew to a mighty rumbling, and out of the caverns the kobolds came tumbling.

WITCHWOOD APPLE.name: Witchwood Apple
WITCHWOOD APPLE.flavorText: An apple a day keeps the worgen at bay.

GRIEVOUS BITE.name: Grievous Bite
GRIEVOUS BITE.flavorText: Ooh. I'll have a bite of this, and of this, and of this...

VERANUS.name: Veranus
VERANUS.flavorText: As an empty nester, she just misses her little ones.

MISDIRECTION.name: Misdirection
MISDIRECTION.flavorText: Sometimes it's as simple as putting on a fake mustache and pointing at someone else.

FORBIDDEN ANCIENT.name: Forbidden Ancient
FORBIDDEN ANCIENT.flavorText: This Ancient was banned from the local tavern after tucking a 'Dr. Boom' up its sleeve.

NERUBIAN EGG.name: Nerubian Egg
NERUBIAN EGG.flavorText: Eggs are a good source of protein and Nerubians.

SLAGMAW THE SLUMBERING.name: Slagmaw the Slumbering
SLAGMAW THE SLUMBERING.flavorText: You delved too greedily and too deep. You know what they awoke in the darkness of the Badlands: Rush and Taunt.

JUMBO IMP.name: Jumbo Imp
JUMBO IMP.flavorText: Jumbo in size! Huge in E.V.I.L.!

VRYGHOUL.name: Vryghoul
VRYGHOUL.flavorText: It's pronounced VERY GHOUL. Don't let anyone tell you different.

BLADE DANCE.name: Blade Dance
BLADE DANCE.flavorText: The surest way to clear the dance floor.

COMMANDER ULTHOK.name: Commander Ulthok
COMMANDER ULTHOK.flavorText: He likes to spend his free time in his garden, growing Bloodradish, Bloodcabbage, and his favorite, Bloodbloom.

DEVOUR MIND.name: Devour Mind
DEVOUR MIND.flavorText: A mind is a terrible thing to waste. Seconds, anyone?

DRAGON'S FURY.name: Dragon's Fury
DRAGON'S FURY.flavorText: “C’mon Hucklemuck. She’ll never notice if we take just one little coin.”

MOGOR'S CHAMPION.name: Mogor's Champion
MOGOR'S CHAMPION.flavorText: This champion has learned from the best. Except for his target selection.
