FLANKING MANEUVER.name: Flanking Maneuver
FLANKING MANEUVER.flavorText: So, do we have advantage? Can I sneak attack?

PAINTED CANVASAUR.name: Painted Canvasaur
PAINTED CANVASAUR.flavorText: Oh this is a present? Would you like that gift raptor not?

BARGAIN BIN BUCCANEER.name: Bargain Bin Buccaneer
BARGAIN BIN BUCCANEER.flavorText: Thrift stores have the best buccaneers.

DEMONFUSE.name: Demonfuse
DEMONFUSE.flavorText: Very dangerous when attached to a demonbomb.

OBSERVER OF MYSTERIES.name: Observer of Mysteries
OBSERVER OF MYSTERIES.flavorText: Nobody tell him, but he still has his Secrets set to the "Try Me" mode.

BERYLLIUM NULLIFIER.name: Beryllium Nullifier
BERYLLIUM NULLIFIER.flavorText: Why Beryllium? Because it's hard to spell.

TRICK TOTEM.name: Trick Totem
TRICK TOTEM.flavorText: It knows how to sit still and do tricks. Still working on rolling over, though.

ARMORSMITH.name: Armorsmith
ARMORSMITH.flavorText: She accepts guild funds for repairs!

WRATHSPINE ENCHANTER.name: Wrathspine Enchanter
WRATHSPINE ENCHANTER.flavorText: If he could see, he might be better at targeting.

WILDWALKER.name: Wildwalker
WILDWALKER.flavorText: She was born to be something. She is just not quite sure what yet...

EVASIVE DRAKONID.name: Evasive Drakonid
EVASIVE DRAKONID.flavorText: Doesn't respond to spells, hero powers, calls, or text messages.

ANNOYING FAN.name: Annoying Fan
ANNOYING FAN.flavorText: No, Annoy-o-Tron, an air horn is not an instrument.

DOOMED APPRENTICE.name: Doomed Apprentice
DOOMED APPRENTICE.flavorText: Jaina was never good at keeping up apprentices.

HYDRALODON.name: Hydralodon
HYDRALODON.flavorText: Deep beneath the waves, this hydra grew to incredible size based on a steady diet of literally anything that crossed its path.

PIT MASTER.name: Pit Master
PIT MASTER.flavorText: If you win your duel, he'll throw in some of his famous Pit Master barbecue.

SILENT KNIGHT.name: Silent Knight
SILENT KNIGHT.flavorText: He used to be a librarian. Old habits die hard.

THE RUNESPEAR.name: The Runespear
THE RUNESPEAR.flavorText: When asked what the runes do, the tauren smith smiled: "A little of this, a little of that..."

CORRUPTED HEALBOT.name: Corrupted Healbot
CORRUPTED HEALBOT.flavorText: Not so much "corrupted" as "has terrible aim".

POSSESSED LACKEY.name: Possessed Lackey
POSSESSED LACKEY.flavorText: If you don't keep up with your payments, it'll be a repossessed lackey.

SAND BREATH.name: Sand Breath
SAND BREATH.flavorText: After Uldum, EVERYONE had sand breath.

THE LAST KALEIDOSAUR.name: The Last Kaleidosaur
THE LAST KALEIDOSAUR.flavorText: “Impossible!” exclaimed the Silver Hand Recruit, his eyes filled with fear. Uther shook his head, turning the crystal until it caught the light: “Life finds a way.”

NAZMANI BLOODWEAVER.name: Nazmani Bloodweaver
NAZMANI BLOODWEAVER.flavorText: Her first stage name, Ketchupweaver, failed to excite the audience.

SCHOOLING.name: Schooling
SCHOOLING.flavorText: A group of Piranha are known as a Scholomance.

BUILD A SNOWMAN.name: Build a Snowman
BUILD A SNOWMAN.flavorText: This is the coolest spell once you get it rolling.

THROUGH FEL AND FLAMES.name: Through Fel and Flames
THROUGH FEL AND FLAMES.flavorText: It's a Fel spell, but also a FIRE spell.

AUCHENAI SOULPRIEST.name: Auchenai Soulpriest
AUCHENAI SOULPRIEST.flavorText: The Auchenai know the end is coming, but they're not sure when.

FLOWRIDER.name: Flowrider
FLOWRIDER.flavorText: Her music sounds a lot better underwater where you can't hear it at all.

APOTHECARY HELBRIM.name: Apothecary Helbrim
APOTHECARY HELBRIM.flavorText: The best way to maintain your health is to poison everyone else.

ARCANITE RIPPER.name: Arcanite Ripper
ARCANITE RIPPER.flavorText: A guitar with a skull - perfect for headbanging.

EFFICIENT OCTO-BOT.name: Efficient Octo-bot
EFFICIENT OCTO-BOT.flavorText: Pull the lever, Octo-bot... Wrong leverrrrr!

GUARDIAN AUGMERCHANT.name: Guardian Augmerchant
GUARDIAN AUGMERCHANT.flavorText: "What doesn't kill you makes me money!"

RAMMING MOUNT.name: Ramming Mount
RAMMING MOUNT.flavorText: Tavish has some road rage issues to work through.

RELIC VAULT.name: Relic Vault
RELIC VAULT.flavorText: Holds Sire Denathrius' most prized possession - his teddy bear, Jeremy Bearimy.

MALKOROK.name: Malkorok
MALKOROK.flavorText: Garrosh's best buddy. It's true. Look it up.

CHO'GALL.name: Cho'gall
CHO'GALL.flavorText: Even after all this time, Gul'dan still makes Cho'gall go get donuts and coffee.

PACK KODO.name: Pack Kodo
PACK KODO.flavorText: He looks simple, but there’s a lot to unpack.

WHIRLWIND.name: Whirlwind
WHIRLWIND.flavorText: The way to tell seasoned warriors from novice ones: the novices yell "wheeeee" while whirlwinding.

WINDFURY HARPY.name: Windfury Harpy
WINDFURY HARPY.flavorText: Harpies are not pleasant sounding. That's the nicest I can put it.

VOODOO DOCTOR.name: Voodoo Doctor
VOODOO DOCTOR.flavorText: Voodoo is an oft-misunderstood art. But it is art.

UNWILLING SACRIFICE.name: Unwilling Sacrifice
UNWILLING SACRIFICE.flavorText: Stand right... there. Perfect, perfect! Now don't move.

SPAWN OF SHADOWS.name: Spawn of Shadows
SPAWN OF SHADOWS.flavorText: What did you expect to happen? He's a Spawn. Of Shadows.

CHAMELEOS.name: Chameleos
CHAMELEOS.flavorText: He's everyone you want to be.

FROSTWOLF WARMASTER.name: Frostwolf Warmaster
FROSTWOLF WARMASTER.flavorText: “The spoils of war ain’t free… Unless you’re me!”

FOOL'S BANE.name: Fool's Bane
FOOL'S BANE.flavorText: A fool and his bane are soon parted.

NOVICE ENGINEER.name: Novice Engineer
NOVICE ENGINEER.flavorText: "Half of this class will not graduate… since they'll have been turned to chickens." - Tinkmaster Overspark, teaching Gizmos 101.

POWER OF CREATION.name: Power of Creation
POWER OF CREATION.flavorText: Mostly used for party tricks, to be honest.

FLAMEREAPER.name: Flamereaper
FLAMEREAPER.flavorText: Honestly it sows more flame than it reaps.

PARRRLEY.name: Parrrley
PARRRLEY.flavorText: Time to engage in some unfriendly negotiations.

BLACKWATER CUTLASS.name: Blackwater Cutlass
BLACKWATER CUTLASS.flavorText: Popular around Stormwind for slashing prices.

MICRO MACHINE.name: Micro Machine
MICRO MACHINE.flavorText: This card is the real thing.

ROTNEST DRAKE.name: Rotnest Drake
ROTNEST DRAKE.flavorText: Clean your room, or I'm taking your favorite minion away!

TWILIGHT ELDER.name: Twilight Elder
TWILIGHT ELDER.flavorText: Just doesn't understand those Twilight Youngsters any more - with their comic books and their rock music.

HIRED GUN.name: Hired Gun
HIRED GUN.flavorText: He loves his job and would do it for free! (But don't tell his boss!)

BULK UP.name: Bulk Up
BULK UP.flavorText: "For breakfast I usually go for a couple of kodo steaks, 5 Plainstrider eggs and an ice-cold milk to wash it down… all raw."

BANJOSAUR.name: Banjosaur
BANJOSAUR.flavorText: You'll all be singing along once he gets to the tyranno-chorus.

WAVE OF NOSTALGIA.name: Wave of Nostalgia
WAVE OF NOSTALGIA.flavorText: Ja, please don't freeze my minions. No stall, ja????

THISTLE TEA.name: Thistle Tea
THISTLE TEA.flavorText: Aren't Thistles prickly? Why would you drink them? I don't get Rogues.

BLISTERING ROT.name: Blistering Rot
BLISTERING ROT.flavorText: Known as 'Fel Gel' to the Illidari, it's excellent protection against harsh Draenic sunshine.

CAIRNE BLOODHOOF.name: Cairne Bloodhoof
CAIRNE BLOODHOOF.flavorText: Cairne was killed by Garrosh, so... don't put this guy in a Warrior deck. It's pretty insensitive.

GLUTTONOUS OOZE.name: Gluttonous Ooze
GLUTTONOUS OOZE.flavorText: Three time winner of the Un'Goro weapon eating contest.

SPECIMEN CLAW.name: Specimen Claw
SPECIMEN CLAW.flavorText: Great at catching alien species. Not so much their plushies.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/5c/GDB_107_SpecimenClaw_PLay.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ GDB_107_SpecimenClaw_PLay.wav

BATTLEWORN VANGUARD.name: Battleworn Vanguard
BATTLEWORN VANGUARD.flavorText: "Welcome to Dun Baldar Felwings! Do you want 'em mild, spicy, or BURNING Legion?"

COUNTERFEIT COIN.name: Counterfeit Coin
COUNTERFEIT COIN.flavorText: There is something funny about this coin… can't quite put my finger on it…

ENTITLED CUSTOMER.name: Entitled Customer
ENTITLED CUSTOMER.flavorText: "Do you have any idea how much mana I've spent at your store? 6."

LANDSCAPING.name: Landscaping
LANDSCAPING.flavorText: We'll put a happy tree right here... and give him a little friend.

RELIQUARY RESEARCHER.name: Reliquary Researcher
RELIQUARY RESEARCHER.flavorText: What good is a researcher if they're just gunna keep it all a secret?

FORCE-TANK MAX.name: Force-Tank MAX
FORCE-TANK MAX.flavorText: There is a factory in Tanaris for crafting force-tanks, but it only ever made two, because of cost overruns.

WINGS OF HATE (RANK 1).name: Wings of Hate (Rank 1)
WINGS OF HATE (RANK 1).flavorText: For one day each February, they become the Wings of Love.

THE ONE-AMALGAM BAND.name: The One-Amalgam Band
THE ONE-AMALGAM BAND.flavorText: Why be good with ONE instrument when you can be terrible with ALL of them!!!

DEFEND THE DWARVEN DISTRICT.name: Defend the Dwarven District
DEFEND THE DWARVEN DISTRICT.flavorText: Don't shoot until you see the purples of their eyes.

DARKTHORN QUILTER.name: Darkthorn Quilter
DARKTHORN QUILTER.flavorText: Still mad about not being let into the spiders' sewing club.

SCHOOL TEACHER.name: School Teacher
SCHOOL TEACHER.flavorText: She also tutors 3 Piranha Swarmers on her off hours.

RAVEN FAMILIAR.name: Raven Familiar
RAVEN FAMILIAR.flavorText: Quoth the raven, 'Does yours cost more?'

BODY WRAPPER.name: Body Wrapper
BODY WRAPPER.flavorText: She uses pickle slices for the eyes. Keeps them well-preserved.

SANGUINE DEPTHS.name: Sanguine Depths
SANGUINE DEPTHS.flavorText: There may not be any skeletons in the closets at Castle Nathria, but there sure are souls in the basement.

TOURNAMENT ATTENDEE.name: Tournament Attendee
TOURNAMENT ATTENDEE.flavorText: He was so excited to get season tickets to this year's Grand Tournament. He normally doesn't get them at first and has to buy them from Ogre scalpers.

SOULSHARD LAPIDARY.name: Soulshard Lapidary
SOULSHARD LAPIDARY.flavorText: Also known as a soul sequincer.

VICTORIOUS VRYKUL.name: Victorious Vrykul
VICTORIOUS VRYKUL.flavorText: Get three of these and you have a Trikul.

SHADOW WORD: DEATH.name: Shadow Word: Death
SHADOW WORD: DEATH.flavorText: If you miss, it leaves a lightning-bolt-shaped scar on your target.

LIVING MANA.name: Living Mana
LIVING MANA.flavorText: If you truly love your mana, set it free.

IMPENDING CATASTROPHE.name: Impending Catastrophe
IMPENDING CATASTROPHE.flavorText: The imps end you, and the cats... well, they astrophe.

BUG COLLECTOR.name: Bug Collector
BUG COLLECTOR.flavorText: The only one who likes BEEEES!!!

KING TOGWAGGLE.name: King Togwaggle
KING TOGWAGGLE.flavorText: Management of the Kobold Empire requires a careful balance between a lack of social services and fiscal irresponsibility.

HARBOR SCAMP.name: Harbor Scamp
HARBOR SCAMP.flavorText: Hey, that gnome looks awfully fishy…

CARRION STUDIES.name: Carrion Studies
CARRION STUDIES.flavorText: A good read but a little too much fluff.

VORACIOUS READER.name: Voracious Reader
VORACIOUS READER.flavorText: But how much of it is skimming?

FINE PRINT.name: Fine Print
FINE PRINT.flavorText: Text in italics can't hurt you. (Yes it can.)

PRINCE LIAM.name: Prince Liam
PRINCE LIAM.flavorText: "I have a very particular set of skills. Skills that make me a nightmare for witches like you."

MR. SMITE.name: Mr. Smite
MR. SMITE.flavorText: “Please, Mr. Smite was my father. Call me Yorik.”

NERUB'AR WEBLORD.name: Nerub'ar Weblord
NERUB'AR WEBLORD.flavorText: Weblords spend all day making giant trampoline parks.

ELIZA GOREBLADE.name: Eliza Goreblade
ELIZA GOREBLADE.flavorText: Dead men tell no tales, but Undead Pirates are yappers.

SILVER SWORD.name: Silver Sword
SILVER SWORD.flavorText: Silver’s malleability limits its utility as an edged weapon. On the other hand... SHINY!

SIR FINLEY, SEA GUIDE.name: Sir Finley, Sea Guide
SIR FINLEY, SEA GUIDE.flavorText: "No need to worry, ol' chums, I have the map right here. It says to continue going straight down!"

BADLANDS BRAWLER.name: Badlands Brawler
BADLANDS BRAWLER.flavorText: Watch out watch out watch out - R.K.O. outta nowhere!

SPLITTING SPACEROCK.name: Splitting Spacerock
SPLITTING SPACEROCK.flavorText: Space rock. *pew* Spa ce ro ck. *pew* S p a c e r o c k .

HENCH-CLAN SNEAK.name: Hench-Clan Sneak
HENCH-CLAN SNEAK.flavorText: He’d be a lot sneakier if he wasn’t trailing 300 yards of power cable…

SIREN SONG.name: Siren Song
SIREN SONG.flavorText: "Sing along if you know the lyrics! -- WEEWOOWEEWOO!"

CONFECTION CYCLONE.name: Confection Cyclone
CONFECTION CYCLONE.flavorText: "Oh, I thought it was a desert elemental?"

SHOULDER CHECK.name: Shoulder Check
SHOULDER CHECK.flavorText: One... two... yeah, all present and correct.

ACOLYTE OF DEATH.name: Acolyte of Death
ACOLYTE OF DEATH.flavorText: "I see dead people. A LOT of dead people."

FIERCE OUTSIDER.name: Fierce Outsider
FIERCE OUTSIDER.flavorText: Look, if you stopped breaking stuff you wouldn't have to stay outside.

MOR'SHAN WATCH POST.name: Mor'shan Watch Post
MOR'SHAN WATCH POST.flavorText: Pushing into Ashenvale made this post uneventful.

YSIEL WINDSINGER.name: Ysiel Windsinger
YSIEL WINDSINGER.flavorText: Reach down into your lungs. The wind that resides there is your greatest treasure. It provides the gift of song, which is free. *But not less than (1)

LYNESSA SUNSORROW.name: Lynessa Sunsorrow
LYNESSA SUNSORROW.flavorText: A diet of pure magic is great for the complexion but wreaks havoc on one's mood.

ARCHWITCH WILLOW.name: Archwitch Willow
ARCHWITCH WILLOW.flavorText: One of the demons will do all the work while the other gets the same grade.

SPAWNPOOL FORAGER.name: Spawnpool Forager
SPAWNPOOL FORAGER.flavorText: Putting food on the table requires persistence, enthusiasm, and the finest murloc Gloves of Foraging.

BAD OMEN.name: Bad Omen
BAD OMEN.flavorText: What good is a sign from alien life if I CAN'T EVEN READ IT?!

DEAFEN.name: Deafen
DEAFEN.flavorText: Hey, Volsat, we can't hear you. You're on mute.

CAT TRICK.name: Cat Trick
CAT TRICK.flavorText: "I know some new tricks, a lot of good tricks. I will show them to you. Medivh will not mind at all if I do."

BARGAIN BIN.name: Bargain Bin
BARGAIN BIN.flavorText: Used to contain Worgen Greaser until SOMEONE started buffing it.

SUNWING SQUAWKER.name: Sunwing Squawker
SUNWING SQUAWKER.flavorText: Most parrots repeat curses, not blessings.

ARENA FANATIC.name: Arena Fanatic
ARENA FANATIC.flavorText: Her fantasy Rumble league gives double points for dismemberment.

PRODUCT 9.name: Product 9
PRODUCT 9.flavorText: We're fresh out of Toyrantus right now but lemme show you something we have that's just as good!

TIDE POOLS.name: Tide Pools
TIDE POOLS.flavorText: I know they look delicious but do NOT eat them.

FELFIRE POTION.name: Felfire Potion
FELFIRE POTION.flavorText: Kazakus has a squad of imps bottling Felfire round-the-clock and he *still* can't keep up with demand.

CULT SORCERER.name: Cult Sorcerer
CULT SORCERER.flavorText: No matter how many times we tell her not to, she keeps feeding C'Thun scraps under the table.

ONYXIAN DRAKE.name: Onyxian Drake
ONYXIAN DRAKE.flavorText: The best offense is a great defense.

COMPOSTING.name: Composting
COMPOSTING.flavorText: The Treants really give their bodies to the cause.

MICRO MUMMY.name: Micro Mummy
MICRO MUMMY.flavorText: The dramatically detailed terrifically trimmed replica of the real thing!

GUARDIAN ANIMALS.name: Guardian Animals
GUARDIAN ANIMALS.flavorText: The guidelines specifically state: "Students may also bring an ironbeak owl OR an alleycat OR a toad." They never said how big.

CABAL ACOLYTE.name: Cabal Acolyte
CABAL ACOLYTE.flavorText: How did he get to the top of his class? He pulled a few strings!

GRIMESTREET SMUGGLER.name: Grimestreet Smuggler
GRIMESTREET SMUGGLER.flavorText: She's got anything you want. Need the latest derpinger? No problem!

NOZARI.name: Nozari
NOZARI.flavorText: In another timeline, she was called Yeszari.

MOSSY HORROR.name: Mossy Horror
MOSSY HORROR.flavorText: The hills have eyes. And teeth. Pretty bad breath, too.

MAILBOX DANCER.name: Mailbox Dancer
MAILBOX DANCER.flavorText: He is the reason why we have 7 mailboxes in this district.

HIGH PRIEST THEKAL.name: High Priest Thekal
HIGH PRIEST THEKAL.flavorText: "…and then I beat him with 1 Health!"

THELDURIN THE LOST.name: Theldurin the Lost
THELDURIN THE LOST.flavorText: He might be lost, but he knows where you can find these hands.

BOMB LOBBER.name: Bomb Lobber
BOMB LOBBER.flavorText: He lobbies Orgrimmar daily on behalf of bombs.

MENAGERIE MAGICIAN.name: Menagerie Magician
MENAGERIE MAGICIAN.flavorText: Just between us, if things get tight the Menagerie Magician position will probably be the first to go.

TENTACLE TENDER.name: Tentacle Tender
TENTACLE TENDER.flavorText: It's a messy job but somebody's got to do it. Well, actually, nobody should do this.

WICKED WITCHDOCTOR.name: Wicked Witchdoctor
WICKED WITCHDOCTOR.flavorText: You can easily defeat her by either dealing 4 damage, or dropping a house on her.

MANTLE SHAPER.name: Mantle Shaper
MANTLE SHAPER.flavorText: You got a fireplace? I've got a guy who shapes mantles.

DEMOLITION RENOVATOR.name: Demolition Renovator
DEMOLITION RENOVATOR.flavorText: "Look, the Sire said he wanted something more open concept..."

DANG-BLASTED ELEMENTAL.name: Dang-Blasted Elemental
DANG-BLASTED ELEMENTAL.flavorText: We were told that "Dag-Nabbin' Dang-Blastin' Rootin'-Tootin' High-Falutin' Elemental" was too long.

CERA'THINE FLEETRUNNER.name: Cera'thine Fleetrunner
CERA'THINE FLEETRUNNER.flavorText: World Record CTF Champion 16 years running.

BARRENS TRAPPER.name: Barrens Trapper
BARRENS TRAPPER.flavorText: Just add a bit of murloc meat for bait. Beasts can’t resist that special seasoning…

WEALTH REDISTRIBUTOR.name: Wealth Redistributor
WEALTH REDISTRIBUTOR.flavorText: WOULD YE LIKE CASH BACK? [ ] YAR HAR [ ] YO HO

RECONNAISSANCE.name: Reconnaissance
RECONNAISSANCE.flavorText: “But Commander, I already did the connaissance.”

LORD JARAXXUS.name: Lord Jaraxxus
LORD JARAXXUS.flavorText: "TRIFLING GNOME! YOUR ARROGANCE WILL BE YOUR UNDOING!!!!"

LAVA BURST.name: Lava Burst
LAVA BURST.flavorText: It's like an ocean of liquid magma in your mouth!

COLD STORAGE.name: Cold Storage
COLD STORAGE.flavorText: Sapphiron's favorite treat always was popsicles.

OONDASTA.name: Oondasta
OONDASTA.flavorText: Adorning devilsaurs with armor and feathers is a respected job in troll culture, although it has a high turnover rate.

GRILLMASTER.name: Grillmaster
GRILLMASTER.flavorText: Do you want your steak well done, rare, or LEGENDARY?

PIT SNAKE.name: Pit Snake
PIT SNAKE.flavorText: It could be worse. It could be a Snake Pit.

EONAR, THE LIFE-BINDER.name: Eonar, the Life-Binder
EONAR, THE LIFE-BINDER.flavorText: Protector of all living things, she once saved the nascent world-soul of Azeroth from annihilation. It seems mercy was her greatest wisdom.

KALIMOS, PRIMAL LORD.name: Kalimos, Primal Lord
KALIMOS, PRIMAL LORD.flavorText: All that's missing is a little heart.

WANDMAKER.name: Wandmaker
WANDMAKER.flavorText: She creates incredibly affordable wands of all shapes and sizes. But not owls. The owl is all-natural.

AMBIENT LIGHTSPAWN.name: Ambient Lightspawn
AMBIENT LIGHTSPAWN.flavorText: Make sure it's smaller than your other lightspawns for the best fill lighting.

MASTER OF DISGUISE.name: Master of Disguise
MASTER OF DISGUISE.flavorText: She's actually a male tauren. People don't call him "Master of Disguise" for nothing.

HEROIC STRIKE.name: Heroic Strike
HEROIC STRIKE.flavorText: Really, if you're a hero, this is every strike.

DEMONHEART.name: Demonheart
DEMONHEART.flavorText: Virtually every member of the pro demon lobby is a warlock. Weird.

ARCANE FLAKMAGE.name: Arcane Flakmage
ARCANE FLAKMAGE.flavorText: Ancient pandaren proverb: He who is without secrets lacks flak.

DRAGON SPEAKER.name: Dragon Speaker
DRAGON SPEAKER.flavorText: All of his speeches really drag on.

APEXIS SMUGGLER.name: Apexis Smuggler
APEXIS SMUGGLER.flavorText: "S-secrets? I don't have any! Whoa, look, a spell!"

SERVICE ACE.name: Service Ace
SERVICE ACE.flavorText: No shirt, no shoes, YES service!

SILENCE.name: Silence
SILENCE.flavorText: Reserved for enemy spellcasters, evil liches from beyond the grave, and karaoke nights at the Grim Guzzler.

NATALIE SELINE.name: Natalie Seline
NATALIE SELINE.flavorText: She discovered Xal'atath, Blade of the Black Empire, a terrible weapon of shadow magic that could both swallow a soul and cut a mean julienne.

REPACKAGE.name: Repackage
REPACKAGE.flavorText: I don't want to play with you anymore.

GRIZZLED WIZARD.name: Grizzled Wizard
GRIZZLED WIZARD.flavorText: When he was young, he was an Outrageous Magus.

SUNSAPPER LYNESSA.name: Sunsapper Lynessa
SUNSAPPER LYNESSA.flavorText: Paladins are sooo lawful that they start feeling like a Rogue just by sitting on someone else's beach chair.

OASIS OUTLAWS.name: Oasis Outlaws
OASIS OUTLAWS.flavorText: With their oasis polluted by the Bloodrock Mining Company, Snake Eyes has set aside her differences with the outlaws of the Badlands to put an end to Bloodrock's operation.

NIGHTMARE AMALGAM.name: Nightmare Amalgam
NIGHTMARE AMALGAM.flavorText: Be all that you can be.

SEAL FATE.name: Seal Fate
SEAL FATE.flavorText: Firmly press the seal of your fates instead of leaving the flap open.

STEWARD OF DARKSHIRE.name: Steward of Darkshire
STEWARD OF DARKSHIRE.flavorText: Turns out divine shields are way cheaper if you buy in bulk.

INVENTOR'S AURA.name: Inventor's Aura
INVENTOR'S AURA.flavorText: Ok, fine, I'll read the manual…

ELWYNN BOAR.name: Elwynn Boar
ELWYNN BOAR.flavorText: Be grateful we lowered the requirement from 65,340,285.

RAZORMANE BATTLEGUARD.name: Razormane Battleguard
RAZORMANE BATTLEGUARD.flavorText: Where there's a quill, there's a way.

AVENGING WRATH.name: Avenging Wrath
AVENGING WRATH.flavorText: Wham! Wham! Wham! Wham! Wham! Wham! Wham! Wham!

CHEATY ANKLEBITER.name: Cheaty Anklebiter
CHEATY ANKLEBITER.flavorText: Famed hunter of the deadly Achilliosaur.

COWARDLY GRUNT.name: Cowardly Grunt
COWARDLY GRUNT.flavorText: Cowardice is the wisest part of valor.

WHELP WRANGLER.name: Whelp Wrangler
WHELP WRANGLER.flavorText: "Gosh darn it! How did these winged, airborne creatures manage to escape my knee-high, fenced enclosure AGAIN!?"

SUFFOCATING SHADOWS.name: Suffocating Shadows
SUFFOCATING SHADOWS.flavorText: "Reading is good for you," they said.

SKELETAL DRAGON.name: Skeletal Dragon
SKELETAL DRAGON.flavorText: I wish to complain about this dragon what I purchased not half an hour ago from this very boutique.

DOCTOR KRASTINOV.name: Doctor Krastinov
DOCTOR KRASTINOV.flavorText: He is not a medical doctor.

IMPORTED TARANTULA.name: Imported Tarantula
IMPORTED TARANTULA.flavorText: Which forbidden forest did you get this from?

VOID RIPPER.name: Void Ripper
VOID RIPPER.flavorText: You had to put the portable hole inside the bag of holding, didn't you?!

SERVANT OF KALIMOS.name: Servant of Kalimos
SERVANT OF KALIMOS.flavorText: He's doing his best, but his mom thinks that if he had just applied himself in school Kalimos would be working for HIM.

KABAL LACKEY.name: Kabal Lackey
KABAL LACKEY.flavorText: I'll tell you one thing he doesn't lack: GUMPTION.

RALLYING BLADE.name: Rallying Blade
RALLYING BLADE.flavorText: As far as blades go, this one is pretty great in the motivation department.

KURTRUS ASHFALLEN.name: Kurtrus Ashfallen
KURTRUS ASHFALLEN.flavorText: Kurtrus fled the Black Temple, abandoning Illidan's cause, to seek revenge against the Dreadlord Anetheron.

CURIOUS GLIMMERROOT.name: Curious Glimmerroot
CURIOUS GLIMMERROOT.flavorText: George promised to be good. But it's easy for little Glimmerroots to forget.

DRAGONKIN SORCERER.name: Dragonkin Sorcerer
DRAGONKIN SORCERER.flavorText: Dragonkin Sorcerers be all "I'm a wizard" and everyone else be all "daaaaang".

COOKIE THE COOK.name: Cookie the Cook
COOKIE THE COOK.flavorText: Unsurprisingly, "Seafood Surprise" was no one's favorite dish.

STAR VULPERA.name: Star Vulpera
STAR VULPERA.flavorText: He was a star before he even flew his first ship.

DUSKHAVEN HUNTER.name: Duskhaven Hunter
DUSKHAVEN HUNTER.flavorText: After a short paws, she's back to herself again.

LUCKYDO BUCCANEER.name: Luckydo Buccaneer
LUCKYDO BUCCANEER.flavorText: You can't just leave a Luckydo somewhere. You gotta keep 'em with you! Especially in Gadgetzan!

WAXMANCY.name: Waxmancy
WAXMANCY.flavorText: The waxmancer works with flame and form, giving shape to figures warm. Some think he's a crazy creeper, but crafting minions is simply cheaper.

GRUUL.name: Gruul
GRUUL.flavorText: He's Gruul "the Dragonkiller". He just wanted to cuddle them… he never meant to…

JADE SPIRIT.name: Jade Spirit
JADE SPIRIT.flavorText: "He's so cute! I just want to squeeze him, then use him for Jade Golem parts!" - Aya Blackpaw

BLOOD TO ICHOR.name: Blood To Ichor
BLOOD TO ICHOR.flavorText: For his next trick, he turns the ichor back to blood and stuffs it back in you.

BIG OL' WHELP.name: Big Ol' Whelp
BIG OL' WHELP.flavorText: A chonker, a real absolute unit.

CRYSTALWEAVER.name: Crystalweaver
CRYSTALWEAVER.flavorText: The trick is soaking the crystals in warm milk to soften them up.

CHO'GALL, TWILIGHT CHIEFTAIN.name: Cho'gall, Twilight Chieftain
CHO'GALL, TWILIGHT CHIEFTAIN.flavorText: He's got it all, the gumption, gall, and Cho.

BEST IN SHELL.name: Best in Shell
BEST IN SHELL.flavorText: The agility course takes a while.

REDEMPTION.name: Redemption
REDEMPTION.flavorText: I am not sure how you get demptioned the first time. It’s a mystery!

BONEGUARD LIEUTENANT.name: Boneguard Lieutenant
BONEGUARD LIEUTENANT.flavorText: Underneath all that impressive armor, he's just skin and bones. Okay, maybe just bones.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/50/VO_AT_089_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_089_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/7b/VO_AT_089_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_089_ATTACK_02.wav You face death!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/58/VO_AT_089_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_089_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

METAL DETECTOR.name: Metal Detector
METAL DETECTOR.flavorText: Weirdly still works on Sand Coins.

BURGLY BULLY.name: Burgly Bully
BURGLY BULLY.flavorText: He only burgles to pay the bills. He is really just a bully at heart.

RUSTSWORN CULTIST.name: Rustsworn Cultist
RUSTSWORN CULTIST.flavorText: "Rust… I love it. It's all coarse, and rough, and irritating. And it gets everywhere."

VEXALLUS.name: Vexallus
VEXALLUS.flavorText: He only casts the spells once - it's Shmexallus that casts the copy.

C'THUN.name: C'Thun
C'THUN.flavorText: C'Thun's least favorite Hearthstone card: Eye for an Eye.

MUSTER FOR BATTLE.name: Muster for Battle
MUSTER FOR BATTLE.flavorText: "I'm bringing the guacamole!" – One of the most successful (yet rare) Silver Hand rallying cries

FELSTRING HARP.name: Felstring Harp
FELSTRING HARP.flavorText: Playing it will singe your fingers and wither your soul, but at least it never needs restringing!

BATTLE VICAR.name: Battle Vicar
BATTLE VICAR.flavorText: She's the most down-to-earth paladin you'll ever meet... until she stands up.

SOULFIRE.name: Soulfire
SOULFIRE.flavorText: Are you lighting a soul on fire? Or burning someone with your OWN soul? This seems like an important distinction.

PEACEFUL PIPER.name: Peaceful Piper
PEACEFUL PIPER.flavorText: "Is there anything worth more than peace and love on the planet Azeroth?"

WATERCOLOR ARTIST.name: Watercolor Artist
WATERCOLOR ARTIST.flavorText: They've amassed a largely aquatic body of work, painting lakes, rivers and self portraits.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/1/14/TID_716_TidalRevenant_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ TID_716_TidalRevenant_Play.wav <summon sound>

ASTRAL COMMUNION.name: Astral Communion
ASTRAL COMMUNION.flavorText: Hey! Moon! Can I have some mana crystals?

FRAMESTER.name: Framester
FRAMESTER.flavorText: "Who put these beans in my pocket?!" -Man With Beans in Pocket

NORDRASSIL DRUID.name: Nordrassil Druid
NORDRASSIL DRUID.flavorText: The World Tree Nordrassil provides life-giving energy to the world--and excellent mana savings.

KAZAKUS, GOLEM SHAPER.name: Kazakus, Golem Shaper
KAZAKUS, GOLEM SHAPER.flavorText: With a little love and some tenderness, we’ll CRUSH OUR FOES!

WATER MOCCASIN.name: Water Moccasin
WATER MOCCASIN.flavorText: You need to be specific when you're ordering waterproof shoewear.

CRUEL TASKMASTER.name: Cruel Taskmaster
CRUEL TASKMASTER.flavorText: "I'm going to need you to come in on Sunday." - Cruel Taskmaster

FUTURE EMISSARY.name: Future Emissary
FUTURE EMISSARY.flavorText: When Murozond attacked the past, Nozdormu sought help from the future, even journeying as far as the Forbidden Reach.

GOLDEN SCARAB.name: Golden Scarab
GOLDEN SCARAB.flavorText: Who actually puts all the gold plating on these things, and why?

BARRICADE.name: Barricade
BARRICADE.flavorText: The Alliance and Horde join forces to enforce the fire safety capacity.

WITCH'S APPRENTICE.name: Witch's Apprentice
WITCH'S APPRENTICE.flavorText: Is she a frog that became a witch, or a witch that became a frog?

IVORY ROOK.name: Ivory Rook
IVORY ROOK.flavorText: Bringing back this cycle was risky, but the Ivory Queen thought it was worth the gambit.

MOGU CULTIST.name: Mogu Cultist
MOGU CULTIST.flavorText: Mogu cultists have the worst team-building exercises.

STORMWIND FREEBOOTER.name: Stormwind Freebooter
STORMWIND FREEBOOTER.flavorText: "Just don't stab the ankles! I want his boots!"

SUSPICIOUS PIRATE.name: Suspicious Pirate
SUSPICIOUS PIRATE.flavorText: EVERY party should be a costume party.

THE PURATOR.name: The Purator
THE PURATOR.flavorText: With the rise of the undead, the Curator sees it as his duty to take care of them.

SHIMMERING TEMPEST.name: Shimmering Tempest
SHIMMERING TEMPEST.flavorText: HATES being summoned for Kirin Tor party lighting.

RELIQUARY OF SOULS.name: Reliquary of Souls
RELIQUARY OF SOULS.flavorText: These three represent Anger, Desire, and Suffering. Much like raid night guild chat.

LESSER DIAMOND SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Diamond Spellstone
LESSER DIAMOND SPELLSTONE.flavorText: A diamond, white, this stone the eighth A precious jewel for those of faith A whispered prayer restores the lost But none among them know the cost.

CAPTAIN'S LOG.name: Captain's Log
CAPTAIN'S LOG.flavorText: Akama loves a nice comfy log to captain on.

DESPERATE PRAYER.name: Desperate Prayer
DESPERATE PRAYER.flavorText: Woah, we're halfway there, woah oh...

ARCANOLOGIST.name: Arcanologist
ARCANOLOGIST.flavorText: What did you draw? Shhhh… it’s a secret.

SHELL GAME.name: Shell Game
SHELL GAME.flavorText: I thiiink… It's under all three of 'em!

ARCHIMONDE.name: Archimonde
ARCHIMONDE.flavorText: Archimonde joined Sargeras in search of power, and in doing so became one of the strongest forces within the Burning Legion who laid waste to countless planets… but in the end he still lost to a wisp.

IMPROVE MORALE.name: Improve Morale
IMPROVE MORALE.flavorText: "The beatings will continue until MY morale improves."

ARENA PATRON.name: Arena Patron
ARENA PATRON.flavorText: Everybody with a ticket get in here!

MINDBREAKER.name: Mindbreaker
MINDBREAKER.flavorText: He's a mind breaker, dream taker, ghoul trainer, don't you mess around with him.

FROSTWYRM'S FURY.name: Frostwyrm's Fury
FROSTWYRM'S FURY.flavorText: Terrible destruction, but minty fresh breath!

WEASEL TUNNELER.name: Weasel Tunneler
WEASEL TUNNELER.flavorText: He's the reason the First Bank of Gadgetzan has steel floors.

KARGATH BLADEFIST.name: Kargath Bladefist
KARGATH BLADEFIST.flavorText: He rules the Shattered Hand orc clan with an iron... bladefist.

CALL TO ARMS.name: Call to Arms
CALL TO ARMS.flavorText: More personal than a text to arms.

OGREMANCER.name: Ogremancer
OGREMANCER.flavorText: After their third attempt, Tharg began to suspect that Krul was summoning the skeletons on purpose.

SHADOWBORN.name: Shadowborn
SHADOWBORN.flavorText: You merely adopted the shadows; I was born in them!

MALEVOLENT STRIKE.name: Malevolent Strike
MALEVOLENT STRIKE.flavorText: "I don't know how those got in there, but I'm blaming you two."

STARGAZING.name: Stargazing
STARGAZING.flavorText: See those dots up there? Those are called "stars." Except for that one. That's called an "airplane."

SPIDER BOMB.name: Spider Bomb
SPIDER BOMB.flavorText: Wrecks a dude, any size. Catches thieves, eats those guys. Look out! Here comes a Spider Bomb!

LADY DARKVEIN.name: Lady Darkvein
LADY DARKVEIN.flavorText: You're so vein. I bet you think this flavor text is about you.

THE LOBOTOMIZER.name: The Lobotomizer
THE LOBOTOMIZER.flavorText: This may hurt a little, but don't worry, you won't remember it.

TAELAN FORDRING.name: Taelan Fordring
TAELAN FORDRING.flavorText: After growing up with the Scarlet Crusade for most of his life, Taelan finally realized they were maybe not the nicest people.

PRIZE PLUNDERER.name: Prize Plunderer
PRIZE PLUNDERER.flavorText: But he'll never be able to plunder the prize of a happy childhood.

FERAL RAGE.name: Feral Rage
FERAL RAGE.flavorText: Let's be honest. One option is a lot ragier than the other.

COERCE.name: Coerce
COERCE.flavorText: "Give me your lunch money, or the sandwich gets it!"

CHAMPION OF STORMS.name: Champion of Storms
CHAMPION OF STORMS.flavorText: Has some grievances it just can't wait to air out.

STORM'S WRATH.name: Storm's Wrath
STORM'S WRATH.flavorText: How many dragons does it take to destroy a hot air balloon? One, two, three, CRUNCH!

BLINGTRON 3000.name: Blingtron 3000
BLINGTRON 3000.flavorText: PREPARE PARTY SERVOS FOR IMMEDIATE DEPLOYMENT.

AZSHARAN MOONCATCHER.name: Azsharan Mooncatcher
AZSHARAN MOONCATCHER.flavorText: The light of Elune faded from the ruins of Zin-Azshari, but not its treasures.

RECKLESS FLURRY.name: Reckless Flurry
RECKLESS FLURRY.flavorText: Look. Cautious Flurries will only get you so far in life.

AGENCY ESPIONAGE.name: Agency Espionage
AGENCY ESPIONAGE.flavorText: What gnomish monitoring devices lack in subtlety, they make up for in robustness.

CIRCUS MEDIC.name: Circus Medic
CIRCUS MEDIC.flavorText: Just be careful not to mix this with any creepy eyeballs, tentacles, or dark whispers, and you'll be fine in the morning.

VENDETTA.name: Vendetta
VENDETTA.flavorText: A vengeful and vicarious vanguard against violent villains or vexed victims.

FEN CREEPER.name: Fen Creeper
FEN CREEPER.flavorText: He used to be called Bog Beast, but it confused people because he wasn't an actual beast. Boom, New Name!

INITIATION.name: Initiation
INITIATION.flavorText: The things a murloc's gotta go through to graduate from Scholomance…

LESSER JASPER SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Jasper Spellstone
LESSER JASPER SPELLSTONE.flavorText: In ancient woods, elves fought the curse The demon’s shadow to disperse But hatred raged and frail souls turned Now horned and hooved their forests burned.

FLOOP'S GLORIOUS GLOOP.name: Floop's Glorious Gloop
FLOOP'S GLORIOUS GLOOP.flavorText: How much gloop could Floop's Gloop gloop if Floop's Gloop could gloop gloop?

DISGUISED WANDERER.name: Disguised Wanderer
DISGUISED WANDERER.flavorText: He wanders east... always into the east.

PRINCE TALDARAM.name: Prince Taldaram
PRINCE TALDARAM.flavorText: Three Princes stand before you. This one wants to copy others.

MECHAGNOME GUIDE.name: Mechagnome Guide
MECHAGNOME GUIDE.flavorText: Theme park? Tropical island? Fiery pit of despair? We've got something for everyone.

WEAPONS ATTENDANT.name: Weapons Attendant
WEAPONS ATTENDANT.flavorText: Hotel policy states that you must leave your weapons at the front desk. But GOOD NEWS! You can also buy weapons at the back desk!!

GROOVY CAT.name: Groovy Cat
GROOVY CAT.flavorText: "Like, what if we're all just cards living in this box called Hearthstone, man?"

COSTUMED ENTERTAINER.name: Costumed Entertainer
COSTUMED ENTERTAINER.flavorText: Just remember not to talk. It breaks character.

ODYN, PRIME DESIGNATE.name: Odyn, Prime Designate
ODYN, PRIME DESIGNATE.flavorText: The best offense is a good defense. 30 defense to be exact.

PINT-SIZE POTION.name: Pint-Size Potion
PINT-SIZE POTION.flavorText: I hope you didn't disenchant your Shadow Word: Horror!

AIRLOCK BREACH.name: Airlock Breach
AIRLOCK BREACH.flavorText: Open the pod bay doors, Maladaar.

ANCIENT SHADE.name: Ancient Shade
ANCIENT SHADE.flavorText: Warning: Do not expose to direct sunlight.

QUARTZITE CRUSHER.name: Quartzite Crusher
QUARTZITE CRUSHER.flavorText: It's not just a weapon… it's a rock!

BLOODSWORN MERCENARY.name: Bloodsworn Mercenary
BLOODSWORN MERCENARY.flavorText: You look really hurt. You could use a friend!

OVERDRAFT.name: Overdraft
OVERDRAFT.flavorText: Wait. It costs mana to be out of mana?!

FROZEN BUCKLER.name: Frozen Buckler
FROZEN BUCKLER.flavorText: "Hey, I bet I could shatter this."

REDSCALE DRAGONTAMER.name: Redscale Dragontamer
REDSCALE DRAGONTAMER.flavorText: Sir Finley made this look a lot easier three expansions ago...

THE SUNWELL.name: The Sunwell
THE SUNWELL.flavorText: The Lich King had extinguished the light of the Sunwell once before - it will take all the might Silvermoon can muster to defend it!

FORCE OF NATURE.name: Force of Nature
FORCE OF NATURE.flavorText: "I think I'll just nap under these trees. Wait... AAAAAHHH!" - Blinkfizz, the Unfortunate Gnome

ANIMATE DEAD.name: Animate Dead
ANIMATE DEAD.flavorText: In the old days they used to animate the dead one bone at a time... it's all done by computer now.

HEART OF THE WILD.name: Heart of the Wild
HEART OF THE WILD.flavorText: In each of us beats a wild heart. Except the Forsaken.

ALLEYCAT.name: Alleycat
ALLEYCAT.flavorText: To be a cool cat in Gadgetzan, you gotta have bling.

BLOODSAIL HOWLER.name: Bloodsail Howler
BLOODSAIL HOWLER.flavorText: They saw their fate a closin' Aboard a pirate ship On deck: The Howlin' Hozen About to let one rip.

TRAMPLING RHINO.name: Trampling Rhino
TRAMPLING RHINO.flavorText: "Whew. I thought you said 'Trampoline Rhino.' Now that would have been scary."

CHARGE.name: Charge
CHARGE.flavorText: "Guys! Guys! Slow down!" - some kind of non-warrior minion

MEANSTREET MARSHAL.name: Meanstreet Marshal
MEANSTREET MARSHAL.flavorText: Remember, submit your bribes directly to the Marshal - it's the law!

STORMWIND CHAMPION.name: Stormwind Champion
STORMWIND CHAMPION.flavorText: When Deathwing assaulted the capital, this soldier was the only member of his squad to survive. Now he's all bitter and stuff.

SILK STITCHING.name: Silk Stitching
SILK STITCHING.flavorText: The slogan of their very exclusive sewing club is "You can't stitch with us."

HYENA ALPHA.name: Hyena Alpha
HYENA ALPHA.flavorText: Everything the sun touches is ours—so long as it's already dead.

SORCEROUS SUBSTITUTE.name: Sorcerous Substitute
SORCEROUS SUBSTITUTE.flavorText: This substitute's substitution is a dangerous institution.

DYN-O-MATIC.name: Dyn-o-matic
DYN-O-MATIC.flavorText: Star player on the inter-office Boomball team.

SOULCIOLOGIST MALICIA.name: Soulciologist Malicia
SOULCIOLOGIST MALICIA.flavorText: If you value your life, don't call it a "soft science."

REVOLVE.name: Revolve
REVOLVE.flavorText: "Please don't ride the carousel for thirty minutes after eating. After the carousel eats, I mean."

VOLCANOMANCY.name: Volcanomancy
VOLCANOMANCY.flavorText: Do it again, this time with Pompeii and circumstance.

CHAOS NOVA.name: Chaos Nova
CHAOS NOVA.flavorText: Illin' Illidan laying down the damage, flinging out the chaos as far as he can manage.

CURSE OF RAFAAM.name: Curse of Rafaam
CURSE OF RAFAAM.flavorText: This is what happens when Rafaam stubs his toe unexpectedly.

LIGHTBOMB.name: Lightbomb
LIGHTBOMB.flavorText: This is what happens when you allow goblins to be priests.

LOTUS ASSASSIN.name: Lotus Assassin
LOTUS ASSASSIN.flavorText: For 5000g, you can just give the Jade Lotus any name and they will assassinate and/or embarrass them.

SWAMP KING DRED.name: Swamp King Dred
SWAMP KING DRED.flavorText: Swamp King Dred, more like Swamp King Dead, amiright?

WARBOT.name: Warbot
WARBOT.flavorText: Mass production of warbots was halted when it was discovered that they were accidentally being produced at "sample size."

SOUTHSEA DECKHAND.name: Southsea Deckhand
SOUTHSEA DECKHAND.flavorText: Pirates are into this new fad called "Planking".

RAM COMMANDER.name: Ram Commander
RAM COMMANDER.flavorText: Get your RAM in pairs for better performance.

UNDERTAKER.name: Undertaker
UNDERTAKER.flavorText: In a world where you can run to a spirit healer and resurrect yourself, Undertakers do pretty light business.

IDOL'S ADORATION.name: Idol's Adoration
IDOL'S ADORATION.flavorText: That is a mic, not a door.

FORBIDDEN WORDS.name: Forbidden Words
FORBIDDEN WORDS.flavorText: Please confirm your age before reading this flavor text.

IMP SWARM (RANK 1).name: Imp Swarm (Rank 1)
IMP SWARM (RANK 1).flavorText: Not a cauldron, or a mischief, or a cackle, but a swarm.

ANUBISATH SENTINEL.name: Anubisath Sentinel
ANUBISATH SENTINEL.flavorText: He's actually a 1/1 who picked up the hammer from the last guy.

DISCIPLE OF AMITUS.name: Disciple of Amitus
DISCIPLE OF AMITUS.flavorText: "Oh great Amitus, I took your style advice on the poncho, but pray tell - one or two golden gloves?"

MALFURION'S GIFT.name: Malfurion's Gift
MALFURION'S GIFT.flavorText: "May this imbue you with the life of the party!" -Malfurion

DIRTY RAT.name: Dirty Rat
DIRTY RAT.flavorText: It's not his fault… Someone keeps stealing his soap!

WEE SPELLSTOPPER.name: Wee Spellstopper
WEE SPELLSTOPPER.flavorText: Bane of spellcasters and spelling bees everywhere.

SILITHID SWARMER.name: Silithid Swarmer
SILITHID SWARMER.flavorText: If your hero doesn't attack, it's just "Silithid Loner".

BLAZING BATTLEMAGE.name: Blazing Battlemage
BLAZING BATTLEMAGE.flavorText: Weaponized an ancient technique once used to slice cold butter.

HUMILITY.name: Humility
HUMILITY.flavorText: This card makes something really damp. Oh wait. That's "Humidity."

AMBER WHELP.name: Amber Whelp
AMBER WHELP.flavorText: What is a Bronze Whelp's favorite garnish? A little thyme!

SASQUAWK.name: Sasquawk
SASQUAWK.flavorText: He makes your last turn this turn. But if you play him next turn, your next turn is this turn. Doing both would make this turn last turn and next turn this turn. Which turn is this next turn last turn?

ENSMALLEN.name: Ensmallen
ENSMALLEN.flavorText: Come on, you know- I ensmallen, you ensmallen? He she me Ensmallen? Ensmallogy: the study of ensmallening?! IT'S FIRST GRADE.

MOONBEAM.name: Moonbeam
MOONBEAM.flavorText: The light of the moon may have disappeared from Zin-Azshari after the Sundering, but not its power.

RISE TO THE OCCASION.name: Rise to the Occasion
RISE TO THE OCCASION.flavorText: Faith is never lost, only repurposed.

VARIAN WRYNN.name: Varian Wrynn
VARIAN WRYNN.flavorText: Leader of the Alliance! Father of Anduin! Also he likes to play Arena, and he averages 12 wins.

ELDRITCH HORROR.name: Eldritch Horror
ELDRITCH HORROR.flavorText: Often wonders what path his life might have taken if he wasn't named, you know, "Eldritch Horror".

SHATTERED REFLECTIONS.name: Shattered Reflections
SHATTERED REFLECTIONS.flavorText: Get mad at your mirror once, see Shattered Reflections forever :(

GUARDIAN OF KINGS.name: Guardian of Kings
GUARDIAN OF KINGS.flavorText: Holy beings from the beyond are so cliché!

DAY AT THE FAIRE.name: Day at the Faire
DAY AT THE FAIRE.flavorText: Karl knew he would someday regret that turkey leg.

SPLISH-SPLASH WHELP.name: Splish-Splash Whelp
SPLISH-SPLASH WHELP.flavorText: Little Whelpy, you're the one You make Mana lots of fun

ZEREK, MASTER CLONER.name: Zerek, Master Cloner
ZEREK, MASTER CLONER.flavorText: His original name was Aerek. Then the first clone was Berek. They went evil around Merek.

DRAGGED BELOW.name: Dragged Below
DRAGGED BELOW.flavorText: I know this is a frustrating situation you’re in, Captain, but there’s no need to curse.

BLOOD TROLL SAPPER.name: Blood Troll Sapper
BLOOD TROLL SAPPER.flavorText: Main supplier of Blood Troll Syrup to the Intercontinental Hut of Funnel Cakes.

PATCHWERK.name: Patchwerk
PATCHWERK.flavorText: This card is so good, it might need patch work.

BLOOD OF G'HUUN.name: Blood of G'huun
BLOOD OF G'HUUN.flavorText: An attempted cure becomes disease, blooming and thriving as rot and decay.

BENEVOLENT DJINN.name: Benevolent Djinn
BENEVOLENT DJINN.flavorText: Wish 1: funnel cakes. Wish 2: funnel cakes. Wish 3: FUNNEL CAKES.

GROOK FU MASTER.name: Grook Fu Master
GROOK FU MASTER.flavorText: Grook Fu, the ancient Hozen art of bashing heads with a stick.

ANUB'AR AMBUSHER.name: Anub'ar Ambusher
ANUB'AR AMBUSHER.flavorText: Originally he was called "Anub'ar Guy who bounces a guy back to your hand", but it lacked a certain zing.

PARK PANTHER.name: Park Panther
PARK PANTHER.flavorText: Somebody called animal control once. It didn't work out very well for anybody.

MICROTECH CONTROLLER.name: Microtech Controller
MICROTECH CONTROLLER.flavorText: Best-selling author of "How to Make Friends You Completely Control."

ARGENT COMMANDER.name: Argent Commander
ARGENT COMMANDER.flavorText: The Argent Dawn stands vigilant against the Scourge, as well as people who cut in line at coffee shops.

TENTACLE OF N'ZOTH.name: Tentacle of N'Zoth
TENTACLE OF N'ZOTH.flavorText: Because EVERYDAY is the Day of the Tentacle of N'zoth.

MADDEST BOMBER.name: Maddest Bomber
MADDEST BOMBER.flavorText: Talk about a name that limits design space.

ICE TRAP.name: Ice Trap
ICE TRAP.flavorText: I literally watched the Hunter place it down in front of me and I still stepped in it.

THE JAILER.name: The Jailer
THE JAILER.flavorText: At one point, The Jailer served as Arbiter over the souls of the Shadowlands. He was the epitome of an unbiased, righteous judge of character. WAS.

WEAPONS PROJECT.name: Weapons Project
WEAPONS PROJECT.flavorText: Harrison Jones was kicked off this project.

QUARTZ ELEMENTAL.name: Quartz Elemental
QUARTZ ELEMENTAL.flavorText: These elementals, along with feldspar and mica, are often taken for granite.

OVERFLOW.name: Overflow
OVERFLOW.flavorText: It's a high five followed by a low tide.

SI:7 SKULKER.name: SI:7 Skulker
SI:7 SKULKER.flavorText: Burying bones and calling it skullduggery.

BOG CREEPER.name: Bog Creeper
BOG CREEPER.flavorText: He's tried other things, but bog sidling, bog ambling, and bog trundling just aren't as effective as bog creeping.

TEMPLE BERSERKER.name: Temple Berserker
TEMPLE BERSERKER.flavorText: He's back. He's angry. And he's here to wrap things up.

YMIRJAR DEATHBRINGER.name: Ymirjar Deathbringer
YMIRJAR DEATHBRINGER.flavorText: Purple cotton candy is the snack of choice in Ymirheim.

IRON SENSEI.name: Iron Sensei
IRON SENSEI.flavorText: Mechs like learning from him because he really speaks their language. 0110100001101001

SHADOW WORD: DEVOUR.name: Shadow Word: Devour
SHADOW WORD: DEVOUR.flavorText: Devouring souls is like a buffet. You have to take a little bit of everything.

PRIMAL FUSION.name: Primal Fusion
PRIMAL FUSION.flavorText: Golce and Dabbana have a new line of Earth Totems available at vendors everywhere this holiday season.

SPIRIT LASH.name: Spirit Lash
SPIRIT LASH.flavorText: We've got spirit, yes we do! We've got spirit, stolen from you!

SPEAKER GIDRA.name: Speaker Gidra
SPEAKER GIDRA.flavorText: If a teacher lectures in a forest, does she even make a sound?

ALL FEL BREAKS LOOSE.name: All Fel Breaks Loose
ALL FEL BREAKS LOOSE.flavorText: Maybe we should have made the bars closer together…

BOOMMASTER FLARK.name: Boommaster Flark
BOOMMASTER FLARK.flavorText: Every good plan requires a bit of patience. And a lot of explosives.

GRAVITY LAPSE.name: Gravity Lapse
GRAVITY LAPSE.flavorText: Did someone forget to pay the gravity bill?

INFESTED GOBLIN.name: Infested Goblin
INFESTED GOBLIN.flavorText: Trust us. DON'T go cheap on the scarab repellent.

DOOMMAIDEN.name: Doommaiden
DOOMMAIDEN.flavorText: You merely adopted the doom. I was maiden it.

HOPE OF QUEL'THALAS.name: Hope of Quel'Thalas
HOPE OF QUEL'THALAS.flavorText: Hey, give me a minute. I just need to load my.... uh, hope.

BURNDOWN.name: Burndown
BURNDOWN.flavorText: Trust me, the next 3 cards in my deck are FIRE.

ANCIENT WATCHER.name: Ancient Watcher
ANCIENT WATCHER.flavorText: Why do its eyes seem to follow you as you walk by?

WIND-UP BURGLEBOT.name: Wind-up Burglebot
WIND-UP BURGLEBOT.flavorText: Don't blame the bot for his crimes... Blame whoever keeps winding him up!

TWISTED KNOWLEDGE.name: Twisted Knowledge
TWISTED KNOWLEDGE.flavorText: People eat eight spiders in their sleep per year. Centaurs have two rib cages. Dwarves are just counterfeit titans.

RIVER CROCOLISK.name: River Crocolisk
RIVER CROCOLISK.flavorText: Edward "Lefty" Smith tried to make luggage out of a river crocolisk once.

YOUNG DRAGONHAWK.name: Young Dragonhawk
YOUNG DRAGONHAWK.flavorText: They were the inspiration for the championship Taurenball team: The Dragonhawks.

CRUD CARETAKER.name: Crud Caretaker
CRUD CARETAKER.flavorText: All it takes is a little love and a LOT of junk!

SLEET SKATER.name: Sleet Skater
SLEET SKATER.flavorText: How do you do, fellow Ice Elementals?

CENARION WARD.name: Cenarion Ward
CENARION WARD.flavorText: Don't ask about his right hand. He's still growing into it.

TAMSIN ROAME.name: Tamsin Roame
TAMSIN ROAME.flavorText: In life, Tamsin Roame was one of the Alliance's most promising mages; now she is the Horde's most dangerous warlock.

CATHEDRAL OF ATONEMENT.name: Cathedral of Atonement
CATHEDRAL OF ATONEMENT.flavorText: You'll actually find more than one tonement here.

AZSHARAN SCROLL.name: Azsharan Scroll
AZSHARAN SCROLL.flavorText: Kids these days are always scrolling on their tomes.

GLACIAL ADVANCE.name: Glacial Advance
GLACIAL ADVANCE.flavorText: You just wait, I'll get there in 10 years and then you'll be sorry.

STRANGLETHORN HEART.name: Stranglethorn Heart
STRANGLETHORN HEART.flavorText: The Stranglethorn mentality is to be happy with the bare necessities.

CALL OF THE GRAVE.name: Call of the Grave
CALL OF THE GRAVE.flavorText: Necromancy is motivational speaking for the dead.

MAGMA RAGER.name: Magma Rager
MAGMA RAGER.flavorText: He likes to think he is powerful, but pretty much anyone can solo Molten Core now.

ARFUS.name: Arfus
ARFUS.flavorText: There must always be a Lick King.

BOLNER HAMMERBEAK.name: Bolner Hammerbeak
BOLNER HAMMERBEAK.flavorText: Show him how to do something once, and he can do it a thousand times. This turn.

GOLGANNETH, THE THUNDERER.name: Golganneth, the Thunderer
GOLGANNETH, THE THUNDERER.flavorText: With dominion over the seas and skies, Golganneth fearlessly wields the power of nature to serve the Pantheon.

IMMORTAL PRELATE.name: Immortal Prelate
IMMORTAL PRELATE.flavorText: She protec. She attac. But most importantly, she come bac.

DWARVEN SHARPSHOOTER.name: Dwarven Sharpshooter
DWARVEN SHARPSHOOTER.flavorText: Scissors, knives, needles, you name it! He'll shoot it.

INCINDIUS.name: Incindius
INCINDIUS.flavorText: "I had nothing to do with that eruption! I never even met Kezandius!"

TENTACLED MENACE.name: Tentacled Menace
TENTACLED MENACE.flavorText: He calls this one the "Calamari Special."

RINGMASTER'S BATON.name: Ringmaster's Baton
RINGMASTER'S BATON.flavorText: A mech, a dragon, and a pirate walk into an Old God's gaping maw. The mech was too crunchy, the dragon was too hot, but the pirate was just right.

GRAND MAGUS ANTONIDAS.name: Grand Magus Antonidas
GRAND MAGUS ANTONIDAS.flavorText: He's really disappointed Jaina became a frost mage.

FLAME BEHEMOTH.name: Flame Behemoth
FLAME BEHEMOTH.flavorText: Always look both ways before crossing the Formation Grounds.

CONVOKE THE SPIRITS.name: Convoke the Spirits
CONVOKE THE SPIRITS.flavorText: The spirits prefer to convoke when there's some hot gossip to discuss.

INKMASTER SOLIA.name: Inkmaster Solia
INKMASTER SOLIA.flavorText: Solia marks the Kabal with intricate tattoos that grant immense power. Also it makes it harder for other gangs to recruit from their numbers. BACK OFF, GOONS.

DARK ALLEY PACT.name: Dark Alley Pact
DARK ALLEY PACT.flavorText: "With your help, I can finally install some proper lighting in this alley."

POSSESSED VILLAGER.name: Possessed Villager
POSSESSED VILLAGER.flavorText: It's like a pinata! A lame disgusting horrific pinata.

BABBLING BOOK.name: Babbling Book
BABBLING BOOK.flavorText: His idol is the Green Hills of Stranglethorn, and he won't shut up about it.

TAR SLICK.name: Tar Slick
TAR SLICK.flavorText: Has +2 Attack on its opponent's turn.

CHAR.name: Char
CHAR.flavorText: There's just no point trying to add flavor to this now.

ANCIENT OF BLOSSOMS.name: Ancient of Blossoms
ANCIENT OF BLOSSOMS.flavorText: His new shampoo is really working!

PSYCH-O-TRON.name: Psych-o-Tron
PSYCH-O-TRON.flavorText: "Annoyinger-o-Tron" was just too unwieldy. And accurate.

GRIMSCALE CHUM.name: Grimscale Chum
GRIMSCALE CHUM.flavorText: Listen, see? We'll take 'em to the docks, see? And throw 'em in the sea, see?

MYSTIFIED TO'CHA.name: Mystified To'cha
MYSTIFIED TO'CHA.flavorText: We hired your elementary school math teacher to make this card.

DRUM SOLOIST.name: Drum Soloist
DRUM SOLOIST.flavorText: "Was I rushin' or was I dragon?"

SHADOW HUNTER VOL'JIN.name: Shadow Hunter Vol'jin
SHADOW HUNTER VOL'JIN.flavorText: You wouldn’t see this swap-meet on the Zandalari Roadshow.

COSMIC KEYBOARD.name: Cosmic Keyboard
COSMIC KEYBOARD.flavorText: Mine is signed by Algalon himself.

OVERWHELM.name: Overwhelm
OVERWHELM.flavorText: Scholomance student Brewfest prank gone terribly, terribly awry.

WRATHSPIKE BRUTE.name: Wrathspike Brute
WRATHSPIKE BRUTE.flavorText: You scratch her back, her back scratches back.

UNLEASH FEL.name: Unleash Fel
UNLEASH FEL.flavorText: Why'd you put it on a leash in the first place?

MAEXXNA.name: Maexxna
MAEXXNA.flavorText: Maexxna gets super mad when people introduce her as "Maxina" or "Maxxy".

LOTHRAXION THE REDEEMED.name: Lothraxion the Redeemed
LOTHRAXION THE REDEEMED.flavorText: So infused with the Light, he has to wear double sleep masks at night.

RAVEN IDOL.name: Raven Idol
RAVEN IDOL.flavorText: Was petrified when it found out it didn't make the cut for Azerothian Idol.

SIGIL OF TIME.name: Sigil of Time
SIGIL OF TIME.flavorText: Sigil of Right A Down Right A Down.

BLADED CULTIST.name: Bladed Cultist
BLADED CULTIST.flavorText: He has a poor understanding of the law of diminishing returns.

FEL CANNON.name: Fel Cannon
FEL CANNON.flavorText: The box says, "New and improved, with 200% more fel!"

AZSHARAN RITUAL.name: Azsharan Ritual
AZSHARAN RITUAL.flavorText: The harmonious silence surrounding the ritual was unceremoniously BROKEN when HAROLD began eating stale potato chips.

ICE CREAM PEDDLER.name: Ice Cream Peddler
ICE CREAM PEDDLER.flavorText: I scream, you scream, we all scream when we see a Freeze Mage.

ARANASI BROODMOTHER.name: Aranasi Broodmother
ARANASI BROODMOTHER.flavorText: She's got a big brood and a big mood.

SWAMP LEECH.name: Swamp Leech
SWAMP LEECH.flavorText: A face only a druid could love.

ELDER LONGNECK.name: Elder Longneck
ELDER LONGNECK.flavorText: And so the bartender says, “Why the long neck?”

DINOMANCY.name: Dinomancy
DINOMANCY.flavorText: Anyone can dinomance. Just put your lips together and RAAWWWAARGGGH.

WAR GOLEM.name: War Golem
WAR GOLEM.flavorText: Golems are not afraid, but for some reason they still run when you cast Fear on them. Instinct, maybe? A desire to blend in?

HAMMER OF WRATH.name: Hammer of Wrath
HAMMER OF WRATH.flavorText: A good paladin has many tools. Hammer of Wrath, Pliers of Vengeance, Hacksaw of Justice, etc.

LIVING HORIZON.name: Living Horizon
LIVING HORIZON.flavorText: Even in the darkest of days, the sun never sets on the Badlands.

ICE BLOCK.name: Ice Block
ICE BLOCK.flavorText: Ice is nice, and will suffice!

GENEROUS MUMMY.name: Generous Mummy
GENEROUS MUMMY.flavorText: Yeah, she's mummified, but her money hasn’t dried up!

VIOLET TEACHER.name: Violet Teacher
VIOLET TEACHER.flavorText: If you don't pay attention, you may be turned into a pig. And then you get your name on the board.

AZSHARAN SWEEPER.name: Azsharan Sweeper
AZSHARAN SWEEPER.flavorText: The enchanted objects of Zin-Azshari have extremely long warranties.

ZEREK'S CLONING GALLERY.name: Zerek's Cloning Gallery
ZEREK'S CLONING GALLERY.flavorText: Cloning can be a jarring experience.

EXARCH AKAMA.name: Exarch Akama
EXARCH AKAMA.flavorText: Akama fiercely led the Vindicators in the Draenei's quest to find a new home. If only he knew what would await him on the planet of Draenor…

SWARM OF LOCUSTS.name: Swarm of Locusts
SWARM OF LOCUSTS.flavorText: Good things never come in swarms.

NAGA GIANT.name: Naga Giant
NAGA GIANT.flavorText: He might be giant, but he’s still a couple thousand protein shakes away from competing in the Colossal Wrestling Championship.

TINKERTOWN TECHNICIAN.name: Tinkertown Technician
TINKERTOWN TECHNICIAN.flavorText: Won't you take me to... Tinkertown?

BRIGHTWING.name: Brightwing
BRIGHTWING.flavorText: Little faerie dragons are made of sugar and spice and maniacal vice.

CRIMSON COMMANDER.name: Crimson Commander
CRIMSON COMMANDER.flavorText: "Wait… why do I have a Deathrattle?"

WORKSHOP JANITOR.name: Workshop Janitor
WORKSHOP JANITOR.flavorText: She works in a magical toy shop and they just gave her a regular mop? Make it make sense.

TOTEMIC EVIDENCE.name: Totemic Evidence
TOTEMIC EVIDENCE.flavorText: Every totem is evidence of a tree's murder.

CORE RAGER.name: Core Rager
CORE RAGER.flavorText: It takes a special kind of hunter to venture deep into a firey lava pit and convince a monster who lives there to come home and be a cuddly housepet.

ICE WALKER.name: Ice Walker
ICE WALKER.flavorText: Ice Walker you say? He doesn't have feet!

GILBLIN STALKER.name: Gilblin Stalker
GILBLIN STALKER.flavorText: "Shhh, I think I hear something." "Ah, it's probably nothing." - Every Henchman

MYSTERIOUS BLADE.name: Mysterious Blade
MYSTERIOUS BLADE.flavorText: It knows every secret you have left.

EVERSONG PORTAL.name: Eversong Portal
EVERSONG PORTAL.flavorText: In retrospect, it's pretty impressive that they had the Lynxes just ready to go.

DRAGONFIRE POTION.name: Dragonfire Potion
DRAGONFIRE POTION.flavorText: No one was brave enough to fire the dragon in person… so they made the potion do it.

SNAKE EYES.name: Snake Eyes
SNAKE EYES.flavorText: Hey, put ALL of your hands on the table!

INFEST.name: Infest
INFEST.flavorText: The best part is the look on their face when you jump out of the cake! Err… corpse.

MALCHEZAAR'S IMP.name: Malchezaar's Imp
MALCHEZAAR'S IMP.flavorText: Malchezaar used to have an imp named Dobby working for him, but there was a tragic accident.

DEFENDER OF ARGUS.name: Defender of Argus
DEFENDER OF ARGUS.flavorText: You wouldn’t think that Argus would need this much defending. But it does.

DENDROLOGIST.name: Dendrologist
DENDROLOGIST.flavorText: He's teaching his little buddy to talk, but all it says is, "I am Gloop."

THADDIUS, MONSTROSITY.name: Thaddius, Monstrosity
THADDIUS, MONSTROSITY.flavorText: Feugen is positive that Thaddius will see play, but Stalagg seems negative about it.

MAJORDOMO EXECUTUS.name: Majordomo Executus
MAJORDOMO EXECUTUS.flavorText: You thought Executus turned you into Ragnaros, but really Ragnaros was in you the whole time.

SPICE BREAD BAKER.name: Spice Bread Baker
SPICE BREAD BAKER.flavorText: The secret ingredient is love. And a LOT of butter.

DIVINE BREW.name: Divine Brew
DIVINE BREW.flavorText: I'm on a cleanse, do you have any Light drinks?

G'HUUN THE BLOOD GOD.name: G'huun the Blood God
G'HUUN THE BLOOD GOD.flavorText: All of the other Old Gods used to laugh and call him names. They never let poor G'huun join in any Old God games.

RED MANA WYRM.name: Red Mana Wyrm
RED MANA WYRM.flavorText: It has double the Attack. "Go on." And double the Health. "Yes??" And its trigger has twice the effect. "WHAT???" And it costs… Five times more.

JOTUN, THE ETERNAL.name: Jotun, the Eternal
JOTUN, THE ETERNAL.flavorText: He doesn't look like a turtle?

DARKFALLEN SHADOW.name: Darkfallen Shadow
DARKFALLEN SHADOW.flavorText: Manathirst AND Reborn?! Pick a side!

SHALE SPIDER.name: Shale Spider
SHALE SPIDER.flavorText: The 2nd member of the VERY exclusive Is-Called-A-Spider-But-Isn't-A-Beast Club.

PLAGUE SCIENTIST.name: Plague Scientist
PLAGUE SCIENTIST.flavorText: The excruciating pain means it's working!

MURLOC TIDECALLER.name: Murloc Tidecaller
MURLOC TIDECALLER.flavorText: This guy gets crazy strong at family reunions.

DEFROST.name: Defrost
DEFROST.flavorText: Shouldn't this NOT be a Frost spell?

FOCUSED WILL.name: Focused Will
FOCUSED WILL.flavorText: Extreme focus is almost as effective as a really flashy distraction.

CRYSTALSMITH KANGOR.name: Crystalsmith Kangor
CRYSTALSMITH KANGOR.flavorText: He wants to tank, but Boom always makes him play support.

VIVID NIGHTMARE.name: Vivid Nightmare
VIVID NIGHTMARE.flavorText: "I… I dreamed I accidentally crafted a golden Millhouse! It was so REAL!"

SCRAP SHOT.name: Scrap Shot
SCRAP SHOT.flavorText: Make your foe's armor your fauna's fashion!

WAR MASTER VOONE.name: War Master Voone
WAR MASTER VOONE.flavorText: War Master sounds cooler than Dragon Sitter.

WALKING MOUNTAIN.name: Walking Mountain
WALKING MOUNTAIN.flavorText: The hills are alive with the sound of YEEEEHAAAWWWW!

ARCANE FLETCHER.name: Arcane Fletcher
ARCANE FLETCHER.flavorText: Stop trying to make fletch happen. It's not going to happen.

PICK POCKET.name: Pick Pocket
PICK POCKET.flavorText: He'll pick anyone's pocket, except a gnome's. He'd never stoop so low.

LIGHTSTEED.name: Lightsteed
LIGHTSTEED.flavorText: All the steed, half the calories.

WHIRLWEAVER.name: Whirlweaver
WHIRLWEAVER.flavorText: Of all the creations from the Construct Quarter, a naga combined with water is the most intuitive.

INJURED BLADEMASTER.name: Injured Blademaster
INJURED BLADEMASTER.flavorText: He claims it is an old war wound, but we think he just cut himself shaving.

CRYSTALLINE GREATMACE.name: Crystalline Greatmace
CRYSTALLINE GREATMACE.flavorText: The only difference between a mace and a greatmace is... PRESENTATION!

SCALED NIGHTMARE.name: Scaled Nightmare
SCALED NIGHTMARE.flavorText: I like it because it scales.

BLUBBER BARON.name: Blubber Baron
BLUBBER BARON.flavorText: When oil, railroad, steel, robber, and red are all already taken, your options are limited.

PORTAL KEEPER.name: Portal Keeper
PORTAL KEEPER.flavorText: No longer allowed to be “it” when playing demon tag.

SCARAB KEYCHAIN.name: Scarab Keychain
SCARAB KEYCHAIN.flavorText: "How do you keep losing your keys!? They couldn't have just gotten up and walked away!"

BLOODSEEKER.name: Bloodseeker
BLOODSEEKER.flavorText: What do you mean shooting them in the back isn’t honorable?!

MINDGAMES.name: Mindgames
MINDGAMES.flavorText: Sometimes it feels like this is all a game.

WEIGHT OF THE WORLD.name: Weight of the World
WEIGHT OF THE WORLD.flavorText: Unluckily for him, Azeroth has a tendency to get bigger every 2 years or so.

CHOPSHOP COPTER.name: Chopshop Copter
CHOPSHOP COPTER.flavorText: Invention is the mother of entropy.

FROSTWOLF KENNELS.name: Frostwolf Kennels
FROSTWOLF KENNELS.flavorText: The 1 reason Alliance members defect to the Horde is to adopt a cute frostwolf puppy.

WASTELAND SCORPID.name: Wasteland Scorpid
WASTELAND SCORPID.flavorText: After they get to a certain size, it doesn't matter if they're poisonous or not.

MENAGERIE WARDEN.name: Menagerie Warden
MENAGERIE WARDEN.flavorText: Please? Can I keep him? I promise to clean his cage every day.

ANACHRONOS.name: Anachronos
ANACHRONOS.flavorText: "That's it, you're all in time out!"

HOLOTECHNICIAN.name: Holotechnician
HOLOTECHNICIAN.flavorText: Ironically, operating the spotlight comes with very little recognition.

THE GARDEN'S GRACE.name: The Garden's Grace
THE GARDEN'S GRACE.flavorText: The perfect place to hold Conchella.

HARROWING OX.name: Harrowing Ox
HARROWING OX.flavorText: Dead or alive, you're pulling that plow.

NETHERWALKER.name: Netherwalker
NETHERWALKER.flavorText: You got to Nethercrawl before you can Netherwalk.

CORROSIVE BREATH.name: Corrosive Breath
CORROSIVE BREATH.flavorText: It's a breath of fresh terror!

FLIPPER FRIENDS.name: Flipper Friends
FLIPPER FRIENDS.flavorText: Despite the harsh conditions, friends can still be found under the sea.

ARCHMAGE VARGOTH.name: Archmage Vargoth
ARCHMAGE VARGOTH.flavorText: He's an archmage, but he might want to brush up on the basics... like aiming.

OWLONIUS.name: Owlonius
OWLONIUS.flavorText: They said you sound like an owl.

PUNCH CARD.name: Punch Card
PUNCH CARD.flavorText: Don't forget to punch out when you Cleave.

DON'T FEED THE ANIMALS.name: Don't Feed the Animals
DON'T FEED THE ANIMALS.flavorText: They're still cleaning up the mess from the last time someone fed the basilisk a deep fried candybar.

CARNIVOROUS CUBE.name: Carnivorous Cube
CARNIVOROUS CUBE.flavorText: He's always grumpy until he's eaten his first barista of the morning.

HECKLEBOT.name: Hecklebot
HECKLEBOT.flavorText: Built by goblins, designed by a troll.

PELICAN DIVER.name: Pelican Diver
PELICAN DIVER.flavorText: The pelican’s beak is so big, some Colossal minions can even fit inside!* *This is a lie.

CARRION DRAKE.name: Carrion Drake
CARRION DRAKE.flavorText: Fits easily into overhead luggage bins.

MIDNIGHT WOLF.name: Midnight Wolf
MIDNIGHT WOLF.flavorText: Three of these would make for an EPIC T-shirt.

CHARGED DEVILSAUR.name: Charged Devilsaur
CHARGED DEVILSAUR.flavorText: What happens when a dinosaur mixes soda and pop rocks.

SUMMONING WARD.name: Summoning Ward
SUMMONING WARD.flavorText: You couldn't handle one Snowflipper Penguin. So what hope do you have… against two?!

BOGBEAM.name: Bogbeam
BOGBEAM.flavorText: Some think the mysterious bright lights in the bog are alien invaders, others think they're just swamp gas. Turns out, it's just druids.

YOUNG PRIESTESS.name: Young Priestess
YOUNG PRIESTESS.flavorText: She can't wait to learn Power Word: Fortitude Rank 2.

DOOMHAMMER.name: Doomhammer
DOOMHAMMER.flavorText: Orgrim Doomhammer gave this legendary weapon to Thrall. His name is a total coincidence.

STUDENT OF THE STARS.name: Student of the Stars
STUDENT OF THE STARS.flavorText: She is getting her major in Ursa.

DARKSPEAKER.name: Darkspeaker
DARKSPEAKER.flavorText: People often think that Darkspeaker is the arch nemesis of Lightspeaker, but that title actually belongs to Heavyspeaker.

COMMAND THE ILLIDARI.name: Command the Illidari
COMMAND THE ILLIDARI.flavorText: Give me an R! Give me a U! Give me an S! Give me an H! You two, you’re exclamation points!

ICEHOWL.name: Icehowl
ICEHOWL.flavorText: This massive yeti just closes his eyes and charges at the nearest target. The nearest Target is a couple blocks away and has sick deals on skateboards.

CRYSTALSONG PORTAL.name: Crystalsong Portal
CRYSTALSONG PORTAL.flavorText: Experience the draw of the wild!

AKALI, THE RHINO.name: Akali, the Rhino
AKALI, THE RHINO.flavorText: Most trolls only get to “AAAAHHH!” and don’t make it to the “kali” part.

SHADY BARTENDER.name: Shady Bartender
SHADY BARTENDER.flavorText: One sin and tonic, coming right up.

GAIA, THE TECHTONIC.name: Gaia, the Techtonic
GAIA, THE TECHTONIC.flavorText: Always planning ahead, Ini knew she'd need this invention to protect all her other inventions.

PLAYHOUSE GIANT.name: Playhouse Giant
PLAYHOUSE GIANT.flavorText: WARNING: NOT A PLAYHOUSE. DO NOT ATTEMPT TO CLIMB.

GILDED GARGOYLE.name: Gilded Gargoyle
GILDED GARGOYLE.flavorText: You hear a coin rattling inside the slotted gargoyle...What could it mean?

CORRUPTED SEER.name: Corrupted Seer
CORRUPTED SEER.flavorText: For seers, it's very handy to have your crystal ball hanging right in front of your face.

STOLEN GOODS.name: Stolen Goods
STOLEN GOODS.flavorText: It fell off a kodo, I promise!

NOXIOUS INFILTRATOR.name: Noxious Infiltrator
NOXIOUS INFILTRATOR.flavorText: Noxious, but not toxic - he's very polite!

TOMB LURKER.name: Tomb Lurker
TOMB LURKER.flavorText: She hangs out in all the tombs, but she rarely posts.

KOBOLD HERMIT.name: Kobold Hermit
KOBOLD HERMIT.flavorText: To truly understand candles, it takes YEARS of quiet contemplation.

NIGHTBLADE.name: Nightblade
NIGHTBLADE.flavorText: Your face is the place you'd probably least like a dagger, and where rogues are most likely to deliver them.

STONEHILL DEFENDER.name: Stonehill Defender
STONEHILL DEFENDER.flavorText: Briefly tried stand-up comedy under the name "Stonehill Offender", but turtles are just too thin-skinned.

PRIMORDIAL STUDIES.name: Primordial Studies
PRIMORDIAL STUDIES.flavorText: A long forgotten tome whose very essence seeps of magic. 40 dust, used.

DISPOSAL ASSISTANT.name: Disposal Assistant
DISPOSAL ASSISTANT.flavorText: A bright green liquid that people say is bad for you... That's either hazardous waste OR a new popular brand of soft drink.

HOLY RIPPLE.name: Holy Ripple
HOLY RIPPLE.flavorText: I still prefer the taste of banana fudge ripple.

WING COMMANDER MULVERICK.name: Wing Commander Mulverick
WING COMMANDER MULVERICK.flavorText: “A board full of 2-Health minions? This is what I call a target rich environment.”

SELFLESS SIDEKICK.name: Selfless Sidekick
SELFLESS SIDEKICK.flavorText: "I got a real sense of humility from her when she bashed that quilboar's head in."

DALARAN MAGE.name: Dalaran Mage
DALARAN MAGE.flavorText: You don't see a lot of Dalaran warriors.

CONCOCTOR.name: Concoctor
CONCOCTOR.flavorText: "A dash of death, with a pinch of death, and a sprinkle of… death!"

SUPERCOLLIDER.name: Supercollider
SUPERCOLLIDER.flavorText: Boom's Second Law of Motion: HIT IT VERY HARD!

GALAKROND, THE NIGHTMARE.name: Galakrond, the Nightmare
GALAKROND, THE NIGHTMARE.flavorText: The enormous creature unfurled terrifying claws dripping with poisonous ichor. King Togwaggle was pleased, but inwardly disappointed the great Nightmare refused to wear the candle.

REINCARNATE.name: Reincarnate
REINCARNATE.flavorText: It's like birth, except you're an adult and you were just dead a second ago.

BOGSTROK CLACKER.name: Bogstrok Clacker
BOGSTROK CLACKER.flavorText: This clacker's crackers for hacking slackers into whack attackers.

EVOLVE.name: Evolve
EVOLVE.flavorText: So you say you want an evolution. Well, you know. We all want to change the board.

RELIC OF EXTINCTION.name: Relic of Extinction
RELIC OF EXTINCTION.flavorText: Faster than an asteroid, and just as effective.

TAINTED REMNANT.name: Tainted Remnant
TAINTED REMNANT.flavorText: A sore sight of eyesores for sore eyes.

DIGGING STRAIGHT DOWN.name: Digging Straight Down
DIGGING STRAIGHT DOWN.flavorText: You only make this mistake once.

STONESKIN ARMORER.name: Stoneskin Armorer
STONESKIN ARMORER.flavorText: Pretty sensitive for someone made of thick skin.

FACELESS BEHEMOTH.name: Faceless Behemoth
FACELESS BEHEMOTH.flavorText: Rejected names: Forty-Foot Faceless, Big ol' No-face, Huge Creature Sans Face, Teddy.

OMEGA MEDIC.name: Omega Medic
OMEGA MEDIC.flavorText: She feels waiting for healing makes you appreciate it more.

BONECHEWER VANGUARD.name: Bonechewer Vanguard
BONECHEWER VANGUARD.flavorText: She came here to taunt you and chew on bones, and she's all outta bones.

EXPIRED MERCHANT.name: Expired Merchant
EXPIRED MERCHANT.flavorText: The "best by" date is more like a guideline.

INFECTIOUS SPORELING.name: Infectious Sporeling
INFECTIOUS SPORELING.flavorText: "The best thing about being me—there’s so many 'me's."

HEX.name: Hex
HEX.flavorText: If you Hex a Murloc... it really isn't much of a change, is it?

RAT PACK.name: Rat Pack
RAT PACK.flavorText: He's gonna do it his way.

VITALITY TOTEM.name: Vitality Totem
VITALITY TOTEM.flavorText: You can usually find these at the totemist's market on Saturdays.

E.T.C., GOD OF METAL.name: E.T.C., God of Metal
E.T.C., GOD OF METAL.flavorText: There are Old Gods and then there are Rock Gods.

CREEPY PAINTING.name: Creepy Painting
CREEPY PAINTING.flavorText: I do not like this painting, Harth. Its smug aura mocks me.

SKY CLAW.name: Sky Claw
SKY CLAW.flavorText: Carefully engineered to never grab the Mimiron plush toy.

POWERMACE.name: Powermace
POWERMACE.flavorText: People assume that shamans control the elements, but really, they have to ask them stuff and the elements are like, "Yeah ok, sure."

HOWLING BLAST.name: Howling Blast
HOWLING BLAST.flavorText: For Death Knights, yelling really loudly is a valid attack strategy.

SPARK DRILL.name: Spark Drill
SPARK DRILL.flavorText: Preferred weapon of Dr. Boom's orthodontist.

KATHRENA WINTERWISP.name: Kathrena Winterwisp
KATHRENA WINTERWISP.flavorText: She’s not one of those treehugger elves – but she does like the occasional cuddle.

PRIEST OF THE FEAST.name: Priest of the Feast
PRIEST OF THE FEAST.flavorText: Now that's a world champion cheesecake!

DESERT HARE.name: Desert Hare
DESERT HARE.flavorText: After they're caught, they’re dessert hares.

MAYOR NOGGENFOGGER.name: Mayor Noggenfogger
MAYOR NOGGENFOGGER.flavorText: This flavor text was randomly generated. If it happens to form words and make sense, that is purely by chance.

RUNEFORGE HAUNTER.name: Runeforge Haunter
RUNEFORGE HAUNTER.flavorText: Don't worry, he'll keep an eye on that for you.

ICE RAGER.name: Ice Rager
ICE RAGER.flavorText: He's a lot cooler than Magma Rager.

LOST IN THE JUNGLE.name: Lost in the Jungle
LOST IN THE JUNGLE.flavorText: George and Karl were never heard from again.

JADE SHURIKEN.name: Jade Shuriken
JADE SHURIKEN.flavorText: Good news is, after you remove it from your wound, you can use it to pay your medical bills!

DERAILED COASTER.name: Derailed Coaster
DERAILED COASTER.flavorText: So long as it doesn’t kill you, it's considered part of the ride "experience."

HARMONIC HIP HOP.name: Harmonic Hip Hop
HARMONIC HIP HOP.flavorText: I can name four things that rhyme with 'orange': Four inch, Door hinge, Syringe, and uh… Shmorange.

DARKBOMB.name: Darkbomb
DARKBOMB.flavorText: If you're looking to make an "Emo" deck, this card is perfect!

ANCHORITE.name: Anchorite
ANCHORITE.flavorText: A Priest is nothing without their anchor. Wait, what?

TWILIGHT SUMMONER.name: Twilight Summoner
TWILIGHT SUMMONER.flavorText: If you strike him down, he shall become more powerful than you can possibly imagine.

RUSH THE STAGE.name: Rush the Stage
RUSH THE STAGE.flavorText: Left Shark, get to the stage now!

ANCHARRR.name: Ancharrr
ANCHARRR.flavorText: The problem with anchors is they often end up sinking to the bottom of your deck.

POCKET SAND.name: Pocket Sand
POCKET SAND.flavorText: I was only trying to get it in your eyes, man. YOU didn't need to open your mouth like that!

HIGH EXARCH YREL.name: High Exarch Yrel
HIGH EXARCH YREL.flavorText: There can be no neutrality in the fight against darkness.

FORBIDDEN HEALING.name: Forbidden Healing
FORBIDDEN HEALING.flavorText: No one's quite sure why it's forbidden. And yes, that should make you nervous.

DEADLY POISON.name: Deadly Poison
DEADLY POISON.flavorText: Rogues guard the secrets to poison-making carefully, lest magi start incorporating poison into their spells. Poisonbolt? Rain of Poison? Poison Elemental? Nobody wants that.

BLACKROCK 'N' ROLL.name: Blackrock 'n' Roll
BLACKROCK 'N' ROLL.flavorText: Thank goodness it's not called Black-ska Mountain.

IMPRISONED OBSERVER.name: Imprisoned Observer
IMPRISONED OBSERVER.flavorText: Currently serving two turns on charges of aggravated minion slaughter.

POLLUTED HOARDER.name: Polluted Hoarder
POLLUTED HOARDER.flavorText: Roll ‘greed’ OR THIS COULD HAPPEN TO YOU.

OVERFLOW SURGER.name: Overflow Surger
OVERFLOW SURGER.flavorText: The drip on this elemental is straight fire!

DEATH SPEAKER BLACKTHORN.name: Death Speaker Blackthorn
DEATH SPEAKER BLACKTHORN.flavorText: He can speak death but has a hard time reading it.

SANGUINE SOLDIER.name: Sanguine Soldier
SANGUINE SOLDIER.flavorText: They just need someone to ouch for them.

SHADOW ASCENDANT.name: Shadow Ascendant
SHADOW ASCENDANT.flavorText: When you're at the bottom, there's nowhere to ascend, but up.

BONEWEB EGG.name: Boneweb Egg
BONEWEB EGG.flavorText: Noblegarden is going to be really exciting this year!

KOBOLD ILLUSIONIST.name: Kobold Illusionist
KOBOLD ILLUSIONIST.flavorText: He can make ANYTHING look like a candle.

PATCHES THE PIRATE.name: Patches the Pirate
PATCHES THE PIRATE.flavorText: What do sailors yell when Patches steals their treasure chest full of laws and other things being transported to parliament for a vote? "The Eyes have it!"

STORMPIKE MARSHAL.name: Stormpike Marshal
STORMPIKE MARSHAL.flavorText: The Stormpike have a very direct take on life insurance.

NESTING GOLEM.name: Nesting Golem
NESTING GOLEM.flavorText: NESTING GOLEEEEEEEEEEEEM!!!!!!! Eh… It just doesn't feel the same.

DIVINE FAVOR.name: Divine Favor
DIVINE FAVOR.flavorText: This is not just a favor, but a divine one, like helping someone move a couch with a fold out bed!

BOULDERING BUDDY.name: Bouldering Buddy
BOULDERING BUDDY.flavorText: Why would you buy a walking stick when the forest is full of them!?

DANCING COBRA.name: Dancing Cobra
DANCING COBRA.flavorText: Snakes are just tentacles with fangs.

TRIAL OF THE JORMUNGARS.name: Trial of the Jormungars
TRIAL OF THE JORMUNGARS.flavorText: The defendants were found guilty on 33 counts of wiping raid parties.

AZSHARAN VESSEL.name: Azsharan Vessel
AZSHARAN VESSEL.flavorText: Not even the sturdiest Highborne ship could survive the churning waters of the Sundering.

SARGERAS, THE DESTROYER.name: Sargeras, the Destroyer
SARGERAS, THE DESTROYER.flavorText: Formerly the Defender of the Pantheon, he became disillusioned by his mission and formed the Burning Legion to destroy all life within the universe.

SPORE EMPRESS MOLDARA.name: Spore Empress Moldara
SPORE EMPRESS MOLDARA.flavorText: Sorry for not explaining the Spores in the textbox. We just didn't have that mushroom.

GRAND CRUSADER.name: Grand Crusader
GRAND CRUSADER.flavorText: A veteran of a number of crusades, she is a force for light and goodness. Her latest crusade is against goblin telemarketers.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/51/VO_AT_118_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_118_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/ba/VO_AT_118_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_118_ATTACK_02.wav For the Light!
