HORSESHOE SLINGER.name: Horseshoe Slinger
HORSESHOE SLINGER.flavorText: Some people think this card is broken, but I think it's farrier than that.

SEASCOUT OPERATOR.name: Seascout Operator
SEASCOUT OPERATOR.flavorText: The Mechafish are actually totally autonomous. We gave her a fake control pad, as a joke.

NOBLE MINIBOT.name: Noble Minibot
NOBLE MINIBOT.flavorText: I always get the minibot with the wobbly wheel.

ELDER NADOX.name: Elder Nadox
ELDER NADOX.flavorText: For an Undead, is an elder the least or most dead?

SPYMISTRESS.name: Spymistress
SPYMISTRESS.flavorText: Spies in Outland must blend into the environment. That means hot-pink gear and bright green hair. It’s a weird place.

DON HAN'CHO.name: Don Han'Cho
DON HAN'CHO.flavorText: The brilliant mastermind of the Grimy Goons, Han sometimes thinks about ditching the idiot Cho, but that would just tear him apart.

HALLUCINATION.name: Hallucination
HALLUCINATION.flavorText: It's the good kind of hallucination.

CAMOUFLAGE MOUNT.name: Camouflage Mount
CAMOUFLAGE MOUNT.flavorText: What mount? I don't see anything…

PRINCE KELESETH.name: Prince Keleseth
PRINCE KELESETH.flavorText: Three Princes stand before you. This one wants to buff his brothers.

REPLICATING MENACE.name: Replicating Menace
REPLICATING MENACE.flavorText: It's a car! *Whomp whomp whomp* It's a robot! *Whomp whom-CRUNCH* It's… three.. smaller robots!

CHILL-O-MATIC.name: Chill-o-matic
CHILL-O-MATIC.flavorText: After a number of island vacations, he thought the Storm Peaks would be a nice change of pace.

REDEEMED PARIAH.name: Redeemed Pariah
REDEEMED PARIAH.flavorText: "Look at this stick. Look at it!"

SPIRIT CLAWS.name: Spirit Claws
SPIRIT CLAWS.flavorText: They'll be MUCH easier to use once they add the spiritthumb.

RIMETONGUE.name: Rimetongue
RIMETONGUE.flavorText: Warriors are red, Frost spells are blue, If you're being hit by a weapon, Rimetongue's got you.

APOTHEOSIS.name: Apotheosis
APOTHEOSIS.flavorText: Defined as the absolute pinnacle of existence. Plus Lifesteal.

SOCK PUPPET SLITHERSPEAR.name: Sock Puppet Slitherspear
SOCK PUPPET SLITHERSPEAR.flavorText: The right hand of Queen Azshara is Lady Vashj. This is her left hand.

AEON REAVER.name: Aeon Reaver
AEON REAVER.flavorText: Ripping centuries asunder helps him manage his busy schedule.

SLUDGE BELCHER.name: Sludge Belcher
SLUDGE BELCHER.flavorText: DO NOT GIVE HIM A ROOT BEER.

BRONZE EXPLORER.name: Bronze Explorer
BRONZE EXPLORER.flavorText: Always ready to explore new friendships! Except with Deathwing.

ARCANE DEVOURER.name: Arcane Devourer
ARCANE DEVOURER.flavorText: Likes her magic with a pinch of salt.

CLONING DEVICE.name: Cloning Device
CLONING DEVICE.flavorText: Zerek got sick of fighting over the remote.

NIGHT HOWLER.name: Night Howler
NIGHT HOWLER.flavorText: Honestly, he howls during the day, too.

VIVID SPORES.name: Vivid Spores
VIVID SPORES.flavorText: Hey man, I just feel like... death is just a construct of our imaginations, ya know?

CHRONOBREAKER.name: Chronobreaker
CHRONOBREAKER.flavorText: If he asks to borrow your watch, just say no.

BONE DRAKE.name: Bone Drake
BONE DRAKE.flavorText: The bone drake brings all the dragons to the yard. He would teach you, but you have no cards.

SWEET TOOTH.name: Sweet Tooth
SWEET TOOTH.flavorText: He's been eyeballing that ice cream cone all day!

KEL'THUZAD.name: Kel'Thuzad
KEL'THUZAD.flavorText: Kel'Thuzad could not resist the call of the Lich King. Even when it's just a robo-call extolling the Lich King's virtues.

PRINCE RENATHAL.name: Prince Renathal
PRINCE RENATHAL.flavorText: A lot of kids go through a rebellious phase, but Prince Renathal's was a bit extreme.

MOSH PIT.name: Mosh Pit
MOSH PIT.flavorText: Let the Corpses hit the floor!

DEMONWRATH.name: Demonwrath
DEMONWRATH.flavorText: Demons are not angry most of the time. You have to play this card in order to really bring it out of them.

MECHA-SHARK.name: Mecha-Shark
MECHA-SHARK.flavorText: "Why didn't you just build a normal submarine. Only you can fit inside" "WhY DiDn'T YoU JuSt BuIlD anormalsub-WHY DO YOU THINK WREZIG!! If you can build a freaking Mecha-Shark, then you build a freaking Mecha-Shark!"

KHAZ'GOROTH.name: Khaz'goroth
KHAZ'GOROTH.flavorText: Creator of the titan-forged races, Khaz'goroth intended them to safeguard the world of Azeroth from corruption and discord.

MAN THE CANNONS.name: Man the Cannons
MAN THE CANNONS.flavorText: Now THAT’S a lotta splash damage!

BRONZE GATEKEEPER.name: Bronze Gatekeeper
BRONZE GATEKEEPER.flavorText: "You have my shield! And the rest of me too."

TYR.name: Tyr
TYR.flavorText: Brought me back to life, S Tyr card.

ROCKBITER WEAPON.name: Rockbiter Weapon
ROCKBITER WEAPON.flavorText: This would be real handy if your enemy is made of rock.

CUTTHROAT BUCCANEER.name: Cutthroat Buccaneer
CUTTHROAT BUCCANEER.flavorText: In life he worked as a sword swallower.

SOUL CLEAVE.name: Soul Cleave
SOUL CLEAVE.flavorText: The way to a demon's soul is through its stomach.

CROW'S NEST LOOKOUT.name: Crow's Nest Lookout
CROW'S NEST LOOKOUT.flavorText: The extra eyes means he sees extra good.

LIGHTNING REFLEXES.name: Lightning Reflexes
LIGHTNING REFLEXES.flavorText: If you can dodge a lightning bolt, you can dodge a ball.

OPTIMISTIC OGRE.name: Optimistic Ogre
OPTIMISTIC OGRE.flavorText: "What if this goes wrong?" "But what if this goes right?"

JADE BLOSSOM.name: Jade Blossom
JADE BLOSSOM.flavorText: Meditating under a jade blossom is said to grant you wisdom, unless you have a pollen allergy.

DEATH'S BITE.name: Death's Bite
DEATH'S BITE.flavorText: "Take a bite outta Death." - McScruff the Deathlord

AZERITE CHAIN GANG.name: Azerite Chain Gang
AZERITE CHAIN GANG.flavorText: How long can this go on? For 6 years at least!

CORRUPT THE WATERS.name: Corrupt the Waters
CORRUPT THE WATERS.flavorText: This is why Hagatha is banned from public pools.

DEFIAS LEPER.name: Defias Leper
DEFIAS LEPER.flavorText: Do NOT eat Cookie’s Seafood Surprise.

KAEL'THAS SUNSTRIDER.name: Kael'thas Sunstrider
KAEL'THAS SUNSTRIDER.flavorText: “Descent of Dragons was merely a set back!”

SINSTONE TOTEM.name: Sinstone Totem
SINSTONE TOTEM.flavorText: This one's heavier than the wooden totems. Mostly from the weight of your sins.

EUREKA!.name: Eureka!
EUREKA!.flavorText: Genius is 1% inspiration, and 99% drawing your Deathwing.

WRETCHED QUEEN.name: Wretched Queen
WRETCHED QUEEN.flavorText: Mind your head when you're around her.

POZZIK, AUDIO ENGINEER.name: Pozzik, Audio Engineer
POZZIK, AUDIO ENGINEER.flavorText: "I'm down here, fixin' all the Gnomish tech that breaks down mid-set while that buffoon Fizzle is up there taking pictures of the sky. YOU tell ME who's the better engineer!"

RENEW.name: Renew
RENEW.flavorText: I am rejuvenated, I am renewed, I am my own nightlight!

BOTTOMFEEDER.name: Bottomfeeder
BOTTOMFEEDER.flavorText: Someone keeps adding fish to my deck, and I'm going to get to the bottom of it.

RUMBLETUSK SHAKER.name: Rumbletusk Shaker
RUMBLETUSK SHAKER.flavorText: Rub a dub dub, three trolls in a tub. And who do you think dey be? Da Shaker, Da Breaker, and Da Undatakah. And all of dem comin' for me.

MOLTEN RUNE.name: Molten Rune
MOLTEN RUNE.flavorText: It's post-ancient modern realist neoclassical impressionist art. No idea what it means though.

WHEEL OF DEATH!!!.name: Wheel of DEATH!!!
WHEEL OF DEATH!!!.flavorText: Why don't the good guys ever get a wheel?

SERGEANT SALLY.name: Sergeant Sally
SERGEANT SALLY.flavorText: "Who is she? Where did she come from? We don't even have a police force here in Gadgetzan!!" - Mayor Noggenfogger

NECROMECHANIC.name: Necromechanic
NECROMECHANIC.flavorText: If at first you don't succeed, die, die again.

ANNOY-O-MODULE.name: Annoy-o-Module
ANNOY-O-MODULE.flavorText: Every ten seconds it asks if you want to update.

ASTRAL AUTOMATON.name: Astral Automaton
ASTRAL AUTOMATON.flavorText: You'll want to summon an automaTON of these.

GURUBASHI HYPEMON.name: Gurubashi Hypemon
GURUBASHI HYPEMON.flavorText: Throw your hands in the air! They cost (1).

SHATTERSHAMBLER.name: Shattershambler
SHATTERSHAMBLER.flavorText: Someone didn’t realize the ‘cold, black heart’ thing was supposed to be a metaphor.

CHEMICAL SPILL.name: Chemical Spill
CHEMICAL SPILL.flavorText: I said spill the TEA, not the acid!

RAKE.name: Rake
RAKE.flavorText: When you're done shredding through your enemies, use it on your leaves!

MOR'SHAN ELITE.name: Mor'shan Elite
MOR'SHAN ELITE.flavorText: "Fear not the orc who has slain a million training dummies, but the orc who keeps CAMPING MY CORPSE!"

INVITATION COURIER.name: Invitation Courier
INVITATION COURIER.flavorText: Sending mail via steward is soooo old school.

GREY SAGE PARROT.name: Grey Sage Parrot
GREY SAGE PARROT.flavorText: Nothing is more terrifying than a parrot squawking "Pyroblast!"

DAR'KHAN DRATHIR.name: Dar'Khan Drathir
DAR'KHAN DRATHIR.flavorText: You're telling me that you didn't suspect him of being evil, even though the first four letters of his name are D-A-R-K?

TOTEMIC SMASH.name: Totemic Smash
TOTEMIC SMASH.flavorText: Trolls are the first group to have a totem survive atmospheric re-entry.

PIERCING SHOT.name: Piercing Shot
PIERCING SHOT.flavorText: Goblins hate wasting money on unnecessary ammunition.

TOGWAGGLE'S SCHEME.name: Togwaggle's Scheme
TOGWAGGLE'S SCHEME.flavorText: "Many minions equals many treasures for king. Kobold arithmetic!"

PARTY UP!.name: Party Up!
PARTY UP!.flavorText: Random? But what if we don't get a tank?

INSTRUMENT TECH.name: Instrument Tech
INSTRUMENT TECH.flavorText: A tech card without Tradeable? CRINGE.

SOUL SPLIT.name: Soul Split
SOUL SPLIT.flavorText: Spoiler: they're both the evil twin.

HAGATHA THE WITCH.name: Hagatha the Witch
HAGATHA THE WITCH.flavorText: Curse-bringer, tree-twister, mother of wretched things…Hanzo main.

MECHA'THUN.name: Mecha'thun
MECHA'THUN.flavorText: "Your software will fail. Your users will abandon you. You are already obsolete."

FATE WEAVER.name: Fate Weaver
FATE WEAVER.flavorText: Do not draw the attention of a Fate Weaver, for it will always loom over your destiny.

BLOODSAIL CULTIST.name: Bloodsail Cultist
BLOODSAIL CULTIST.flavorText: They're really just in it for the Blood Parrot.

BRANN BRONZEBEARD.name: Brann Bronzebeard
BRANN BRONZEBEARD.flavorText: Contains 75% more fiber than his brother Magni!

FOREST GUIDE.name: Forest Guide
FOREST GUIDE.flavorText: "Just sign this waiver, and we'll be on our way."

CORPSE EXPLOSION.name: Corpse Explosion
CORPSE EXPLOSION.flavorText: What? It's not like they were using them anymore.

BONECHEWER BRAWLER.name: Bonechewer Brawler
BONECHEWER BRAWLER.flavorText: When you get this swole, arrows are basically free acupuncture.

STONE SENTINEL.name: Stone Sentinel
STONE SENTINEL.flavorText: He and his friends just want to rock out.

EDUCATED ELEKK.name: Educated Elekk
EDUCATED ELEKK.flavorText: "This reminds me of a saying. 'An elekk never…' something. I can't remember."

PREDATION.name: Predation
PREDATION.flavorText: No need to worry! The squid is actually being sent to a nice kelp farm upstate.

HALVERIA DARKRAVEN.name: Halveria Darkraven
HALVERIA DARKRAVEN.flavorText: You know someone's cool when their name sounds like a font.

PLAGUE STRIKE.name: Plague Strike
PLAGUE STRIKE.flavorText: Not wanting to infect anyone with his cold, the Death Knight politely coughed into his shoulder.

RAZORFEN ROCKSTAR.name: Razorfen Rockstar
RAZORFEN ROCKSTAR.flavorText: Quilboar feel Rock in their blood. And blood in their rocks.

MOTHERSHIP.name: Mothership
MOTHERSHIP.flavorText: Has been known to abduct sea cows and leave kelp circles.

SILVERLEAF POISON.name: Silverleaf Poison
SILVERLEAF POISON.flavorText: Kazakus has taken to a more direct approach in recent times.

RELIQUARY SEEKER.name: Reliquary Seeker
RELIQUARY SEEKER.flavorText: The Reliquary considers itself the equal of the League of Explorers. The League of Explorers doesn't.

MASS RESURRECTION.name: Mass Resurrection
MASS RESURRECTION.flavorText: One's company, two's a crowd, and three's a “mass” resurrection, apparently.

CAREFREE COOKIE.name: Carefree Cookie
CAREFREE COOKIE.flavorText: Moisturized, unbothered, and in his cauldron.

PUZZLEMASTER KHADGAR.name: Puzzlemaster Khadgar
PUZZLEMASTER KHADGAR.flavorText: Khadgar Khadgar in the ball, who is the smartest white-haired, tall, handsome mage of them all?

TAURAJO BRAVE.name: Taurajo Brave
TAURAJO BRAVE.flavorText: "He's brave, but splinters will make any Tauren cry."

DETAILED NOTES.name: Detailed Notes
DETAILED NOTES.flavorText: The Rangari Scouts pride themselves on their highly accurate notes.

BATTLEGROUND BATTLEMASTER.name: Battleground Battlemaster
BATTLEGROUND BATTLEMASTER.flavorText: Farm! No wait… Mine! No wait… 3 to Smith—they're taking Farm. Get there now!

LOVE EVERLASTING.name: Love Everlasting
LOVE EVERLASTING.flavorText: Poison Bloom was accused of plagiarizing the "Ooh, how long can this go on (ooh yeah)" hook from an old-school musical group called The Saronite Chain Gang.

FLARE.name: Flare
FLARE.flavorText: Not only does it reveal your enemies, but it's also great for parties!

DEVOURING ECTOPLASM.name: Devouring Ectoplasm
DEVOURING ECTOPLASM.flavorText: When it's on keto, it only devours tauren.

EMERALD SKYTALON.name: Emerald Skytalon
EMERALD SKYTALON.flavorText: Sworn protectors of Ysera at the Emerald Dragonshrine, these majestic owls have been touched by the powers of the Emerald Dream, taking on an almost crystalline appearance.

DEATH ROLL.name: Death Roll
DEATH ROLL.flavorText: There's a Crocolisk on my boot!

METEOR.name: Meteor
METEOR.flavorText: When you absolutely, positively have to kill all the dinosaurs.

DISCIPLINARIAN GANDLING.name: Disciplinarian Gandling
DISCIPLINARIAN GANDLING.flavorText: "He doesn’t grade on a curve, but on a sharp spike instead."

LINECRACKER.name: Linecracker
LINECRACKER.flavorText: "Tell me if you’ve heard this one!"

EARTHEN SCALES.name: Earthen Scales
EARTHEN SCALES.flavorText: You can make your own Earthen Scales at home. Step 1: Roll around in the dirt. Step 2: Magic.

MOK'NATHAL LION.name: Mok'Nathal Lion
MOK'NATHAL LION.flavorText: Never underestimate a lioness when her pride is on the line.

SHADOWBOXER.name: Shadowboxer
SHADOWBOXER.flavorText: Punching is its primary function. Also, its secondary function.

DEMONIC PROJECT.name: Demonic Project
DEMONIC PROJECT.flavorText: Another group project where Jaraxxus doesn't do any work.

POGO-HOPPER.name: Pogo-Hopper
POGO-HOPPER.flavorText: Once you hop, you just can't stop!

STABLEMASTER.name: Stablemaster
STABLEMASTER.flavorText: Takes way better care of her pets than her brother, Unstablemaster.

LIGHTNING BLOOM.name: Lightning Bloom
LIGHTNING BLOOM.flavorText: Curiously, this plant never blooms in the same place twice.

ENSLAVED FEL LORD.name: Enslaved Fel Lord
ENSLAVED FEL LORD.flavorText: He's not really chained up. He just wears that to scare the imps when they get too unruly.

ASHEN ELEMENTAL.name: Ashen Elemental
ASHEN ELEMENTAL.flavorText: "The castle was nice but the fireplaces were too small - 2/5 stars"

WIND-UP ENFORCER.name: Wind-Up Enforcer
WIND-UP ENFORCER.flavorText: Code 6404.5 clearly states that all Enforcers remain in their packaging until told by authorized personnel.

POTION OF MADNESS.name: Potion of Madness
POTION OF MADNESS.flavorText: You'd be insane NOT to drink it!

SEA SHANTY.name: Sea Shanty
SEA SHANTY.flavorText: Time for some well-earned arrr and arrr.

SANCTUM CHANDLER.name: Sanctum Chandler
SANCTUM CHANDLER.flavorText: Has been burning at both ends to keep the place illuminated.

SCORCH.name: Scorch
SCORCH.flavorText: The hoof. The hoof. The hoof is on fire.

PRIMORDIAL EXPLORER.name: Primordial Explorer
PRIMORDIAL EXPLORER.flavorText: "We're letting the poisonous dude carry the bags?"

THE 8 HANDS FROM BEYOND.name: The 8 Hands From Beyond
THE 8 HANDS FROM BEYOND.flavorText: It was a one-eyed, eight-handed, giant purple planet eater.

CURSED SOUVENIR.name: Cursed Souvenir
CURSED SOUVENIR.flavorText: Most souvenirs are considered tacky and soulless. This one is certainly not one of those things!

BOON OF THE ASCENDED.name: Boon of the Ascended
BOON OF THE ASCENDED.flavorText: Ascension is not some external power granted to you, it is the power you find within yourself.

BARONESS VASHJ.name: Baroness Vashj
BARONESS VASHJ.flavorText: Vashj was supposed to make an appearance in "The Sunken City," but after a freak accident in "Ashes of Outland," she ended up here.

BLASTCRYSTAL POTION.name: Blastcrystal Potion
BLASTCRYSTAL POTION.flavorText: There's a fine line between "potion" and "grenade". Wait. Actually, there's not.

GOLIATH, SNEED'S MASTERPIECE.name: Goliath, Sneed's Masterpiece
GOLIATH, SNEED'S MASTERPIECE.flavorText: “Listen, this baby has blades, rockets, and rocket blades. Only thing it doesn’t have is good gas mileage.”

CRABATOA.name: Crabatoa
CRABATOA.flavorText: This giant crab loves to sink entire naval fleets, but it'll settle for a single dinghy in a pinch.

SHAKU, THE COLLECTOR.name: Shaku, the Collector
SHAKU, THE COLLECTOR.flavorText: Aya even staged an intervention once, but Shaku still insists that he is not a hoarder.

GLINDA CROWSKIN.name: Glinda Crowskin
GLINDA CROWSKIN.flavorText: Summon an unlimited* number of minions!** *Six **Wisps

DARKBISHOP BENEDICTUS.name: Darkbishop Benedictus
DARKBISHOP BENEDICTUS.flavorText: Dark Bishop takes Light Pawn, check.

BUNNY STOMPER.name: Bunny Stomper
BUNNY STOMPER.flavorText: Has a PhD in stomputational chemistry.

RAID THE SKY TEMPLE.name: Raid the Sky Temple
RAID THE SKY TEMPLE.flavorText: "Why can't I hold all these scrolls?"

FUNGAL FORTUNES.name: Fungal Fortunes
FUNGAL FORTUNES.flavorText: Far superior to a beanstalk boondoggle.

METAMORPHOSIS.name: Metamorphosis
METAMORPHOSIS.flavorText: As the humble caterpillar becomes a beautiful butterfly, so too does a demon hunter become a hideous mass of writhing destruction and unfettered chaos.

UNIDENTIFIED ELIXIR.name: Unidentified Elixir
UNIDENTIFIED ELIXIR.flavorText: "Here, taste this." (Slurp) "What is it?" "I don't know, I found it in one of the labs."

BOLSTER.name: Bolster
BOLSTER.flavorText: The best offense is a good defense.

FREEZING POTION.name: Freezing Potion
FREEZING POTION.flavorText: This is delicious! Oh no. BRAIN FREEEEEEEZE!

CLIMACTIC NECROTIC EXPLOSION.name: Climactic Necrotic Explosion
CLIMACTIC NECROTIC EXPLOSION.flavorText: The less legible the band's logo, the more hardcore it is.

SHADOWED SPIRIT.name: Shadowed Spirit
SHADOWED SPIRIT.flavorText: They can't all be grim grinning ghosts.

DRAGONCALLER ALANNA.name: Dragoncaller Alanna
DRAGONCALLER ALANNA.flavorText: Her secret is using a gentle voice and carrying a baggie of hotdogs.

CELESTIAL DREAMER.name: Celestial Dreamer
CELESTIAL DREAMER.flavorText: If you think her job is easy, YOU try falling asleep on cue.

PRIVATE EYE.name: Private Eye
PRIVATE EYE.flavorText: Eye see what you did there.

RIVENDARE, WARRIDER.name: Rivendare, Warrider
RIVENDARE, WARRIDER.flavorText: More like the 4 Horsemen of the "Can't Get Here On Time."

SWORD OF THE FALLEN.name: Sword of the Fallen
SWORD OF THE FALLEN.flavorText: Hoarding secrets is no fun, so play each and every one.

GADGETZAN SOCIALITE.name: Gadgetzan Socialite
GADGETZAN SOCIALITE.flavorText: Comment on her height, and she'll go from flapper to kneecapper in seconds flat.

IMMORTALIZED IN STONE.name: Immortalized in Stone
IMMORTALIZED IN STONE.flavorText: They all secretly have 'Deathrattle: Become very mortalized.'

DARIUS CROWLEY.name: Darius Crowley
DARIUS CROWLEY.flavorText: You either die a villain, or live long enough to see yourself become the hero.

BOOM SQUAD.name: Boom Squad
BOOM SQUAD.flavorText: Discover the meaning of squad goals.

DEVOTED MANIAC.name: Devoted Maniac
DEVOTED MANIAC.flavorText: There are plenty of apathetic maniacs, but they couldn't be bothered.

CORPORAL.name: Corporal
CORPORAL.flavorText: When he’s sitting in the graveyard ready to rez, he’s incorporal.

SHADOW BOLT.name: Shadow Bolt
SHADOW BOLT.flavorText: It’s a Bolt. It's made out of Shadow. What more do you need to know!

QUESTING EXPLORER.name: Questing Explorer
QUESTING EXPLORER.flavorText: Earned her merit badges the hard way—twelve zhevra hooves at a time.

WITCHWOOD GRIZZLY.name: Witchwood Grizzly
WITCHWOOD GRIZZLY.flavorText: You know what they say about people with big hands? Small bears.

LIBRAM OF JUDGMENT.name: Libram of Judgment
LIBRAM OF JUDGMENT.flavorText: You really can't judge a book by its cover.

GLAIVETAR.name: Glaivetar
GLAIVETAR.flavorText: Might need tuning, I think it's a bit sharp.

FIENDISH CIRCLE.name: Fiendish Circle
FIENDISH CIRCLE.flavorText: Like a knitting circle, but less evil.

ELISE THE TRAILBLAZER.name: Elise the Trailblazer
ELISE THE TRAILBLAZER.flavorText: Reno taught her that blazing her own trail is a lot more fun than following someone else's map.

BLOODFURY POTION.name: Bloodfury Potion
BLOODFURY POTION.flavorText: You know what really makes my blood boil? The skyrocketing price of Bloodfury potions!

RECORD SCRATCHER.name: Record Scratcher
RECORD SCRATCHER.flavorText: A Rogue's favorite audio sample is an orchestral stab.

MYRMIDON.name: Myrmidon
MYRMIDON.flavorText: He didn't have time to Myrmidon the other half of his armor before combat started.

MURLOC RAIDER.name: Murloc Raider
MURLOC RAIDER.flavorText: Mrrraggglhlhghghlgh, mrgaaag blarrghlgaahahl mrgggg glhalhah a bghhll graggmgmg Garrosh mglhlhlh mrghlhlhl!!

ROCKET BOOTS.name: Rocket Boots
ROCKET BOOTS.flavorText: This is the happiest moment of Grik's life. We'll miss him.

ANIMATED BERSERKER.name: Animated Berserker
ANIMATED BERSERKER.flavorText: He'd be a lot easier to animate if he would just stand still.

MARK OF Y'SHAARJ.name: Mark of Y'Shaarj
MARK OF Y'SHAARJ.flavorText: Y'Shaarj had three sons: Mark, Theodore, and Chris.

FLICKERING LIGHTBOT.name: Flickering Lightbot
FLICKERING LIGHTBOT.flavorText: These bots are sent out with nearly drained batteries, for dramatic effect.

INNER DEMON.name: Inner Demon
INNER DEMON.flavorText: Critical component of any tragic backstory.

AMPLIFIED ELEKK.name: Amplified Elekk
AMPLIFIED ELEKK.flavorText: Before this show can continue, we have to bass-boost the elephant in the room.

SKARR, THE CATASTROPHE.name: Skarr, the Catastrophe
SKARR, THE CATASTROPHE.flavorText: We're not in Karazhan anymore, Reno.

TOL'VIR WARDEN.name: Tol'vir Warden
TOL'VIR WARDEN.flavorText: Ferocious in combat… and even more terrifying in pet battles.

DEFILE.name: Defile
DEFILE.flavorText: This spell was originally designed to help warlocks clean up their hard drives.

DUEL!.name: Duel!
DUEL!.flavorText: If you don’t fight to the death, it’s Duel Yielding.

C'THUN'S CHOSEN.name: C'Thun's Chosen
C'THUN'S CHOSEN.flavorText: He gave her a promise ring and everything.

STOWAWAY.name: Stowaway
STOWAWAY.flavorText: Cut him a break. Even economy class tickets are pretty expensive these days.

JUNGLE GYM.name: Jungle Gym
JUNGLE GYM.flavorText: Yeah, I work out at the gym. The one with all the plushies and toys.

SELFISH SHELLFISH.name: Selfish Shellfish
SELFISH SHELLFISH.flavorText: Keeps any ancient book it finds all to its shelf.

PENANCE.name: Penance
PENANCE.flavorText: This is what happens when you don’t give a sincere apology.

CANDLE BREATH.name: Candle Breath
CANDLE BREATH.flavorText: "And Waxadred shall light their fires, with roaring breath hotter than pyres! Come before him, scamp and vandal, pledge your faith and lift your candle!"

RELENTLESS PURSUIT.name: Relentless Pursuit
RELENTLESS PURSUIT.flavorText: If you steal a Demon Hunter's corn dog, you'll get what's coming.

IXLID, FUNGAL LORD.name: Ixlid, Fungal Lord
IXLID, FUNGAL LORD.flavorText: We suggest crafting Ixlid; he'll grow on you. Literally.

DEEPWATER EVOKER.name: Deepwater Evoker
DEEPWATER EVOKER.flavorText: "Cap'n! We've hit an iceberg! ...No, it’s not my fault!"

EXARCH OTHAAR.name: Exarch Othaar
EXARCH OTHAAR.flavorText: The temptation of limitless knowledge led some Eredar to join the Burning Legion. In the Sha’tari Draenei, the study of everything lives on.

PRIMORDIAL GLYPH.name: Primordial Glyph
PRIMORDIAL GLYPH.flavorText: It's the Ancient Tol'vir symbol for "Whoops!"

CANNIBALIZE.name: Cannibalize
CANNIBALIZE.flavorText: The Silvermoon health inspector has some choice words for the Lich King.

SHADOWBLADE SLINGER.name: Shadowblade Slinger
SHADOWBLADE SLINGER.flavorText: Throwing knives isn’t easy for a warlock. It’s quite painful, in fact.

FROZEN MAMMOTH.name: Frozen Mammoth
FROZEN MAMMOTH.flavorText: *record scratch* "So, you may be wondering how I got here."

PATHMAKER.name: Pathmaker
PATHMAKER.flavorText: You can never choose the wrong path if you make your own.

PLOT OF SIN.name: Plot of Sin
PLOT OF SIN.flavorText: It's a great plot, but it's riddled with holes.

SHADOWLIGHT SCHOLAR.name: Shadowlight Scholar
SHADOWLIGHT SCHOLAR.flavorText: Imagine having the power of soul magic and using it as a reading light.

POMPOUS THESPIAN.name: Pompous Thespian
POMPOUS THESPIAN.flavorText: Alas poor Annoy-o-Tron! A fellow of infinite jest, of most excellent fancy!

JEEVES.name: Jeeves
JEEVES.flavorText: This robot is a lean, mean, butlerin' machine.

WISP.name: Wisp
WISP.flavorText: If you hit an Eredar Lord with enough Wisps, it will explode. But why?

SHIFTY SOPHOMORE.name: Shifty Sophomore
SHIFTY SOPHOMORE.flavorText: Experienced enough to do crimes, inexperienced enough to be super obvious about it.

MAD HATTER.name: Mad Hatter
MAD HATTER.flavorText: He's entirely bonkers. All the best goblins are.

CAMOUFLAGED DIRIGIBLE.name: Camouflaged Dirigible
CAMOUFLAGED DIRIGIBLE.flavorText: "What does that cloud look like to you?" "Trouble."

ARATHI WEAPONSMITH.name: Arathi Weaponsmith
ARATHI WEAPONSMITH.flavorText: 50% off fist weapons, limited time only!

DREADLORD'S BITE.name: Dreadlord's Bite
DREADLORD'S BITE.flavorText: When it gets too dull, it's more of a nibble.

FIRE SALE.name: Fire Sale
FIRE SALE.flavorText: Everything is 50% off now that our warehouse burned down.

ADORABLE INFESTATION.name: Adorable Infestation
ADORABLE INFESTATION.flavorText: Some cards are strong by sheer power; others draw strength from love.

HEDGE MAZE.name: Hedge Maze
HEDGE MAZE.flavorText: If you keep seeing a statue of the Sire, you’re not going in circles. There’s just so many of them.

IN FORMATION!.name: In Formation!
IN FORMATION!.flavorText: None can doubt the strength of the Scholomance student body.

SELECTIVE BREEDER.name: Selective Breeder
SELECTIVE BREEDER.flavorText: His ethics are top notch. Just look at that smiling kitty!

KABAL TRAFFICKER.name: Kabal Trafficker
KABAL TRAFFICKER.flavorText: She ships illicit mana crystals around the world in packages marked: FUNNEL CAKE.

SPIRIT BOMB.name: Spirit Bomb
SPIRIT BOMB.flavorText: Might take a few episodes to power up.

THE DARKNESS.name: The Darkness
THE DARKNESS.flavorText: I would rather light a single candle than curse the darkness. But I'm willing to do both.

PUDDLESTOMPER.name: Puddlestomper
PUDDLESTOMPER.flavorText: He pays homage to Morgl, the great murloc oracle! (Who doesn't??)

JOURNEY BELOW.name: Journey Below
JOURNEY BELOW.flavorText: Don't stop believing there's something below.

TICKET MASTER.name: Ticket Master
TICKET MASTER.flavorText: You can exchange one ticket for a bear or save up thousands for a tacky light-up paperweight!

GENZO, THE SHARK.name: Genzo, the Shark
GENZO, THE SHARK.flavorText: Infamous in the seedy underground card rooms of Gadgetzan, he got his nickname winning the coveted Shark Plushie in the city's first Hearthstone tournament.

SHATTERSKIN GARGOYLE.name: Shatterskin Gargoyle
SHATTERSKIN GARGOYLE.flavorText: Don't worry, this one's just a statue.

THE BOOMSHIP.name: The Boomship
THE BOOMSHIP.flavorText: Dr. Boom ends his motivational speeches by dropping the mechs.

DREAMBOAT.name: Dreamboat
DREAMBOAT.flavorText: As the only member that can sing underwater, Paz saved Poison Bloom's Zin-Azshari tour from failure.

CLOAKSCALE CHEMIST.name: Cloakscale Chemist
CLOAKSCALE CHEMIST.flavorText: Her suit was fitted using a scale model.

RAINBOW GLOWSCALE.name: Rainbow Glowscale
RAINBOW GLOWSCALE.flavorText: She prefers saying that she has Arcane, Fel, Fire, Frost, Holy, Nature, and Shadow Spell Damage +1.

FORTUNE TELLER.name: Fortune Teller
FORTUNE TELLER.flavorText: "I see a giant piano in your future."

INFERNAL STRATAGEM.name: Infernal Stratagem
INFERNAL STRATAGEM.flavorText: Archimonde INSISTS on calling it a stratagem instead of a strategy because it "sounds cooler."

EVIL GENIUS.name: EVIL Genius
EVIL GENIUS.flavorText: You do not want to be on the business end of this intellect!

SABOTAGE.name: Sabotage
SABOTAGE.flavorText: Rogues can't stand it. They know you planned it! They are going to set you straight!

AUTODEFENSE MATRIX.name: Autodefense Matrix
AUTODEFENSE MATRIX.flavorText: We call it the bubble machine.

TENDING TAUREN.name: Tending Tauren
TENDING TAUREN.flavorText: That racial bonus to Herbalism finally paid off.

DRONE DECONSTRUCTOR.name: Drone Deconstructor
DRONE DECONSTRUCTOR.flavorText: You have to deconstruct to reconstruct.

TWIN-FIN FIN TWIN.name: Twin-fin Fin Twin
TWIN-FIN FIN TWIN.flavorText: They call him Murloc Joe, winner of the Big M Memorial Surf Off Competition.

LIGHTBRINGER'S HAMMER.name: Lightbringer's Hammer
LIGHTBRINGER'S HAMMER.flavorText: This entire city must be purged. Or at least just the minions.

FIGHT PROMOTER.name: Fight Promoter
FIGHT PROMOTER.flavorText: "Yeah, I can get you Knuckles. No, no, he's been clean for *weeks*."

RECKLESS ROCKETEER.name: Reckless Rocketeer
RECKLESS ROCKETEER.flavorText: One Insane Rocketeer. One Rocket full of Explosives. Infinite Fun.

ENCHANTED CAULDRON.name: Enchanted Cauldron
ENCHANTED CAULDRON.flavorText: Do you smell what the cauldron is cooking? If so, we apologize.

VIOLET SPELLWING.name: Violet Spellwing
VIOLET SPELLWING.flavorText: A bird in the hand is worth three missiles in the grave.

AWAKEN!.name: Awaken!
AWAKEN!.flavorText: This is an alarm clock you can't ignore.

ARCHMAGE ARUGAL.name: Archmage Arugal
ARCHMAGE ARUGAL.flavorText: His worgen children call him Archmage AROO-OO-OO-OO-gal.

COPYCAT.name: Copycat
COPYCAT.flavorText: Whatever you do, DON’T let two of them meet.

SNEED'S OLD SHREDDER.name: Sneed's Old Shredder
SNEED'S OLD SHREDDER.flavorText: When Sneed was defeated in the Deadmines, his shredder was sold at auction to an anonymous buyer. (Probably Hogger.)

BURROWING SCORPID.name: Burrowing Scorpid
BURROWING SCORPID.flavorText: It's a game of hide and go sting.

DILIGENT NOTETAKER.name: Diligent Notetaker
DILIGENT NOTETAKER.flavorText: You never know what cards are going to be on the test.

DARKMIRE MOONKIN.name: Darkmire Moonkin
DARKMIRE MOONKIN.flavorText: Birds of a feather Moonfire together.

WATERCANNON.name: Watercannon
WATERCANNON.flavorText: There's a teeny tiny pirate trapped in each of the water balloons. Free them!

DRAIN SOUL.name: Drain Soul
DRAIN SOUL.flavorText: Cleans even the toughest clogs with just a flick of the wrist!

CYCLE OF HATRED.name: Cycle of Hatred
CYCLE OF HATRED.flavorText: If you run 2 of these, would that make it the bi-cycle of hatred?

RAGNAROS, LIGHTLORD.name: Ragnaros, Lightlord
RAGNAROS, LIGHTLORD.flavorText: What happens when you try and corrupt a corrupted firelord? DOUBLE NEGATIVE, INSECT!

FEIGN DEATH.name: Feign Death
FEIGN DEATH.flavorText: The hardest part about doing a "Feign Death" convincingly is learning how to make the right smell. It takes a lot of commitment.

WASTE WARDEN.name: Waste Warden
WASTE WARDEN.flavorText: Recycle that can, or you get the cuffs!

PARTNER IN CRIME.name: Partner in Crime
PARTNER IN CRIME.flavorText: "You know what we need? Some rope." "That's stupid. Name one thing you'd need a rope for."

BLACK HOLE.name: Black Hole
BLACK HOLE.flavorText: That's right! The square goes in the black hole.

HARMONIC DISCO.name: Harmonic Disco
HARMONIC DISCO.flavorText: "Worry not, festival patrons! A disco is hardly any means for panic!"

PURIFYING POWER.name: Purifying Power
PURIFYING POWER.flavorText: I sure do love making my minions better!

TREASURE HUNTER EUDORA.name: Treasure Hunter Eudora
TREASURE HUNTER EUDORA.flavorText: How hard could it be to hunt treasure? It doesn't even run away when you shoot it!

ARMORED GOON.name: Armored Goon
ARMORED GOON.flavorText: Armored except for non-critical areas, such as the head, torso, fists and thighs.

PARTY ANIMAL.name: Party Animal
PARTY ANIMAL.flavorText: He's the wildlife of the party!

FROZEN OVER.name: Frozen Over
FROZEN OVER.flavorText: We will find out who wins when we return in the spring.

GOREHOWL.name: Gorehowl
GOREHOWL.flavorText: Grommash Hellscream's famous axe. Somehow this ended up in Prince Malchezaar's possession. Quite the mystery!

INFILTRATOR LILIAN.name: Infiltrator Lilian
INFILTRATOR LILIAN.flavorText: She'll get to the bottom of this even if it kills her. Twice!

RATTLEGORE.name: Rattlegore
RATTLEGORE.flavorText: He looks bad now, but he was pretty handsome in his 20/20s.

BIG-TIME RACKETEER.name: Big-Time Racketeer
BIG-TIME RACKETEER.flavorText: "It'd be a shame if someone disenchanted those Legendaries."

PIT LORD.name: Pit Lord
PIT LORD.flavorText: Mannoroth, Magtheridon, and Brutallus may be dead, but it turns out there are a LOT of pit lords.

LINEDANCE PARTNER.name: Linedance Partner
LINEDANCE PARTNER.flavorText: Where did you come from? (Linedance Partner's Battlecry) Where did you go? (Face)

GOODY TWO-SHIELDS.name: Goody Two-Shields
GOODY TWO-SHIELDS.flavorText: These are my shields. There are at least two like them, and both are mine.

DISEASED VULTURE.name: Diseased Vulture
DISEASED VULTURE.flavorText: He's off the twig! He's kicked the bucket! THIS IS AN EX-VULTURE!

SHIFTING SHADE.name: Shifting Shade
SHIFTING SHADE.flavorText: Yeah, it's cooler in the shade, but you're also more likely to get JACKED.

MASTER SWORDSMITH.name: Master Swordsmith
MASTER SWORDSMITH.flavorText: He's currently trying to craft a "flail-axe", but all the other swordsmiths say it can't be done.

FAN THE HAMMER.name: Fan the Hammer
FAN THE HAMMER.flavorText: I thought Kurtrus was more of a fan of glaives.

WOLFRIDER.name: Wolfrider
WOLFRIDER.flavorText: Orcish raiders ride wolves because they are well adapted to harsh environments, and because they are soft and cuddly.

PARTY CRASHER.name: Party Crasher
PARTY CRASHER.flavorText: "Do you ever wonder why you don't get invited anywhere?" "… no, not really."

WRAPPED GOLEM.name: Wrapped Golem
WRAPPED GOLEM.flavorText: The end result of one of the greatest wrap battles of all time.

TAMSIN'S PHYLACTERY.name: Tamsin's Phylactery
TAMSIN'S PHYLACTERY.flavorText: Eau de Morte. Guaranteed to take your date’s breath away

IMPLOYEE OF THE MONTH.name: Imployee of the Month
IMPLOYEE OF THE MONTH.flavorText: Imployee of the Month, 666 months running.

RIGHTEOUS CAUSE.name: Righteous Cause
RIGHTEOUS CAUSE.flavorText: "And I hereby dub thee a cadet of the Explorer’s League! NEXT!"

TROLL BATRIDER.name: Troll Batrider
TROLL BATRIDER.flavorText: "Quiet! The bat can't hear where he's goin'!"

ALDOR ATTENDANT.name: Aldor Attendant
ALDOR ATTENDANT.flavorText: Will check to make sure you have a valid libramary card.

DREADPRISON GLAIVE.name: Dreadprison Glaive
DREADPRISON GLAIVE.flavorText: Keep your allies close. Keep your evil demons in your weapon.

DARNASSUS ASPIRANT.name: Darnassus Aspirant
DARNASSUS ASPIRANT.flavorText: She loves mana crystals, she hates mana crystals. So fickle!
