MAD SCIENTIST.name: Mad Scientist
MAD SCIENTIST.flavorText: His mother wanted him to be a mage or a warlock, but noooooooo, he had to go and be a scientist like his father.

CHROMAGGUS.name: Chromaggus
CHROMAGGUS.flavorText: Left head and right head can never agree about what to eat for dinner, so they always end up just eating ramen again.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/52/BRM_031_Chromaggus_EnterPlay_1.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ BRM_031_Chromaggus_EnterPlay_1.wav <summon sound>

SUNWELL INITIATE.name: Sunwell Initiate
SUNWELL INITIATE.flavorText: Initiates don’t study pronunciation until level 20.

SEAFORIUM BOMBER.name: Seaforium Bomber
SEAFORIUM BOMBER.flavorText: Dress for the bomb you want, not the bomb you have.

FIELD CONTACT.name: Field Contact
FIELD CONTACT.flavorText: That's not a knife... THIS is a knife!

SHADOW SCULPTOR.name: Shadow Sculptor
SHADOW SCULPTOR.flavorText: Carving out new territory in the realm of shadow puppetry.

CHARGED HAMMER.name: Charged Hammer
CHARGED HAMMER.flavorText: You can only pick it up if you are worthy.

EXCAVATION SPECIALIST.name: Excavation Specialist
EXCAVATION SPECIALIST.flavorText: With the jungles of Un’goro mapped out and the ruins of Uldum fully uncovered, explorers have to go a little out of their depth in their search of the great unknown.

BOOMBOSS THO'GRUN.name: Boomboss Tho'grun
BOOMBOSS THO'GRUN.flavorText: Ever since the Bloodrock Company hired this guy, business has been booming!

CHILL VIBES.name: Chill Vibes
CHILL VIBES.flavorText: "You're listening to 47.7 Shaman FM radio. It's time to kick back, relax, and take in the music."

FLINT FIREARM.name: Flint Firearm
FLINT FIREARM.flavorText: You'll never guess why they call him that.

SEAL OF LIGHT.name: Seal of Light
SEAL OF LIGHT.flavorText: The walrus of Light restores EIGHT Health.

Y'SHAARJ, RAGE UNBOUND.name: Y'Shaarj, Rage Unbound
Y'SHAARJ, RAGE UNBOUND.flavorText: When he's working out, he binds all that rage back into a ponytail.

COBALT GUARDIAN.name: Cobalt Guardian
COBALT GUARDIAN.flavorText: Guardians used to be built out of Adamantium, but production got moved to Gadgetzan and Cobalt was cheap.

CURSE OF WEAKNESS.name: Curse of Weakness
CURSE OF WEAKNESS.flavorText: Warlocks refer to this as a "balance change."

DARKSPEAR BERSERKER.name: Darkspear Berserker
DARKSPEAR BERSERKER.flavorText: "If I die, I'm taking my hero down with me."

CLUMSY STEWARD.name: Clumsy Steward
CLUMSY STEWARD.flavorText: "Aww, bummer! I spilled coffee all over your cards! Dang it! What a shame!"

GLAIVEZOOKA.name: Glaivezooka
GLAIVEZOOKA.flavorText: For the times when a regular bazooka just isn't enough.

MUROZOND THE INFINITE.name: Murozond the Infinite
MUROZOND THE INFINITE.flavorText: "Well, I'm glad YOU knew what I should be doing this turn."

HAND OF GUL'DAN.name: Hand of Gul'dan
HAND OF GUL'DAN.flavorText: His skull also draws three cards. Imagine how many cards he could draw with HIS ENTIRE BODY!

THE DEMON SEED.name: The Demon Seed
THE DEMON SEED.flavorText: Just need some elbow grease to get this working. Oh, and your soul.

DARK INQUISITOR XANESH.name: Dark Inquisitor Xanesh
DARK INQUISITOR XANESH.flavorText: Fear is the mind-killer, and also the name of my wurm.

SIGHTLESS WATCHER.name: Sightless Watcher
SIGHTLESS WATCHER.flavorText: What he lacks in sight, he makes up for in sleight-of-tentacle tricks.

SECURITY!!.name: SECURITY!!
SECURITY!!.flavorText: Check all of the boxes that contain VENGEANCE to play this card.

BLADESTORM.name: Bladestorm
BLADESTORM.flavorText: Dear minions: Woosh, woosh, woosh, woosh, woosh. Best regards, Bladestorm

BOOM WRENCH.name: Boom Wrench
BOOM WRENCH.flavorText: Boom, the Inventor; Can he fix it? Boom, the Inventor; No he can't!

JANDICE BAROV.name: Jandice Barov
JANDICE BAROV.flavorText: Her parents own Scholomance. Of course she's going to play tricks on the students!

LOST SPIRIT.name: Lost Spirit
LOST SPIRIT.flavorText: She simply refuses to ask for directions.

VIOLET SPELLSWORD.name: Violet Spellsword
VIOLET SPELLSWORD.flavorText: If you have to wield a spell and a sword, then neither is performing to expectation.

EVIL QUARTERMASTER.name: EVIL Quartermaster
EVIL QUARTERMASTER.flavorText: He trained for a whole year to become quarter-master. Three more, and he'll be a full-master.

TRAVELMASTER DUNGAR.name: Travelmaster Dungar
TRAVELMASTER DUNGAR.flavorText: Our travel options will take you to Paradise and beyond!

FISHY FLYER.name: Fishy Flyer
FISHY FLYER.flavorText: Like a fish out of water.

DRAGON GOLEM.name: Dragon Golem
DRAGON GOLEM.flavorText: I have a Dragon, I have a Golem. UH! Dragon Golem!

NAVAL MINE.name: Naval Mine
NAVAL MINE.flavorText: A Naval Mine? I'd rather it be Naval Yours.

GIANT MASTODON.name: Giant Mastodon
GIANT MASTODON.flavorText: Still salty about it not being the "Year of the Mastodon."

FLANKING STRIKE.name: Flanking Strike
FLANKING STRIKE.flavorText: Wolves to the left and arrows to the right, here I am stuck in the middle with you.

SECURITY AUTOMATON.name: Security Automaton
SECURITY AUTOMATON.flavorText: Honestly, I feel less secure when it's around.

DJINNI OF ZEPHYRS.name: Djinni of Zephyrs
DJINNI OF ZEPHYRS.flavorText: If you want your wish granted, don't rub him the wrong way.

MOUNTAIN BEAR.name: Mountain Bear
MOUNTAIN BEAR.flavorText: If they want your picnic basket, I recommend giving it to them.

TIMELINE ACCELERATOR.name: Timeline Accelerator
TIMELINE ACCELERATOR.flavorText: The future is NOW! No wait, NOW!

SPIRIT OF THE BADLANDS.name: Spirit of the Badlands
SPIRIT OF THE BADLANDS.flavorText: That's the spirit! Of the Badlands.

JOLLY ROGER.name: Jolly Roger
JOLLY ROGER.flavorText: That's a great pose, Roger. But this time try happier, and with your mouth open.

VARDEN DAWNGRASP.name: Varden Dawngrasp
VARDEN DAWNGRASP.flavorText: Varden Dawngrasp could wield fire, summon hailstorms, and morph a night elf into a sheep with a snap of their fingers. Knowing how malleable reality could be, certain labels felt downright trivial.

RESKA, THE PIT BOSS.name: Reska, the Pit Boss
RESKA, THE PIT BOSS.flavorText: Overseer of the Bloodrock Mine, Reska will work you to the bone. They'll then reanimate your bones and work THOSE bones to the bone.

VARIAN, KING OF STORMWIND.name: Varian, King of Stormwind
VARIAN, KING OF STORMWIND.flavorText: Man, this guy is so cool. Sure hope nothing happens to him.

POWER INFUSION.name: Power Infusion
POWER INFUSION.flavorText: It infuses, it enthuses, it amuses!

EMBERSCALE DRAKE.name: Emberscale Drake
EMBERSCALE DRAKE.flavorText: The third little dragon made his armor out of adamantite.

SLIMESCALE DIVER.name: Slimescale Diver
SLIMESCALE DIVER.flavorText: You try putting on a wetsuit with scales.

VOID VIRTUOSO.name: Void Virtuoso
VOID VIRTUOSO.flavorText: That is one interesting dress code.

GERMINATION.name: Germination
GERMINATION.flavorText: I regret asking how sporelings are made.

SOULEATER'S SCYTHE.name: Souleater's Scythe
SOULEATER'S SCYTHE.flavorText: Would you like those souls for here or to-go?

BLAST WAVE.name: Blast Wave
BLAST WAVE.flavorText: If you’re burning and you know it, wave your hands!

TRACKING.name: Tracking
TRACKING.flavorText: For the person who just cannot decide what card to put into a deck!

SNUGGLE TEDDY.name: Snuggle Teddy
SNUGGLE TEDDY.flavorText: Someone really put their heart into making this.

SUNSET VOLLEY.name: Sunset Volley
SUNSET VOLLEY.flavorText: When the light is just right during Golden Hour, that is when you take out the selfie stick and start casting.

MECHANICAL YETI.name: Mechanical Yeti
MECHANICAL YETI.flavorText: The yetis of Chillwind Point are a source of both inspiration and savage beatings.

ERODED SEDIMENT.name: Eroded Sediment
ERODED SEDIMENT.flavorText: A perfect minion for those feeling sedimental about their past.

HIGH PRIEST AMET.name: High Priest Amet
HIGH PRIEST AMET.flavorText: All minions are equal, but some minions are more equal than others.

PROMOTION.name: Promotion
PROMOTION.flavorText: And with the new title of 'Golden Hand Recruit', you also get a pay raise!

SCARLET SUBJUGATOR.name: Scarlet Subjugator
SCARLET SUBJUGATOR.flavorText: At the Scarlet Monastery, he learned the sacred art of kicking people when they're up.

GROUNDSKEEPER.name: Groundskeeper
GROUNDSKEEPER.flavorText: It’s tricky for dryads to tend the garden without trampling the flowers.

BATTLEWORN FACELESS.name: Battleworn Faceless
BATTLEWORN FACELESS.flavorText: "I shall hug him and squeeze him and call him Earthen George."

VENOMIZER.name: Venomizer
VENOMIZER.flavorText: Keeps getting banned for toxic behavior.

SHADOW ESSENCE.name: Shadow Essence
SHADOW ESSENCE.flavorText: Difficult to bottle up and sell. But it packs a punch.

ICEBLOOD TOWER.name: Iceblood Tower
ICEBLOOD TOWER.flavorText: “Why is it called Iceblood Tower?” “Not really sure. Anyways, try not to lose your footing on any of the frozen bodies as you make your way in.”

SAFETY INSPECTOR.name: Safety Inspector
SAFETY INSPECTOR.flavorText: "All right, you're good. No sign of safety anywhere."

OGRE-GANG RIDER.name: Ogre-Gang Rider
OGRE-GANG RIDER.flavorText: Doesn't know his ride from his left.

SPECTRAL KNIGHT.name: Spectral Knight
SPECTRAL KNIGHT.flavorText: What do Faerie Dragons and Spectral Knights have in common? They both love pasta!

LEATHERCLAD HOGLEADER.name: Leatherclad Hogleader
LEATHERCLAD HOGLEADER.flavorText: The Hogchoppers, the terrors of Tanaris, can always be found at one tavern or another in Gadgetzan, refueling for totally real and legit adventures that they go on.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/35/VO_CFM_810_Female_Quilboar_Attack_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_CFM_810_Female_Quilboar_Attack_02.wav <death sound>

THERAZANE.name: Therazane
THERAZANE.flavorText: You thought we forgot about her, didn't you? *nervous laughter*

TOOTHY CHEST.name: Toothy Chest
TOOTHY CHEST.flavorText: Do you want to eat an adventurer? I want to eat an adventurer!

DISCIPLE OF EONAR.name: Disciple of Eonar
DISCIPLE OF EONAR.flavorText: If you do not receive his rose, you will have to pack your bags and leave Ulduar immediately.

CALL TO THE STAND.name: Call to the Stand
CALL TO THE STAND.flavorText: Don't worry, there is a chair for you to sit in. It's very misleading.

ARCANE KEYSMITH.name: Arcane Keysmith
ARCANE KEYSMITH.flavorText: She sells all manner of keys: from A flat to G sharp.

SKETCH ARTIST.name: Sketch Artist
SKETCH ARTIST.flavorText: Never ask an artist how many pieces they've finished.

MESSENGER RAVEN.name: Messenger Raven
MESSENGER RAVEN.flavorText: You can make a collect CAW!

UNSLEEPING SOUL.name: Unsleeping Soul
UNSLEEPING SOUL.flavorText: It's 3 am. Do you know where your soul is?

IMPRISONED ANTAEN.name: Imprisoned Antaen
IMPRISONED ANTAEN.flavorText: Can I get a pair of size XXXXXL manacles?

LUNAR VISIONS.name: Lunar Visions
LUNAR VISIONS.flavorText: The true mystery of lunar visions is how there is nothing to watch when there are so many channels.

KODOHIDE DRUMKIT.name: Kodohide Drumkit
KODOHIDE DRUMKIT.flavorText: Stolen from a druidic drum circle, now destined to make music that is actually good.

IL'GYNOTH.name: Il'gynoth
IL'GYNOTH.flavorText: Well, that just sounds like damage with extra steps.

SORCERER'S GAMBIT.name: Sorcerer's Gambit
SORCERER'S GAMBIT.flavorText: After "the incident," the Stockades really had to reevaluate their anti-mage protocols.

HOOKED SCIMITAR.name: Hooked Scimitar
HOOKED SCIMITAR.flavorText: Oooooooooooow. I'm hooked on a scimitar!

GONE FISHIN'.name: Gone Fishin'
GONE FISHIN'.flavorText: Rogues want me Fish fear me

SHIELD OF ASKARA.name: Shield of Askara
SHIELD OF ASKARA.flavorText: One can never have too many shields.

RETURN POLICY.name: Return Policy
RETURN POLICY.flavorText: Sorry, the Workshop has a strict 'no-takesies-backsies' policy.

MIRE KEEPER.name: Mire Keeper
MIRE KEEPER.flavorText: "Hey.... Is that Mire for sale?" "No. I'm keeping it."

AZSHARAN SABER.name: Azsharan Saber
AZSHARAN SABER.flavorText: Even in ancient times, the Night Elves were committed cat people.

ORIGAMI CRANE.name: Origami Crane
ORIGAMI CRANE.flavorText: I was born with 1-Health and paper skin.

CRIMINAL LINEUP.name: Criminal Lineup
CRIMINAL LINEUP.flavorText: Number 1, could you please sing the opening to "I Want It That Way"?

HELYA.name: Helya
HELYA.flavorText: Named after the first thing Odyn said after landing a sick kickflip.

ROTFACE.name: Rotface
ROTFACE.flavorText: Daddy! I think I made a Legendary!

SN1P-SN4P.name: SN1P-SN4P
SN1P-SN4P.flavorText: "It's gonna be snip this, snap that. Bada-snip, bada-snap!"

TYRANTUS.name: Tyrantus
TYRANTUS.flavorText: Millennia of evolutionary pressures turned his species into the Faerie Dragons we know today.

HULKING OVERFIEND.name: Hulking Overfiend
HULKING OVERFIEND.flavorText: To hulk, perhaps, to fiend: ay, there's the rub.

KNIFE VENDOR.name: Knife Vendor
KNIFE VENDOR.flavorText: "They're perfectly safe! These gloves totally aren't hiding any bandages."

ASVEDON, THE GRANDSHIELD.name: Asvedon, the Grandshield
ASVEDON, THE GRANDSHIELD.flavorText: If you think that's strong, you should see his Great Great Grandshield.

BLAZECALLER.name: Blazecaller
BLAZECALLER.flavorText: For when a flamecaller just won't do.

SNAKE OIL SELLER.name: Snake Oil Seller
SNAKE OIL SELLER.flavorText: This oil is absolutely essential to your gameplan.

WAILING VAPOR.name: Wailing Vapor
WAILING VAPOR.flavorText: If you have The Vapors, your Humors might be imbalanced.

DOWN WITH THE SHIP.name: Down with the Ship
DOWN WITH THE SHIP.flavorText: It has been a privilege playing with you tonight.

GIFTS OF AZSHARA.name: Gifts of Azshara
GIFTS OF AZSHARA.flavorText: Barber: What do you want? Naga: You ever have a thirst for arcane power? Barber: Say no more.

UNENDING SWARM.name: Unending Swarm
UNENDING SWARM.flavorText: swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm -

PERSISTENT PEDDLER.name: Persistent Peddler
PERSISTENT PEDDLER.flavorText: Loves pyramid schemes and bike rides.

GANG UP.name: Gang Up
GANG UP.flavorText: If you are thinking about visiting Moonbrook, you better roll deep.

CAVALRY HORN.name: Cavalry Horn
CAVALRY HORN.flavorText: The clarion call of the Alliance skipping every objective and going straight to Drek’Thar.

SAYGE, SEER OF DARKMOON.name: Sayge, Seer of Darkmoon
SAYGE, SEER OF DARKMOON.flavorText: There are no secrets between us... or refunds.

TROGGZOR THE EARTHINATOR.name: Troggzor the Earthinator
TROGGZOR THE EARTHINATOR.flavorText: He keeps earthinating the countryside despite attempts to stop him.

DEVILSAUR EGG.name: Devilsaur Egg
DEVILSAUR EGG.flavorText: A key ingredient in all discerning Funnel Cake recipes.

CRABRIDER.name: Crabrider
CRABRIDER.flavorText: "Now I'm falling asleep and she's calling a crab…"

HANDLE WITH BEAR.name: Handle with Bear
HANDLE WITH BEAR.flavorText: We guarantee your luggage will arrive at the speed of bear.

BANDERSMOSH.name: Bandersmosh
BANDERSMOSH.flavorText: The Shudderwock finds him particularly frumious.

ARBOR UP.name: Arbor Up
ARBOR UP.flavorText: If you can’t outrun a tree, you really shouldn’t be here anyway.

CLOUD PRINCE.name: Cloud Prince
CLOUD PRINCE.flavorText: "In West Cloudidelphia, born and raised; flinging lightning for the rest of my days."

FOSSILIZED DEVILSAUR.name: Fossilized Devilsaur
FOSSILIZED DEVILSAUR.flavorText: This was the only job he could get after the dinosaur theme park debacle.

LEYLINE MANIPULATOR.name: Leyline Manipulator
LEYLINE MANIPULATOR.flavorText: The shortest distance between two points is a leyline.

STICK UP.name: Stick Up
STICK UP.flavorText: Dude, Velarok, give me a minute to play my turn, the rope's burning!

AUSPICIOUS SPIRITS.name: Auspicious Spirits
AUSPICIOUS SPIRITS.flavorText: "I'm not AWE-spicious, but I am a little spicious."

ASTALOR BLOODSWORN.name: Astalor Bloodsworn
ASTALOR BLOODSWORN.flavorText: I hear his third phase is even more intense.

FIREWORKER.name: Fireworker
FIREWORKER.flavorText: The one job where a spark of creativity is unwanted.

TIMELESS BLESSING.name: Timeless Blessing
TIMELESS BLESSING.flavorText: To defeat the combined power of Murozond and C'Thun, Nozdormu would need heroes of Azeroth's past, present, and future.

DEVOUT DUNGEONEER.name: Devout Dungeoneer
DEVOUT DUNGEONEER.flavorText: "Please do smaller pulls, this is my first time healing."

PACKAGE RUNNER.name: Package Runner
PACKAGE RUNNER.flavorText: He could go... all... the... way!

HARTH STONEBREW.name: Harth Stonebrew
HARTH STONEBREW.flavorText: "Grab a slice by the hearth and enjoy the festivities. This celebration is for all of us!" -Harth

CHEATY SNOBOLD.name: Cheaty Snobold
CHEATY SNOBOLD.flavorText: This one will knock you out cold.

WEBWEAVE.name: Webweave
WEBWEAVE.flavorText: O, what a tangled web we weave, hoping spiders dodge the cleave.

MECHA-LEAPER.name: Mecha-Leaper
MECHA-LEAPER.flavorText: Now to find my Mecha-Macaw and my Mecha-Titus and we'll be Mecha-Set.

WILDHEART GUFF.name: Wildheart Guff
WILDHEART GUFF.flavorText: Guff faced his biggest challenge yet: making friends on a battlefield.

RAIN OF TOADS.name: Rain of Toads
RAIN OF TOADS.flavorText: "Oh, THAT'S how she brings the warts!"

BRRRLOC.name: Brrrloc
BRRRLOC.flavorText: He may be frozen fish, but he fights fresh!

DRAKONID CRUSHER.name: Drakonid Crusher
DRAKONID CRUSHER.flavorText: Drakonids were created to have all the bad parts of a dragon in the form of a humanoid. But, like, why?

CRYSTAL BROKER.name: Crystal Broker
CRYSTAL BROKER.flavorText: Broke: Crystals Woke: Blueberry Fruit Gummies

RANGER GILLY.name: Ranger Gilly
RANGER GILLY.flavorText: Get you someone who looks at you the way Ranger Gilly looks at that Crocolisk.

FLAME WARD.name: Flame Ward
FLAME WARD.flavorText: Not to be confused with the burn ward.

FELSCALE EVOKER.name: Felscale Evoker
FELSCALE EVOKER.flavorText: So it’s a demon and a naga, but NOT a dragon?

BARRENS SCAVENGER.name: Barrens Scavenger
BARRENS SCAVENGER.flavorText: When the hundredth centaur dropped, so did her bracers.

LAZUL'S SCHEME.name: Lazul's Scheme
LAZUL'S SCHEME.flavorText: "What's that you're dreaming? You're weak and you're screaming! It must be my scheming..."

YSERA THE DREAMER.name: Ysera the Dreamer
YSERA THE DREAMER.flavorText: Quick! Quick! Write it down before you forget them all!

GRANITE FORGEBORN.name: Granite Forgeborn
GRANITE FORGEBORN.flavorText: If he stops being useful, just turn him into a kitchen countertop.

THE FOREST'S AID.name: The Forest's Aid
THE FOREST'S AID.flavorText: Delicious Forest’s Aid! Made from real forests.

ASHTONGUE BATTLELORD.name: Ashtongue Battlelord
ASHTONGUE BATTLELORD.flavorText: Demons have destroyed the lives of the Ashtongue draenei. Now he’s got a shoulder-axe to grind.

ELITE TAUREN CHAMPION.name: Elite Tauren Champion
ELITE TAUREN CHAMPION.flavorText: Strumming his guitar with a molten ember from the first fire of Azeroth, E.T.C.'s ear-splitting, heart-wrenching, head-banging solo held back Magatha and her forces of evil, single-handedly saving music for centuries to come.

BLIGHTNOZZLE CRAWLER.name: Blightnozzle Crawler
BLIGHTNOZZLE CRAWLER.flavorText: "Well we HAD it contained. Then you went and gave it legs!"

CONJURE MANA BISCUIT.name: Conjure Mana Biscuit
CONJURE MANA BISCUIT.flavorText: So THIS is why she was AFK.

CLOAK OF SHADOWS.name: Cloak of Shadows
CLOAK OF SHADOWS.flavorText: Only worthy emperors can see the cloak.

EAGER UNDERLING.name: Eager Underling
EAGER UNDERLING.flavorText: Eager to please, even if it kills him.

TOXFIN.name: Toxfin
TOXFIN.flavorText: I'm addicted to him, but I know that he's Toxfin.

SOUP VENDOR.name: Soup Vendor
SOUP VENDOR.flavorText: Fresh from the floor of the arena!

EVOLVING SPORES.name: Evolving Spores
EVOLVING SPORES.flavorText: The most powerful mushrooms are commonly found in boxes marked with "?".

EMBRACE THE SHADOW.name: Embrace the Shadow
EMBRACE THE SHADOW.flavorText: For when your Auchenai Soulpriests call in sick.

BEACHED WHALE.name: Beached Whale
BEACHED WHALE.flavorText: Call me Illidan. Some years ago — never mind how long precisely — having little or no gold in my purse, and nothing particular to interest me on Azeroth, I thought I would fly about a little and see the demony part of the world…

TINYFIN'S CARAVAN.name: Tinyfin's Caravan
TINYFIN'S CARAVAN.flavorText: Movin' right along, mrgl mrg mrgl mrg.

TRANSLOCATION INSTRUCTOR.name: Translocation Instructor
TRANSLOCATION INSTRUCTOR.flavorText: *Translocates behind you* psssh... nothin personnel, kid.

CHENVAALA.name: Chenvaala
CHENVAALA.flavorText: Like the Dragon Soul. If dragons had souls of ice.

AMPHIBIOUS ELIXIR.name: Amphibious Elixir
AMPHIBIOUS ELIXIR.flavorText: Made by frogs, for frogs, from frogs.

DRAKKARI ENCHANTER.name: Drakkari Enchanter
DRAKKARI ENCHANTER.flavorText: Drakkari sorceresses have the irritating habit of repeating themselves at the end of every sentence. Every sentence.

OBSIDIAN REVENANT.name: Obsidian Revenant
OBSIDIAN REVENANT.flavorText: What is this? A Reven for Ants?!

WILDPAW CAVERN.name: Wildpaw Cavern
WILDPAW CAVERN.flavorText: Adventurers were quite confused when they saw how many boots were frozen to the ceiling.

CORPSE RAISER.name: Corpse Raiser
CORPSE RAISER.flavorText: He was just minding his business, farming corpses, when you meddling adventurers came along.

ANYFIN CAN HAPPEN.name: Anyfin Can Happen
ANYFIN CAN HAPPEN.flavorText: Theme song by Ellie Goldfin and Blagghghlrlrl Harris.

DRAGON'S PACK.name: Dragon's Pack
DRAGON'S PACK.flavorText: Each dragon's pack is guaranteed to have at least one rare.

SHADOW WORD: STEAL.name: Shadow Word: Steal
SHADOW WORD: STEAL.flavorText: Anduin will literally take your stuff and say it's a Shadow Word.

UNSTABLE GHOUL.name: Unstable Ghoul
UNSTABLE GHOUL.flavorText: Filling your Ghouls with Rocket Fuel is all the rage at Necromancer school.

HAUNTING NIGHTMARE.name: Haunting Nightmare
HAUNTING NIGHTMARE.flavorText: Not as scary as the one where all my teeth fall out.

JADE DISPLAY.name: Jade Display
JADE DISPLAY.flavorText: The Jade Lotus just releases the same product every year but with an upgraded camera.

WAVE POOL THRASHER.name: Wave Pool Thrasher
WAVE POOL THRASHER.flavorText: Used to be called Wave Pool Splasher until 'The Incident'.

TRAM MECHANIC.name: Tram Mechanic
TRAM MECHANIC.flavorText: He looks at life through sludge-tinted glasses.

SECRET PLAN.name: Secret Plan
SECRET PLAN.flavorText: The secret is... There is no plan!

TWISTED FROSTWING.name: Twisted Frostwing
TWISTED FROSTWING.flavorText: Not currently valid in the Twist format.

TYR'S TEARS.name: Tyr's Tears
TYR'S TEARS.flavorText: Liek this if u cri evertim

GENN GREYMANE.name: Genn Greymane
GENN GREYMANE.flavorText: Ever since Sylvanas killed his son, he's dreamed of getting… even.

DEATH STRIKE.name: Death Strike
DEATH STRIKE.flavorText: A little embarrassing when used on large minions.

OASIS THRASHER.name: Oasis Thrasher
OASIS THRASHER.flavorText: Didn't get tickets for E.T.C.'s show.

ENTRAPPED SORCERESS.name: Entrapped Sorceress
ENTRAPPED SORCERESS.flavorText: "If you're a city guard, you have to tell me. Otherwise, it's entrapment."

SAIDAN THE SCARLET.name: Saidan the Scarlet
SAIDAN THE SCARLET.flavorText: An orc mage accidentally kited him all the way from Stratholme.

KNIGHT OF THE DEAD.name: Knight of the Dead
KNIGHT OF THE DEAD.flavorText: A Paladin will follow their oath to slay the undead, even when they count themselves among them.

RHYTHMDANCER RISA.name: Rhythmdancer Risa
RHYTHMDANCER RISA.flavorText: Shadowstep to the left! Double jump to the right! Class cross!

JEWELED SCARAB.name: Jeweled Scarab
JEWELED SCARAB.flavorText: It's amazing what you can do with super glue!

ALLEY ARMORSMITH.name: Alley Armorsmith
ALLEY ARMORSMITH.flavorText: The rent is cheap and she passes the savings onto YOU!

JUICY PSYCHMELON.name: Juicy Psychmelon
JUICY PSYCHMELON.flavorText: It's not juicy at all. IT'S JUST MESSING WITH YOUR HEAD.

ETERNAL SENTINEL.name: Eternal Sentinel
ETERNAL SENTINEL.flavorText: Just try to avoid eye contact.

BRITTLEBONE BUCCANEER.name: Brittlebone Buccaneer
BRITTLEBONE BUCCANEER.flavorText: How much does a pirate pay for corn? A buck an ear arr arr arrr arrr!

KRONX DRAGONHOOF.name: Kronx Dragonhoof
KRONX DRAGONHOOF.flavorText: The only one who knows how to properly prepare Galakrond's coffee.

PRIMORDIAL WAVE.name: Primordial Wave
PRIMORDIAL WAVE.flavorText: A primordial hello to you too!

TWIN EMPEROR VEK'LOR.name: Twin Emperor Vek'lor
TWIN EMPEROR VEK'LOR.flavorText: Do they make decisions based on age? "I'm two minutes older therefore we burn this village."

RAT SENSEI.name: Rat Sensei
RAT SENSEI.flavorText: The old teacher needed to find some tokens with attitude.

NORTHWATCH COMMANDER.name: Northwatch Commander
NORTHWATCH COMMANDER.flavorText: It was all going well until some Horde had the cunning idea of attacking from the south.

CONVICTION (RANK 1).name: Conviction (Rank 1)
CONVICTION (RANK 1).flavorText: It was the strength of Cariel's faith that emboldened the defenders of Northwatch that day. Although the strength of her giant hammer didn’t exactly hurt either.

SON OF HODIR.name: Son of Hodir
SON OF HODIR.flavorText: You look dehydrated, drink some water! Come on, chug! Chug! Chug! Chug!

DRILLY THE KID.name: Drilly the Kid
DRILLY THE KID.flavorText: "I HATE that nickname. Call me Drilliam!"

FACELESS CORRUPTOR.name: Faceless Corruptor
FACELESS CORRUPTOR.flavorText: What does Madame Lazul have against faces?!

RUSTSWORN INITIATE.name: Rustsworn Initiate
RUSTSWORN INITIATE.flavorText: The Rusted Legion's training leaves a little to be desired. He hasn't even had a tetanus shot yet!

COLDARRA DRAKE.name: Coldarra Drake
COLDARRA DRAKE.flavorText: The Grand Tournament has a "No dragons allowed" policy, but it's rarely enforced.

AWAKENING TREMORS.name: Awakening Tremors
AWAKENING TREMORS.flavorText: A rude followup to the Sleepy Tremors.

PRIMALFIN CHAMPION.name: Primalfin Champion
PRIMALFIN CHAMPION.flavorText: Sure, he'll return your stuff. OVER HIS DEAD BODY!

OGRE-GANG OUTLAW.name: Ogre-Gang Outlaw
OGRE-GANG OUTLAW.flavorText: Why don't they just buy another hat?

EADRIC THE PURE.name: Eadric the Pure
EADRIC THE PURE.flavorText: Nobody rocks a monocle like Eadric.

HUNTSMAN ALTIMOR.name: Huntsman Altimor
HUNTSMAN ALTIMOR.flavorText: He loves all his Gargons equally. (Hecutis is his favorite and it's not close.)

SEAFLOOR SAVIOR.name: Seafloor Savior
SEAFLOOR SAVIOR.flavorText: "TURTLE PROCURED. ADMINISTRATING BANDAGES AND KISSES. BOO BOO MUST BE ELIMINATED."

SAND DRUDGE.name: Sand Drudge
SAND DRUDGE.flavorText: Loves long walks on the beach, raising the dead, and chocolates.

BILEFIN TIDEHUNTER.name: Bilefin Tidehunter
BILEFIN TIDEHUNTER.flavorText: Bile actually makes for surprisingly sturdy fins.

BUILDING-BLOCK GOLEM.name: Building-Block Golem
BUILDING-BLOCK GOLEM.flavorText: I HOPE YOU STEP ON A 1-COST MINION!

GRAVE RUNE.name: Grave Rune
GRAVE RUNE.flavorText: I'm gravely sorry to rune this.

PATCHWORK PALS.name: Patchwork Pals
PATCHWORK PALS.flavorText: "I'll name you Misha, you Huffer, and you can be the third one."

TRAVEL SECURITY.name: Travel Security
TRAVEL SECURITY.flavorText: "You're just gonna let ANY 8-Cost minion get past you!?" "...Yeah..."

REEFWALKER.name: Reefwalker
REEFWALKER.flavorText: A gentle giant with some not-so-gentle friends.

PERPETUAL FLAME.name: Perpetual Flame
PERPETUAL FLAME.flavorText: Flame is perpetual.* *Perpetual only applies to current turn.

GLOOP SPRAYER.name: Gloop Sprayer
GLOOP SPRAYER.flavorText: "Are you sure that's enough gloop?" "Hold on."

WITCHING HOUR.name: Witching Hour
WITCHING HOUR.flavorText: The gates to the Gilnean pet cemetary MUST remain locked at all times.

ANCIENT HARBINGER.name: Ancient Harbinger
ANCIENT HARBINGER.flavorText: "honey, can u run down to the store and pick up some 10 cost minions? thx"

PILOTED REAPER.name: Piloted Reaper
PILOTED REAPER.flavorText: New facial recognition systems keep out the Lorewalkers and Doomsayers.

WITCH'S CAULDRON.name: Witch's Cauldron
WITCH'S CAULDRON.flavorText: Eye of murloc, ear of bat, foot of Fordring, fur of cat…

HOWLING COMMANDER.name: Howling Commander
HOWLING COMMANDER.flavorText: Enlistment in her battalion comes with several pairs of earplugs.

MENAGERIE MUG.name: Menagerie Mug
MENAGERIE MUG.flavorText: He's a chip off the old jug.

CHROMATIC EGG.name: Chromatic Egg
CHROMATIC EGG.flavorText: Nefarian was known for creating two things: horrible monsters and excellent breakfasts.

IMPRISONED SATYR.name: Imprisoned Satyr
IMPRISONED SATYR.flavorText: "C'mon down to Illhoof's bargain bin! When the satyr's free, he'll lower your fee!"

SPLITTING IMAGE.name: Splitting Image
SPLITTING IMAGE.flavorText: Sometimes you get punched so hard they see double.

OPEN THE CAGES.name: Open the Cages
OPEN THE CAGES.flavorText: "Coming out of my cage, and I'm dead by turn nine..."

GAHZ'RILLA.name: Gahz'rilla
GAHZ'RILLA.flavorText: The Sen'jin High football team is The Gahz'rillas.

RODENT NEST.name: Rodent Nest
RODENT NEST.flavorText: Pig sty? No, this is a rat's nest.

HORRENDOUS GROWTH.name: Horrendous Growth
HORRENDOUS GROWTH.flavorText: Stop picking at it! You’re only making it worse.

DRAGON SOUL.name: Dragon Soul
DRAGON SOUL.flavorText: Crafted by Deathwing's goblin horde, but the dragon added the rainbow sparkles himself.

DEVIATE DREADFANG.name: Deviate Dreadfang
DEVIATE DREADFANG.flavorText: Even with wings, snakes STILL don't have legs.

LOTUS AGENTS.name: Lotus Agents
LOTUS AGENTS.flavorText: Mostly, they stand around and look cool.

DREADED MOUNT.name: Dreaded Mount
DREADED MOUNT.flavorText: This is the summoning that never ends, and it goes on and on my friends...

BLOATED PYTHON.name: Bloated Python
BLOATED PYTHON.flavorText: This is why Scholomance engineering students prefer C++.

LAKE THRESHER.name: Lake Thresher
LAKE THRESHER.flavorText: "There’s a monster in the lake?!" "That’s not a monster, that’s Gary."

TERRIBLE CHEF.name: Terrible Chef
TERRIBLE CHEF.flavorText: Anyone can cook! But not them.

UNEARTHED RAPTOR.name: Unearthed Raptor
UNEARTHED RAPTOR.flavorText: Still hunting for the ones who earthed him.

STORMWIND AVENGER.name: Stormwind Avenger
STORMWIND AVENGER.flavorText: "I swear if you heal me I will DPS."

VERDANT LONGNECK.name: Verdant Longneck
VERDANT LONGNECK.flavorText: Always sticking its neck into other people’s business.

LAVA SHOCK.name: Lava Shock
LAVA SHOCK.flavorText: Chocolate lava cake is shockingly delicious.

VULPERA TOXINBLADE.name: Vulpera Toxinblade
VULPERA TOXINBLADE.flavorText: The blade works well enough on its own… but this is just in case.

BREATH OF DREAMS.name: Breath of Dreams
BREATH OF DREAMS.flavorText: Ysera has the worst morning breath.

HOBGOBLIN.name: Hobgoblin
HOBGOBLIN.flavorText: Hobgoblins are meeting next week to discuss union benefits. First on the list: dental plan.

DOLLMASTER DORIAN.name: Dollmaster Dorian
DOLLMASTER DORIAN.flavorText: The children were puzzled by the scratches covering the insides of their toy-boxes.

FRONT LINES.name: Front Lines
FRONT LINES.flavorText: With the line in the sand crossed, the battle for the Throne of Tides had begun.

AZSHARAN DEFECTOR.name: Azsharan Defector
AZSHARAN DEFECTOR.flavorText: "I've got a sinking feeling about this evil Queen."

SANDWASP QUEEN.name: Sandwasp Queen
SANDWASP QUEEN.flavorText: Oooh, see that wasp! Watch that sting! Dig in the Sandwasp Queen!

BOTTOMLESS TOY CHEST.name: Bottomless Toy Chest
BOTTOMLESS TOY CHEST.flavorText: That's right, it goes in the toy chest.

SHADOWCRAFTER SCABBS.name: Shadowcrafter Scabbs
SHADOWCRAFTER SCABBS.flavorText: Sneaking behind enemy lines isn't so different from being a line cook. People are hostile, something's on fire, and your only hope is to get out of there with all your fingers.

NEPTULON.name: Neptulon
NEPTULON.flavorText: Neptulon is "The Tidehunter". He’s one of the four elemental lords. And he and Ragnaros get together and make really amazing saunas.

LIFEWEAVER.name: Lifeweaver
LIFEWEAVER.flavorText: Lifeweaving is all well and good until it's time to cut the thread.

STRANDED SPACEMAN.name: Stranded Spaceman
STRANDED SPACEMAN.flavorText: Would you say you're floating in a most peculiar way?

DECK OF WONDERS.name: Deck of Wonders
DECK OF WONDERS.flavorText: "Pick a card, any card. Wait! No! Not that one!" - Last words of previous owner

SHIP'S CHIRURGEON.name: Ship's Chirurgeon
SHIP'S CHIRURGEON.flavorText: Knows the answer to every medical question except how to pronounce his name.

FIREWORKS TECH.name: Fireworks Tech
FIREWORKS TECH.flavorText: She learns by trial and error. Mostly error.

SNOWCHUGGER.name: Snowchugger
SNOWCHUGGER.flavorText: Do the slow chant when he waddles by: "Chug! Chug! Chug!"

BOUNTY WRANGLER.name: Bounty Wrangler
BOUNTY WRANGLER.flavorText: With a smile like that and Coins in her hands, she's one greedy grinner.

LIVING PRAIRIE.name: Living Prairie
LIVING PRAIRIE.flavorText: Whoooooa, we're half way there Whooa-oh, -

SWINETUSK SHANK.name: Swinetusk Shank
SWINETUSK SHANK.flavorText: Comes with a rack of ribs!

BLACKSCALE BRUTE.name: Blackscale Brute
BLACKSCALE BRUTE.flavorText: Black, the scales of angry Naga! Red, the flames of Azshari's past!

UNIDENTIFIED CONTRACT.name: Unidentified Contract
UNIDENTIFIED CONTRACT.flavorText: The terms of service are constantly changing.

PET COLLECTOR.name: Pet Collector
PET COLLECTOR.flavorText: "And I'll call you Mrs. Snugglepants, and you Bubblecuddle, and you Cutie Cakes, and you ..."

HANDMAIDEN.name: Handmaiden
HANDMAIDEN.flavorText: Why did she unspool the last roll of royal toilet paper?!

STORMCRACK.name: Stormcrack
STORMCRACK.flavorText: WARNING: DO NOT TOUCH THE PURPLE BALL OF LIGHTNING

MURKWATER SCRIBE.name: Murkwater Scribe
MURKWATER SCRIBE.flavorText: The pen is mightier than the trident.

PRISON BREAKER.name: Prison Breaker
PRISON BREAKER.flavorText: Flavor fail! Demolition Renovator did it FIRST!

TERRORSCALE STALKER.name: Terrorscale Stalker
TERRORSCALE STALKER.flavorText: Likes to scare his friends half to death.

CARNIVOROUS CUBICLE.name: Carnivorous Cubicle
CARNIVOROUS CUBICLE.flavorText: Hey, no eating at your desk!

OMEGA DEVASTATOR.name: Omega Devastator
OMEGA DEVASTATOR.flavorText: The Alpha Devastator didn’t devastate enough. The Beta Devastator devastated too much. But the Omega was just right!

ARID STORMER.name: Arid Stormer
ARID STORMER.flavorText: Some people chase storms, some storms chase elementals.

CUTTING CLASS.name: Cutting Class
CUTTING CLASS.flavorText: When you actually are the sharpest tool in the shed.

FROSTBITTEN FREEBOOTER.name: Frostbitten Freebooter
FROSTBITTEN FREEBOOTER.flavorText: Alongside Eliza Goreblade and Peggy Brittlebone, the three Pirate Sisters terrorize the sea.

GOING DOWN SWINGING.name: Going Down Swinging
GOING DOWN SWINGING.flavorText: Halveria was outcast from Gilneas for being too edgy, which she sees as an achievement.

THRIVE IN THE SHADOWS.name: Thrive in the Shadows
THRIVE IN THE SHADOWS.flavorText: Why would your spells be afraid of the dark? It's easier to nap there.

CALL OF THE WILD.name: Call of the Wild
CALL OF THE WILD.flavorText: "Hello. Misha, Leokk and Huffer aren't here right now, but if you leave a message we'll get back to you right away." BEEP.

VENOMANCER.name: Venomancer
VENOMANCER.flavorText: Eight times the death of regular-mancers.

OPEN THE WAYGATE.name: Open the Waygate
OPEN THE WAYGATE.flavorText: Although powerful, the incantation is simple. It’s just a jump to the left, and then a step to the right.

INFESTED WATCHER.name: Infested Watcher
INFESTED WATCHER.flavorText: This is why you don't eat watermelon seeds.

HOT COALS.name: Hot Coals
HOT COALS.flavorText: This is what Greatfather Winter gives you when you've been REALLY naughty.

ARCANE TYRANT.name: Arcane Tyrant
ARCANE TYRANT.flavorText: Tyrant is such a strong word.

LOST EXARCH.name: Lost Exarch
LOST EXARCH.flavorText: She resisted the temptation of the Burning Legion's power only to fall victim to the Scourge.

RIGHTEOUS PROTECTOR.name: Righteous Protector
RIGHTEOUS PROTECTOR.flavorText: Original name was Tubular Protector, but this seems more bodacious.

EBON DRAGONSMITH.name: Ebon Dragonsmith
EBON DRAGONSMITH.flavorText: Having a furnace-mouth is really handy for a blacksmith.

MOORABI.name: Moorabi
MOORABI.flavorText: Most disturbing is how Moorabi covers all those frozen minions with flavored syrup.

WRENCHCALIBUR.name: Wrenchcalibur
WRENCHCALIBUR.flavorText: Whoso pulleth out this wrench from the toolbox is rightwise king of the lab.

LIFE SENTENCE.name: Life Sentence
LIFE SENTENCE.flavorText: Also sentenced to laugh and love.

MUCKMORPHER.name: Muckmorpher
MUCKMORPHER.flavorText: Fan favorite in the muck morphin' sewer strangers.

ICECROWN BROCHURE.name: Icecrown Brochure
ICECROWN BROCHURE.flavorText: The Icecrown ski slopes really are to die for.

BATTERHEAD.name: Batterhead
BATTERHEAD.flavorText: When it comes to problem-solving, he always uses his head.

BABA NAGA.name: Baba Naga
BABA NAGA.flavorText: A folktale told to Naga children to scare them from swimming too close to the surface.

FROSTFIN CHOMPER.name: Frostfin Chomper
FROSTFIN CHOMPER.flavorText: If you want good sushi, it is important to always keep your murlocs on ice.

ROKARA, THE VALOROUS.name: Rokara, the Valorous
ROKARA, THE VALOROUS.flavorText: As strong-willed and stubborn as her first day in the Horde, Rokara now wielded a weapon that rivaled even her tenacity.

DOUBLE JUMP.name: Double Jump
DOUBLE JUMP.flavorText: The key to every speed run.

COPPERTAIL SNOOP.name: Coppertail Snoop
COPPERTAIL SNOOP.flavorText: Scavenges both nuts and bolts for the winter.

BIBLIOMITE.name: Bibliomite
BIBLIOMITE.flavorText: He did NOT want to cast a spell.

COGHAMMER.name: Coghammer
COGHAMMER.flavorText: So you ripped this out of a machine, carved some runes on it, stuck it on a handle, and now it's a weapon of great divine power? Seems legit.

SANGUINE REVELER.name: Sanguine Reveler
SANGUINE REVELER.flavorText: Have some! This drink is to die for!

PROSECUTOR MEL'TRANIX.name: Prosecutor Mel'tranix
PROSECUTOR MEL'TRANIX.flavorText: "Your Honor. The Defense isn't a clown, he's the whole circus."

MASS PRODUCTION.name: Mass Production
MASS PRODUCTION.flavorText: Whenever you cast this, we make a new Nemsy portrait.

CURIO COLLECTOR.name: Curio Collector
CURIO COLLECTOR.flavorText: Experts worry that curios are a gateway to face-collecting.

FOGSAIL FREEBOOTER.name: Fogsail Freebooter
FOGSAIL FREEBOOTER.flavorText: Goes cheap on wardrobe so he can spend on weaponry.

DEMONFIRE.name: Demonfire
DEMONFIRE.flavorText: Demonfire is like regular fire except for IT NEVER STOPS BURNING HELLLPPP

LAKKARI FELHOUND.name: Lakkari Felhound
LAKKARI FELHOUND.flavorText: Guaranteed to track tar all over your carpet.

ACHERUS VETERAN.name: Acherus Veteran
ACHERUS VETERAN.flavorText: This is my Runeblade. There are many like it but this one is mine.

CORRIDOR CREEPER.name: Corridor Creeper
CORRIDOR CREEPER.flavorText: It likes the smell of dead things, which is curious, as it has no visible nose.

REMORNIA, LIVING BLADE.name: Remornia, Living Blade
REMORNIA, LIVING BLADE.flavorText: Was it the lead pipe... the candlestick... or the unhinged, sentient, bloodthirsty sword?

SUNREAVER WARMAGE.name: Sunreaver Warmage
SUNREAVER WARMAGE.flavorText: What, did you expect the Sunreavers to be coldages?

BRAZEN ZEALOT.name: Brazen Zealot
BRAZEN ZEALOT.flavorText: Some paladins really Light it up.

CONSUME MAGIC.name: Consume Magic
CONSUME MAGIC.flavorText: Please be mindful when consuming raw or undercooked magic.

GALAKROND, THE UNBREAKABLE.name: Galakrond, the Unbreakable
GALAKROND, THE UNBREAKABLE.flavorText: The ground quaked beneath the behemoth as Dr. Boom continued: "…with over 400 TONS of solid Storm Silver plate." Then he beeped a small remote. "And luxury spikes!"

STEALER OF SOULS.name: Stealer of Souls
STEALER OF SOULS.flavorText: The tooth fairy gig didn't work out.

IDOL OF Y'SHAARJ.name: Idol of Y'Shaarj
IDOL OF Y'SHAARJ.flavorText: Without a tongue, it speaks in seven. Without a voice, its echo lingers forever.

BLINK FOX.name: Blink Fox
BLINK FOX.flavorText: It's like, SUPER bad at staring contests.

GALAKROND, THE UNSPEAKABLE.name: Galakrond, the Unspeakable
GALAKROND, THE UNSPEAKABLE.flavorText: Lazul called Galakrond’s name, her voice echoed by whispers from the deep. Both of Galakrond’s eyes opened… and then other eyes opened, as well.

DEAD AIR.name: Dead Air
DEAD AIR.flavorText: We'll be right back after a word from our specters.

FIRE HAWK.name: Fire Hawk
FIRE HAWK.flavorText: It’s our fault for making all those card backs that look like food.

TICKET SCALPER.name: Ticket Scalper
TICKET SCALPER.flavorText: Takes ten percent off the top.

HEAVY METAL!.name: Heavy Metal!
HEAVY METAL!.flavorText: This metal is so heavy it will satisfy your iron requirements for the next year.

GIGANTOTEM.name: Gigantotem
GIGANTOTEM.flavorText: Totem Golem's uncle, gone too soon.

STAGE HAND.name: Stage Hand
STAGE HAND.flavorText: Holds everything himself because people wouldn't stop touching the prop table.

FELRATTLER.name: Felrattler
FELRATTLER.flavorText: It only rattles when YOU'RE in danger.

MIRACLE SALESMAN.name: Miracle Salesman
MIRACLE SALESMAN.flavorText: "Hey! Hope you’re well. Have you ever wanted to be your own boss?"

RHYTHM AND ROOTS.name: Rhythm and Roots
RHYTHM AND ROOTS.flavorText: For Zok's latest song, he decided to go back to his roots. Like the ones on a tree. Tree roots.

DRAKKARI EMBALMER.name: Drakkari Embalmer
DRAKKARI EMBALMER.flavorText: A troll in life, death, and online forums.

EXTRA ARMS.name: Extra Arms
EXTRA ARMS.flavorText: All the better to hug you with!

HIDDEN CACHE.name: Hidden Cache
HIDDEN CACHE.flavorText: There is an urban legend that the first Toxic Sewer Ooze was born because a rookie Goon stashed an open container of milk in a Hidden Cache.

SHADOW WORD: HORROR.name: Shadow Word: Horror
SHADOW WORD: HORROR.flavorText: It's more succinct than "Shadow Word: Suck Into Vortex."

MARSH DRAKE.name: Marsh Drake
MARSH DRAKE.flavorText: She would have gotten away with it, if it weren't for that meddling Drakeslayer.

ARANNA, THRILL SEEKER.name: Aranna, Thrill Seeker
ARANNA, THRILL SEEKER.flavorText: "Aranna, I feel like you only came to this island so you could use the zipline."

KEEPER OF THE GROVE.name: Keeper of the Grove
KEEPER OF THE GROVE.flavorText: These guys just show up and start Keeping your Groves without even asking.

BAIT AND SWITCH.name: Bait and Switch
BAIT AND SWITCH.flavorText: Oh my god, the bait and switch works every time!

SPECTRAL TRAINEE.name: Spectral Trainee
SPECTRAL TRAINEE.flavorText: After graduating at the top of her class from Scholomance, she was granted an eternal scholarship to study abroad in Naxxramas.

GORMOK THE IMPALER.name: Gormok the Impaler
GORMOK THE IMPALER.flavorText: Gormok has been giving impaling lessons in a small tent near the tournament grounds. For only 25g you too could learn the fine art of impaling!

ENVOY OF LAZUL.name: Envoy of Lazul
ENVOY OF LAZUL.flavorText: "Note to self: possess someone who's local and knows directions next time."

SKY MOTHER AVIANA.name: Sky Mother Aviana
SKY MOTHER AVIANA.flavorText: It's a bird! It's a plane! It's 10 copies of Leeroy Jenkins!

SPIRIT OF THE BAT.name: Spirit of the Bat
SPIRIT OF THE BAT.flavorText: Nah nah nah nah, nah nah nah nah, nah nah nah nah, nah nah nah nah

SPAWN OF DEATHWING.name: Spawn of Deathwing
SPAWN OF DEATHWING.flavorText: Aww, who’s the most dangerous threat to the world? You are!

AQUA ARCHIVIST.name: Aqua Archivist
AQUA ARCHIVIST.flavorText: Do not summon! I JUST had to put all my scrolls in rice.

JAINA'S GIFT.name: Jaina's Gift
JAINA'S GIFT.flavorText: "On this day, my magic will bring us together." -Jaina

MYSTERY EGG.name: Mystery Egg
MYSTERY EGG.flavorText: Which came first, the Mukla or the egg?

LIFESAVING AURA.name: Lifesaving Aura
LIFESAVING AURA.flavorText: One ring to rule them all, and in the sunlight save them.

CONQUEROR'S BANNER.name: Conqueror's Banner
CONQUEROR'S BANNER.flavorText: Olgra, I love your new tapestry! Where did you get it?

LIBRAM OF WISDOM.name: Libram of Wisdom
LIBRAM OF WISDOM.flavorText: The best wisdom is passed on.

AIR RAID.name: Air Raid
AIR RAID.flavorText: It's difficult to get an air raid together. You have to get twenty-five people, and they all want to play a paladin!

DARK ARAKKOA.name: Dark Arakkoa
DARK ARAKKOA.flavorText: There's a whole gradient of Arakkoa! This one is on the darker side.

KUN THE FORGOTTEN KING.name: Kun the Forgotten King
KUN THE FORGOTTEN KING.flavorText: Aya siphons a bit of Kun's soul to animate each golem in her Jade army. To his credit, he's being a great sport about it.

RUNIC CARVINGS.name: Runic Carvings
RUNIC CARVINGS.flavorText: "That totem was beautiful… and you runed it!"

DARKMOON DIRIGIBLE.name: Darkmoon Dirigible
DARKMOON DIRIGIBLE.flavorText: "It's dirigible? I don’t even know what diriging is!"

CHARGED CALL.name: Charged Call
CHARGED CALL.flavorText: You have a collect call from "AL'AKIR, LORD OF AIR AND THE FOUR WINDS." Do you accept these charges?

PSYCHE SPLIT.name: Psyche Split
PSYCHE SPLIT.flavorText: This is how the arakkoa make friends.

PLUCKY PAINTFIN.name: Plucky Paintfin
PLUCKY PAINTFIN.flavorText: Not everyone can become a great painter. But a great painter can come from anywhere.

THE GLASS KNIGHT.name: The Glass Knight
THE GLASS KNIGHT.flavorText: She seems scary, but she's got a glass jaw.

INFINITE AMALGAM.name: Infinite Amalgam
INFINITE AMALGAM.flavorText: The Infinite Amalgam sought Gammy, the greatest among them, though it feared the queen of the amalgams would never be found.

ARGENT BRAGGART.name: Argent Braggart
ARGENT BRAGGART.flavorText: Not sure why he's bragging, he's got the same stats as the next guy.

KEL'THUZAD, THE INEVITABLE.name: Kel'Thuzad, the Inevitable
KEL'THUZAD, THE INEVITABLE.flavorText: Looks like Kel'Thuzad is borrowing some of Mr. Bigglesworth's nine lives.

DREADSTEED.name: Dreadsteed
DREADSTEED.flavorText: Crescendo himself summoned this steed, riding it to victory in the Grand Tournament. Wherever he rides, an army of riders ride behind him, supporting the legendary champion.

POP'GAR THE PUTRID.name: Pop'gar the Putrid
POP'GAR THE PUTRID.flavorText: All around the arid badlands The Outlaws chased the Townsfolk Gerry had a train full of sludge POP! goes the sludge train

GARRISON COMMANDER.name: Garrison Commander
GARRISON COMMANDER.flavorText: He'll never admit it, but he pushes you hard because he really cares about you.

BULWARK OF AZZINOTH.name: Bulwark of Azzinoth
BULWARK OF AZZINOTH.flavorText: This plate turned shield you shall wield, praying its powers fel will serve you well.

CONE OF COLD.name: Cone of Cold
CONE OF COLD.flavorText: Magi of the Kirin Tor were casting Cubes of Cold for many years before Cones came into fashion some 90 years ago.

TIMEWINDER ZARIMI.name: Timewinder Zarimi
TIMEWINDER ZARIMI.flavorText: With how generous Whizbang's return policy is, Zarimi has never been busier.

SHIMMERFLY.name: Shimmerfly
SHIMMERFLY.flavorText: Plenty of buzz around this card.

WEBSPINNER.name: Webspinner
WEBSPINNER.flavorText: Spider cocoons are like little piñatas!

JUNGLE GIANTS.name: Jungle Giants
JUNGLE GIANTS.flavorText: Forming the Golakka Crater was the end of Barnabus' disastrous career as a dancer.

UNSTABLE PORTAL.name: Unstable Portal
UNSTABLE PORTAL.flavorText: The denizens of Azeroth have no idea how much work goes into stabilizing portals. We spend like 30% of GDP on portal upkeep.

OCTO-MASSEUSE.name: Octo-masseuse
OCTO-MASSEUSE.flavorText: Oh yeah, all of those are the spots.

KOBOLD MINER.name: Kobold Miner
KOBOLD MINER.flavorText: A mining kobold that costs 2, has very low health, and gives you resources… what is this, Warcraft Rumble?

PELAGOS.name: Pelagos
PELAGOS.flavorText: He's a great judge of character.

MIND EATER.name: Mind Eater
MIND EATER.flavorText: Watch out brain, she'll chew you up! She's a Mind Eater!

SCOURGELORD GARROSH.name: Scourgelord Garrosh
SCOURGELORD GARROSH.flavorText: "You dare to challenge me? Come! Draw your last breath - and then, you are mine."

DEATHWING, DRAGONLORD.name: Deathwing, Dragonlord
DEATHWING, DRAGONLORD.flavorText: To his credit, Deathwing really took to heart the feedback he was receiving that he needed to be "more of a team player".

UTHER OF THE EBON BLADE.name: Uther of the Ebon Blade
UTHER OF THE EBON BLADE.flavorText: "Step forward. Confess! Once I was a mere servant of the Light. Now I alone stand in judgement."

MYTHICAL TERROR.name: Mythical Terror
MYTHICAL TERROR.flavorText: You cannot pet the Terror in Hearthstone.

TORRENT.name: Torrent
TORRENT.flavorText: Weeks of underwater cross-training have really built up her fourarms.

HAUNTING VISIONS.name: Haunting Visions
HAUNTING VISIONS.flavorText: When you're awake at 3 AM and can't stop thinking about that time you called your teacher "mom."

PETTY THEFT.name: Petty Theft
PETTY THEFT.flavorText: Room service at a pirate hotel really cleans house.

NOZDORMU.name: Nozdormu
NOZDORMU.flavorText: Time to write some flavor text.

GIGGLING TOYMAKER.name: Giggling Toymaker
GIGGLING TOYMAKER.flavorText: "HAHAhehehe. Hahaha he." -Me when I'm making toys

ARCANE LUMINARY.name: Arcane Luminary
ARCANE LUMINARY.flavorText: They say true value is the cards you find along the way.

ARGENT LANCE.name: Argent Lance
ARGENT LANCE.flavorText: The stripes make it look like a candy cane, but we recommend against licking it.

WHETSTONE HATCHET.name: Whetstone Hatchet
WHETSTONE HATCHET.flavorText: A bad hatchet can make a good spear better.

GALVANIZER.name: Galvanizer
GALVANIZER.flavorText: Also known as a power zinc.

HAILBRINGER.name: Hailbringer
HAILBRINGER.flavorText: Knows every way to greet someone.

CRYSTAL LION.name: Crystal Lion
CRYSTAL LION.flavorText: Standard issue recruit gear: 1 silver sword, 1 Lordaeron insignia, 2 bags of crystal kibble.

STORMWIND PIPER.name: Stormwind Piper
STORMWIND PIPER.flavorText: Throws crazy parties with the Rat King—except when it's raining.

BOLF RAMSHIELD.name: Bolf Ramshield
BOLF RAMSHIELD.flavorText: Bolf keeps coming in 2nd at the Grand Tournament. It might be his year this year, if Lebron doesn't enter.
