voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/4/43/VO_AT_124_ATTACK_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_124_ATTACK_04.wav Who's next?!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/f/f2/VO_AT_124_DEATH_05.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_124_DEATH_05.wav <death sound>

FOR QUEL'THALAS!.name: For Quel'Thalas!
FOR QUEL'THALAS!.flavorText: For kwell-kell.. for kell… for kwee- for the city!

FLOPPY HYDRA.name: Floppy Hydra
FLOPPY HYDRA.flavorText: If you cut one of its heads off, it'll grow back twice as cute!

SHIELDED MINIBOT.name: Shielded Minibot
SHIELDED MINIBOT.flavorText: He chooses to believe what he is programmed to believe!

OCTOSARI.name: Octosari
OCTOSARI.flavorText: Eight arms of sand-flinging, foe-wringing, card-slinging fury!

GOLD PANNER.name: Gold Panner
GOLD PANNER.flavorText: "I don't know why everyone's got their overalls in a jumble with Azerite minin' when there's all this GOLD for the takin'!"

WAR CACHE.name: War Cache
WAR CACHE.flavorText: It's much tidier than Illidan's storage locker.

FAIRE ARBORIST.name: Faire Arborist
FAIRE ARBORIST.flavorText: The bad apple never falls far from the treant.

BELLIGERENT GNOME.name: Belligerent Gnome
BELLIGERENT GNOME.flavorText: Maybe don't put this one in your garden.

TUSKARR JOUSTER.name: Tuskarr Jouster
TUSKARR JOUSTER.flavorText: Just could not be talked out of using his turtle for the joust...

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/b2/VO_AT_104_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_104_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/2f/VO_AT_104_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_104_ATTACK_02.wav Turtle power!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/7b/VO_AT_104_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_104_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

GATHER YOUR PARTY.name: Gather Your Party
GATHER YOUR PARTY.flavorText: Thrilling adventure! Danger guaranteed! Loot uncertain! Death optional! Who’s with me?

MECH-BEAR-CAT.name: Mech-Bear-Cat
MECH-BEAR-CAT.flavorText: Crushes buildings with his BEAR hands.

STITCHED TRACKER.name: Stitched Tracker
STITCHED TRACKER.flavorText: He's just exercising his right to bear arms.

WAGGLE PICK.name: Waggle Pick
WAGGLE PICK.flavorText: Kobolds informally refer to its effect as a deathwaggle.

ANODIZED ROBO CUB.name: Anodized Robo Cub
ANODIZED ROBO CUB.flavorText: It's adorable! AND OH MY GOODNESS WHY IS IT EATING MY FACE

TURBULUS.name: Turbulus
TURBULUS.flavorText: "Passengers, we will be experiencing some minor Turbulus in the next few expansions."

NERUBIAN VIZIER.name: Nerubian Vizier
NERUBIAN VIZIER.flavorText: One of the essential constructors of the Northrend wide web.

BLOOD IN THE WATER.name: Blood in the Water
BLOOD IN THE WATER.flavorText: Fish are friends, not food! Gilgoblins on the other hand…

TOY BOAT.name: Toy Boat
TOY BOAT.flavorText: Try playing seven of these in one turn fast.

RESIZING POUCH.name: Resizing Pouch
RESIZING POUCH.flavorText: Just don't put a Resizing Pouch inside the Resizing Pouch.

TOY CAPTAIN TARIM.name: Toy Captain Tarim
TOY CAPTAIN TARIM.flavorText: Whizbang is now the sole proprietor of Un'Goro.

SWARTHY SWORDSHINER.name: Swarthy Swordshiner
SWARTHY SWORDSHINER.flavorText: Everyone knows swords are slashier when they're shiny!

IMPRISONED GAN'ARG.name: Imprisoned Gan'arg
IMPRISONED GAN'ARG.flavorText: Factory Direct Fiery War Axe. Please allow two turns for delivery.

REPULSIVE GARGANTUAN.name: Repulsive Gargantuan
REPULSIVE GARGANTUAN.flavorText: "EW, YUCK, GROSS, ICKY-" "Stop, you're hurting my feelings!"

ARMORED WARHORSE.name: Armored Warhorse
ARMORED WARHORSE.flavorText: Yep. It's a horse... wearing armor... going to war.

DARKSHIRE LIBRARIAN.name: Darkshire Librarian
DARKSHIRE LIBRARIAN.flavorText: Do NOT be late with your overdue fines.

OMEGA ASSEMBLY.name: Omega Assembly
OMEGA ASSEMBLY.flavorText: They told Dr. Boom he could only pick one. He disagreed.

FREQUENCY OSCILLATOR.name: Frequency Oscillator
FREQUENCY OSCILLATOR.flavorText: Our lawyer made us change the flavor text of this card so we wouldn't get sued.

GAZLOWE.name: Gazlowe
GAZLOWE.flavorText: Gazlowe was voted "Most Likely to Explode" in high school.

DEATHWEB SPIDER.name: Deathweb Spider
DEATHWEB SPIDER.flavorText: The itsy bitsy spiders climbed up the village wall. Then came the witch and the spiders ate them all.

RANCOR.name: Rancor
RANCOR.flavorText: Wise men say "Only fools rush in." Wise Orcs say the opposite.

RATS OF EXTRAORDINARY SIZE.name: Rats of Extraordinary Size
RATS OF EXTRAORDINARY SIZE.flavorText: They don't care if you believe they exist.

BLACKWING TECHNICIAN.name: Blackwing Technician
BLACKWING TECHNICIAN.flavorText: This is who you go to when your Blackwing needs a tune up. Don't go to a cut rate Blackwing tune up shop!

TOTALLY TOTEMS.name: Totally Totems
TOTALLY TOTEMS.flavorText: Hmph. Should've been Grace of Air Totem. Hmph.

VOLCANIC POTION.name: Volcanic Potion
VOLCANIC POTION.flavorText: The secret ingredient in Kazakus's award-winning chili recipe.

DEATHWARDEN.name: Deathwarden
DEATHWARDEN.flavorText: Ride or die takes on a new meaning.

MORDRESH FIRE EYE.name: Mordresh Fire Eye
MORDRESH FIRE EYE.flavorText: You're not hardcore unless you died hardcore.

CRAZED CHEMIST.name: Crazed Chemist
CRAZED CHEMIST.flavorText: You don't have to be crazy to work here, but it helps.

SARONITE SHAMBLER.name: Saronite Shambler
SARONITE SHAMBLER.flavorText: They play the best rock music at the saro-nite club.

SKYDIVING INSTRUCTOR.name: Skydiving Instructor
SKYDIVING INSTRUCTOR.flavorText: "Is it dangerous?" "For me? Not at all. Now jump!"

RED HERRING.name: Red Herring
RED HERRING.flavorText: He's got gill-ty written all over him!

EVASIVE CHIMAERA.name: Evasive Chimaera
EVASIVE CHIMAERA.flavorText: One head only tells the truth, while the other head only tells lies. But they both spit poison.

LOKHOLAR THE ICE LORD.name: Lokholar the Ice Lord
LOKHOLAR THE ICE LORD.flavorText: Suddenly the names of Iceblood Tower and Iceblood Garrison make a lot more sense.

POSSESSIFIER.name: Possessifier
POSSESSIFIER.flavorText: Beating the best, being the best, and brainwashing the rest.

DEFIAS CLEANER.name: Defias Cleaner
DEFIAS CLEANER.flavorText: His house cleaning service is quite thorough. Not a spot to be found... or any of your stuff!

FIRE PLUME'S HEART.name: Fire Plume's Heart
FIRE PLUME'S HEART.flavorText: Why does an active volcano need to be defended? To save its ash.

BLASTMASTER BOOM.name: Blastmaster Boom
BLASTMASTER BOOM.flavorText: He's gonna fly through the air with the greatest of grease.

SHOCK HOPPER.name: Shock Hopper
SHOCK HOPPER.flavorText: Who is shocked about a frog hopping?

STEAM SURGER.name: Steam Surger
STEAM SURGER.flavorText: Explorers nicknamed him the Teapot Elemental.

JAN'ALAI, THE DRAGONHAWK.name: Jan'alai, the Dragonhawk
JAN'ALAI, THE DRAGONHAWK.flavorText: You mess with the Bird, you get the Firelord.

DALARAN ASPIRANT.name: Dalaran Aspirant
DALARAN ASPIRANT.flavorText: Is he aspiring or inspiring? Make up your mind!

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/a/a7/VO_AT_006_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_006_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/6c/VO_AT_006_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_006_ATTACK_02.wav So. Here's where you're wrong!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/73/VO_AT_006_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_006_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

LIFE FROM DEATH.name: Life from Death
LIFE FROM DEATH.flavorText: Just because you came up with a nicer name for it doesn't mean that necromancy is any more justified.

SKYCAP'N KRAGG.name: Skycap'n Kragg
SKYCAP'N KRAGG.flavorText: What's more boss than riding a parrot with a jawbone for a shoulderpad while wielding a giant hook-lance-thing and wearing a pirate hat? NOTHING.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/f/f2/VO_AT_070_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_070_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/0/0a/VO_AT_070_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_070_ATTACK_02.wav Avast!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/55/VO_AT_070_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_070_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

MAGTHERIDON, UNRELEASED.name: Magtheridon, Unreleased
MAGTHERIDON, UNRELEASED.flavorText: Playing with this card can be penalized with up to a two-year suspension. Please wait until the card is officially released.

MANIC SOULCASTER.name: Manic Soulcaster
MANIC SOULCASTER.flavorText: When casting a tournament, you really have to put your soul into it!

SINDRAGOSA.name: Sindragosa
SINDRAGOSA.flavorText: "I recognize your effort but I think your magic still has room for improvement." - Sindragosa after taking a class on giving constructive feedback.

ASTRAL TIGER.name: Astral Tiger
ASTRAL TIGER.flavorText: Astral kitty litter is surprisingly hard to find.

CRUISE CAPTAIN LORA.name: Cruise Captain Lora
CRUISE CAPTAIN LORA.flavorText: To your left is our award winning spa area! And to the right, THE PRISON OF YOGG-SARON!

CLEAR THE WAY.name: Clear the Way
CLEAR THE WAY.flavorText: The terrifying part is the gryphons' squeaky voices afterward.

STONEMAUL ANCHORMAN.name: Stonemaul Anchorman
STONEMAUL ANCHORMAN.flavorText: "Brug will read anything you put on the parchment prompter. Anything."

STARLIGHT GROOVE.name: Starlight Groove
STARLIGHT GROOVE.flavorText: In space, no one can hear you groove.

ILLIDARI INQUISITOR.name: Illidari Inquisitor
ILLIDARI INQUISITOR.flavorText: Armed with fear, big eyes, ruthless efficiency, almost fanatical devotion to your hero, and nice brown robes.

XYRELLA, THE DEVOUT.name: Xyrella, the Devout
XYRELLA, THE DEVOUT.flavorText: Xyrella thought she was only saving her daughter. Her actions may very well have saved the entire world.

ARCANE GOLEM.name: Arcane Golem
ARCANE GOLEM.flavorText: Having Arcane golems at home really classes up the place, and as a bonus they are great conversation pieces.

FEARLESS FLAMEJUGGLER.name: Fearless Flamejuggler
FEARLESS FLAMEJUGGLER.flavorText: This is incredibly easy with 6 arms.

DEATHMATCH PAVILION.name: Deathmatch Pavilion
DEATHMATCH PAVILION.flavorText: Worth it for the stuffed toy at the end.

KARA KAZHAM!.name: Kara Kazham!
KARA KAZHAM!.flavorText: This is what happens when you tell Khadgar to set the table.

XAVIUS.name: Xavius
XAVIUS.flavorText: Xavius has grand nightmares of summoning Sargeras into this world, but a few Satyr will have to do for now.

ONYX MAGESCRIBE.name: Onyx Magescribe
ONYX MAGESCRIBE.flavorText: Sometimes you gotta spend spells to earn spells.

LUNAR TRAILBLAZER.name: Lunar Trailblazer
LUNAR TRAILBLAZER.flavorText: Changing legend into fact, she will ride into history.

THE MISTCALLER.name: The Mistcaller
THE MISTCALLER.flavorText: Calling the mist doesn't sound all that great. "Ooooh, it is slightly damp now!"

DARK SKIES.name: Dark Skies
DARK SKIES.flavorText: "It's a drizzle of fire. A fine mist, really."

INARA STORMCRASH.name: Inara Stormcrash
INARA STORMCRASH.flavorText: A fan favorite, Inara is always met with thunderous applause.

TAINTED ZEALOT.name: Tainted Zealot
TAINTED ZEALOT.flavorText: The love she shares seems to go nowhere. Now she's lost her Light, tosses and turns, she can't sleep at night...

SUSPICIOUS PEDDLER.name: Suspicious Peddler
SUSPICIOUS PEDDLER.flavorText: The best snake oil this side of Azeroth.

BLATANT DECOY.name: Blatant Decoy
BLATANT DECOY.flavorText: "Hah! You is being tricked by ME! Togwaggle!"

POWER WORD: GLORY.name: Power Word: Glory
POWER WORD: GLORY.flavorText: The promise of glory is a powerful tool to get minions to do your bidding. Only slightly less powerful than the promise of an ice cream bar!

SOUL SEEKER.name: Soul Seeker
SOUL SEEKER.flavorText: The Soul Seeker's job is to look for a snitch.

NEFARIAN.name: Nefarian
NEFARIAN.flavorText: They call him "Blackwing" because he's a black dragon...... and he's got wings.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/20/VO_BRMA13_1_HP_GENERIC_18.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BRMA13_1_HP_GENERIC_18.wav
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/20/VO_BRMA13_1_HP_GENERIC_18.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BRMA13_1_HP_GENERIC_18.wav Your magic is mine!

GUESS THE WEIGHT.name: Guess the Weight
GUESS THE WEIGHT.flavorText: "And then at the last second, I'll shapeshift into cat form!"

SEADEVIL STINGER.name: Seadevil Stinger
SEADEVIL STINGER.flavorText: Pretty harmless unless you're a Seadevil.

NEFERSET THRASHER.name: Neferset Thrasher
NEFERSET THRASHER.flavorText: Tough to do skateboard tricks with four legs.

STONEBORN GENERAL.name: Stoneborn General
STONEBORN GENERAL.flavorText: Leads with an iron fist and a stony demeanor.

PROFESSOR SLATE.name: Professor Slate
PROFESSOR SLATE.flavorText: "Don’t worry, this will be over in a second. It might FEEL like an eternity, but I assure you, it’s quite quick!"

BRASSWING.name: Brasswing
BRASSWING.flavorText: I’ve seen this before. You just have to time it right to avoid the dragon.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/75/AV_340_Brasswing_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ AV_340_Brasswing_Play.wav <summon sound>

RISING WAVES.name: Rising Waves
RISING WAVES.flavorText: How do you expect them to do the wave if their arms are buried in the sand??

FURIOUS ETTIN.name: Furious Ettin
FURIOUS ETTIN.flavorText: One head is a morning person. The other head hates morning people.

MISTWRAITH.name: Mistwraith
MISTWRAITH.flavorText: One little Mistwraith sitting in a tree. M-I-S-T-I-N-G.

DESERT OBELISK.name: Desert Obelisk
DESERT OBELISK.flavorText: The Obelisk of the Stars can hide an entire land from prying eyes! Or zap a rando.

BAZAAR MUGGER.name: Bazaar Mugger
BAZAAR MUGGER.flavorText: Premium muggings at a discount price.

HEMET, JUNGLE HUNTER.name: Hemet, Jungle Hunter
HEMET, JUNGLE HUNTER.flavorText: The goblin travel agency lost his luggage, but he's still having a great vacation!

CRYSTAL POWER.name: Crystal Power
CRYSTAL POWER.flavorText: Often used as healing crystals, but also good for throwing at people.

FATE SPLITTER.name: Fate Splitter
FATE SPLITTER.flavorText: "What's the matter with these scissors!? The thread won't cut!!"

RAZORSCALE.name: Razorscale
RAZORSCALE.flavorText: A razorscale, razormane, and razorclaw walk into the tavern.

ROLLING FIREBALL.name: Rolling Fireball
ROLLING FIREBALL.flavorText: Why don't they ever run perpendicular?

TOURNAMENT MEDIC.name: Tournament Medic
TOURNAMENT MEDIC.flavorText: The medic tournament is less entertaining than the Grand Tournament.

VELEN, LEADER OF THE EXILED.name: Velen, Leader of the Exiled
VELEN, LEADER OF THE EXILED.flavorText: For an exiled dude, he's pretty popular!

CRESCENDO.name: Crescendo
CRESCENDO.flavorText: The more you flail your arms, the better the orchestra plays! Yup, that's definitely how it works.

PIT FIGHTER.name: Pit Fighter
PIT FIGHTER.flavorText: What did the pits ever do to you?

TRAM HEIST.name: Tram Heist
TRAM HEIST.flavorText: How are they gunna steal the whole tram!?

IMP-LOSION.name: Imp-losion
IMP-LOSION.flavorText: The shrapnel is waaaaay worse than the explosion.

ONYXIAN WARDER.name: Onyxian Warder
ONYXIAN WARDER.flavorText: Throwing more whelps at the problem might not help, but they certainly will hurt.

LIVING DRAGONBREATH.name: Living Dragonbreath
LIVING DRAGONBREATH.flavorText: If you want that muscular physique, you've really gotta feel the burn.

HYDRATION TOTEM.name: Hydration Totem
HYDRATION TOTEM.flavorText: This filtered water really cleanses the spirit.

LOATHEB.name: Loatheb
LOATHEB.flavorText: Loatheb used to be a simple Bog Beast. This is why we need stricter regulations on mining and agriculture.

ANCIENT MAGE.name: Ancient Mage
ANCIENT MAGE.flavorText: Sometimes he forgets and just wanders into someone else's game.

VOLCANO.name: Volcano
VOLCANO.flavorText: Many young shaman summon a volcano as their first school project.

AUDIO AMPLIFIER.name: Audio Amplifier
AUDIO AMPLIFIER.flavorText: And you thought we were putting Wildheart Guff in Core. We'd never do that! WINK WINK.

FANDRAL STAGHELM.name: Fandral Staghelm
FANDRAL STAGHELM.flavorText: Always manages to mention "Back when I was creating the World Tree…" in EVERY conversation. Sheesh! Enough already.

WRATHGUARD.name: Wrathguard
WRATHGUARD.flavorText: After playing against 5 Annoy-O-Trons, any normal guard will become a Wrathguard.

ROCKET AUGMERCHANT.name: Rocket Augmerchant
ROCKET AUGMERCHANT.flavorText: "Don't worry, this won't hurt me a bit."

HAWKSTRIDER RANCHER.name: Hawkstrider Rancher
HAWKSTRIDER RANCHER.flavorText: I prefer the Hawkstrider Nacho Cheeser.

CLIFF DIVE.name: Cliff Dive
CLIFF DIVE.flavorText: "Is it safe?" "Sure, we have plenty of replacement pirates."

HOSTILE INVADER.name: Hostile Invader
HOSTILE INVADER.flavorText: "And my Axe!" "And my Axe!" "And my Axe!"

GHASTLY CONJURER.name: Ghastly Conjurer
GHASTLY CONJURER.flavorText: Wearing purple after the holidays? GHASTLY!

TRADE PRINCE GALLYWIX.name: Trade Prince Gallywix
TRADE PRINCE GALLYWIX.flavorText: Gallywix believes in supply and demand. He supplies the beatings and demands you pay up!

LIGHT OF THE PHOENIX.name: Light of the Phoenix
LIGHT OF THE PHOENIX.flavorText: It's 3 in the morning, could you PLEASE put out that phoenix?!

CLAY MATRIARCH.name: Clay Matriarch
CLAY MATRIARCH.flavorText: I hope you didn't need all that purple clay.

CACTUS CONSTRUCT.name: Cactus Construct
CACTUS CONSTRUCT.flavorText: "I am not Malfurion! I am CACTUS LORD!"

RAZORMANE RAIDER.name: Razormane Raider
RAZORMANE RAIDER.flavorText: "Call me hedgehog one more time. I dare you."

DRAGON BREEDER.name: Dragon Breeder
DRAGON BREEDER.flavorText: Deathwing would have been more well-adjusted if he'd been raised by this guy.

INCRIMINATING PSYCHIC.name: Incriminating Psychic
INCRIMINATING PSYCHIC.flavorText: Good news: He knows Kazakus's secret identity! Bad news: Now he's here.

EXPLODINEER.name: Explodineer
EXPLODINEER.flavorText: Explodineeeer... explodifaaaar... explode whereeeever you aaaaare...

TOMB WARDEN.name: Tomb Warden
TOMB WARDEN.flavorText: Also known as an ancient copy machine.

KAZAKUSAN.name: Kazakusan
KAZAKUSAN.flavorText: Kazakus had always seemed too clever a sort to bottle a brew that could do him any harm. Perhaps it should come as no surprise, then, that the originator of the Dragonfire Potion was a dragon himself.

SHIFTING SCROLL.name: Shifting Scroll
SHIFTING SCROLL.flavorText: Next turn, this is going to be AMAZING.

WARMAUL CHALLENGER.name: Warmaul Challenger
WARMAUL CHALLENGER.flavorText: Old gladiator rules: first one to die loses.

ROTTEN RODENT.name: Rotten Rodent
ROTTEN RODENT.flavorText: It's dead, but it's not a mouse.

EXTRATERRESTRIAL EGG.name: Extraterrestrial Egg
EXTRATERRESTRIAL EGG.flavorText: I'll have mine starry-side up please.

ZEPHRYS THE GREAT.name: Zephrys the Great
ZEPHRYS THE GREAT.flavorText: "Of course it's perfect, you're just not seeing how to use it."

MELTED MAKER.name: Melted Maker
MELTED MAKER.flavorText: Melts what he makes (cheese) and makes a mean melt (grilled cheese).

LADY PRESTOR.name: Lady Prestor
LADY PRESTOR.flavorText: To her credit, the best bodyguard for the king WOULD be a dragon in disguise.

CELESTIAL INK SET.name: Celestial Ink Set
CELESTIAL INK SET.flavorText: "Dear Mother, I have a lot of spells and burst in my hand. You should maybe run more armor and healing next time. Cordially, Your child"

MEETING STONE.name: Meeting Stone
MEETING STONE.flavorText: "I'm clicking on it, but nothing's happening."

BANANA BUFFOON.name: Banana Buffoon
BANANA BUFFOON.flavorText: You could say he has a certain appeal.

OMEGA MIND.name: Omega Mind
OMEGA MIND.flavorText: Has a side-business selling her lipstick shade, "Omega Red."

MAN'ARI MOSHER.name: Man'ari Mosher
MAN'ARI MOSHER.flavorText: "E.T.C. is sooo mainstream. Have you heard of Blight Boar?"

MAXIMA BLASTENHEIMER.name: Maxima Blastenheimer
MAXIMA BLASTENHEIMER.flavorText: Believe it or not, this is only the faire's fourth most dangerous game.

WICKERCLAW.name: Wickerclaw
WICKERCLAW.flavorText: They say pets tend to look like their owners.

V-07-TR-0N PRIME.name: V-07-TR-0N Prime
V-07-TR-0N PRIME.flavorText: Long after the titans' departure, Mimiron dreamed of creating something with an approximation of their power. He may have actually succeeded!

SPIKED WHEEL.name: Spiked Wheel
SPIKED WHEEL.flavorText: Great for driving, terrible for steering.

COILFANG CONSTRICTOR.name: Coilfang Constrictor
COILFANG CONSTRICTOR.flavorText: How do you know when someone has a crush on you? They take your breath away.

FURNACEFIRE COLOSSUS.name: Furnacefire Colossus
FURNACEFIRE COLOSSUS.flavorText: Smelts in his mouth, not in your hand.

RUNEFORGING.name: Runeforging
RUNEFORGING.flavorText: I swear the runes are genuine!

VAL'KYR SOULCLAIMER.name: Val'kyr Soulclaimer
VAL'KYR SOULCLAIMER.flavorText: My Ghoul friend is back and you're gonna be in trouble.

FROSTY D\u00c9COR.name: Frosty Décor
FROSTY D\u00c9COR.flavorText: "Yeah, Nature magic pays the bills, but my passion lies elsewhere."

SWEETENED SNOWFLURRY.name: Sweetened Snowflurry
SWEETENED SNOWFLURRY.flavorText: "You want a piece of me!? Will that be one scoop or two?"

VOODOO HEXXER.name: Voodoo Hexxer
VOODOO HEXXER.flavorText: The Silver Hand recruits shuddered in terror when they saw the dreaded totem of the Hexxer: A tiny little snowman, impaled with pins.

ARCANE WATCHER.name: Arcane Watcher
ARCANE WATCHER.flavorText: Now his watch has ended… until you have Spell Damage.

ENCHANTER.name: Enchanter
ENCHANTER.flavorText: "I know Scourgebane! Your materials and tips appreciated!"

THE CRYSTAL COVE.name: The Crystal Cove
THE CRYSTAL COVE.flavorText: For some strange reason, everyone that hangs out at the Crystal Cove has the same name...

ROBOCALLER.name: Robocaller
ROBOCALLER.flavorText: When I was your age, robocallers had to dial themselves!

RABID WORGEN.name: Rabid Worgen
RABID WORGEN.flavorText: "I'm sorry, son. We had to send Old Howler off…to a farm…to play…"

VIOLET WURM.name: Violet Wurm
VIOLET WURM.flavorText: It's wurms all the way down.

YOGG-SARON, UNLEASHED.name: Yogg-Saron, Unleashed
YOGG-SARON, UNLEASHED.flavorText: Has been known to monologue before he strikes.

CELESTIAL ALIGNMENT.name: Celestial Alignment
CELESTIAL ALIGNMENT.flavorText: "Is my deck any good?" "I mean, if the stars align."

CHEESEMONGER.name: Cheesemonger
CHEESEMONGER.flavorText: Secretly, the Big Cheese of SI:7.

FROST LICH CROSS-STITCH.name: Frost Lich Cross-Stitch
FROST LICH CROSS-STITCH.flavorText: Do not fear power... Fear those who SEW IT!

POWER WORD: TENTACLES.name: Power Word: Tentacles
POWER WORD: TENTACLES.flavorText: Because you're wrapped in a protective layer of… tentacles?

BATTLEFIELD NECROMANCER.name: Battlefield Necromancer
BATTLEFIELD NECROMANCER.flavorText: Coming soon: the Hand Necromancer and the Deck Necromancer.

THORIGNIR DRAKE.name: Thorignir Drake
THORIGNIR DRAKE.flavorText: Throwing your children at enemies qualifies you for Worst Mother of the Year.

MANA GIANT.name: Mana Giant
MANA GIANT.flavorText: Spell more and save more with a GIANT discount!

FIRST DAY OF SCHOOL.name: First Day of School
FIRST DAY OF SCHOOL.flavorText: "Report to the bookstore to buy your books, the alchemist to buy your potions, and then get your wands at the… wandryroom?"

HEMET NESINGWARY.name: Hemet Nesingwary
HEMET NESINGWARY.flavorText: It's hard to make a living as a hunter in a world where beasts instantly reappear minutes after you kill them.

DISCIPLE OF ARGUS.name: Disciple of Argus
DISCIPLE OF ARGUS.flavorText: "Aw nuts, I put both ends in the pencil sharpener."

CHIEF INSPECTOR.name: Chief Inspector
CHIEF INSPECTOR.flavorText: Empty your pockets, I know you’ve got a Wandering Monster in there!

DREADLICH TAMSIN.name: Dreadlich Tamsin
DREADLICH TAMSIN.flavorText: At a certain point, you stop mocking death and start becoming it.

THE VORAXX.name: The Voraxx
THE VORAXX.flavorText: I am the Voraxx. I speak for the weeds.

RUMBLE ENTHUSIAST.name: Rumble Enthusiast
RUMBLE ENTHUSIAST.flavorText: There's always room for one more game in the tavern!

MINECART CRUISER.name: Minecart Cruiser
MINECART CRUISER.flavorText: Where are you drivin', Minecart Cruiser? Where is your bounty, fortune, and fame?

DISCOVERY OF MAGIC.name: Discovery of Magic
DISCOVERY OF MAGIC.flavorText: It's in a book, just take a look!

ROCK MASTER VOONE.name: Rock Master Voone
ROCK MASTER VOONE.flavorText: After several audience members were burnt to a crisp, Voone's band became a lot less all-in on Dragons.

COMBUSTION.name: Combustion
COMBUSTION.flavorText: Sally is friends with three Silverhand Recruits conveniently standing in a line. After casting this spell, how many friends does she have left? (Show your work.)

SINFUL SOUS CHEF.name: Sinful Sous Chef
SINFUL SOUS CHEF.flavorText: If this dinner party goes well, she thinks she has a good shot at being on Fel's Kitchen.

TREASURE GUARD.name: Treasure Guard
TREASURE GUARD.flavorText: The real treasure was the Naga we met along the way.

STOCKADES PRISONER.name: Stockades Prisoner
STOCKADES PRISONER.flavorText: She was arrested for lockpicking. Her imprisonment was not well thought out.

ASTRAL RIFT.name: Astral Rift
ASTRAL RIFT.flavorText: Let's see what's behind rift number one!

LIGHTFORGED ZEALOT.name: Lightforged Zealot
LIGHTFORGED ZEALOT.flavorText: Card-carrying member of the Paladins Only Paladin Club.

TRINKET TRACKER.name: Trinket Tracker
TRINKET TRACKER.flavorText: Dashing through the snow On an undead trinket craze Over the hills we go Tracking all the way!

RELENTLESS WRATHGUARD.name: Relentless Wrathguard
RELENTLESS WRATHGUARD.flavorText: Ugh, for the love of... could they just send a Relenting Smileguard for once!?

MOTION DENIED.name: Motion Denied
MOTION DENIED.flavorText: DO NOT PASS GO. DO NOT COLLECT 200 GOLD.

HYSTERIA.name: Hysteria
HYSTERIA.flavorText: "My mount and I share a special connection. Just not a good one."

VESSINA.name: Vessina
VESSINA.flavorText: She wasn't happy when Hagatha sent her back to Uldum. But her "angry" hiss sounds like her "happy" hiss, so no one knew the difference.

GOBLIN AUTO-BARBER.name: Goblin Auto-Barber
GOBLIN AUTO-BARBER.flavorText: This guy is excellent at adjusting your haircut and/or height.

SKELEMANCER.name: Skelemancer
SKELEMANCER.flavorText: What do you mean there's no such thing as "Skelemancy?" But "Dinomancy" is ok?

BLACKGUARD.name: Blackguard
BLACKGUARD.flavorText: "Did I ever tell you the story of when I single-handedly took down a 29/29 C'thun?" - Reno Jackson

HENCH-CLAN HAG.name: Hench-Clan Hag
HENCH-CLAN HAG.flavorText: The Hench Clan is an equal opportunity employer, no matter which parts of you came from where.

TRAVELING HEALER.name: Traveling Healer
TRAVELING HEALER.flavorText: Some heroes have soft hearts and hard shells.

PARTY FAVOR TOTEM.name: Party Favor Totem
PARTY FAVOR TOTEM.flavorText: It's the gift (totem) that keeps on giving (totems)!

HEMET, FOAM MARKSMAN.name: Hemet, Foam Marksman
HEMET, FOAM MARKSMAN.flavorText: So THIS is who's been lowering the power level of all those Hearthstone cards in a foamly fashion.

FROM DE OTHER SIDE.name: From De Other Side
FROM DE OTHER SIDE.flavorText: Why did Drakuru cross the road?

EYE FOR AN EYE.name: Eye for an Eye
EYE FOR AN EYE.flavorText: Justice sometimes takes the form of a closed fist into a soft cheek.

DETONATION JUGGERNAUT.name: Detonation Juggernaut
DETONATION JUGGERNAUT.flavorText: Did you really need a whole giant mecha-suit just for one bundle of dynamite?

DREAD RAVEN.name: Dread Raven
DREAD RAVEN.flavorText: Fun Fact: A group of three Dread Ravens is an unkindness. Four is lethal!

JITTERBUG.name: Jitterbug
JITTERBUG.flavorText: The only bug that was intentional.

GRIMTOTEM BUZZKILL.name: Grimtotem Buzzkill
GRIMTOTEM BUZZKILL.flavorText: I'd be mad too if you called me a 'buzzkill'.

GLACIAL MYSTERIES.name: Glacial Mysteries
GLACIAL MYSTERIES.flavorText: The secret is in the frosting.

FROM THE DEPTHS.name: From the Depths
FROM THE DEPTHS.flavorText: "This is why I'm afraid of the deep end of the pool."

STAR POWER.name: Star Power
STAR POWER.flavorText: Five of the spectators were star-struck.

GRIMTOTEM BOUNTY HUNTER.name: Grimtotem Bounty Hunter
GRIMTOTEM BOUNTY HUNTER.flavorText: He’ll take a big weight off your shoulders.

TAK NOZWHISKER.name: Tak Nozwhisker
TAK NOZWHISKER.flavorText: "One for me and one for future me!"

FELSCREAM BLAST.name: Felscream Blast
FELSCREAM BLAST.flavorText: All the souls start running when they see the felscream truck.

GRAVEYARD SHIFT.name: Graveyard Shift
GRAVEYARD SHIFT.flavorText: "Why are we even open at night? This place is dead!"

IRONCLAD.name: Ironclad
IRONCLAD.flavorText: With one inch of clearance, Ironclad proved ineffective against speedbumps.

WING BLAST.name: Wing Blast
WING BLAST.flavorText: Emeriss uses Wing Blast. It's super effective!

ANUBISATH WARBRINGER.name: Anubisath Warbringer
ANUBISATH WARBRINGER.flavorText: Some dogs will bring you a bone or a squeaky toy. This one brings war!

COMMANDER RHYSSA.name: Commander Rhyssa
COMMANDER RHYSSA.flavorText: Two people can keep a secret as long as neither of them are Commander Rhyssa.

SIGIL OF FLAME.name: Sigil of Flame
SIGIL OF FLAME.flavorText: "Huh, it reads F-I-R-E. Wonder what that means?"

MERCH SELLER.name: Merch Seller
MERCH SELLER.flavorText: "Sorry, we're all out of Mediums. All we've got left are Gnome, Extra Large, and Annihilan."

IMPRISONED VILEFIEND.name: Imprisoned Vilefiend
IMPRISONED VILEFIEND.flavorText: If you do the time, you gotta make up the time.

TOXMONGER.name: Toxmonger
TOXMONGER.flavorText: Not all spiders are born poisonous. That's where he comes in.

VOLTAIC BURST.name: Voltaic Burst
VOLTAIC BURST.flavorText: Batteries have three components: Cathode, Anode, and Overload.

SCARLET WEBWEAVER.name: Scarlet Webweaver
SCARLET WEBWEAVER.flavorText: Isn't that nice? The spider made the explorer a sleeping bag!

POWER WORD: FEAST.name: Power Word: Feast
POWER WORD: FEAST.flavorText: Some people are here for the stellar, world-renowned academic program. Others are here for the buffet.

ROCK RAGER.name: Rock Rager
ROCK RAGER.flavorText: Still doesn't understand why he can't beat Paper Rager.

LION'S FRENZY.name: Lion's Frenzy
LION'S FRENZY.flavorText: Only as sharp as your draw.

HEX LORD MALACRASS.name: Hex Lord Malacrass
HEX LORD MALACRASS.flavorText: Extremely awkward cousin of Hex Lord Malaclass.

UNDYING DISCIPLE.name: Undying Disciple
UNDYING DISCIPLE.flavorText: We get it, you're undead. But jumping out of a grave? That's a bit much.

CRANE GAME.name: Crane Game
CRANE GAME.flavorText: This claw machine is RIGGED! I keep getting demons that bite me!

SPAWN OF N'ZOTH.name: Spawn of N'Zoth
SPAWN OF N'ZOTH.flavorText: Who's a cute widdle N'Zoth? You are! Yes you are! Yes you're the cutest widdle N'Zoth in the whole world!!!

FEUGEN.name: Feugen
FEUGEN.flavorText: Feugen is sad because everyone likes Stalagg better.

SHARKFIN FAN.name: Sharkfin Fan
SHARKFIN FAN.flavorText: His taste in soup is criminal.

FLOBBIDINOUS FLOOP.name: Flobbidinous Floop
FLOBBIDINOUS FLOOP.flavorText: Of all the scientists, he has the most knowledge (when measured in volume).

SERVICE BELL.name: Service Bell
SERVICE BELL.flavorText: The bell tolls for us! Waiter, we need more water!

RISING WINDS.name: Rising Winds
RISING WINDS.flavorText: Do not talk to me or my chick ever again.

SCARAB EGG.name: Scarab Egg
SCARAB EGG.flavorText: They say you can’t make an omelet without AHHH THEY’RE EATING MY FACE!

CRYSTAL STAG.name: Crystal Stag
CRYSTAL STAG.flavorText: Arrives alone, but usually leaves with a friend just like him.

NOFIN'S IMP-OSSIBLE.name: Nofin's Imp-ossible
NOFIN'S IMP-OSSIBLE.flavorText: They have faces only a morrglr could love.

DRAKEFIRE AMULET.name: Drakefire Amulet
DRAKEFIRE AMULET.flavorText: "...and I only had to climb up the mountains in Winterspring 50 times!"

SOUL INFUSION.name: Soul Infusion
SOUL INFUSION.flavorText: People called him a soulless monster. We're not sure this is better.

SAXOPHONE SOLOIST.name: Saxophone Soloist
SAXOPHONE SOLOIST.flavorText: He used to play to crowds of adoring Murlocs, but 20 years later all that's left is gigs at secluded clubs and regrets. Where did all the time go? His dreams of fame and fortune, snuffed out like the flame of a small candle in a dimly lit bar. Nothing but smoke in the wind.

MARROWSLICER.name: Marrowslicer
MARROWSLICER.flavorText: Perfect for killing the first boss in Icecrown Citadel.

NAGRAND SLAM.name: Nagrand Slam
NAGRAND SLAM.flavorText: Come on and slam, and welcome to Nagrand!

YELLING YODELER.name: Yelling Yodeler
YELLING YODELER.flavorText: Maybe it's OK for the Grimtotem to destroy some music forever.

PURSUIT OF JUSTICE.name: Pursuit of Justice
PURSUIT OF JUSTICE.flavorText: "Is this about justice or just us?"

INFESTED WOLF.name: Infested Wolf
INFESTED WOLF.flavorText: A little flea powder will fix that right up.

ETERNIUM ROVER.name: Eternium Rover
ETERNIUM ROVER.flavorText: He's all beeps and smiles but you're just a walking pile of armor to him.

LOST IN THE PARK.name: Lost in the Park
LOST IN THE PARK.flavorText: Mister, have you seen my Archdruid?

SAVORY DEVIATE DELIGHT.name: Savory Deviate Delight
SAVORY DEVIATE DELIGHT.flavorText: "Savory" is a creative way to put it.

TIDAL SURGE.name: Tidal Surge
TIDAL SURGE.flavorText: Also good for removing pesky stains.

BINDING HEAL.name: Binding Heal
BINDING HEAL.flavorText: By accepting this healing, you agree to the following terms…

MECHANICAL WHELP.name: Mechanical Whelp
MECHANICAL WHELP.flavorText: "Well if I didn't build the whelp and YOU didn't build the whelp…"

PLAGUESPREADER.name: Plaguespreader
PLAGUESPREADER.flavorText: What do they mean by Patient Zero? I'm very patient!

SOOTHSAYER'S CARAVAN.name: Soothsayer's Caravan
SOOTHSAYER'S CARAVAN.flavorText: With tusks like those, you might call her a "Toothsayer."

PRESSURE PLATE.name: Pressure Plate
PRESSURE PLATE.flavorText: The appropriate dishware for stressful situations.

CORNERED SENTRY.name: Cornered Sentry
CORNERED SENTRY.flavorText: The Draenei are seriously considering cancelling "Bring Your Murderous Pet to Work Day."

CLOCKWORK GNOME.name: Clockwork Gnome
CLOCKWORK GNOME.flavorText: Clockwork gnomes are always asking what time it is.

CONDUCTIVITY.name: Conductivity
CONDUCTIVITY.flavorText: That faceless sure didn't put up a lot of (length/cross-sectional area).

STARLIGHT WANDERER.name: Starlight Wanderer
STARLIGHT WANDERER.flavorText: Not all who wander are lost, but some most definitely are and could really use directions right about now.

SLEEPY DRAGON.name: Sleepy Dragon
SLEEPY DRAGON.flavorText: Local villagers call her "Naps Under the Mountain."

OBSIDIANSMITH.name: Obsidiansmith
OBSIDIANSMITH.flavorText: Was able to produce more effective weapons than his predecessor, Kelpsmith.

ROLLING STONE.name: Rolling Stone
ROLLING STONE.flavorText: Sadly, the mariachi band it used to play in gathers no más.

COLAQUE.name: Colaque
COLAQUE.flavorText: Ten thousand years ago, the city of Zin-Azshari fell to the bottom of the sea... and partially onto Colaque's shell.

IGNEOUS ELEMENTAL.name: Igneous Elemental
IGNEOUS ELEMENTAL.flavorText: We wanted to name him "Ingenious Elemental", but he just wasn't that bright.

SHRIEK.name: Shriek
SHRIEK.flavorText: The first warning sign of an oncoming warlock temper tantrum.

GIANT WASP.name: Giant Wasp
GIANT WASP.flavorText: Float like a butterfly, sting like a giant wasp!

MOUNTAINFIRE ARMOR.name: Mountainfire Armor
MOUNTAINFIRE ARMOR.flavorText: Excuse me. Your mountain is on fire.

KLAXXI AMBER-WEAVER.name: Klaxxi Amber-Weaver
KLAXXI AMBER-WEAVER.flavorText: Amberweaving is a specialty course at the local trade school.

SPAMMY ARCANIST.name: Spammy Arcanist
SPAMMY ARCANIST.flavorText: You don't have to jump while spamming, but it’s more fun that way.

BRU'KAN OF THE ELEMENTS.name: Bru'kan of the Elements
BRU'KAN OF THE ELEMENTS.flavorText: The elements crackled through Bru'kan's veins and his life flashed before his eyes. He knew this moment would come, but he wondered, had he given them enough?

MOSH'OGG ANNOUNCER.name: Mosh'Ogg Announcer
MOSH'OGG ANNOUNCER.flavorText: One's play-by-play. The other is off-color.

SHAMBLING CHOW.name: Shambling Chow
SHAMBLING CHOW.flavorText: And step, and shamble, and step, and flip the hair!

BONECHEWER RAIDER.name: Bonechewer Raider
BONECHEWER RAIDER.flavorText: And if that minion has a frisbee, LOOK OUT!

SPIRIT OF THE DEAD.name: Spirit of the Dead
SPIRIT OF THE DEAD.flavorText: Just because you’re dead doesn’t mean you’re off the team.

UNDERKING.name: Underking
UNDERKING.flavorText: "Behold, the Underking! I'm always beneath you, but nothing is beneath me! I hereby declare war on peace and happiness! Soon, all will tremble before me!"

MOONGLADE PORTAL.name: Moonglade Portal
MOONGLADE PORTAL.flavorText: Ain't no party like a Moonglade party ‘cause a Moonglade party got bears.

MILITIA COMMANDER.name: Militia Commander
MILITIA COMMANDER.flavorText: She only needs two commands: "Heel" and "Sic 'em!"

DEMENTED FROSTCALLER.name: Demented Frostcaller
DEMENTED FROSTCALLER.flavorText: He prefers that you refer to him by his nickname: 'Frostwaker.'

WRATHION.name: Wrathion
WRATHION.flavorText: Wrathion, son of Deathwing, is a dragon. Why isn't he tagged as a dragon, you ask? WHAT, ARE YOU TRYING TO BLOW HIS COVER??

CONCERT PROMO-DRAKE.name: Concert Promo-Drake
CONCERT PROMO-DRAKE.flavorText: There's a reason why it's promoting the festival instead of playing in it - it's a rhyme-lost protodrake.

PANTRY SPIDER.name: Pantry Spider
PANTRY SPIDER.flavorText: You have to admit, they make a cute couple.

HELMET HERMIT.name: Helmet Hermit
HELMET HERMIT.flavorText: I’d avoid asking if it wants to join the battle. It’s been pretty crabby lately.

LIGHTNING BREATH.name: Lightning Breath
LIGHTNING BREATH.flavorText: Recipe: One dragon, four wool socks, thick shag carpet.

TERON GOREFIEND.name: Teron Gorefiend
TERON GOREFIEND.flavorText: "You’re fine, friendly minions! You're fine! Don’t tell Mom!"

WORGEN ABOMINATION.name: Worgen Abomination
WORGEN ABOMINATION.flavorText: Does anyone want to play dead!?

DEMONIC DEAL.name: Demonic Deal
DEMONIC DEAL.flavorText: The Burning Legion upped their efforts to sell Argus Timeshares.

FIND THE IMPOSTER.name: Find the Imposter
FIND THE IMPOSTER.flavorText: My money is on the evil advisor to the king.

BLOOD RAZOR.name: Blood Razor
BLOOD RAZOR.flavorText: For the close shave that you've always wanted. Caution: Very sharp.

MARIN THE MANAGER.name: Marin the Manager
MARIN THE MANAGER.flavorText: Mawin! Mawin is what bwings us togethaaa... today.

SLUDGE SLURPER.name: Sludge Slurper
SLUDGE SLURPER.flavorText: You can't stop slurping this delicious sludge!

RAMKAHEN WILDTAMER.name: Ramkahen Wildtamer
RAMKAHEN WILDTAMER.flavorText: She gets to decide what cards go to the Hall of Fame.

SCALERIDER.name: Scalerider
SCALERIDER.flavorText: Do Re Me Fa So La Spear Throw!

STEEL BEETLE.name: Steel Beetle
STEEL BEETLE.flavorText: Steel you can trust—fashioned from the husk of an over-sized creepy-crawly.

DEATH GROWL.name: Death Growl
DEATH GROWL.flavorText: GRRRRR I'M SO ANGRY BECAUSE I'M DEAD!

CORPSICLE.name: Corpsicle
CORPSICLE.flavorText: Comes in three tasty flavors: Gross, Disgusting, and Chocolate!

GOLDSHIRE GNOLL.name: Goldshire Gnoll
GOLDSHIRE GNOLL.flavorText: They're searching for one ring. They're pretty sure someone said Goldshire.

SKETCHY STRANGER.name: Sketchy Stranger
SKETCHY STRANGER.flavorText: More of a 'Painted Stranger' if you ask me.

CREATION PROTOCOL.name: Creation Protocol
CREATION PROTOCOL.flavorText: If you want the destruction protocol, just go in reverse.

SCRIBBLING STENOGRAPHER.name: Scribbling Stenographer
SCRIBBLING STENOGRAPHER.flavorText: A truly staggering 180 scribbles per minute!

DINOSIZE.name: Dinosize
DINOSIZE.flavorText: Comes with fries and a drink.

AKAMA.name: Akama
AKAMA.flavorText: "To many of my people, I am known as a traitor... as Illidan's lapdog. I will remain in the shadows, for now... Actually, maybe I'll just remain in the shadows forever."

GURUBASHI OFFERING.name: Gurubashi Offering
GURUBASHI OFFERING.flavorText: For a limited time, loa blessings are on a pray-one-get-two deal (on selected sacrifices only).

GRIMESTREET PAWNBROKER.name: Grimestreet Pawnbroker
GRIMESTREET PAWNBROKER.flavorText: "I don't know a lot about used GvG cards, so I'm going to have to call in an expert."

SPIRITSINGER UMBRA.name: Spiritsinger Umbra
SPIRITSINGER UMBRA.flavorText: She sees the fate of anyone she meets, but it's always the same: dinosaur attack.

GREEDY SPRITE.name: Greedy Sprite
GREEDY SPRITE.flavorText: Sparkliest of the seven deadly sprites.

SHADOW VISIONS.name: Shadow Visions
SHADOW VISIONS.flavorText: This one’s a bird. And here’s a bunny!

SURVIVAL OF THE FITTEST.name: Survival of the Fittest
SURVIVAL OF THE FITTEST.flavorText: Sometimes the fittest is the one smart enough to not start a fight with seven 6/6 Treants.

FELSABER.name: Felsaber
FELSABER.flavorText: Some drivers rev their engines. This one growls all on its own.

AZSHARAN SENTINEL.name: Azsharan Sentinel
AZSHARAN SENTINEL.flavorText: For some, the Sundering was the collapse of civilization. For others, it was a great core workout.

HENCH-CLAN THUG.name: Hench-Clan Thug
HENCH-CLAN THUG.flavorText: Hard time making ends meet? Hate the League of Explorers? Get a job henching!

FORSAKEN LIEUTENANT.name: Forsaken Lieutenant
FORSAKEN LIEUTENANT.flavorText: WE didn’t forsake him. He CHOSE to defend a tower against the entire Alliance front line by himself.

HOT STREAK.name: Hot Streak
HOT STREAK.flavorText: It's easy to catch fire when you're on fire.

CRUSH.name: Crush
CRUSH.flavorText: Using this card on your enemies is one of the best things in life, according to some barbarians.

SHADOW WORD: UNDEATH.name: Shadow Word: Undeath
SHADOW WORD: UNDEATH.flavorText: We like to call it FUNdeath here!

WINDSHEAR STORMCALLER.name: Windshear Stormcaller
WINDSHEAR STORMCALLER.flavorText: Don't ever doubt Al'Akir's love for basic totems.

FLARK'S BOOM-ZOOKA.name: Flark's Boom-Zooka
FLARK'S BOOM-ZOOKA.flavorText: It used to be a Ba-zooka but we ran out of sheep.

ARCANE MISSILES.name: Arcane Missiles
ARCANE MISSILES.flavorText: You'd think you'd be able to control your missiles a little better since you're a powerful mage and all.

FREE ADMISSION.name: Free Admission
FREE ADMISSION.flavorText: "Quick, get in before someone sees you, or worse, someone sees me."

RECKLESS EXPERIMENTER.name: Reckless Experimenter
RECKLESS EXPERIMENTER.flavorText: It's hard to call her reckless when it's clear she knows what she's doing.

SIF.name: Sif
SIF.flavorText: She is Sif. He is Malygos. They are not the same person. They may have similar spell damage, they may have similar colors but they are different nonetheless.

PIRANHA POACHER.name: Piranha Poacher
PIRANHA POACHER.flavorText: This snack certainly isn’t smiling back…

DOUBLE CROSS.name: Double Cross
DOUBLE CROSS.flavorText: Valeera revealed herself to be a double agent. At which point Maiev felt comfortable revealing that she also was a double agent. And then Scabbs announced to everybody that - get this - he was a double agent.

THING FROM BELOW.name: Thing from Below
THING FROM BELOW.flavorText: Just can't resist the opportunity to hang around with a bunch of totems.

DRUID OF THE PLAINS.name: Druid of the Plains
DRUID OF THE PLAINS.flavorText: Not to be confused with the aeronautically advanced Druid of the Planes.

INJURED KVALDIR.name: Injured Kvaldir
INJURED KVALDIR.flavorText: Don't worry. With a little skin cream he's going to clear right up.

FIRE BREATHER.name: Fire Breather
FIRE BREATHER.flavorText: "Phew! That skull has been stuck between my teeth for hours!"

SPIRIT MOUNT.name: Spirit Mount
SPIRIT MOUNT.flavorText: Bru'kan said his spirit would always be with us. He failed to mention that his raptor’s would be too.

JUNKBOT.name: Junkbot
JUNKBOT.flavorText: One bot's junk is another bot's AWESOME UPGRADE!

DJ MANASTORM.name: DJ Manastorm
DJ MANASTORM.flavorText: Do not sleep on his Tinker Town deep house set - absolutely legendary.

DARK PHARAOH TEKAHN.name: Dark Pharaoh Tekahn
DARK PHARAOH TEKAHN.flavorText: He'll get that League of Explorers and their little murloc too!

GENERAL VEZAX.name: General Vezax
GENERAL VEZAX.flavorText: Contrast this with Specific Vezax, who only gets resummoned if you have exactly 4 Armor.

MINEFIELD.name: Minefield
MINEFIELD.flavorText: Dodge bombs like you're playing Tonksweeper!

KOBOLD TASKMASTER.name: Kobold Taskmaster
KOBOLD TASKMASTER.flavorText: Fabled questgiver of the “Get me candle”, “Get me another candle”, and “Get me 11 more candle” questline.

WILDPAW GNOLL.name: Wildpaw Gnoll
WILDPAW GNOLL.flavorText: A big fan of four-claw discounts.

BLACKSMITHING HAMMER.name: Blacksmithing Hammer
BLACKSMITHING HAMMER.flavorText: Passed through the hands of countless smiths, and eventually the skulls of their enemies.

DEFENSE ATTORNEY NATHANOS.name: Defense Attorney Nathanos
DEFENSE ATTORNEY NATHANOS.flavorText: "Your Honor, my client was simply trying a new tree trimming technique!"

KEYWARDEN IVORY.name: Keywarden Ivory
KEYWARDEN IVORY.flavorText: She learned exactly one thing from her old man: copying.

UMBRAL GEIST.name: Umbral Geist
UMBRAL GEIST.flavorText: “After all, one can't leave his shadow lying about and not miss it sooner or later, don't you agree?”

TEMPLAR CAPTAIN.name: Templar Captain
TEMPLAR CAPTAIN.flavorText: You can combine two of these into a Captain Archon.

HUNTING PARTY.name: Hunting Party
HUNTING PARTY.flavorText: Not sure I’d call it a good party if everyone ends up beside themselves.

RANSACK.name: Ransack
RANSACK.flavorText: "Fred's a talking ghoul. He can do whatever he wants." "I want to steal!"

FEL'DOREI WARBAND.name: Fel'dorei Warband
FEL'DOREI WARBAND.flavorText: "Felerin, I made you a friendship bracelet!" "...what? I said WARband, not WRISTband..."

SERPENT WARD.name: Serpent Ward
SERPENT WARD.flavorText: When snakes get sick, they get sent to the Serpent Ward.

MO'ARG FORGEFIEND.name: Mo'arg Forgefiend
MO'ARG FORGEFIEND.flavorText: Enraged not by fel energies, but by an itchy nose he cannot scratch.

SHAN'DO WILDCLAW.name: Shan'do Wildclaw
SHAN'DO WILDCLAW.flavorText: She holds both an academic post and a scratching post.

TWILIGHT GUARDIAN.name: Twilight Guardian
TWILIGHT GUARDIAN.flavorText: A result of magical experiments carried out by the Black Dragonflight, it's not his fault that he's a vicious killer.

SWORD AND BOARD.name: Sword and Board
SWORD AND BOARD.flavorText: Stab and Slab. Charge and Targe. Slash and Bash. You get the idea.

DR. MORRIGAN.name: Dr. Morrigan
DR. MORRIGAN.flavorText: She will NOT STOP until she gets tenure.

MASK OF C'THUN.name: Mask of C'Thun
MASK OF C'THUN.flavorText: Hide in the mask, but it will wear you. Through its gleaming eye, you shall see true.

FUNHOUSE MIRROR.name: Funhouse Mirror
FUNHOUSE MIRROR.flavorText: Funhouse mirror on the wall, Who's the tallest gnome of all?

NORGANNON.name: Norgannon
NORGANNON.flavorText: His tremendous arcane magic was strong enough to save all of the spirits of the titans after Sargeras destroyed their physical forms.

UNDERCITY VALIANT.name: Undercity Valiant
UNDERCITY VALIANT.flavorText: Almost went to play for Stormwind before signing with Undercity.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/d/d9/VO_AT_030_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_030_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e2/VO_AT_030_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_030_ATTACK_02.wav Join us in death!
