POISON SEEDS.name: Poison Seeds
POISON SEEDS.flavorText: "Poisonseed Bagel" is the least popular bagel at McTiggin's Druidic Bagel Emporium.

TITANFORGED TRAPS.name: Titanforged Traps
TITANFORGED TRAPS.flavorText: Always place it underneath their health pack.

BLOOD WITCH.name: Blood Witch
BLOOD WITCH.flavorText: Like a sloppy joe for vampires.

NEW HEIGHTS.name: New Heights
NEW HEIGHTS.flavorText: The sky's the limit (or at least 99 is).

UNCHAINED GLADIATOR.name: Unchained Gladiator
UNCHAINED GLADIATOR.flavorText: We can't possibly buff this card any more, just look at him!

BOOTSTRAP SUNKENEER.name: Bootstrap Sunkeneer
BOOTSTRAP SUNKENEER.flavorText: Part of the deck, part of the crew.

BIG BAD ARCHMAGE.name: Big Bad Archmage
BIG BAD ARCHMAGE.flavorText: "My, my, what big minions I have!"

IMPRISONED CELESTIAL.name: Imprisoned Celestial
IMPRISONED CELESTIAL.flavorText: "Look at your deck, now back to me, now back at your deck, now back to me. Who am I? None of your—I'm on a horse."

CATRINA MUERTE.name: Catrina Muerte
CATRINA MUERTE.flavorText: She always manages to lift your spirits.

PARTY PLANNER VONA.name: Party Planner Vona
PARTY PLANNER VONA.flavorText: She's known for her popular "occult ritual to summon an otherworldly being" parties.

SI:7 ASSASSIN.name: SI:7 Assassin
SI:7 ASSASSIN.flavorText: You can't keep the streets clean if you're afraid to get your hands dirty.

SLITHERING DEATHSCALE.name: Slithering Deathscale
SLITHERING DEATHSCALE.flavorText: Colossal minions know her better as Slithering Damagescale.

AXE FLINGER.name: Axe Flinger
AXE FLINGER.flavorText: Once a lowly "Stick Flinger", he's been relentless on the path to his ultimate dream: "Tauren Flinger".

BUCCANEER.name: Buccaneer
BUCCANEER.flavorText: The best part of buccaneering is the pants.

MURDER ACCUSATION.name: Murder Accusation
MURDER ACCUSATION.flavorText: Quote From Man Murdered: "What are you gonna do, murder me?"

RATCHET PRIVATEER.name: Ratchet Privateer
RATCHET PRIVATEER.flavorText: There's a fine line between privateering and pirating. It comes down to tax breaks.

INSTRUCTOR FIREHEART.name: Instructor Fireheart
INSTRUCTOR FIREHEART.flavorText: When you have fire in your heart, even death can't stop you.

WISHING WELL.name: Wishing Well
WISHING WELL.flavorText: Wishing upon a star? Pssshhh, that's so childish. Anyways, let me throw all my Coins into this well.

TIDELOST BURROWER.name: Tidelost Burrower
TIDELOST BURROWER.flavorText: Burrowing may not be for everyone, but I dig it.

FLYING MACHINE.name: Flying Machine
FLYING MACHINE.flavorText: To operate, this contraption needs a hula doll on the dashboard. Otherwise it's just a “falling machine.”

PLAGUEBRINGER.name: Plaguebringer
PLAGUEBRINGER.flavorText: One sip and you've got the grippe.

WHACK-A-GNOLL.name: Whack-A-Gnoll
WHACK-A-GNOLL.flavorText: Need closure on your Hardcore WoW character dying in Westfall? Step right up!

SABOTEUR.name: Saboteur
SABOTEUR.flavorText: Listen all y'all it's a saboteur!

FLOECASTER.name: Floecaster
FLOECASTER.flavorText: His real name is Melvin, but he prefers his friends call him ... <sigh> ..."Floecaster."

DREAD DESERTER.name: Dread Deserter
DREAD DESERTER.flavorText: "I uh... need to go walk my uh… fish."

SHADOW CHORD: DISTORT.name: Shadow Chord: Distort
SHADOW CHORD: DISTORT.flavorText: For some unknown reason, using distortion intentionally in your music will attract hundreds of geckos to your location.

FAMISHED FOOL.name: Famished Fool
FAMISHED FOOL.flavorText: He's not hungry for food, he's starving for attention!

INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY.name: Investment Opportunity
INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY.flavorText: "It's a real fixer-upper. I mean a REAL fixer upper."

SARUUN.name: Saruun
SARUUN.flavorText: BORN FROM THE HEAT DEATH OF COLLIDING SUPERNOVAS, SARUUN SEEKS TO INCINERATE ALL THAT WHICH REVOLVES AROUND THEM TO MERE ASHES AND STARDUST!!!! Which is pretty neato!

CARIEL ROAME.name: Cariel Roame
CARIEL ROAME.flavorText: Cariel had pledged her honor to the Alliance, but when someone matching her long-lost sister's description was sighted at the Crossroads, Cariel did the unthinkable: she abandoned her post and set out across the Barrens.

KINGPIN PUD.name: Kingpin Pud
KINGPIN PUD.flavorText: The good, the bad, and the ugly stats for the Cost.

EMBALMING RITUAL.name: Embalming Ritual
EMBALMING RITUAL.flavorText: "Guess what! We're getting a new cat."

BUFFET BIGGUN.name: Buffet Biggun
BUFFET BIGGUN.flavorText: "Look, I just want to know what kind of monster put raisins in this."

KING PHAORIS.name: King Phaoris
KING PHAORIS.flavorText: When you're the king of the cats, the whole desert is your litterbox.

PRINCE VALANAR.name: Prince Valanar
PRINCE VALANAR.flavorText: Three Princes stand before you. This one devours one after another.

ELISE, BADLANDS SAVIOR.name: Elise, Badlands Savior
ELISE, BADLANDS SAVIOR.flavorText: From the library to the field, she's proved herself to be a leading intellectual.

UR'ZUL HORROR.name: Ur'zul Horror
UR'ZUL HORROR.flavorText: You face face face face face Jaraxxus!

MUCKBORN SERVANT.name: Muckborn Servant
MUCKBORN SERVANT.flavorText: Party guests never tip as well as the patrons in Bob's tavern.

SPHERE OF SAPIENCE.name: Sphere of Sapience
SPHERE OF SAPIENCE.flavorText: This is what it sounds like when spheres scry.

BRASS KNUCKLES.name: Brass Knuckles
BRASS KNUCKLES.flavorText: For the goon that wants to make a fashion statement.

BLOWGILL SNIPER.name: Blowgill Sniper
BLOWGILL SNIPER.flavorText: Imagine how much further his darts would go if he had lungs instead of gills!

SOUND THE BELLS!.name: Sound the Bells!
SOUND THE BELLS!.flavorText: Weirdly, the bells stop ringing after 5.

PRIMAL DUNGEONEER.name: Primal Dungeoneer
PRIMAL DUNGEONEER.flavorText: They wanted a Mature Dungeoneer. Instead they got this.

ARROGANT CRUSADER.name: Arrogant Crusader
ARROGANT CRUSADER.flavorText: To be honest, he was kind of a jerk even BEFORE he was bitten by that ghoul.

RAIN OF FIRE.name: Rain of Fire
RAIN OF FIRE.flavorText: You know it’s autumn when the skies rain brimstone and fire. Also: pumpkin spice!

EREDAR BRUTE.name: Eredar Brute
EREDAR BRUTE.flavorText: After a while, the glowing purple stress ball became ineffective at containing his rage.

FLOATING WATCHER.name: Floating Watcher
FLOATING WATCHER.flavorText: "Evil Eye Watcher of Doom" was the original name, but marketing felt it was a bit too aggressive.

ICE REVENANT.name: Ice Revenant
ICE REVENANT.flavorText: There must have been some magic in that old ice mace we found.

ZOMBEEEES!!!.name: ZOMBEEEES!!!
ZOMBEEEES!!!.flavorText: In your brain, in your brain, Zombees, Zombees, Zombees-ees-ees.

DECK OF LUNACY.name: Deck of Lunacy
DECK OF LUNACY.flavorText: Voted "Most Lunacy" in Madness Monthly magazine.

POWER CHORD: SYNCHRONIZE.name: Power Chord: Synchronize
POWER CHORD: SYNCHRONIZE.flavorText: "It's all about you, girl On your 16,000th birthday"

GOLAKKA GLUTTON.name: Golakka Glutton
GOLAKKA GLUTTON.flavorText: We lost our last cook to one of these.

PARAGLIDE.name: Paraglide
PARAGLIDE.flavorText: I can see my hand from here!!!!!

NOXIOUS CADAVER.name: Noxious Cadaver
NOXIOUS CADAVER.flavorText: Shouldn't have eaten that gas station sushi.

WOLPERTINGER.name: Wolpertinger
WOLPERTINGER.flavorText: Scholomance student Brewfest prank gone awry.

ILLUMINATE.name: Illuminate
ILLUMINATE.flavorText: BEHOLD THE GLORY OF A NEW CUP!

CABAL SHADOW PRIEST.name: Cabal Shadow Priest
CABAL SHADOW PRIEST.flavorText: You never know who may be secretly working for the Cabal....

PSYFIEND.name: Psyfiend
PSYFIEND.flavorText: Listens to a LOT of K-pop.

INNER FIRE.name: Inner Fire
INNER FIRE.flavorText: Good idea: Buffing your minions. Bad idea: Starting a conversation in the Barrens.

KNICKKNACK SHACK.name: Knickknack Shack
KNICKKNACK SHACK.flavorText: In a hole in the ground there... was a tourist trap?

ANCHORED TOTEM.name: Anchored Totem
ANCHORED TOTEM.flavorText: The Naga devised the perfect retaliation to any pirates dropping anchor in their domain: vandalism.

MOGU'SHAN WARDEN.name: Mogu'shan Warden
MOGU'SHAN WARDEN.flavorText: All these guys ever do is talk about the Thunder King. BOOOORRRINNG!

CRYOSTASIS.name: Cryostasis
CRYOSTASIS.flavorText: We'll thaw you out when we find a cure!

FEL GUARDIANS.name: Fel Guardians
FEL GUARDIANS.flavorText: What happened after the guardians tripped? They Fel.

MENAGERIE JUG.name: Menagerie Jug
MENAGERIE JUG.flavorText: It's art imitating Battlegrounds imitating life.

LAWFUL LONGARM.name: Lawful Longarm
LAWFUL LONGARM.flavorText: Loves to lob law bombs from his law blog.

SYNTHESIZE.name: Synthesize
SYNTHESIZE.flavorText: After the invention of elemental audio processing, Azeroth went through a major synth phase.

CRYSTALLIZER.name: Crystallizer
CRYSTALLIZER.flavorText: This elf's winning the arms race.

SPOTLIGHT.name: Spotlight
SPOTLIGHT.flavorText: Everyone's eyes are on you! Well, they're also looking at the giant Elemental that we're using as a spotlight, but mainly at you!

RAINBOW SEAMSTRESS.name: Rainbow Seamstress
RAINBOW SEAMSTRESS.flavorText: Is this card any good? It would seam sew.

ARCANE DYNAMO.name: Arcane Dynamo
ARCANE DYNAMO.flavorText: We ran out of jars, so we started putting brains in other stuff.

HEDRA THE HERETIC.name: Hedra the Heretic
HEDRA THE HERETIC.flavorText: Hedra was cast out millennia ago for her divisive opinions among the Naga, such as "Turning into evil underwater serpent people was bad, actually."

DOOMERANG.name: Doomerang
DOOMERANG.flavorText: Guaranteed to return your weapon directly to your hand! (Wear gloves. Thick ones.)

PETTING ZOO.name: Petting Zoo
PETTING ZOO.flavorText: Welcome to the petting zoo. DO NOT TOUCH THE ANIMALS.

BUCKET OF SOLDIERS.name: Bucket of Soldiers
BUCKET OF SOLDIERS.flavorText: Life is like a bucket of soldiers. You never know what bonus effects you're gonna get.

ANCIENT MYSTERIES.name: Ancient Mysteries
ANCIENT MYSTERIES.flavorText: I'm not saying it was aliens, but it was TOTALLY aliens!

DIVINE RAGER.name: Divine Rager
DIVINE RAGER.flavorText: For when you need to rage, rage against the dying of the Light.

COWBELL SOLOIST.name: Cowbell Soloist
COWBELL SOLOIST.flavorText: Hot take: We need LESS cowbell. Much, much less.

PEBBLY PAGE.name: Pebbly Page
PEBBLY PAGE.flavorText: A good friend will lighten your Overload.

HOG RANCHER.name: Hog Rancher
HOG RANCHER.flavorText: Suspiciously close to a Quilboar village.

DEVOLVE.name: Devolve
DEVOLVE.flavorText: Ragnaros looked down. He looked like some kind of War Golem. "WHAT HAVE YOU DONE TO ME," he yelled. But all that came out was a deep grinding sound. He began to cry.

INFERNAL STAPLER.name: Infernal Stapler
INFERNAL STAPLER.flavorText: Excuse me, I believe you have my stapler…

WEAPONIZED WASP.name: Weaponized Wasp
WEAPONIZED WASP.flavorText: Dr. Boom had one simple request: wasps with flippin' laser beams attached to their heads.

REVENANT RASCAL.name: Revenant Rascal
REVENANT RASCAL.flavorText: Turns out his face really did get stuck that way.

EYE OF THE STORM.name: Eye of the Storm
EYE OF THE STORM.flavorText: If that's the eye, I would hate to see the rest of the storm.

GRACE OF THE HIGHFATHER.name: Grace of the Highfather
GRACE OF THE HIGHFATHER.flavorText: The fish was thiiiiis big, can you believe it?

MONKEY BUSINESS.name: Monkey Business
MONKEY BUSINESS.flavorText: Why aren't the bananas randomly split???

CROWD SURFER.name: Crowd Surfer
CROWD SURFER.flavorText: I'm pretty sure it's the band that's supposed to be crowd surfing, but you do you little dude.

TOKI, TIME-TINKER.name: Toki, Time-Tinker
TOKI, TIME-TINKER.flavorText: Just a twist to the left, one quarter turn to the right and … oops! Well, we didn’t need that timeline anyway.

CHILLBLADE CHAMPION.name: Chillblade Champion
CHILLBLADE CHAMPION.flavorText: It slices, it dices, it vaporizes! The Chillblade will make a Champion out of even the lowliest gnome.

ANKA, THE BURIED.name: Anka, the Buried
ANKA, THE BURIED.flavorText: "You look familiar. Were you at my first funeral?"

FINAL GASP.name: Final Gasp
FINAL GASP.flavorText: And with a raspy whisper, he uttered his final words, "rez plz."

FLAME JUGGLER.name: Flame Juggler
FLAME JUGGLER.flavorText: At first he liked juggling chain saws, but then he thought, "Flames are better! Because FIRE!"

PIPSI PAINTHOOF.name: Pipsi Painthoof
PIPSI PAINTHOOF.flavorText: "Earthmother guide my paintbrush strokes, especially on the eyes."

RHEASTRASZA.name: Rheastrasza
RHEASTRASZA.flavorText: Rheastrasza ascends above loyalty to just her dragonflight to serve all dragonkind. She believes all flights deserve a future and will give her life for the future dragon prince.

DEADSCALE KNIGHT.name: Deadscale Knight
DEADSCALE KNIGHT.flavorText: His favorite spell is Chum Explosion.

DEVOLVING MISSILES.name: Devolving Missiles
DEVOLVING MISSILES.flavorText: Most intermural spell-dueling contests end with a field of wisps.

ELISE THE ENLIGHTENED.name: Elise the Enlightened
ELISE THE ENLIGHTENED.flavorText: From cartographer to combatant, Elise has taken the road less traveled—because no one else could find it on a map.

FROST STRIKE.name: Frost Strike
FROST STRIKE.flavorText: Anyone up for some frost bowling?

DARKMOON STATUE.name: Darkmoon Statue
DARKMOON STATUE.flavorText: As far as workplace injuries go, Silas is protected by his statue of limitations.

IRONBARK.name: Ironbark
IRONBARK.flavorText: "The important thing, son, is to protect your spores! I have spoken!"

STEAM GUARDIAN.name: Steam Guardian
STEAM GUARDIAN.flavorText: Its boiling steam and erupting magma serve as a pretty good form of 2-Factor Authentication.

PILFER.name: Pilfer
PILFER.flavorText: The class is always greener on the other side of the board.

INFESTED TAUREN.name: Infested Tauren
INFESTED TAUREN.flavorText: The Overmind and the Old Gods are surprisingly similar.

CHATTY BARTENDER.name: Chatty Bartender
CHATTY BARTENDER.flavorText: "So a Venthyr, an Old God, and a Tauren walk into a bar…"

DARK PROPHECY.name: Dark Prophecy
DARK PROPHECY.flavorText: It's always a dark prophecy with Madame Lazul. Where's my happy, fluffy prophecy?!

SERPENTSHRINE PORTAL.name: Serpentshrine Portal
SERPENTSHRINE PORTAL.flavorText: This is why you never flush a three-cost minion.

SHIMMERING COURSER.name: Shimmering Courser
SHIMMERING COURSER.flavorText: A courser is a courser of course, of course, she's more of a unicorn than a horse...

SOUTHSEA SCOUNDREL.name: Southsea Scoundrel
SOUTHSEA SCOUNDREL.flavorText: "…and here we see the Southsea Scoundrel in their natural habitat: a den of scum and villainy."

FURIOUS FOWLS.name: Furious Fowls
FURIOUS FOWLS.flavorText: They were already mad and you had to call them 'foul'??

SHADOWJEWELER HANAR.name: Shadowjeweler Hanar
SHADOWJEWELER HANAR.flavorText: What is a shadowjeweler? A miserable little pile of secrets.

SOLDIER'S CARAVAN.name: Soldier's Caravan
SOLDIER'S CARAVAN.flavorText: It’s a clown car… for JUSTICE!

MAKING MUMMIES.name: Making Mummies
MAKING MUMMIES.flavorText: "I do say, this gives me the vapors every single time!"

DOOR OF SHADOWS.name: Door of Shadows
DOOR OF SHADOWS.flavorText: Upon arrival, please ring the doorbell of shadows, and wipe your shoes on the doormat of shadows before entering.

ETHEREAL PEDDLER.name: Ethereal Peddler
ETHEREAL PEDDLER.flavorText: Yeah, sure. That Ragnaros "fell off the back of a truck".

SMELT.name: Smelt
SMELT.flavorText: Due to his heightened olfactory system, Kha'zgoroth is cursed with always being the one that dealt it.

SECURE THE DECK.name: Secure the Deck
SECURE THE DECK.flavorText: "Tied it down, boss. I don't really know why you asked me to do that."

REMOTE CONTROL.name: Remote Control
REMOTE CONTROL.flavorText: For some reason, my dog keeps trying to eat this.

ALTAR OF FIRE.name: Altar of Fire
ALTAR OF FIRE.flavorText: "I now pronounce you, Crispy and Fried."

JOB SHADOWER.name: Job Shadower
JOB SHADOWER.flavorText: "Our prosperity… is beyond… a shadow of… a doubt! Ok, got it!"

SNAKEBITE.name: Snakebite
SNAKEBITE.flavorText: Don't look her in the eyes or you'll turn to ROCK!

PHARAOH CAT.name: Pharaoh Cat
PHARAOH CAT.flavorText: Mightiest of mousers, enduring in kingship of the upper and lower cat tree, conqueror of the red dot, the all-wise Catshepsut.

UNSEEN SABOTEUR.name: Unseen Saboteur
UNSEEN SABOTEUR.flavorText: Far more effective than the flamboyant saboteur.

SCALDING GEYSER.name: Scalding Geyser
SCALDING GEYSER.flavorText: ”Wow, what’s that land formation called?” “It s’cald a Geyser.”

SPRING THE TRAP.name: Spring the Trap
SPRING THE TRAP.flavorText: Talk about starting off on the wrong foot.

PYROS.name: Pyros
PYROS.flavorText: If you strike her down, she shall become more powerful than you can possibly… well, she'll become a 6/6 anyways.

PIP THE POTENT.name: Pip the Potent
PIP THE POTENT.flavorText: One time, I was trying to get Pip's attention to warn her that the dangerous outlaw Cheery Ollie, who also goes by just 'O', was headed her way. "Pip! Pip! Cheery O!", I shouted.

CANAL SLOGGER.name: Canal Slogger
CANAL SLOGGER.flavorText: "Another Monday in the canals huh? What a slog."

BLOOD MATRIARCH LIADRIN.name: Blood Matriarch Liadrin
BLOOD MATRIARCH LIADRIN.flavorText: All's fair in blood and war.

BREATH OF SINDRAGOSA.name: Breath of Sindragosa
BREATH OF SINDRAGOSA.flavorText: Is it cold in here or is it just Sindragosa?

POTIONMASTER PUTRICIDE.name: Potionmaster Putricide
POTIONMASTER PUTRICIDE.flavorText: "Good news everyone! I'm a Rogue card now!"

BONECALLER.name: Bonecaller
BONECALLER.flavorText: Hello, am I speaking to the undead of the household? We have been trying to reach you about your skeleton's extended warranty.

DIVINE TOLL.name: Divine Toll
DIVINE TOLL.flavorText: Never send to know for whom the bell tolls.

GHOST WRITER.name: Ghost Writer
GHOST WRITER.flavorText: This eccentric scribe was cursed to an afterlife of never being recognized for his talents! Muahaha!

DRAKONID OPERATIVE.name: Drakonid Operative
DRAKONID OPERATIVE.flavorText: His job is to spy on the Goons and the Jade Lotus, but he's OBVIOUSLY a dragon so it's pretty hard work.

SANCTUM SPELLBENDER.name: Sanctum Spellbender
SANCTUM SPELLBENDER.flavorText: "I'll take that... and that... aaand that."

REMIXED DISPENSE-O-BOT.name: Remixed Dispense-o-bot
REMIXED DISPENSE-O-BOT.flavorText: "Mine gave me free money!" "Mine gave me free ice cream!" "… mine gave me two sheep that explode. They were free but I still want a refund."

ANIMA GOLEM.name: Anima Golem
ANIMA GOLEM.flavorText: The Dark Animus is evil and mysterious and huge and unable to write sentences that utilize proper grammar.

FIREBRAND.name: Firebrand
FIREBRAND.flavorText: Too cool for school, too hot for thought.

BLADEMASTER SAMURO.name: Blademaster Samuro
BLADEMASTER SAMURO.flavorText: Artists paint their visions meticulously on canvas. Blademasters paint with, uh, broader strokes.

SIR FINLEY MRRGGLTON.name: Sir Finley Mrrgglton
SIR FINLEY MRRGGLTON.flavorText: In addition to fluent Common, he also speaks fourteen dialects of 'mrgl'.

KOBOLD STICKYFINGER.name: Kobold Stickyfinger
KOBOLD STICKYFINGER.flavorText: He no take candle. He take sword.

C'THUN, THE SHATTERED.name: C'Thun, the Shattered
C'THUN, THE SHATTERED.flavorText: My grandfather's deck has no useless cards!

SMOTHERING STARFISH.name: Smothering Starfish
SMOTHERING STARFISH.flavorText: Is a sucker for small talk.

BLOODBLOOM.name: Bloodbloom
BLOODBLOOM.flavorText: Help save mana. Donate blood today!

DRUID OF THE FLAME.name: Druid of the Flame
DRUID OF THE FLAME.flavorText: Druids who fought too long in Northrend were easily seduced by Ragnaros; a mug of hot chocolate was generally all it took.

RINLING'S RIFLE.name: Rinling's Rifle
RINLING'S RIFLE.flavorText: This rifle needs a muzzle for its muzzle.

SCARGIL.name: Scargil
SCARGIL.flavorText: Wanna know how he got those scars? So does he.

CORONER.name: Coroner
CORONER.flavorText: It was at this moment the Coroner decided to become a farmer instead.

ELECTRA STORMSURGE.name: Electra Stormsurge
ELECTRA STORMSURGE.flavorText: "The coin? You used me for THE COIN!?"

TRAINING SESSION.name: Training Session
TRAINING SESSION.flavorText: Instructor Razuvious's training turns the Scourge's Death Knights into hardened killing machines. His merciless routines focus on breaking down his underlings until they build up a resistance to his strength.

VEX CROW.name: Vex Crow
VEX CROW.flavorText: As birds of ill omen, these crows often summon Doomsayers.

BARRENS BLACKSMITH.name: Barrens Blacksmith
BARRENS BLACKSMITH.flavorText: "Maybe someday you’ll make it to Gadgetzan, kid."

SHADOW WALTZ.name: Shadow Waltz
SHADOW WALTZ.flavorText: They're dancing to one of Rin's demonic symphonies. Her music might not be famous now, but just you wait!

BURNING BLADE ACOLYTE.name: Burning Blade Acolyte
BURNING BLADE ACOLYTE.flavorText: Wields a disappointingly normal looking blade.

JURY DUTY.name: Jury Duty
JURY DUTY.flavorText: The most criminal thing about paladins is that they actually like jury duty.

GREEN JELLY.name: Green Jelly
GREEN JELLY.flavorText: This card really breaks out of the mold.

DIREWOLF COMMANDER.name: Direwolf Commander
DIREWOLF COMMANDER.flavorText: When you’re riding a wolf, it’s in charge and you're allowed to make suggestions.

INVINCIBLE.name: Invincible
INVINCIBLE.flavorText: No it's not, I can see it right there.

CONSTRUCT QUARTER.name: Construct Quarter
CONSTRUCT QUARTER.flavorText: It's not alive! IT'S NOT ALIIIIIVE!!!

COVER ARTIST.name: Cover Artist
COVER ARTIST.flavorText: The Faceless Ones are servants of Yogg-Saron, and they feed on fear. Right now they are feeding on our fear of you realizing we copied this flavor text.

DARKMOON MAGICIAN.name: Darkmoon Magician
DARKMOON MAGICIAN.flavorText: Darkmoon Magicians pull rabbits out of their hats, and wins out of their... hats.

MELOMANIA.name: Melomania
MELOMANIA.flavorText: I once saw a horse that had watermelons for hair. It was a melon mane, ya?!

RAZORBOAR.name: Razorboar
RAZORBOAR.flavorText: And this little pig built his house out of VENGEANCE.

ANUBISATH DEFENDER.name: Anubisath Defender
ANUBISATH DEFENDER.flavorText: Also comes running when he hears a can opener.

LOR'THEMAR THERON.name: Lor'themar Theron
LOR'THEMAR THERON.flavorText: Out of all his life accomplishments, making a 2/2 Tinyfin is his finest.

PRIMALFIN TOTEM.name: Primalfin Totem
PRIMALFIN TOTEM.flavorText: Emits a sound only murlocs can hear, which is good because it’s REALLY annoying.

DINOTAMER BRANN.name: Dinotamer Brann
DINOTAMER BRANN.flavorText: Brann's new dino-taming hobby is going well—his pet can already make him sit, stand, and roll over!

WRETCHED RECLAIMER.name: Wretched Reclaimer
WRETCHED RECLAIMER.flavorText: "Ok, here's the plan. We kill you, then bring you back." "Stronger?" "No, about the same."

SHADOW SUFFUSION.name: Shadow Suffusion
SHADOW SUFFUSION.flavorText: Be honest - you had to look up what that means.

K9-0TRON.name: K9-0tron
K9-0TRON.flavorText: You merely adopted the Battlegrounds. I was born in it. Molded by it.

HYDRATION STATION.name: Hydration Station
HYDRATION STATION.flavorText: They're drinking in herds... they do drink in herds.

BOLA SHOT.name: Bola Shot
BOLA SHOT.flavorText: On second thought, bolas aren't very good against flying worms.

DEADLY FORK.name: Deadly Fork
DEADLY FORK.flavorText: For a proper setting, place the deadly fork after the salad fork, but before the dinner fork.

SCOURGE TROLL.name: Scourge Troll
SCOURGE TROLL.flavorText: This is where I'd put my Deathrattle - IF I HAD ONE!

BOMB SQUAD.name: Bomb Squad
BOMB SQUAD.flavorText: Please don't explode! Please don't explode! Please don't explode!

DEAD MAN'S HAND.name: Dead Man's Hand
DEAD MAN'S HAND.flavorText: I got two pair, Rags and Armorsmiths. What you got?

GLORY CHASER.name: Glory Chaser
GLORY CHASER.flavorText: When you've reached the peak of competition twice, how hard can winning one valley be?

DIVINE STRENGTH.name: Divine Strength
DIVINE STRENGTH.flavorText: Every year a few paladins get disqualified from the Westfall weight lifting championship for using Divine Strength.

CHITTERING TUNNELER.name: Chittering Tunneler
CHITTERING TUNNELER.flavorText: Ear to the ground, he carefully interpreted the chittering noises: “You wanna cast a spell? I wanna cast a spell!”

TWILIGHT'S CALL.name: Twilight's Call
TWILIGHT'S CALL.flavorText: If you’re experiencing resurrection sickness, press 1.

LESSER ONYX SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Onyx Spellstone
LESSER ONYX SPELLSTONE.flavorText: The trolls of old embraced the gift A jewel of black for daggers swift No party lasts who finds the stone Those wielding it soon stand alone.

FRAZZLED FRESHMAN.name: Frazzled Freshman
FRAZZLED FRESHMAN.flavorText: "Late to bed, early to rise, makes a student unable to open her eyes."

GOBLIN BOMB.name: Goblin Bomb
GOBLIN BOMB.flavorText: They're Dr. Boom's babies. His baby boomers.

FLIGHTMASTER DUNGAR.name: Flightmaster Dungar
FLIGHTMASTER DUNGAR.flavorText: Flight’s a little bumpy, but there’s plenty of legroom.

WITCH OF THE ARCH-THIEF.name: Witch of the Arch-Thief
WITCH OF THE ARCH-THIEF.flavorText: A minion fit for a king.

KEYBOARD SOLOIST.name: Keyboard Soloist
KEYBOARD SOLOIST.flavorText: Give her a hand, everybody! Or maybe 4!

FROZEN TOUCH.name: Frozen Touch
FROZEN TOUCH.flavorText: Is this what Bob was talking about when he said he served a drink to a Death Knight once?

SKYBARGE.name: Skybarge
SKYBARGE.flavorText: It's more of a ship-gun than a gunship.

MIRACLE GROWTH.name: Miracle Growth
MIRACLE GROWTH.flavorText: I’ve got NO idea what’s in that fertilizer.

VITALITY SURGE.name: Vitality Surge
VITALITY SURGE.flavorText: If your vitality lasts longer than four hours, consult a Priest.

RHYME SPINNER.name: Rhyme Spinner
RHYME SPINNER.flavorText: For ONCE we're not talking about ice!

FANGBOUND DRUID.name: Fangbound Druid
FANGBOUND DRUID.flavorText: Bound by the law of the fang, these druid floss their teeth twice a day.

DOZING MARKSMAN.name: Dozing Marksman
DOZING MARKSMAN.flavorText: It's the sleeper of the set.

GLOWSTONE GYREWORM.name: Glowstone Gyreworm
GLOWSTONE GYREWORM.flavorText: Believe it or not, this is Tram Conductor Gerry's Gyreworm. But is it pronounced Gerry's Gyreworm, Gerry's Gyreworm, Gerry's Gyreworm, or Gerry's Gyreworm?

VICIOUS FLEDGLING.name: Vicious Fledgling
VICIOUS FLEDGLING.flavorText: A youngster who is truly hungry for self-improvement.

ASTROMANCER SOLARIAN.name: Astromancer Solarian
ASTROMANCER SOLARIAN.flavorText: Loyal to Kael'thas Sunstrider, this blood elf mage sought arcane power in the Void. Did she find it... or did IT find her?

TOTEMIC SURGE.name: Totemic Surge
TOTEMIC SURGE.flavorText: It's not really advanced shamanic magic, you just draw nasty eyebrows on them.

SHADOW COUNCIL.name: Shadow Council
SHADOW COUNCIL.flavorText: Why is everybody in Outland replacing their hands?!

FORGE OF SOULS.name: Forge of Souls
FORGE OF SOULS.flavorText: Powerful weaponry forged by Bronjahm, the Godfather of Souls.

DISCIPLE OF GALAKROND.name: Disciple of Galakrond
DISCIPLE OF GALAKROND.flavorText: Raising Galakrond will cause thurible, thurible damage.

NIGHTSHADE BUD.name: Nightshade Bud
NIGHTSHADE BUD.flavorText: It actually thrives in partial sunlight.

RAYLLA, SAND SCULPTOR.name: Raylla, Sand Sculptor
RAYLLA, SAND SCULPTOR.flavorText: Is this flavor text raylla the best we can do?

DR. BOOM'S SCHEME.name: Dr. Boom's Scheme
DR. BOOM'S SCHEME.flavorText: “We did it! We blew up the vault!” “You mean the vault door?” “Oh. The doooor…”

MALYGOS THE SPELLWEAVER.name: Malygos the Spellweaver
MALYGOS THE SPELLWEAVER.flavorText: After many years, Malygos has decided mortals can use magic. ALL THE MAGIC!

SUMMONING STONE.name: Summoning Stone
SUMMONING STONE.flavorText: Sometimes it feels like it's always the same slackers that are waiting for a summon.

GASLIGHT GATEKEEPER.name: Gaslight Gatekeeper
GASLIGHT GATEKEEPER.flavorText: This girl is such a boss.

PRIESTESS OF FURY.name: Priestess of Fury
PRIESTESS OF FURY.flavorText: Furious that she only has six warglaives. The Sightless Watcher has eight! The fel is always greener on the other side.

MORTAL ERADICATION.name: Mortal Eradication
MORTAL ERADICATION.flavorText: Clearly anything with 6 or more health is immortal. Such as Street Trickster. We are nerfing Street Trickster for lore accuracy.

SNATCH AND GRAB.name: Snatch and Grab
SNATCH AND GRAB.flavorText: Snatch grabbed the snacks and Grab snatched the grub. The perfect crime.

URSATRON.name: Ursatron
URSATRON.flavorText: It's been programmed to include all the bear necessities.

SPIRIT OF THE RHINO.name: Spirit of the Rhino
SPIRIT OF THE RHINO.flavorText: Where did they get this preposterous hypothesis?

MOROES.name: Moroes
MOROES.flavorText: Moroes runs an army of stewards, but still ends up inflating the balloons himself.

CYCLOPIAN CRUSHER.name: Cyclopian Crusher
CYCLOPIAN CRUSHER.flavorText: Really puts the rusher in crusher. Uses its one eye to C.

NETHRANDAMUS.name: Nethrandamus
NETHRANDAMUS.flavorText: Missed the big descent with the other dragons. But better late and nether!

DEVOURING PLAGUE.name: Devouring Plague
DEVOURING PLAGUE.flavorText: "How’d we miss this one in Uldum?" —Rafaam

HEROIC INNKEEPER.name: Heroic Innkeeper
HEROIC INNKEEPER.flavorText: We reserve the right to refuse service to any 1/1.

SI:7 INFORMANT.name: SI:7 Informant
SI:7 INFORMANT.flavorText: Sitting in a tavern all day and looking scary is hard work, but somebody has to do it.

TOPPLE THE IDOL.name: Topple the Idol
TOPPLE THE IDOL.flavorText: No Old Gods or Kings, only Naga.

STREET SWEEPER.name: Street Sweeper
STREET SWEEPER.flavorText: The sweeper hit of the set.

BRU'KAN.name: Bru'kan
BRU'KAN.flavorText: Bru'kan, his body weathered and weary, felt his time nearing its end. Teaching brave champions like Rokara gives him hope for a greater future.

FLAMEWAKER.name: Flamewaker
FLAMEWAKER.flavorText: Flamewakers HATE being confused for Flamewalkers. They just wake up fire, they don’t walk on it. Walking on fire is CRAZY.

OGRE-GANG ACE.name: Ogre-Gang Ace
OGRE-GANG ACE.flavorText: 100% chance to not play by the rules.

PARROT SANCTUARY.name: Parrot Sanctuary
PARROT SANCTUARY.flavorText: Did you know? It's very loud in a parrot sanctuary. This has been bird facts with Ranger Gilly.

SUL'THRAZE.name: Sul'thraze
SUL'THRAZE.flavorText: “Griftah here with de Sul’chop. One chop, you get four damage. Two chops, eight damage - you gonna change de way you fight."

GUITAR SOLOIST.name: Guitar Soloist
GUITAR SOLOIST.flavorText: She is the hero of the guitar. The guitar hero. Trademark.

SKYVATEER.name: Skyvateer
SKYVATEER.flavorText: When you go without fruits in an airship, you get a nasty case of skyvy.

NORTH SEA KRAKEN.name: North Sea Kraken
NORTH SEA KRAKEN.flavorText: You have no idea how tired this guy is of being released.

SPIRIT PEDDLER.name: Spirit Peddler
SPIRIT PEDDLER.flavorText: *facepalm* I asked for an art piece of a ghost on a bicycle...

NEEDLEROCK TOTEM.name: Needlerock Totem
NEEDLEROCK TOTEM.flavorText: You put the Needlerock in to get the Bloodrock out.

BOVINE SKELETON.name: Bovine Skeleton
BOVINE SKELETON.flavorText: The secret cow level has been unearthed.

MALYGOS, ASPECT OF MAGIC.name: Malygos, Aspect of Magic
MALYGOS, ASPECT OF MAGIC.flavorText: It's official. We can say Malygeese.

PACK TACTICS.name: Pack Tactics
PACK TACTICS.flavorText: "Just you wait, I’ll go get on my main!"

AZALINA SOULTHIEF.name: Azalina Soulthief
AZALINA SOULTHIEF.flavorText: The cards are always golden on the other side.

SANDBOX SCOUNDREL.name: Sandbox Scoundrel
SANDBOX SCOUNDREL.flavorText: "Really? A bunch of fake plastic gems AGAIN!?"

NIGHT ELF HUNTRESS.name: Night Elf Huntress
NIGHT ELF HUNTRESS.flavorText: A triple threat, all on her own.

WHIRLPOOL.name: Whirlpool
WHIRLPOOL.flavorText: In the southern hemisphere, it actually summons all minions instead.

BUTTONS.name: Buttons
BUTTONS.flavorText: "I'll give you an arm and a leg for your Flametongue Pin."

WYRM WEAVER.name: Wyrm Weaver
WYRM WEAVER.flavorText: Studied basket weaving as an undergrad.

DIG FOR TREASURE.name: Dig for Treasure
DIG FOR TREASURE.flavorText: "Woohoo! I'm so glad I dug up a pirate!"

MOLTEN BREATH.name: Molten Breath
MOLTEN BREATH.flavorText: Pizza so hot it burns OTHER PEOPLE’S MOUTHS.

KAJA'MITE CREATION.name: Kaja'mite Creation
KAJA'MITE CREATION.flavorText: You made this? I made this.

ALWAYS A BIGGER JORMUNGAR.name: Always a Bigger Jormungar
ALWAYS A BIGGER JORMUNGAR.flavorText: I saw it! It's big, scary, and blue!

FROZEN SHADOWEAVER.name: Frozen Shadoweaver
FROZEN SHADOWEAVER.flavorText: She still wears her Frozen Shadoweave set despite the many, many nerfs. She just can't let it go!

RAID NEGOTIATOR.name: Raid Negotiator
RAID NEGOTIATOR.flavorText: "What do you mean by aggressive negotiation tactics?" "Negotiations in bear form."

GRAVE HORROR.name: Grave Horror
GRAVE HORROR.flavorText: Trolls can regenerate lost limbs, but this is what they do with the leftovers.

FIREWORK ELEMENTAL.name: Firework Elemental
FIREWORK ELEMENTAL.flavorText: The brightest spark can still go dark.

SACRIFICIAL SUMMONER.name: Sacrificial Summoner
SACRIFICIAL SUMMONER.flavorText: Summoning will cost you an arm and a brother.

REND BLACKHAND.name: Rend Blackhand
REND BLACKHAND.flavorText: Rend believes he is the True Warchief of the Horde and he keeps editing the wikipedia page for "Warchief of the Horde" to include his picture.

PRISMATIC ELEMENTAL.name: Prismatic Elemental
PRISMATIC ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Disappointed they were rejected from the Magical Guardian tryouts.

TIME-LOST PROTODRAKE.name: Time-Lost Protodrake
TIME-LOST PROTODRAKE.flavorText: Weird way to say "late" but ok.

DUN BALDAR BRIDGE.name: Dun Baldar Bridge
DUN BALDAR BRIDGE.flavorText: At least there's no fall damage in Hearthstone.

MARSHSPAWN.name: Marshspawn
MARSHSPAWN.flavorText: Hopes to someday promote to Marshsqueen.

MINI-MAGE.name: Mini-Mage
MINI-MAGE.flavorText: He is sometimes found hiding in the treasure chest in the Gurubashi Arena.

EXPLOSIVE SHEEP.name: Explosive Sheep
EXPLOSIVE SHEEP.flavorText: How is this supposed to work? Your enemies think, "Hey! Cute sheep!" and run over to cuddle it?

REFRESHMENT VENDOR.name: Refreshment Vendor
REFRESHMENT VENDOR.flavorText: Menu: Funnel cakes, carrots, popcorn, jormungar steaks. It's hard serving a diverse clientele.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/7d/VO_AT_111_PLAY_ALT1_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_111_PLAY_ALT1_02.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/74/VO_AT_111_ATTACK_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_111_ATTACK_03.wav Grrr, pay up!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/cd/VO_AT_111_DEATH_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_111_DEATH_04.wav But I have... more... cakes...

CAVERN SHINYFINDER.name: Cavern Shinyfinder
CAVERN SHINYFINDER.flavorText: They call her the candled vandal.

RAID THE DOCKS.name: Raid the Docks
RAID THE DOCKS.flavorText: Winning the annual Ratchet Regatta really went to their heads.

ARCANE BRILLIANCE.name: Arcane Brilliance
ARCANE BRILLIANCE.flavorText: They could probably do with a dash of Arcane Humility.

UNLEASH THE BEAST.name: Unleash the Beast
UNLEASH THE BEAST.flavorText: The Kirin Tor have always been lax in enforcing leash laws.

GRAVE DIGGING.name: Grave Digging
GRAVE DIGGING.flavorText: Grave digging as a profession has high turnover; it's important to maintain headcount.

ARTIFICER XY'MOX.name: Artificer Xy'mox
ARTIFICER XY'MOX.flavorText: "The anticipation to use this relic is killing me! Though, it will more likely kill you."

BALL HOG.name: Ball Hog
BALL HOG.flavorText: "There's no hog in team... ANYMORE! I QUIT!"

BLACKWATER BEHEMOTH.name: Blackwater Behemoth
BLACKWATER BEHEMOTH.flavorText: What's a Blackwater Behemoth's favorite meal? Fish n' Ships.

MASTER OF EVOLUTION.name: Master of Evolution
MASTER OF EVOLUTION.flavorText: Will be really useful in the new "Hearthémon" game.

WILDFIRE.name: Wildfire
WILDFIRE.flavorText: The Barrens were a lush jungle. Then this happened.

ARCANE AMPLIFIER.name: Arcane Amplifier
ARCANE AMPLIFIER.flavorText: Not on good terms with warlocks.

WAX ELEMENTAL.name: Wax Elemental
WAX ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Takes double damage from wick-based weapons.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/f/fd/LOOT_117_WaxElemental_PLay.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ LOOT_117_WaxElemental_PLay.wav

FROST GIANT.name: Frost Giant
FROST GIANT.flavorText: Don't ask him about the beard. JUST DON'T.

COUNTERFEIT BLADE.name: Counterfeit Blade
COUNTERFEIT BLADE.flavorText: Don't worry, the blade retracts into the handle!

CORNELIUS ROAME.name: Cornelius Roame
CORNELIUS ROAME.flavorText: Raised two perfectly normal daughters. Then one died and brought doom to Stormwind.

VENOMOUS SCORPID.name: Venomous Scorpid
VENOMOUS SCORPID.flavorText: Despite what Guff says, he is NOT a "nice little guy."

VANESSA VANCLEEF.name: Vanessa VanCleef
VANESSA VANCLEEF.flavorText: Some people collect stamps or flowers. She collects enemies.

DURNHOLDE IMPOSTER.name: Durnholde Imposter
DURNHOLDE IMPOSTER.flavorText: Assassins of the Infinite Dragonflight waited for their moment to strike at Thrall before he ever became Warchief.

STUBBORN GASTROPOD.name: Stubborn Gastropod
STUBBORN GASTROPOD.flavorText: Stubbornly pursuing its dream to become Azeroth's fastest animal!

PROSTHETIC HAND.name: Prosthetic Hand
PROSTHETIC HAND.flavorText: It's creaky and it's rusty! It's spooky and it's dusty!

HERALD OF CHAOS.name: Herald of Chaos
HERALD OF CHAOS.flavorText: They used to be called the Heralds of Order before all of this silly Sundering nonsense.

FANCY PACKAGING.name: Fancy Packaging
FANCY PACKAGING.flavorText: Wow, this card is great value! Until you open it.

QUEEN AZSHARA.name: Queen Azshara
QUEEN AZSHARA.flavorText: Hobbies include: Ordering subjects around, making deals with old gods, and taking long walks under the beach.

SPELLCOILER.name: Spellcoiler
SPELLCOILER.flavorText: "Look, I know plenty of spells. I just need to see one first is all."

PILOTED SHREDDER.name: Piloted Shredder
PILOTED SHREDDER.flavorText: Once upon a time, only goblins piloted shredders. These days, everyone from Doomsayer to Lorewalker Cho seems to ride one.

HOOKED REAVER.name: Hooked Reaver
HOOKED REAVER.flavorText: The hook is just an accessory. He can reave just fine without it.

LORD GODFREY.name: Lord Godfrey
LORD GODFREY.flavorText: Betrayed the Alliance. Betrayed the Horde. All for 200 achievement points and a sweet, sweet hat.

STRONGSHELL SCAVENGER.name: Strongshell Scavenger
STRONGSHELL SCAVENGER.flavorText: It isn't "grave robbing" when there's no grave. It's just scavenging…

EGGNAPPER.name: Eggnapper
EGGNAPPER.flavorText: Often misunderstood, it's just that he likes to use the eggs as pillows.

PACKAGE DEALER.name: Package Dealer
PACKAGE DEALER.flavorText: I'm always getting my neighbor's mail. And my other neighbor. And my other neighbor. I'm stealing their packages.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/c2/VO_ULD_184_Male_Kobold_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_ULD_184_Male_Kobold_Play_01.wav EVIL get you!

SMUG SENIOR.name: Smug Senior
SMUG SENIOR.flavorText: You want to see something funny? Go visit him in five years.

SINFUELED GOLEM.name: Sinfueled Golem
SINFUELED GOLEM.flavorText: That poor golem is going to be stuck as a guard forever. He can never get a head!

WORGEN ROADIE.name: Worgen Roadie
WORGEN ROADIE.flavorText: "I asked for an instrument, and you give me a CURSED BLADE!?"

OUTFIT TAILOR.name: Outfit Tailor
OUTFIT TAILOR.flavorText: She has this terrible habit of eating melted cheese while on the job.

SWITCHEROO.name: Switcheroo
SWITCHEROO.flavorText: Would you rather fight one Whale-sized Goldfish, or 100 Goldfish-sized Whales?
